(15, '2017-02-13 13:08:02', 'Kuki Miss Mutesi na Miss Iradukunda batazitabira.....', 'Ubuyobozi bwa Inspiration Back Up ireberera inyungu za Miss Rwanda 2016 Mutesi Jolly na Miss Rwamda 2017 Iradukunda Elsa, buratangaza ko batazitabira irushanwa rya nyampinga w’Afurika (Miss Africa) kuko ngo ntaryo bazi.', 'Ubuyobozi bwa Inspiration Back Up ireberera inyungu za Miss Rwanda 2016 Mutesi Jolly na Miss Rwamda 2017 Iradukunda Elsa, buratangaza ko batazitabira irushanwa rya nyampinga w’Afurika (Miss Africa) kuko ngo ntaryo bazi. \r\n\r\nKuwa 20 Gicurasi 2017 biteganijwe ko i Kigali hazabera amarushanwa yo gutora nyampinga w’Afurika azwi nka ’Miss Africa’\r\n\r\nIri rushanwa rigiye kuba ku nshuro ya kabiri, umwaka ushize wa 2016 ryari ryabereye muri Afurika y’Epfo ryegukanwa n’umukobwa wo muri Ghana witwa Rebecca Asamoah, icyo gihe u Rwanda rwari rwahagarariwe na Miss Kundwa Doriane watashye amara masa.\r\n\r\nTwashatse kumenya niba no muri uyu mwaka wa 2017 hari nyampinga w’u Rwanda uzitabira aya marushanwa, tubaza umuyobozi wa Rwanda Inspiration Back Up Kagame Ishimwe Dieu Donne urebera inyungu za Miss Mutesi Jolly na Miss Iradukunda Elsa, atubwira ko ayo marushanwa ntayo bazi.\r\n\r\nYagize ati “ayo marushanwa ntayo turamenya, twe ntayo tuzi, ntabwo bigeze badutumira.”\r\n\r\nTwamubajije niba bo batarabonye itangazo ryatanzwe n’abategura iri rushanwa bahamagarira ibihugu kuryitabira dore ko ndetse hari n’abatangiye kwiyandikisha adusubiza agira ati “Ubwo ntiturabishaka\r\n\r\nBiteganijwe ko iri rushanwa rizahuza abakobwa bakomoka mu bihugu bigera kuri 40 byo muri Afurika.\r\n\r\nAbakobwa bazahatana bazatangira kugera mu Rwanda kuwa 05 no kuwa 06 Gicurasi, mu minsi bazamara mu Rwanda bakazakora ibikorwa bitandukanye birimo gusura ahantu nyaburanga hatandukanye ho mu Rwanda.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSRC@MAKURUKI.rw\r\n', 'MISS.jpg', 0, 'admin', 5, 12, 'head', 80),
(16, '2017-03-07 16:21:16', 'Umugani wa Ngunda ( igice cya mbere )', 'Habayeho umugabo akitwa Ngunda. Uwo mugabo yari icyago, yari ishyano, yari igisahiranda ; uko yaryaga ni nako yahingaga. Yahingaga Rubona yose agakubitaho na Musasu. Iyo ni yo yari isambu ye. Ndetse ngo imisozi yâ€™i Rwanda ni amabimba Ngunda yashingaga. Uwo mugabo yari afite nâ€™imirima ku Nyundo ya Bugoyi', '<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">Arakunyarukira\r\nashaka umugore, akaba, umukobwa wa Gacumu. Arongera ashaka undi, akaba umukobwa\r\nwa Mirenge ku Ntenyo. Ashakiraho nâ€™abandi bane, bose bashyika batandatu. Ukuntu\r\nyaryaga, nta mugore umwe wajyaga kumubumba.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">Umunsi\r\numwe Ngunda aribwira, ati Â« ngiye kwa databukwe kumuha umubyizi. Â» Ngunda\r\narakugendera no ku Ntenyo, abwira kwa sebukwe ati Â«munkwikirire amasuka mirongo\r\nitanu njye kubaha umubyizi. Â» K wa sebukwe bakaba abakungu, amasuka\r\nbarayakwikira, barayamuha, ajya guhinga.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">Atangirira\r\nmu Rugondo, ahinga Ntenyo yose, abirinduka. mu Kinyoro kwa Byakuzacumu. Ngunda\r\nagakubita isuka hasi kabiri, ubwa gatatu ,akazamura agafuni. Ngunda amara atyo\r\namasuka yose, ntiyasiga nâ€™imwe, abona guhingura. Nuko wa murima Ngunda ahinze,\r\nMirenge awoherezamo abatezi. Abatezi bakorera kubura hasi no kubura hejuru,\r\nbarihata cyane ariko ubuhinge burabananira.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">Mirenge\r\nabibonye ati Â« uyu muntu waduhingiye atya, na twe tumuhembe. Â» Babaga Ingumba\r\nkabombo, bashesha amafu, bavomesha amazi yo kuvuga imitsima, benga nâ€™ amayoga\r\nmenshi ndetse nâ€™ abaturanyi bazana amazimano.<br>\r\nInyama zimaze gushya nâ€™imitsima imaze kuvugwa bazana ibidasesa badendezaho\r\ninyama, bazana nâ€™imbehe nyinshi zuzuye umufa, bakwiza ibibindi byâ€™inzoga mu nzu\r\nyose, amarobe yâ€™imitsima bayuzuza ibyibo nâ€™amakangara.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">Byose\r\nbamaze kubitunganya, bahamagara umukwe wabo ngo naze afungure. Maze bamuha\r\namazi arakaraba, bamubisa mu nzu ararya.<br>\r\nMuramu we abarira ko amaze kurya, amushyira amazi yo gukaraba. Ngunda amubonye\r\naramubwira ati Â«jye nduzi ko iyi nka nyitonoye, abahungu bayiriye bariye inka\r\niryoshye ! Â»<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;margin-left:0in;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:19.2pt;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#363D45;letter-spacing:.9pt\">Kwa\r\nMirenge bumvise iryo jambo barumirwa. Mirenge abwira umugore we ati Â« dore\r\numukwe wacu ntaho atereye kandi yadukoreye. None tabaranya uzane akari gasigaye\r\nmumwongere nâ€™izindi nzoga. Jye icyampa ngo yijute irya none.<br>\r\nNuko Ngunda bamushyira ukuguru kwari gusigaye bamuzanira nâ€™inzoga. Koko rero ni\r\nho yari akigera mu mahina yo kurya, agakaraga irobe ryâ€™umutsima akariyongobeza.\r\nImikarago yâ€™umutsima ikabisikana nâ€™intongo zâ€™inyama nâ€™umufa. Byose\r\nakabivundiranya akaroha mu nda. Ngunda akagira umuheha witwa Ruvunabataka; yaba\r\nawukubise mu kibindi cyâ€™inzoga, akagisoma umusa umwe akaba arakonoje.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#363D45;\r\nletter-spacing:.9pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Nuko amaze kurya arasohoka; asohoka yimyoza ngo ntacyo\r\nariye. Nyamara ubwo yari amaze ingumba yose wenyine kandi bamuhaye nâ€™ibibindi\r\nbyâ€™inzoga na byo biguze inka. Byose arabitsemba, agenda abibogekeye mu ibondo\r\nrimwe. Nuko kwa sebukwe baramuherekeza arataha. Basigara batangarira inda nini\r\nya Ngunda.</span>', 'ngunda.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 121),
(17, '2017-03-07 16:40:49', 'Rwanda â€“ Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa', 'Rwanda â€“ Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa -Do not leave Rwanda without seeing the Traditional Dances and Musical Performances such as the famous Intore Dance â€“ you will not see dances performed such as the Land of a Thousand Hills â€“ Rwanda.', '<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Music and Dance is a&nbsp;long-established and&nbsp;integral part\r\nof Rwandan Life and Culture and is part of&nbsp;&nbsp; every festival,\r\ncelebration such as Birth, naming of children, marriage, Birthdays and\r\nAnniversaries and any other occasion imaginable such as family\r\ngatherings.&nbsp; Rwandaâ€™s Culture and People thrive off of Music and Dance\r\nthat move the soul.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">During the late afternoon and early evenings&nbsp;families and\r\nfriends often gather drinking traditional beer and share a meal while telling\r\nstories about their day and week and there is always&nbsp; music and dance for\r\nall the enjoy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">There is no celebratory occasion in Rwanda where one finds no\r\nmusic and dance to liven up the celebration, whatever it may be and that is\r\nespecially true if there are visitors in the gathering.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Today as Tourism has greatly increased the number visitors to\r\nRwanda, most Lodges often have traditional Dance and Musical performances in\r\nthe late afternoons or early evenings to the delight of the guests.&nbsp;\r\nTraditional Rwandan Dancers are accompanied by an orchestra&nbsp;of five to\r\nseven members producing a harmonious, yet explosive sound that grabs your soul,\r\nno matter what your background is.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n\r\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n</span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#603913;letter-spacing:-.4pt\">&nbsp;Rwanda\r\nâ€“ Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa â€“ Different\r\nDances and Musical Instrument:<o:p></o:p></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n\r\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n</span></div>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#603913\">Intore Dance of Warriors:<v:shapetype id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\" path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\">\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\">\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\">\r\n </v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:f></v:formulas>\r\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\">\r\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\">\r\n</o:lock></v:path></v:stroke></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"Picture_x0020_3\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1029\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\" Rwanda - Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa\" style=\"width:303pt;height:303pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/HAZWIN~1/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image001.jpg\" o:title=\" Rwanda - Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape><o:p></o:p></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The word Intore translated from Kinyarwanda into English means\r\nChosen Ones â€“ Leaders.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The Male Dancers were selected based on their physical and moral\r\nqualities, since Intore is more than&nbsp; a dance and the learning of dance\r\nsteps, but Intore Dancer were educated in the&nbsp;ways of everyday royal\r\ncourt&nbsp;behavior and how to conduct themselves among Royalty and mainly King\r\nâ€“ the Mwami of Rwanda.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">They gave inspiration through their dance as there was preparation\r\nfor the hunt or even for battle as they danced the dance of Heroes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The Intore Dancers through Music â€“ Dance â€“ Shouts based on\r\nstrength gave inspiration, inner confidence as they faced the enemy, went on a\r\nhunt watching the Dance of Heroes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><v:shape id=\"Picture_x0020_2\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1028\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\"Rwanda-royal-drummers\" style=\"width:262.5pt;height:117.75pt;\r\n visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/HAZWIN~1/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image002.jpg\" o:title=\"Rwanda-royal-drummers\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Dances were also performed after a successful hunt or battle as\r\nthey celebrated the victory in the court of the King.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The dancers were accompanied&nbsp; &nbsp;drummer â€“ the number 13\r\nwas the&nbsp;&nbsp;symbol of Royal Power.&nbsp; Traditionally men were drummers\r\nâ€“ today you an also find women drummers performing.&nbsp; In the days of old\r\nthe drums announced the presence of the Mwami â€“ the King â€“ the drums were also\r\na way that the King communicated with his people.&nbsp; To be a Royal Drummer\r\nmeant a position of high status in the Kingâ€™s Court.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Today Intore Dances Dancers are most often accompanied by a drum\r\norchestra made up of about seven to nine members whose drumming provide a\r\nharmonious and yet powerful melody of intertwining rhythms.&nbsp; You will also\r\nfind while drummers and dancers perform&nbsp;the audience will clap their hands\r\nâ€“ something that gives added rhythm and even encourage dancers to outdo their\r\nlast performance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#603913\">Umushagiriro/Umushayayo Dance of\r\nWomen:<v:shape id=\"Picture_x0020_1\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1027\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" alt=\" Rwanda - Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa\" style=\"width:303pt;height:303pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square\">\r\n <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:/Users/HAZWIN~1/AppData/Local/Temp/msohtmlclip1/01/clip_image003.jpg\" o:title=\" Rwanda - Home of some of The Best Cultural Dances and Music in Africa\">\r\n</v:imagedata></v:shape><o:p></o:p></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The&nbsp;Dance\r\nof Women&nbsp;is more gentle and graceful&nbsp;and unusual in Africa.&nbsp; Its\r\nstrength is the Graceful movement of Rwandan women highlight kindness,\r\ngoodness, purity and the radiant beauty of what many consider Africaâ€™s most\r\nbeautiful women â€“ even though as often is the case the Womenâ€™s Dance is based\r\nupon the movement of<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://kabiza.com/kabiza-wilderness-safaris/ankole-cows-in-uganda-rwanda-the-cattle-of-kings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ankole Cows- Uganda â€“ Rwanda â€“ the Cattle of Kings\"><span style=\"color:#19196A\">Ankole Cattle</span></a><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The femaleâ€™s dance is usually compared to ballet. It is meant to\r\ndisplay the grace as well as the beauty of the women of Rwanda as they emulate\r\nthe movements of cows and wildlife though you would never know that as you\r\nwatch the graceful, artistic movements of the Women Dancers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">In Rwandan Traditional â€“ Cultural Dance Men dance and portray\r\nCourage, Strength and Confidence while Women through Dancing so forth, love,\r\ncare, nurture and their&nbsp;graceful &nbsp;feminine strength.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#603913\">Ukurambagiza â€“ Dance of\r\nCourtship:<o:p></o:p></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The Dance of courtship where men and women dance together â€“ it is\r\nalso called the Dance of Fiances and in Kinyarwanda Ukurambagiza.&nbsp; In this\r\nunmarried women participate in the dance of courtship until they are married\r\nallowing their beauty to be accented by movement and dance.&nbsp; The rituals\r\nof birds and wildlife are emulated such as the mating dance of the Gray Crested\r\nCranes.&nbsp; It is a most gracious dance to view.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#603913\">Umuganura Harvest Festival:<o:p></o:p></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The Belgian Colonial Authorities banned the Harvest Festival in\r\n1925 because they feared that the King would gain too much power since it was\r\nthe second most important even in the kingdom after coronation of a new king.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">In recent times the Rwandan Government has reinstated the Harvest\r\nFestival with many more things added than in times past.&nbsp; The harvest\r\nfestival had been part of traditional Rwandan Culture for centuries where\r\npeople gathered to celebrate share the first fruits of the harvest, this was\r\naccompanied music, dance, telling of stories and local brew.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The women dancers dressed in festive gowns to perform dances of\r\nthanksgiving and honor the Traditional Deity that had blessed them with a\r\nbountiful harvest and a time to bring and bless seeds for the new harvest to\r\ncome.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#603913\">Musical Instruments used:<o:p></o:p></span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Music â€“ Vocal Performances and Dance were often accompanied by\r\nvarious Rwandan instruments like such as the Ingoma Drum made from a special\r\ntree and covered with cowhide.&nbsp; The Inaganga â€“ which is a guitar like\r\ninstruments with 9 to 12 strings and come in plain or highly ornate woo.\r\nfrom&nbsp;Umyungu wood.&nbsp; The Umuduli is a single string, almost bow like\r\ninstrument and then there is the Rwandan Horn called the Amakondera.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;line-height:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Rwandan Traditional Dances are not to be missed â€“ you are missing\r\nout on one of the parts of Uganda â€“ its culture and its people â€“ let us make\r\nsure as we prepare your safari&nbsp;itinerary that Rwandan Dance and Music are\r\na part of it.&nbsp; Enjoy Rwanda â€“ its millions of Smiles and the many\r\ntraditional Dance and Music Performancesâ€¦<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'intore.jpg', 0, 'admin', 4, 3, 'head', 99),
(20, '2017-03-16 07:39:23', 'Kuki Miss Mutesi na Miss Iradukunda batazitabira amarushanwa ya MISS AFRICA azabera i Kigali?', 'Ubuyobozi bwa Inspiration Back Up ireberera inyungu za Miss Rwanda 2016 Mutesi Jolly na Miss Rwamda 2017 Iradukunda Elsa, buratangaza ko batazitabira irushanwa rya nyampinga wâ€™Afurika (Miss Africa) kuko ngo ntaryo bazi.', '<p>Kuwa 20 Gicurasi 2017 biteganijwe ko i Kigali hazabera amarushanwa yo gutora nyampinga wâ€™Afurika azwi nka â€™Miss Africaâ€™</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iri rushanwa rigiye kuba ku nshuro ya kabiri, umwaka ushize wa 2016 \r\nryari ryabereye muri Afurika yâ€™Epfo ryegukanwa nâ€™umukobwa wo muri Ghana \r\nwitwa Rebecca Asamoah, icyo gihe u Rwanda rwari rwahagarariwe na Miss \r\nKundwa Doriane watashye amara masa.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Twashatse kumenya niba no muri uyu mwaka wa 2017 hari nyampinga wâ€™u \r\nRwanda uzitabira aya marushanwa, tubaza umuyobozi wa Rwanda Inspiration \r\nBack Up Kagame Ishimwe Dieu Donne urebera inyungu za Miss Mutesi Jolly \r\nna Miss Iradukunda Elsa, atubwira ko ayo marushanwa ntayo bazi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yagize ati <i>â€œayo marushanwa ntayo turamenya, twe ntayo tuzi, ntabwo bigeze badutumira.â€<br class=\"autobr\">\r\n</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Twamubajije niba bo batarabonye itangazo ryatanzwe nâ€™abategura iri \r\nrushanwa bahamagarira ibihugu kuryitabira dore ko ndetse hari \r\nnâ€™abatangiye kwiyandikisha adusubiza agira ati<i> â€œUbwo ntiturabishaka</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Biteganijwe ko iri rushanwa rizahuza abakobwa bakomoka mu bihugu bigera kuri 40 byo muri Afurika.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abakobwa bazahatana bazatangira kugera  mu Rwanda  kuwa 05 no kuwa 06\r\n Gicurasi, mu minsi bazamara mu Rwanda bakazakora ibikorwa bitandukanye \r\nbirimo gusura ahantu nyaburanga hatandukanye ho mu Rwanda.</p><p><br></p><p>src Makuruki.rw<br></p>', 'miss.jpg', 0, 'admin', 5, 12, '', 154),
(21, '2017-03-16 07:56:24', 'Urubuto rwâ€™umwembe rukungahaye kuri vitamini nyinshi zifitiye umubiri akamaro .', 'Umwembe ni urubuto rufitiye umubiri akamaro kuko ukungahaye kuri vitamin C ikenerwa mu gukora poroteyini zâ€™ingenzi ku menyo, imikaya, amagufwa, imiyoboro yâ€™amaraso', '<p>Umwembe ni urubuto rufitiye umubiri akamaro kuko ukungahaye kuri \r\nvitamin C ikenerwa mu gukora poroteyini zâ€™ingenzi ku menyo, imikaya, \r\namagufwa, imiyoboro yâ€™amaraso, mu gukiza ibisebe, ikanagira uruhare mu \r\ngukora indurwe yâ€™umwijima kandi ikanafasha mu ikoreshwa ryâ€™imunyungugu \r\nwa fer wongera amaraso mu mubiri.</p>\r\n<p>Impuguke mu byâ€™imirire,&nbsp; Philippe&nbsp; Grand&nbsp; avuga ko umwembe ari \r\nurubuto&nbsp; ruribwa nâ€™abantu benshi kandi ko nkâ€™uko akomeza abisobanura ngo\r\n umwembe ukize ku ntungamubiri zitandukanye umubiri wâ€™umuntu ukenera,&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\ncyane cyane kuri vitamine&nbsp; A na C ariko hanabonekamo vitamine B.</p><p>Vitamini C igira uruhare mu mikurire yâ€™imikaya, ikingira umubiri \r\nindwara yâ€™inzira zâ€™ubuhumekero nka asima, indwara zâ€™impiswi, macinya, \r\ngusukura amaraso nno kurinda kanseri zitandukanye.&nbsp; Iyo vitamine kandi \r\nibonekamo ku gipimo cya miligarama 22 na 100.</p>\r\n<p>Amazi yâ€™igishishwa cyayo kuyogesha mu kanwa bikingira indwara zimwe \r\nna zimwe zo mu kanwa, amazi yâ€™ibibabi nâ€™igishishwa bibijije bikavura \r\nimpiswi na macinya , mu gihe ibibabi byâ€™imyembe bikiri bito, iyo \r\nbitapfunwe na byo bivura impiswi na macinya.</p>\r\n<p>Amatembabuzi&nbsp; yâ€™umwembe kandi akoreshwa mu gufatanya impapuro&nbsp; ariko \r\nbisaba kwitonderwa kuko hari ubwo bigira ingaruka ku mubiri nko \r\ngupfuruta mu gihe indabo na zo&nbsp; zatera ikibazo mu mikorere yâ€™inzira \r\nzâ€™ubuhumekero ku bantu bamwe na bamwe kuko imibiri yâ€™abantu iba idakora \r\nkimwe.</p>\r\n<p>Umwembe kandi na none ufitiye umubiri akamaro kuko ukungahaye kuri \r\nvitamine A ikenerwa&nbsp; mu kurwanya indwara zâ€™ubuhumyi, igabanya kuba&nbsp; \r\numuntu yafatwa nâ€™indwara ya kanseri cyane cyane iyâ€™impyiko, mu kanwa, \r\nibere, mu mihogo nâ€™izibasiraga inzira zâ€™ubuhumekero.</p>\r\n<p>Uretse vitamini A, hari nâ€™izindi zifasha&nbsp; mu gutuma habaho \r\nkwiyuburura kâ€™umubiri, ingirangingo zishaje zigasimburwa nâ€™izindi.&nbsp; \r\nVitamini E na B ibonekamo ibyiciro bya B1, B2 iboneka ku bagore gusa, \r\nhanabonekamo vitamine B6, ituma umwuka mwiza (oxygÃ¨ne) ugera mu bice \r\nbyose byâ€™umubiri.</p>\r\n<p>Vitamine A ibonekamo ku bagore gusa, ikaba irinda indwara kandi \r\nikagira uruhare mu gukura kâ€™umwana batwite kimwe no kwibaruka, ikomera \r\nryâ€™amagufwa nâ€™ubuzima bwâ€™ingirangingo. Vitamine A iboneka mu biryo \r\nbyinshi: amavuta yâ€™umwijima wâ€™ifi yitwa morue kimwe nâ€™inyama yâ€™umwijima \r\nmuri rusange, ikimuri, umuhondo wâ€™igi no mu mata.</p>\r\n<p>Akenshi nâ€™ubwo iboneka ku bikomoka ku matungo, inaba mu myembe, muri \r\nkaroti, mu ibijumba,&nbsp; mu ishu, muri epinari, no mu ipapayi. Imyembe \r\ninakungahaye ku myunyungugu yitwa potasiyumu&nbsp; ugira uruhare mu kwikanya \r\nno kwikanyura kwâ€™imitsi, umutima, impyiko, kugwa ibinya nâ€™umunaniro.</p><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0L0fPfp.jpg\" width=\"276\"><br><p><strong>Intungamubiri ziri mu mwembe kuri garama 100</strong></p>\r\n<p>Abahanga mu bumenyi bwâ€™imbonezamirire babitangaje kuko ngo muri \r\ngarama ijana zâ€™umwembe haba harimo amazi ku kigereranyo cya 82 kugera \r\nkuri 83,5 %;&nbsp; kandi amazi agira uruhare runini mu gusohora imyanda mu \r\nmubiri , poroteyini yo ibonekamo ku gipimo cya 0,5 kugera kuri 0,6 g&nbsp; mu\r\n gihe&nbsp; ibitera imbaraga birimo biboneka hagati ya 56 kugeza kuri 65 \r\nkcal, ibinyamavuta&nbsp; bibonekamo ku kigereranyo cya 0,1 03g bikaba bimwe \r\nmu bitanga ingufu naho ibinyasukari bibonekamo hagati yâ€™igipimo cya \r\ngarama 13,4 na garama 17,&nbsp; na byo bitanga ingufu.</p>\r\n<p>Imyembe inakungahaye ku myunyungugu yitwa potasiyumu ugira uruhare mu\r\n kwikanya no kwikanyura kwâ€™imitsi, umutima, impyiko , kugwa ibinya \r\nnâ€™umunaniro. Hanabonekamo sodiyumu, fosifore hagati yâ€™igipimo cya \r\nmiligarama 22 na 25, feri igira uruhare mu kongera amaraso mu mubiri \r\nifitemo miligarama 1 na 1,2; kalisiyumu yo ifite miligarama&nbsp; hagati ya \r\n20 na 22 , manyeziyumu ni hagati ya garama 8 na 9.</p>\r\n<p>Hifashishijwe&nbsp; urubuga rwa interineti Â«SantÃ© Canada. Fichier canadien\r\n sur les Ã©lÃ©ments nutritifs, 2010 Â» hagaragaraho ko umwembe mubisi \r\nubonekamo ibitera imbaraga ku gipimo cya garama 67, poroteyini yo ifite \r\ngarama 0,5 ; ibinyasukari ni garama 17,6&nbsp; nâ€™ibinyamavuta bifite garama \r\n0,3.</p>\r\n<p>Umwembe mubisi kandi ushobora gukoreshwa mu guhumuza ibiryo&nbsp; cyane \r\ncyane inyama zâ€™ibiguruka, izâ€™ibishuhe (le canard) nâ€™izâ€™ingurube.</p><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1uLJ7pl.jpg\" width=\"259\"><br>', 'umwembe.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 10, 'break', 159),
(22, '2017-03-16 08:27:14', 'Umugani wa Ngunda ( igice cya kabiri )', 'Ngunda aba aho, aba iciro ryâ€™imigani. Rimwe amaze guhaga ariyumvira ati Â« harya ngo mu Rwanda nta muntu wahwanya na njye kurya ? Emwe ni koko.', 'Umugani wa<br> Ngunda ( igice<br> cya kabiri )<br> Mu nkuru yacu iheruka twabagejejeho ibya<br> Ngunda mu gice cya mbere. Mwiyumviye<br> ubuhangange bwâ€™ uyu mugabo ari na ho havuye<br> ibyifuzo byâ€™ uko twabagezaho igice cya kabiri<br> ari na cyo twabazaniye muri iyi nkuru.<br> Ngunda aba aho, aba iciro ryâ€™imigani. Rimwe<br> amaze guhaga ariyumvira ati Â« harya ngo mu<br> Rwanda nta muntu wahwanya na njye kurya ?<br> Emwe ni koko. Dore na we ibi biryo byose maze<br> mu mwanya muto. Nyamara byatetswe mu<br> minsi itandatu. Ariko ga rubanda, no<br> kundenganya barandenganya! Ndya rimwe gusa<br> mu cyumweru.<br> Ariko bo bakarya kenshi buri munsi. Kandi nta<br> muntu nâ€™umwe twahiga mu guhinga cyangwa<br> kubasha indi mirimo. Yego... ndarya ariko uko<br> ndya ni ko nkora. Ubwo sindi igisambo uko<br> bamvuga. Ahubwo ndi umugabo, igihangange<br> ndetse... Kandi ga ye umenya Ruganzu<br> yahingishije. Ese icyatumye atandarika ni iki ?<br> Henga muhime njye kumuvumba. Â»<br> (Kwa Ruganzu)<br> Ngunda: - Gahorane amashyo nâ€™ingoma<br> Nyagasani ! Umva<br> ikinzanye, Nyagasani. Nje kubaramutsa no<br> kubafunguza. Numvise<br> yuko ngo mwahingishije, nyoberwa icyababujije<br> kundarika kandi nzi<br> ko nta muntu nâ€™umwe wandusha guhinga. Ibyo<br> Nyagasani ntacyo<br> bitwaye, mupfe kumvumbya gusa.<br> Ruganzu : - Koko na njye sinzi uko<br> byandenzeho. Ndakuzi kuri ubu uba<br> wahamaze wafatiriye nâ€™ ahandi. Ariko se nari<br> kubona inzoga<br> ziguhagije nâ€™inda yawe niyiziye? Ndetse nâ€™ubu<br> ubanza<br> ntari bubone izo nkuvumbyaho ngo mbone<br> nâ€™izihaza abahinzi banjye.<br> Ngunda: - Na njye sinaguhemukira. Reka<br> kumvumbya, pfa kunsogongeza<br> gusa nigendere. Nzaba nza kuvumba ikindi gihe<br> cyangwa se uzanyitumirira.<br> Ruganzu: -Ngunda se, ningusogongeza, ko nzi<br> isogongera ryawe,<br> ntuzinogozamo abahinzi banjye bagaheba ?<br> Ngaho nibajye<br> kukwereka, ariko uramenye !<br> Ngunda: - Ndasogongera gusa mba nkuroga !<br> Ndetse mfite urugendo, iyo<br> mungirira vuba nkareba uko natwaza iri zuba.<br> Ruganzu: - Umunyanzoga ntumuzi ? Genda<br> bagusogongeze. Ngiye kureba<br> abahinzi.<br> Ngunda : - Yewe sha ! Shobuja arambwiye ngo<br> nsogongeza ku nzoga.<br> Umunyanzoga: - Nabumvaga. Ariko se<br> ntuntamaze! Dore usheshe akanguhe.<br> Dore inzoga ngiziriya. Singombye kukugenda<br> mu nyuma, ndi<br> muri rwinshi. Enda umuheha.<br> Ngunda: - Oya wihorere, nifitiye uwanjye<br> Ruvunabataka. Nawukuye mu<br> ishyamba, nkawugendana mu ruhago kuko<br> ntamenya gusomesha<br> iyindi miheha.<br> Umunyanzoga: - Ni uko rero genda. Uri umuntu<br> mukuru wibwire.<br> (Ngunda agarutse)<br> Mbe:Ngunda ko wijuse cyane ubigenjeje ute ?<br> Ngunda : - Navuye imuhira abagore banjye<br> bamaze kungaburira. Kandi no<br> gusogongera ko ndasogongeye; ahubwo genda<br> urebe.<br> Umunyanzoga: - Yewe, ndumva ibikoba<br> binkuka, ngiye kureba.<br> Ngunda (wenyine) : - Abanyanzoga baba<br> abapfu ! Ubundi yari asanzwe<br> ayobewe imisogongerere yanjye? Yabaga<br> yazaga ahubwo tukajyana.<br> Nsibye guhembuka, ariko rero byibura nishe<br> akanyota. Ubwo<br> Ruganzu yarebye, yemera ko njya gusogongera<br> azirikana ko nta<br> nzoga nyinshi afite? Umva ko ndi umunyanda<br> nini. Umunyanda nini<br> ntiyanga kugawa. Kandi simpemutse, sinakoze<br> ukundi atambwiye.<br> Yambwiye ngo nsogongere. Na njye<br> nasogongeye, sinyoye. Ubundi<br> bwo buriya buyoga bubiri nibwo yari ateze<br> abahinzi ? Henga ndetse<br> nigendere. Sinashobora kumva imivumo yâ€™<br> abanyanzoga!<br> Twahubirana yanyica. Kandi ga koko<br> ndahemutse ! Nguriya<br> arahindukiye. Mbega umujinya afite! Emwe<br> ndahemutse ! Emwe si<br> uruda rwanjye rwananiranye!?<br> Umunyanzoga (wenyine): - Icyago yagiye.<br> Aramaze na njye sinashakaga<br> kurebana na we. Bahungu se mbigenze nte ?<br> Ruganzu ndamubwira<br> iki ? Abahinzi nibahingura ndabakwiza he?<br> Ndamenya nihisha he?<br> Ararinkoreye Ngunda! Ndahebye, ntawizigira<br> rubanda.. . Ruganzu<br> ntagira umwaga, ariko rero ntabura kumbwira<br> nabi, birakwiye kandi.<br> Nimbona ko arakaye, ndapfa kumusaba<br> imbabazi, ahubwo izo nzoga<br> nzazisubizeho ubwanjye. Mana yâ€™i Rwanda,<br> urampe gukira irya none!<br> Ruganzu : - Mbe Ngunda, iyo nda yawe ko<br> yafoye cyane aho ni amahoro ?<br> Ngunda : - Nyagasani ndasogongeye gusa.<br> None se nari kugira ukundi<br> mutantegetse? Ndetse ndabasezeraho kuko<br> mfite ubwira, nasize<br> umugore wanjye aniha. Ndagira ngo njye<br> kureba ko yaba yaruhutse !<br> Ruganzu: - Ni uko, genda amahoro. Ariko<br> uramenye...<br> Ngunda (ageze hilya): - Nyagasani, abâ€™imuhira<br> nibamvugira nabi, murangirire<br> irnbabazi. Muzirikane ko inda yanjye<br> yantannye! Nasogongeye gusa<br> ariko ahari nakengesheje. Nibibababaza<br> ahubwo nzariha.<br> .<br> Ruganzu: - Genda rwiza, icyo ushaka kuvuga<br> ndacyumva. Abahinzi banjye<br> urabakoze. Ninsanga wazimaze, umenye ko<br> uzariha nka zo kabiri, kandi<br> ntuzasubire kungarukira mu rugo ukundi, kereka<br> ku munsi nagutumiye<br> kumpa umubyizi, ukaba igihano cyawe.<br> Â« Inda nini icura uwayihaye. Â»<br> Â« Uburana urubanza rwâ€™inda ntatsindwa. Â»<br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wayhHm9.jpg\" width=\"259\"><br>', 'mgunda.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 164),
(23, '2017-03-16 18:57:05', 'Amafoto yâ€™ abakobwa bamaze kwiyandikisha bazitabira Miss Africa izabera mu Rwanda uyu mwaka .', 'Muri uyu mwaka wa 2017 biteganyijwe ko amarushanwa yo gushaka Nyampinga wâ€™ Afurika wa 2017 azabera mu Rwanda nkuko byemejwe. ', '<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Muri uyu mwaka wa 2017 biteganyijwe ko amarushanwa yo gushaka Nyampinga wâ€™Afurika wa 2017.Azabera mu Rwanda nkuko byemejwe. Ubu abakobwa bo mu bihugu bitandukanye batangiye kwiyandikisha aho bizarangira taliki ya 20 werurwe ariko kugeza ubu nta mukobwa wâ€™u Rwanda uragaragaraho ko azitabira iri rushanwa. Binyuze ku rubuga rwa MISS Africa Continent ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2017 nibwo bahashyize itangazo ryavuga ko kwiyandikisha&nbsp;&nbsp;byatangiye bongeraho ko kandi iri rushanwa rizabera mu Rwanda mu mujyi wa Kigali. Nkuko babyanditse bavugaga ko kwiya ndikisha bitangiranye niyo taliki ya 20 aho bizamara amezi abiri kugeza iyindi taliki ya 20 Werurwe.Ba Nyammpinga bo mu bihugu bigiye bitandukanye bamaze kwiyandikisha nkuko amafoto&nbsp;&nbsp;agenda ashyirwa kuri urwo rubuga.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Iri rushanwa rigiye kuba ku nshuro ya kabiri rizaba taliki ya 20 Gicurasi aho umwaka ushize ryitabiriwe na Kundwa Doriane&nbsp;</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rVcAt3c.jpg\" width=\"640\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;arial narrow&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(107, 104, 104);\">Tanzania</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rkOTujq.jpg\" width=\"612\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;arial narrow&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(107, 104, 104);\">D R Congo</span></p><p class=\"