(29, '2017-03-17 11:43:54', 'Imigani migufi yâ€™Ikinyarwanda', 'â€¢	Babona isha itamba Bagatan\'urwo bari bambaye. â€¢	Babona zireresa amabya bakagira ngo zimya zose. â€¢	Bagarira yose. â€¢	Bagarira yose ni umwana wâ€™umunyarwanda', 'Imigani migufi y’Ikinyarwanda\r\nA\r\n•	Babona isha itamba Bagatan\'urwo bari bambaye.\r\n•	Babona zireresa amabya bakagira ngo zimya zose.\r\n•	Bagarira yose.\r\n•	Bagarira yose ni umwana w’umunyarwanda.\r\n•	Ufite gisegura anaga ijosi\r\n•	Uraritswe i bwami abanza irage\r\n•	Ushaka urupfu asoma impyisi\r\n•	Bukorikori bwa Nyiranzikoraho yateye ibuye ati narebaga ko riboze\r\n•	Inka nke zigukwera nka so\r\n•	Findi findi irutwa na so araroga.\r\n•	Wiringira ijosi rikakubyarira umwingo\r\n•	Ubwenge buza ubujiji buhise\r\n•	Bagarira yose ntuzi irizera.\r\n•	Bagutumye umurozi w’umugore uhera kuri nyoko.\r\n•	Banegurana ari inenge ba nenge itirora.\r\n•	Baranyerera yaguye Jinja.\r\n•	Barihima ba Mujyanama yasanze bamwendera umugore yica imboro.\r\n•	Barihima ni mwene Mujinya.\r\n•	Bavuga ibyigondoye umuhoro ukajya imbere.\r\n•	Batutira henshi ntibazamenya iyo bataye imihoro.\r\n•	Bavuga ibyigondoye umuhoro ukarakara.\r\n•	Bazirunge zange zibe isogo imboga zirura.\r\n•	Bene amazuru meza ntibaburana n’ibya nyuma.\r\n•	Bene imitsima bayitsimbarayeho.\r\n•	Bigirankana bya Nirwange bamutumye isuka yo guhamba se, ati \"mwa\r\n\r\n', '1489747434imigani.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 14, 'sub', 137),
(32, '2017-03-19 12:28:43', 'Umugabo byaketswe ko afite igisasu yafashwe ashaka kwinjira muri White House', 'Umugabo yatawe muri yombi nyuma yaho atwaye imodoka ayiganisha aho basakira abantu bagiye kwinjira mu Ngoro yâ€™Umukuru wâ€™Igihugu muri Amerika, White House, bikaba byakekwaga ko afite igisasu.', 'Umugabo yatawe muri yombi nyuma yaho atwaye imodoka ayiganisha aho basakira abantu bagiye kwinjira mu Ngoro y’Umukuru w’Igihugu muri Amerika, White House, bikaba byakekwaga ko afite igisasu.\r\n\r\nAbashinzwe umutekano muri White House, Secret Service, batangaje ko uyu mugabo yahise atabwa muri yombi. Ni mu gihe umunyamakuru wa CNN wari uhari yatangaje ko uwo mugabo yavugaga ko afite igisasu.\r\n\r\nImihanda yo muri ako gace yahise ifungwa, gusa ubwo ibi byose byabaga, Perezida Trump ntiyari muri White House ahubwo yari mu rugo rwe Mar-a-Lago muri Leta ya Florida.\r\n\r\nUmuvugizi wa White House, Sean Spicer, yavuze ko uyu mugabo wari utwaye imodoka nta ntwaro yari afite ndetse ashimira abashinzwe umutekano ku kuba bahise bakora akazi kabo.\r\n\r\nIki gikorwa kibaye icya kabiri nyuma yaho mu minsi ishize, umuntu wari ku igari yarivuyeho agasimbuka ashaka kwinjira mu biro by’Umukuru w’Igihugu.\r\n\r\nAbashinzwe umutekano banenzwe bikomeye kuwa 10 Werurwe kuko uyu muntu wari ku igare yafashwe amaze kurenga uruzitiro ari hafi neza y’umuryango w’ibiro by’Umukuru w’Igihugu. Gusa bavuze ko bagiye gukaza umutekano ku buryo nta muntu uzongera gushaka kwinjira muri White House.', '1489922923police.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 8, 'break', 148),
(33, '2017-03-20 13:09:10', 'BYINSHI UTAMENYE KU NYAMBO, INKA ZIRANGA UBWOROZI MU RWANDA RWO HAMBERE', 'Nkâ€™uko amateka yâ€™u Rwanda abigaragaza, Inyambo ni ubwoko bwâ€™inka zari urufatiro rwâ€™ubworozi bwâ€™inka mu Rwanda rwo hambere', '\r\nNk’uko amateka y’u Rwanda abigaragaza, Inyambo ni ubwoko bw’inka zari urufatiro rw’ubworozi bw’inka mu Rwanda rwo hambere. Mu rwego rwo kubungabunga izo nyamamare z’i Rwanda, Ikigo cy’Igihugu gishinzwe iterambere ry’ubuhinzi n’ubworozi (RAB) kikaba cyariyemeje kubungabunga izo nka ngo zitazibagirana mu rwa Gihanga.\r\n\r\nTwibutse ko inka z’Inyambo zari ubukungu ndashyikirwa mu Rwanda rwo hambere. Ibi bigaragazwa n’amazina yazo yazisingizaga, aho amateka agaragaza ko yatangiye ku ngoma y’Umwami YUHI IV GAHINDIRO (ahasaga mu wa 1746) ubwo abanyarwanda batangiye kuzirata ku bw’akamaro kazoo\r\nIby’ingenzi biranga inyambo: \r\nUbwoko bw’inyambo buzwiho kugira ibiburanga by’umwihariko birimo ibi bikurikira : \r\n   Amahembe maremare, arambuye, y’igitare, ateze neza; \r\n   Umubyimba uteranye kandi muremure, igikanu kigamitse, amaso mato; \r\n   Amaguru ateye neza; \r\n   Ibara rimwe ry’ibihogo kandi ku mashyo yose ; \r\n   Muri rusange ni inka iteye amabengeza kandi ishishangirana ishema n’isheja; \r\n   Imfizi igira amabya maremare kandi usanga ari ndende na ngari ugereranije n’andi moko yo muri Afurika y’Iburasirazuba. \r\n\r\n', '1490011750inyambo1.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 10, 'head', 139);
