(41, '2017-03-25 12:51:14', ' Dore uko ibirori byo kwizihiza umunsi mpuzamahanga wâ€™ururimi kavukire byagenze-AMAFOTO', 'Kuri uyu wa 24 Werurwe ni bwo i Remera kuri stade nto, habereye ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza umunsi mpuzamahanga wâ€™ururimi kavukire', '<div class=\"artlead\">Kuri uyu wa 24 Werurwe ni \r\nbwo i Remera kuri stade nto, habereye ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza\r\n umunsi mpuzamahanga wâ€™ururimi kavukire, aho byari bifite \r\ninsanganyamatsiko igira iti,â€Kwiga no kunoza ikinyarwanda ni inshingano \r\nyanjye na we.â€</div>\r\n				<div class=\"artlogo\">\r\n					<br>					\r\n				</div>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n					<p>Ni ibirori byaranzwe nâ€™ubwitabire bwâ€™abanyeshuri bo mu mashuri \r\nyisumbuye bagiye baturuka mu bigo bitandukanye bya hano muri Kigali, \r\nuretse aba banyeshuri ibi birori kandi byaranzwe nâ€™umubare munini \r\nwâ€™abahanzi baturuka mu rugaga rwa muzika nyarwanda ndetse nâ€™abagiye \r\nbaturuka mu rugaga rwâ€™amakinamico, byanatumye abari babyitabiriye \r\nbasusuruka ndetse banishimira uko byagenze.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5566.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5566.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Miss Rwanda n\'ibisonga bye begereye umunyamabanga nshingwabikorwa w\'inteko nyarwanda y\'ururimi n\'umuco Vuningoma James</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Uretse aba bahanzi kandi, hagiye hagaragara nâ€™abandi bazwi mu bikorwa\r\n bitandukanye nkâ€™abakinnyi bâ€™umupira wâ€™amaguru, Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda \r\n2017 nâ€™ibisonga bye nabo bari baje kwizihiza no gushyigikira uyu munsi \r\nmpuzamahanga wâ€™ururimi kavukire.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392519_img_9349.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392519_img_9349.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Mukabacondo Trese wambaye kibikira na Minisitiri Uwacu Julienne wari umushyitsi mukuru</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Mu ijambo ryâ€™umuyobozi wâ€™intebe yâ€™inteko yagarutse cyane ku gushimira\r\n abari bitabiriye ibi birori, aboneraho nâ€™umwanya wo gusobanura uko \r\nkwizihiza uyu munsi wâ€™ururimi kavukire muri uyu mwaka byatangiye, aho \r\nyatangaje ko byatangiye haba inama ku mikoreshereze yâ€™ikinyarwanda muri \r\niki gihe, asobanura ko kandi hatangiwemo ibiganiro 4 birebana nâ€™uruhare \r\nrwâ€™umuryango mu kwigisha no kunoza ikinyarwanda, uruhare \r\nrwâ€™itangazamakuru mu kunoza ikinyarwanda, ikinyarwanda mu burezi \r\nnâ€™imikoreshereze yâ€™ikinyarwanda mu nzego zâ€™abikorera, aha kandi \r\nyasobanuye ko iyi nama yafatiwemo imyanzuro izafasha mu kunoza no kwiga \r\nikinyarwanda.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392307_dsc_5493.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392307_dsc_5493.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a><em><strong><br></strong></em></p><p><em><strong>Umuzungu watunguye benshi uburyo avuga ikinyarwanda akanasakuza</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>Ibi birori nk\'uko amafoto abigaragaza byari byitabiriwe nâ€™abayobozi \r\nbatandukanye, aho umushyitsi mukuru yari Ministiri wâ€™Umuco na Siporo \r\nUwacu Julienne. Mu ijambo rye Minisitiri Uwacu yaboneyeho umwanya wo \r\nkwibutsa abantu ko ikinyarwanda ari umurunga uhuza abanyarwanda kuko ari\r\n ururimi kavukire rwabo bose.</p>\r\n<p>Yibukije abanyarwanda ko buri wese afite inshingano zo \r\nkurusigasira,ariko buri wese akanarwiga kuko buri munsi hari byinshi uru\r\n rurimi rwunguka. Yagaragaje ko kandi kuruvuga no kurwandika ku buryo \r\nbunoze bireba buri munyarwanda. Yasoje iri jambo rye yibutsa buri wese \r\nkumvako kwita ku rurimi bimureba.&nbsp;</p><br><p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490394184_img_9396.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490394184_img_9396.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Bravan yeretswe urukundo n\'abanyeshuri ku buryo bwagaragariye buri wese aho yaje akurikiye Dream boys kurubyiniro<br></em></strong></p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392520_dsc_5505.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392520_dsc_5505.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Abanyeshuri bo mu mashuri yisumbuye ni bo bari benshi muri ibi birori aho bari babukereye dore iko barishimye<br></em></strong></p><p><br></p><br><p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392307_dsc_5490.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392307_dsc_5490.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>&nbsp;Ben Nganji yashimishije benshi</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392416_dsc_5564.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392416_dsc_5564.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Makanyaga na Senderi <br></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392308_dsc_5526.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392308_dsc_5526.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Indatabigwi zo mu rugaga rwa muzika</em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392519_img_9511.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392519_img_9511.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Mu rugaga rw\'amakinamico, amakinamico nayo anmwe mubiranga umuco <br></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490394184_img_9414.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490394184_img_9414.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>imyambaro ibereye ijisho niyo yari yiganje</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Ururimi ni urwacu turukunde turusigasire ni indangagaciro ituranga bene KANYARWANDA.<br></em></strong></p><br><br><br><br>IRAMOSE<br></div>', '14904426741223.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 14, 'head', 241),
(42, '2017-03-27 20:50:02', 'Sobanukirwa bimwe mubintu byaziraga mu muco nyarwanda.', 'Abanyarwanda bo hambere bari bafite imyemerere yabo yihariye, itandukanye niya ubu kuburyo haribintu bakoraga ndetse nibyo birindaga gukora kuko babifataga nkâ€™ibizira', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Abanyarwanda\r\n bo hambere bari bafite imyemerere yabo yihariye, itandukanye niya ubu \r\nkuburyo haribintu bakoraga ndetse nibyo birindaga gukora kuko babifataga\r\n nkâ€™ibizira. muri iki gice kirazira zabaga mu muco \r\nnyarwanda turababwira kirazira zarangwaga hagati ya abashakanye, umuntu \r\nnâ€™umugore, umuntu nâ€™umukobwa ndetse nâ€™umuntu nâ€™umwana.<b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">1.Abashakanye</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">1.Umwishywa barongoje barawumenya cyane, kuko ngo iyo umwanzi\r\nawubonye akabatanga kuwakira, ntibaba bakibyaye.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">2.Uwabyaye impanga azishyingirira rimwe, bakazajya kubasurira\r\nrimwe, kandi bakazatwikururirwa rimwe. Iyo badashyingiriwe rimwe, usigaye\r\nbamukoza hasi, akaryama, ngo abaye umugore, ntabe agikunguriwe n\' uwashyingiwe.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">3.Umugeni ntiyashyira inkono ku ziko, ntakora ku mashyiga,\r\nntayora ivu, atarabonera urugo.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">4. Iyo umugeni atarabonera urugo, igihe aryamye ntahindukira,\r\nkereka abanje kubwira umugabo, bakagurana ikiryamo, umwe akajya aho undi yari\r\nari, umugeni atagize atyo, yaba akenye umugabo we.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">5.Umugeni ntawe yambarana na we atarabyara. </span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">6.Umugeni kandi ntiyanyara aho baramukazi be barora, ngo\r\ninkari ye bayikaranga, akazapfa atabyaye.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">7.Umugeni ntakora ku mashyiga, ntiyarika umutsima\r\nataratekeshwa. Muri icyo gihe aboha icyibo cya Nyabitabo, akazagiha nyirabukwe,\r\niyo yahukanye arakijyana ngo batazakimuzingiramo akabura inzu.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">8.Umugore w\'ikirongore ntasambana, kuko ngo aba ari ukwica\r\nimpindura ye akazabura ibyara, keretse ngo yongeye agasambana n\'uwo mugabo\r\nbasambanye, ngo ni ho yabyara.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">9.Umugabo warongoye ntiyambuka umugezi umugore we atarabonera\r\nurugo, umugabo arabyirinda cyane.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">2.Umuntu nâ€™umugore</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">10. Umuntu yirinda kuvuga icyo umugore yabyaye akiri mu\r\nrweyo,ngo yahora abyara abahungu ,yaba ari umukobwa agahora abyara abakobwa</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">11.\r\n Inka, intama nâ€™ihene ,ntawe uvuga icyozabyaye ngo akivugire hafi yâ€™aho \r\nzabyariye,ngo yahora ikibyara.Bakivugira kure yâ€™aho cyangwa se ku wundi \r\nmunsi</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">12.\r\n Umuntu ushaka guhindura umugore ubyara abakobwa gusa, amukubita \r\nigisura.Inka ,ihene nâ€™intama bibyara ibimasa gusa babigenza batyo \r\nzigahindura imbyaro</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">3.Umuntu nâ€™umukobwa</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">13. Umuntu azira kugera umukobwa intorezo niyo baba\r\nbakina,ngo aba amuzinze akazapfa atarongowe.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">14.\r\n Umuntu ushaka kuzinga umukobwa aragenda, akareba inzuzi ebyiri \r\nurwâ€™igihaza nâ€™urwâ€™umwungu,akazijyana mu mayirabiri,imitwe \r\niterekeranye,ati :â€Izi nzuzi umunsi zahuye nyiranaka azabone umugabo â€œ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">4.Umuntu nâ€™umwana.&nbsp;</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">15. Umuntu azira kurenga umwana ataragenda, iyo amurenze\r\narahindukira akamurengura,kutamurengura ni ukumuzinga ntazagende</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">16. Umuntu yirinda kurenga ingobyi cyangwa umusambi\r\nbaryamishaho umwana utaragenda, kuba ari ukumuzinga umwana agakura nabi</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">17. Umuntu yirinda guterera ku rutugu umwana utaramera\r\namenyo, byatuma atayamera vuba</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">18. Umuntu ntiyakinisha kubika umutemeri ku mwana ukiri muto\r\ncyane, kuba ari ukumuzinga ntazakure</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">19. Umuntu ubikiriye umwana akanga gusinzira, ntiyagira ngo\r\nnasinzire vuba,ni ukumukenya,bakomeza kumubikira</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">20. Umuntu yirinda guca hagati yâ€™abana bâ€™inkurikirane, ngo ni ukubateranya bakazahora bazirana.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">21. Umuntu iyo avuye ku mugezi yikoreye amazi, ntiyahirahira ngo ace hagati yâ€™abana</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">bâ€™abavandimwe,iyo abaciye hagati akoramu mazi avuye kuvoma,akajugunya hagati yabo ngo atabakenya bagapfa.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">IRAMOSE<br></span></p>', '1490640602kirazira.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 129),
(43, '2017-03-28 15:23:52', 'AMAFOTO- Miss Simbi Fanique yifatanyije n\'abafite ubumuga mu gutangiza shampiyona yabo yâ€™umupira wâ€™amaguru', 'Miss Umuhoza Simbi Fanique ni  umwe mu bakobwa bari mwirushanwa rya Miss Rwanda 2017, aza kwegukana ikamba nkâ€™igisonga cya kane muri iri rushanwa, uyu mukobwa mu gushyira mu bikorwa  umushinga we yatangije irushanwa yise â€˜Rwanda Amputee Football Championshipâ€™ rizahuza abafite ubumuga bo mu ntara zose.', '<div class=\"artlogo\">\r\n					<a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/logos/1490691636_logo.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/logos/1490691636_logo.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Simbi Fanique yifatanyije n\'abafite ubumuga mu gutangiza shampiyona yabo yâ€™umupira wâ€™amaguru-AMAFOTO\"></a>					\r\n				</div>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				\r\n					<p>Iki gikorwa cyabereye ku Kimisagara cyari kigamije guteza imbere\r\n no gukura mu bwigunge banongerera icyizere abafite ubumuga dore ko \r\nSimbi Fanique ari na cyo yiyemeje ubwo yari mu irushanwa rya Miss Rwanda\r\n 2017 aho yabishyize mu muhigo yahigiye igihugu nâ€™abanyarwanda muri \r\nrusange.</p>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691755_1.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691755_1.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"fanique\"></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691755_3.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691755_3.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"fanique\"></a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691756_9.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691756_9.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"fanique\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Miss Simbi Fanique asuhuza abakinnyi ku mpande zombi<a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490691858_6.jpg\" rel=\"p