(44, '2017-03-28 17:29:52', 'Miss Rwanda Iradukunda Elysa mu bihe bitandukanye', 'Iradukunda Elsa niwe wambitswe ikamba rya Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda 2017 nyuma yo guhigika abandi bakobwa 14 bari bahanganye ubu wamenya uburyo wakomeza kumu kurikirana.', 'Hari ku itariki 14 Mutarama 2017 ubwo amajonjora yâ€™ibanze ya Miss Rwanda\r\n yatangiraga, ku ikubitiro iri rushanwa ritangirira mu ntara \r\nyâ€™Uburengerazuba, aha ni naho Elsa yatangiriye urugendo rwe yiyamamaza \r\nmuri Miss Rwanda 2017 mu karere ka Rubavu birangira yegukanye ikamba. \r\nReba amwe mu mafoto<br><em></em><strong></strong>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113429__dsc8388.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113429__dsc8388.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"miss Elsa\"></a></strong></p><br>Miss Elysa aratangariza abanyarwanda ndetse nabafana be uburyo baguma kumukurikira kumbuga zihurirwaho nabantu benshi<div class=\"grabarticle gallery\"><div class=\"artbody\"><div class=\"content-wrapper\"><p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113494__dsc8749.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113494__dsc8749.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"miss Elsa\"></a></em></strong></p><p><br><strong><em></em></strong></p></div></div></div><br><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113632__dsc8765.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113632__dsc8765.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"miss Elsa\"></a></em></strong><br><p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5566.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5566.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Miss Rwanda n\'ibisonga bye begereye umunyamabanga nshingwabikorwa w\'inteko nyarwanda y\'ururimi n\'umuco Vuningoma James mu&nbsp; birori byo kwizihiza umunsi mpuzamahanga w\'ururimi kavukire</em></strong><br></p>Miss Rwanda 2017 Iradukunda Elsa, ku bijyanye nâ€™imyidagaduro \r\nyabajijwe uko yidagadura avuga ko akunda koga, gusoma ibitabo bivuga ku \r\nbintu byabayeho ndetse akaba akunda no kumva umuziki.\r\nMiss Iradukunda Elsa abajijwe indirimbo akunda cyane yavuze ko mu \r\nndirimbo akunda ku isonga hazaho indirimbo yâ€™Imana yâ€™umuhanzi Serge \r\nIyamuremye ivuga ngo <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xr6yoA05pcc\">â€˜Nzajya ngukoreraâ€™</a> iyi ndirimbo ikaba yitwa na none <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xr6yoA05pcc\">â€˜Nzaririmba Hoziyana</a><div class=\"clearfix\"> </div><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aeHhdA0.jpg\" width=\"275\"><br>MISS RWANDA yadutangarije ko umukunzi we yajya kuri facebook ukandika \r\nMiss Iradukunda Elsa Official maze ukanda like mugahorana ukamenya amakuru ya MISS \r\nRwanda 2017<br><em>&nbsp;<br>kanda hano ukore like kuri page ya MISS RWANDA.@Miss Iradukunda Elsa Official<br></em><img src=\"https://scontent-lht6-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17553997_178682872648080_5700146087658139200_n.jpg?oh=32dc2b4f5dead64c6fbec528d164b8bc&amp;oe=595932A8\" alt=\"Image may contain: 1 person, text\" class=\"spotlight\" height=\"423\" width=\"299\"><em></em><br>\r\n<br><i>IRAMOSE</i><br><br>', '1490714992miss rwanda.png', 0, 'admin', 5, 12, 'break', 345),
(45, '2017-04-01 20:26:32', 'AMAFOTO-Miss Rwanda Elsa Iradukunda yahembye abanyeshuri bitwaye neza', 'Iradukunda Elsa niwe wambitswe ikamba rya Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda 2017 nyuma yo guhigika abandi bakobwa 14 bari bahanganye ubu akaba yari yasuye intara yâ€™Uburengerazuba akarere ka Rubavu', '<div class=\"artlead\">&nbsp;Miss Rwanda 2017 Iradukunda Elsa mu ntara \r\nyâ€™Uburengerazuba yasuye anahemba abanyeshuri bitwaye neza mu kigo \r\ncyâ€™amushuri abanza cya Rusamaza kibarizwa mu karere ka Rubavu mu murenge\r\n wa Nyundo. dore ko bari bari gusoza igihembwe cya mbere cy\'amasomo \r\nyabo.</div>\r\n				<div class=\"artlogo\">\r\n					<br>					\r\n				</div>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				\r\n					<p>Kuri uyu wa Gatanu tariki 31 Werurwe 2017, Miss Rwanda 2017 \r\nIradukunda Elsa yahembye abana bitwaye neza guhera mu mwaka&nbsp; wa mbere \r\nkugeza mu wa gatandatu akaba yabageneye ibikoresho byâ€™ishuri birimo \r\namakaye, amakaramu, ibikapu batwaramo ibikoresho n\'ibindi. .</p>\r\n<p><strong>AMAFOTO:</strong></p>\r\n<a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042890_8.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042890_8.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042890_7.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042890_7.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042821_3.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042821_3.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042821_4.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042821_4.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042821_5.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042821_5.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042822_6.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042822_6.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042888_1.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042888_1.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042889_9.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042889_9.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042890_10.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201704/attachments/1491042890_10.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda\"></a><br></em></strong>Si uguhemba \r\nabana bitwaye neza gusa ahubwo miss Rwanda 2017 yaniyemeje gufasha abana\r\n 10 batishoboye bari mu mwaka wa mbere akazabafasha mumyigire yabo abaha\r\n ibikoresho, imyambaro, inkweto ndetse nâ€™ibindi bikenerwa nâ€™abanyeshuri \r\nkugeza barangije kwiga amashuri abanza<br><br><br><br><br>IRAMOSE<br>', '1491071192elysa.jpg', 0, 'IRAMOSE', 5, 12, 'head', 329),
(47, '2017-04-05 18:42:23', 'Ibyiza byo kurya urubuto rwâ€™indimu ', 'Imbuto ni bimwe mu biribwa bigira akamaro gakomeye ku muntu, iyo ziriwe neza kandi mu buryo buhoraho zongera ubudahangarwa bwâ€™ubuzima mu buryo butandukanye', '<p>Indimu ni rubuto rugira akamaro kanini  ku buzima bwâ€™umuntu cyane cyane \r\nigafasha uruhu kumera neza,  rimwe na rimwe ikaba nâ€™umuti wâ€™indwara \r\nzitandukanye ,iyo umuntu ayikoresheje neza binyuze mu kuyirya cyangwa \r\nkuyisiga nkâ€™umuti kandi ikamukiza burundu.</p><p>Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe nâ€™urubuga medicalnewstoday.com bugaragaza \r\nko kurya urubuto rwâ€™indimu bigabanya byinshi mu bibazo bikomoka ku \r\nkutagira Vitamine C ndetse umuntu uyirya kenshi aba afite amahirwe make \r\nyo kwandura indwara ya Kanseri.</p>\r\n<p>Mu moko yâ€™imbuto, hari iziribwa cyangwa zigategurwa mu buryo \r\nbutandukanye harimo izo babanza gutara ngo zishye, iziribwa ako kanya \r\nbakimara kuzisoroma nâ€™ibindi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Akamaro ko kurya urubuto rwâ€™indimu:</strong></p>\r\n<p>1.	Bigabanya ibibazo byo kugabanuka kwâ€™amaraso ajya ku bwonko  \r\n(ischemic stroke  risk). Uku kugabanuka bishobora gutuma ubwonko \r\nbudakora neza. Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe ku bagore bagera kuri 19%  \r\nbarya ibiribwa birimo vitamine C bwagaragaje ko byabagabanyirije ikibazo\r\n cyâ€™igabanuka ryâ€™amaraso ajya mu bwonko</p>\r\n<p>2.	Birwanya kanseri : nkâ€™ikiribwa gikungahaye kuri vitamine C, indimu nâ€™umutobe wayo bifasha mu kurwanya kanseri.</p>\r\n<p>3.	Kurya indimu yâ€™umwimerere bifasha uruhu guhangana nâ€™imirasire yâ€™izuba ndetse bikakurinda kuzana iminkanyari.</p>\r\n<p>4.	Birinda Asima (asthma): kurwa Asima biba biri hasi cyane  ku muntu  urya indimu ku kigero cyo hejuru.</p>\r\n<p>5.	Byongera mu mubiri intungamubiri yitwa Iron: iyo mu mubiri wa \r\nmuntu â€˜Ironâ€™ yabaye nke bituma amaraso agabanuka ndetse umuvuduko ukajya\r\n hasi ugereranyije nâ€™uwâ€™umuntu ufite iyi ntungamubiri.</p>\r\n<p>6.	Byongera ubwirinzi bwâ€™umubiri: muri rusange ibiryo bikungahaye \r\nkuri vitamin C  bifasha ubwirinzi bwâ€™umubiri mu  guhangana nâ€™udukoko \r\ndutera ibicurane nâ€™utundi duca intege umubiri wa muntu.</p><p><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DejEmS7.jpg\" width=\"307\">.</p><p>IRAMOSE<br></p>', '1491410543indimuu.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 2, '', 191),
(48, '2017-04-06 13:26:37', 'UMUCO Wâ€™IGIHUGU NI IKI? DORE BIMWE MU BIRANGA UMUCO GAKONDO Wâ€™ABANYARWANDA nicyo Inteko Nyarwanda y\'Ururimi n\'Umuco IBIVUGAHO.', 'UMUCO ni uruhurirane  rwâ€™insobe rugizwe nâ€™ubumenyi, imyemerere, ubugeni, amategeko, imyitwarire yemewe, imico nâ€™ubundi bushobozi bwose nâ€™akamenyero umuntu agenda yunguka nkâ€™umwe mu bagize umuryango.â€', '<em>Nkâ€™uko abanditsi <em>Kroeber A.L. na Kluckhohn&nbsp;<em><em>C. </em></em>babigaragaza mu gitabo bise Culture: a critical review of concepts and definitions.</em>Umuco</em> <em>ugaragarira</em> <em>muri</em> <em>byinshi</em>:\r\n<ul><li>Mu myandikire (<em>Writing</em>),</li><li>Mu myemerere (<em>Belief</em>),</li><li>Mu miririmbire (<em>Music</em>),</li><li>Mu mitekere (<em>Cooking</em>), ndetse no</li><li>Mu byo abanyagihugu bakora.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Umuco Gakondo wâ€™abanyarwanda</strong> ufitanye isano \r\nnâ€™uwâ€™abaturage bo muri Afurika yâ€™ibiyaga bigali. Imiterere yâ€™ubwami \r\nbwâ€™abakurambere, yatangaje cyane ba gashakabuhake<strong>/</strong><em>abakoroni</em> bageze mu Rwanda mbere bitewe nâ€™uburyo bwari bwubakanye (<em>ubwami</em>) ubuhanga (<em>sophisticated organization</em>), ku buryo nta baturage muri Afurika bakekaga ko bagira ubwami bwâ€™ubatse gutyo.\r\n</p><div id=\"attachment_22\" style=\"width: 308px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/Musinga-entoure-de-ses-guerriers-portant-ishabure-1907-1911.jpg\"><img style=\"opacity: 1;\" class=\"wp-image-22\" src=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/Musinga-entoure-de-ses-guerriers-portant-ishabure-1907-1911-300x232.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"230\" width=\"298\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Umwami Musinga akikijwe nâ€™ingabo ze bambaye ishabure, 1907-1911</p></div>\r\n<p><strong>Imyemerere gakondo yâ€™Imana imwe</strong>, mu mibereho yabo, \r\nimigani miremire nâ€™imigufi, ururimi rwâ€™i Kinyarwanda, indirimbo, kuvuza \r\ningoma no guhamiriza bifite uruhare runini mu muco gakondo \r\nwâ€™abanyarwanda ugizwe no kwitabira gutabara/urugamba, abarwanyi, ibikorwa \r\nbyâ€™ubuhinzi, ubworozi, guhiga no kuroba.</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_24\" style=\"width: 213px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/Intore-11.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-24 \" src=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/Intore-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"275\" width=\"203\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Imyidagaduro yarangwaga cyane no guhamiriza no kuvuza ingoma</p></div>\r\n<p><strong>Inka</strong> nâ€™amata, amacumu akozwe mu byuma mu buryo \r\nbutandukanye, amasuka, imiheto, inzoga zâ€™ibitoki â€œurwagwaâ€ nâ€™izâ€™amasaka \r\nâ€ikigajyeâ€ ibyibo nâ€™ibitebo byose ni ibimenyetso bigize umuco gakondo wâ€™abanyarwanda.</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_26\" style=\"width: 284px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/images_098.jpg\"><img style=\"opacity: 1;\" class=\"wp-image-26 size-full\" src=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/images_098.jpg\" alt=\"images_098\" height=\"184\" width=\"274\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Inyambo, zimwe mu nka za kinyarwanda zarangwaga nâ€™amahembe maremare</p></div>\r\n<p><strong>Ubucuzi bwâ€™ubutare (Fer)</strong> buri hafi mu bwatangiye \r\nmbere ku isi. Ibikoresho bikozwe mu biti, mu ibumba, cyangwa mu bimera \r\nbyarangaga ubuzima busanzwe. Ubu ibikoresho bituruka hanze yâ€™u Rwanda \r\nbikoze mu byuma cyangwa palasitike (<em>Plastique</em>), byateye imbere.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kugeza mu kinyejana cya 19</strong>, imyenda yakorwaga mu bishishwa byâ€™ibiti kuburyo byajyaga gusa nâ€™imyenda ikorwa ubu.</p>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_28\" style=\"width: 300px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/ishabure-front-.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-28 size-full\" src=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/ishabure-front-.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"238\" width=\"290\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Uku niko abakobwa bambaraga ishabure ikagira inshunda hasi/Photo Internet</p></div>\r\n<p>Kuva mu gihe cya ba gashakabuhake, imyenda ituruka mu burengerazuba bwâ€™isi (<em>Uburayi nâ€™Amerika</em>) yagiye yiyongera, ariko igitenge gikoze mu ipamba nanubu cyagumye kuba ikimenyetso gihuza umuco gakondo nâ€™iterambere.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Kurongora (<em>Wedding</em>)</strong> ubu ni akanya ko kubahiriza umuco gakondo. Gutanga inkwano, bikorwa nâ€™umukwe bikorerwa ababyeyi bâ€™umugeni (<em>inka, isuka nâ€™ibindi bitewe nâ€™urwego rwâ€™umuryango</em>), ni umusaruro wibiganiro birebire byâ€™ubwumvikane nâ€™ubwubahane hagati yâ€™imiryango.</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_29\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/La-mari%C3%A9e-%C3%A0-sa-famille-par-alliance-aux-amis-et-%C3%A0-la-communaut%C3%A9-des-alentours..jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-29 size-medium\" src=\"http://tohoza.com/plus/quizsakwe/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2014/07/La-mari%C3%A9e-%C3%A0-sa-famille-par-alliance-aux-amis-et-%C3%A0-la-communaut%C3%A9-des-alentours.-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"199\" width=\"300\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Abakobwa baherekeje umugeni ugiye kwiyereka umuryango we nyuma yâ€™ubukwe/Photo Internet</p></div>\r\n<p><strong>Ubuvuzi gakondo, </strong>bwifashisha cyane ibimera bwagumyeho nanubu nubwo haje ubuvuzi bugezweho bwo mu burengerazuba bwâ€™isi (<em>Uburayi nâ€™Amerika</em>).</p>\r\n<p>Umuco nyarwanda ufite byinshi biwuranga, si ibi gusa; umuco nyarwanda\r\n kandi ni ishingiro ryâ€™urukundo umunyarwanda akwiye kugirira igihugu cye\r\n (<em>patriotism</em>) kuko umuco wâ€™igihugu niwo utuma igihugu (u<em> Rwanda</em>) kiba igihugu koko kikagira itandukaniro nâ€™ibindi</p>\r\n<p><b>Inteko Nyarwanda y\'Ururimi n\'Umuco nkuko ibigaragaza kurukuta rwayo ivuga ko</b>:</p><p><b>Umuco</b> ari&nbsp; isangano ryâ€™ibimenyetso byihariye biranga umuryango runaka \r\nwâ€™abantu bikagaragarira mu mitekerereze, imikorere, imyifatire mu \r\nbumenyi no mu mvugo byâ€™imbaga igize uwo muryango.<br>Umuco uturuka ku bintu bitatu (3) by\'ingenzi ari byo umurage, ibihangano n\'ibitirano:<br><br><b>-Umurage:</b> ni ibyo abasekuru badusigiye kandi tugenderaho bikaturanga bikatwitirirwa. <br><br><b>-Ibitirano</b>\r\n ni ibyo tuvana mu bindi bihugu. Aha rero niho Abenegihugu, abahuriye ku\r\n muco runaka ubaranga basabwa kubamaso bagashungura, bakagosora \r\nbakemeranya ibyo bakira bikabaranga mu muco wabo babikuye mu mico \r\ny\'ahandi, kuko ibyiza by\'abandi si ko buri gihe biba ari ibyiza mu muco \r\nwundi runaka.<br> <br><b>-Ibihangano</b> ni ibyo abantu bahanga bigamije gusubiza ibibazo barimo, bakabyifashisha hanyuma bikaza kurangira byiswe umuco wabo. <br>Umuco\r\n nyarwanda rero ni ishingiro ryâ€™ituze mu muryango wâ€™Abanyarwanda kuko \r\nuhuza abanyarwanda mu mikorere, mu mihango, mu migenzo, mu mitekerereze,\r\n mu bihangano byabo kuko bawusangiye kandi ukabaranga.<br><br>Mu rwego \r\nrwo kwiteza imbere no kugira uruhare mu iterambere rirambye, Inteko \r\nNyarwanda y\'Ururimi n\'Umuco irashishikariza buri wese kurangwa \r\nn\'indangagaciro z\'umuco w\'u Rwanda zikaba umusemburo wâ€™iterambere, cyane\r\n cyane binyuze mu burezi nâ€™Itorero, kandi hagashyirwa muri za Kaminuza \r\nnâ€™Amashuri Makuru gahunda zigisha zikanakora ubushakashatsi ku byerekeye\r\n umuco, ururimi rwâ€™Ikinyarwanda, ubugeni, ubuhanzi na muzika. <br>Bimwe \r\nmu bihugu bikize ubu ku isi byagiye bishingira iterambere ryabyo ku muco\r\n wabyo, ndetse bikanawusakaza no hanze yâ€™imbibi zabyo. Iterambere \r\nrishingiye ku muco rigira uruhare ku mibereho myiza yâ€™abaturage: batuye \r\nahantu heza, bafite ubuzima bwiza, bafite ubumenyi, bafite ibikoresho \r\nnkenerwa bya buri munsi. Uko imibereho yâ€™abaturage igenda irushaho kuba \r\nmyiza niko igihugu kigenda kiva mu bihugu biri mu nzira yâ€™amajyambere \r\nkigana mu bikize ku isi.</p><p>Mu nkuru zikurikira tuzagenda tubagezaho nâ€™ibindi bigaragaza itandukaniro hagati yâ€™umuco nyarwanda nâ€™iyahandi.</p><p><br></p><p>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></p>', '1491477997RALC.jpg', 0, 'IRADUKUNDA MOSEs', 6, 10, 'head', 577);
