(53, '2017-04-08 10:29:28', 'Kwibuka23: Miss Rwanda Elsa arasaba urubyiruko kwigira ku mateka kuko utazi iyo ava ntamenya iyo ajya', ' Miss Iradukunda Elsa wâ€™imyaka 19 yâ€™amavuko, uherutse kwambikwa ikamba rya Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda wâ€™umwaka wa 2017, yasabye urubyiruko kwibuka barwanya ingengabitekerezo ya Jenoside, bagashyigikira ibyiza abanyarwanda bagezeho.', '<div class=\"artlead\">Miss Rwanda 2017, Iradukunda\r\n Elsa yatanze ubutumwa bw\'ihumure ku banyarwanda muri ibi bihe byo \r\nkwibuka ku nshuro ya 23 Jenoside yakorewe Abatutsi. Mu butumwa bwe, \r\nyasabye abakiri urubyiruko by\'umwihariko kwigira ku mateka kuko utazi \r\niyo ava atamenya iyo ajya. </div>\r\n				<div class=\"artlogo\">\r\n					<p><strong><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113429__dsc8388.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113429__dsc8388.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"miss Elsa\"></a></strong></p><em></em><br></div>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				\r\n					<p>&nbsp;Miss Iradukunda Elsa wâ€™imyaka 19 \r\nyâ€™amavuko, uherutse kwambikwa ikamba rya Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda wâ€™umwaka \r\nwa 2017, yasabye urubyiruko kwibuka barwanya ingengabitekerezo ya \r\nJenoside, bagashyigikira ibyiza abanyarwanda bagezeho.</p>\r\n<p>Miss Iradukunda Elsa yunzemo ko urubyiruko rukwiye kwigira ku mateka.\r\n Yabasabye kandi guharanira ubumwe nâ€™urukundo abanyarwanda bafite kuko \r\nari yo soko yavomwemo imbaraga zakuye u Rwanda mu mwijima. Yagize ati:</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><i><b>Ubutumwa naha urubyiruko ni ukwibuka Jenoside barwanya \r\ningengabitekerezo ya Jenoside bagashyigikira ibyiza twagezeho baharanira\r\n kwigira ku mateka kugira ngo bavanemo inyigisho kuko burya utazi iyo \r\nava ntamenya iyo ajya kandi bakomeze guharanira ubumwe nâ€™urukundo \r\nabanyarwanda dufite kuko ni yo soko twavomyemo imbaraga zo kuvana \r\nigihugu cyacu mu mwijima tukakijyana mu mucyo kandi ari naho tuzavana \r\nimbaraga zizakomeza guteza imbere igihugu cyacu.</b></i></p><i><b>\r\n</b></i></blockquote><i><b>\r\n</b></i><p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488110485_elsa7.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><br></a></p><p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488110485_elsa7.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113632__dsc8765.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488113632__dsc8765.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"miss Elsa\"></a></em></strong><br></a></p><div class=\"clearfix\"> </div><p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488110485_elsa7.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488110485_elsa7.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda Iradukunda Elsa\"></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Miss Rwanda Iradukunda Elsa arasaba urubyiruko kwigira ku mateka</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488088446_1.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201702/attachments/1488088446_1.jpg\" title=\"Miss Rwanda 2017\" alt=\"Miss Rwanda 2017\"></a></strong></p>\r\n<strong>Miss Rwanda Iradukunda hamwe n\'ibisonga bye bine</strong>', '1491640168MISS 2017 profile.jpg', 0, 'IRAMOSE', 6, 10, 'break', 1342),
(54, '2017-04-10 14:47:26', 'Kwibuka23: INTORE TUYISENGE , MUNYAKAZI DEO na JABA STAR barasaba  urubyiruko byumwihariko gukoresha imbuga nkoranyambaga muguhangana n\'abafobya jenocide yakorewe abatutsi 1994', ' INTORE TUYISENGE ,DEO MUNYAKAZi, JABA STAR bamwe mubagaragara mu muco Nyarwanda nabo  bakaba kuruhembe mukubaka uRwanda batanze ubutumwa bwâ€™ihumure ku barokotse Jenocide yakorewe Abatutsi muri Mata 1994 , bavuga ko ibyabaye bidakwiye kongera kubaho , kandi Abanyarwanda bakwiye gusigasira ibyo bamaze kugeraho.', '<br>Mu butumwa batanze ubutumwa bw\'ihumure ku banyarwanda muri ibi bihe byo \r\nkwibuka ku nshuro ya 23 Jenocide yakorewe Abatutsi. Mu butumwa basabye abakiri urubyiruko by\'umwihariko kwigira ku mateka kuko utazi \r\niyo ava atamenya iyo ajya basaba urubyiruko byumwihariko gukoresha imbuga nkoranyambaga muguhangana n\'abafobya jenoside yakorewe abatutsi.<br>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5587.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><br></a><strong><em>Intore Tuyisenge uyobora urugaga nyarwanda rwa muzika uzwi cyane mundirimbo agenda ahimbira uturere dutandukanye <br></em></strong></p><p><strong><em><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5587.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201703/attachments/1490392417_dsc_5587.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></em></strong></p>\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Jo2U4cb.jpg\" width=\"800\"><p><strong><em>Intore Tuyisenge uyobora urugaga nyarwanda rwa muzika <br></em></strong></p><p><strong>mumagambo ye yagize ati:</strong></p><p><strong>Muri ikigihe twibuka kunshuro ya 23 Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi, Abanyarwanda aho bari hirya nohino bakomeze kwihangana kandi turangwa nibikorwa byo gufasha abayirokotse batishoboye.<br>Ndasaba urubyiruko byimwihariko gukoresha imbuga nkoranyambaga muguhangana n\'abafobya jenoside yakorewe abatutsi</strong></p><p><strong><em>Intore Tuyisenge uyobora urugaga nyarwanda rwa muzika tumubajije ubutumwa yaha abahanzi mubihe nkibi yagize ati:</em></strong></p><p><font size=\"4\"><strong><em>Bamwe mubahanzi bagize uruhare rukomeye muri Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi babiba urwango n\'ingengabitekerezo ya jenoside mu banyarwanda.<br>Abahanzi kuri ubu tugomba gukora ibishoboka umuco w\'ubumwe,urukondo,n\'ubufatanye duhora dutozwa tugomba kuwukwirakwiza kandi tukawuhererekanya n\'ubuvivi kugirango ibyabaye bitazongera ukundi <br></em></strong></font></p><p><font size=\"4\"><strong><em>Uyu ukaba ari umukoro wabahanzi wo kubiba umuco wamahoro No gusigasira ibyagezweho tunabyamamaze hose tubinyujije mu bihangano</em></strong></font></p><p><font size=\"4\"><i><br></i></font></p><p><i><b>Munyakazi uzwiho gucuranga inanga <br></b></i></p><p></p><div class=\"td-post-content\">\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"td-post-featured-image\"><figure><a class=\"td-modal-image\" href=\"http://izubarirashe.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Umucuranzi-Munyakazi-D_o-ari-kumwe-n%C3%86icyamamare-Jef-Neve-ku-rubyiniro.jpg\" data-caption=\"Umucuranzi Munyakazi DÃ©o ari kumwe nâ€™icyamamare Jef Neve ku rubyiniro (Ifoto/Interineti)\"><img class=\"entry-thumb td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"http://izubarirashe.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Umucuranzi-Munyakazi-D_o-ari-kumwe-n%C3%86icyamamare-Jef-Neve-ku-rubyiniro-696x464.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"umucuranzi-munyakazi-d_o-ari-kumwe-naeicyamamare-jef-neve-ku-rubyiniro\" height=\"464\" width=\"696\"></a><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"></figcaption></figure></div><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43048 td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"http://izubarirashe.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/15592172_1608930199415199_930091033_n.jpg\" alt=\"15592172_1608930199415199_930091033_n\" height=\"500\" width=\"750\"></p>\r\n<p><font size=\"5\"><b>&nbsp;Munyakazi</b></font></p><p><i><b>Twaje kwegera Munyakazi DEO umwe mubamaze kugera kure atubwira mumagambo ye ati:</b></i></p><p><i><b>\"Twibuke Genocide yakorewe abatutsi turwanya ingengabitekerezo ya Genocide, dushyigikira ibyiza twagezeho, kandi muhumure mukomere, ibi ntibizongera, dukomezanye nk\'abanyarwanda.</b></i></p><p><i><b>Tumubabjije icyo abona urubyiruko rukwiye gukora muri ibi bihe nawe yagarutse agira ati:</b></i></p><p><i><b>Ninshingano yaburi munyarwanda kurwanya ingenga bitekerezo no gupfobya genocide yakorewe abatutsi gusa nkurubyiruko tuyihashye cyane cyane dukoreshe imbuga nkoranyambaga\"</b></i></p><p><i><b>JABA STAR&nbsp; nawe yagize ubutumwa atangaza </b></i>: uyu azwi cyane mu ndirimbo tugushimiye kwakira abashyitsi<br></p><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pYtu0Qf.jpg\" width=\"526\"><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XvbMt4t.jpg\" height=\"450\" width=\"675\"><br><br><b><br><i>\"Njyewe&nbsp; intore jabastar mwizina ryihuriro rya abahanzi Gakondo mpagarariye baririmba. Twifatanije nabanyarwanda Bose </i><br></b><p><b><i> abahanzi muri rusange kwibuka kunshuro ya 23 jenoside yakorewe abatutsi muri 1994 .nsaba byumwihariko abahanzi muri rusange gukomeza kujya twitabira&nbsp; </i><br></b></p><p><b><i>cyane gahunda yogukora ibihangano indirimbo zo kwibuka tukabigira intego kandi tudategereje gusa ko itariki yo kwibuka igeze. nabasabaga ko nomubihe byose twabigira ihame kuko bifasha beshi kwibuka twiyubaka dusigasira ibyagezweho .</i></b></p><p><i><b>mwizina ry\'itorero ndangamuco imena ribyina imbyino gakondo nanone turasaba gukomeza kwitabira ibiganiro kugirango dukomeze kwibuka abacu bazize ubusa muri jenoside yakorewe abatutsi Imana ikomeze ibane namwe mwese muribibihe twibuka abacu batuvuyemo ikivi cyabo tuzacyusa\"</b><br></i></p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jggXcHS.jpg\" height=\"633\" width=\"633\">IMENA JABA STAR ABEREYE UMUYOBOZI<br></div><p><br></p><p><br></p></div>', '1491828446Kwibuka23-700x441.jpeg', 0, 'admin', 6, 10, 'break', 301),
(56, '2017-04-14 08:20:13', ' Ibintu 5 byâ€™ingirakamaro bikungahaye mu bishishwa byâ€™imineke abantu bajugunya', 'Akamaro kâ€™imineke kazwi na buri wese. Ariko umuneke ufite ibiwugize bigaragara inyuma (ibishishwa) mu kurya imineke ibishishwa bijugunywa kure kuko benshi babifata nkâ€™umwanda. Gusa ibi bishishwa abantu bajugunya ngo bifite akamaro gakomeye cyane ku buzima bwâ€™abantu bwa buri munsi.', '<header class=\"post-header cf\">\r\n	\r\n			\r\n\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		\r\n				<div class=\"heading cf\"><br>\r\n		\r\n		</div><br><a rel=\"prettyPhoto\" href=\"http://www.makuruki.rw/IMG/arton10424.jpg\" title=\"Ibintu 5 byâ€™ingirakamaro bikungahaye mu bishishwa byâ€™imineke abantu bajugunya\" itemprop=\"image\"><br>										\r\n				</a>\r\n								\r\n								\r\n					\r\n\r\n		\r\n			\r\n	</header>Dore akamaro kâ€™ibishishwa byâ€™imineke nâ€™uko wabikoresha bikakugirira umumaro mu mubiri wawe.\r\n\r\n<p><strong>1.ibishishwa byâ€™imineke bituma amenyo yereruka cyane</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abahanga bavuga ko iyo ukoresheje ibishishwa byimineke ku gice kiba \r\ngifashe kâ€™umuneke ukagisiga ku menyo mu gihe cyâ€™ibyumweru bibiri, ubona \r\nimpinduka nyinshi ku menyo yawe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2.bikuraho ibiheri ku mubiri</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nukoresha ibishishwa byâ€™imineke ubisiga mu maso, bizagufasha gukuraho burundu ibiheri byo mu maso.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3 Ibishishwa byâ€™imineke bifasha kugabanya uburibwe</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mu gihe ufite ahantu uri kuribwa bikomotse ku bushye cyangwa ikindi \r\nkintu cyatuma ugira uburibwe bukabije, ngo ushobora gukoresha ibi \r\nbishishwa ubisigaho nyuma yâ€™igihe gito wumva ubiribwe bugenda bushira.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>4.ibishishwa byâ€™imineke bifasha kugabanya ibiro</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Birazwi neza ko imineke ikungahaye kuri potasiyumu(potassium) ariko \r\nabantu benshi ntibazi ko 40% byâ€™iyo potasiyumu biba biri mu bishishwa \r\nbyâ€™imineke, ifite uruhare mu kugabanya ibiro kuko bigizwe nâ€™ibindi bintu\r\n bituma umuntu ubikoresheje aganuka ibiro kuburyo bugaragara.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>5 ibishishwa byimineke bifasha kurinda kanseri yâ€™uruhu</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nyuma yo kurya umuneke umuntu ashobora kujya yisiga ku ruhu \r\nibishishwa byawo ukoresheje igice cyâ€™igishishwa kiba gifashe ku muneke \r\nnyirizina kuko birinda abantu indwara zimwe na zimwe harimo na kanseri \r\nyâ€™uruhu.</p>', '1492150813imineke.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 10, 'sub', 162);
