(64, '2017-04-23 16:58:05', ' Irebere amafoto Utari uzi yâ€™Imiterere ya KIGALI CONVENTION CENTER', 'Kigali Convention Centre igizwe nâ€™ibice bitatu harimo icyumba cyâ€™inama kinini gishobora kwakira icyarimwe abantu ibihumbi bibiri na Magana atanu bicaye neza..', '<p><br><strong>Inyubako Kigali Convention Centre yatashywe \r\ntariki ya 08 Nyakanga 2016 aho yatashywe ku mugaragaro na Perezida wa \r\nRepuburika yâ€™u Rwanda Paul Kagame, ni imwe mu nyubako nini mu Rwanda \r\nyubatswe mu gihe kigera ku myaka itandatu ikaba mu Murenge wa Kimihurura\r\n mu Karere ka Gasabo</strong></p><p>Iyi nyubako yubatse ku buso bwa Hegitari 12,6 ikaba igizwe nâ€™igice \r\ncya Hotel Radisson Blue ikaba yaratwaye akayabo kâ€™amafranga arenga \r\nmiliyoni 320 zâ€™amadorari yâ€™amerika.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tukaba tugiye kubereka bimwe mu bice byâ€™ingenzi bigize iyi nyubako mu\r\n mafoto, yubatswe mu buryo bugaragaza isura nâ€™umuco byâ€™u Rwanda.</p><p><span class=\"spip_document_17682 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<img class=\"no-display appear\" src=\"http://www.makuruki.rw/local/cache-vignettes/L702xH467/dsc_0114-4-2bbe4.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"467\" width=\"702\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><i>Igice cya Kigali Convention Centre</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"spip_document_17716 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<img class=\"no-display appear\" src=\"http://www.makuruki.rw/local/cache-vignettes/L702xH467/dsc_0111-5-4ac2d.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"467\" width=\"702\"></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><i>Igice cya Hotel inyuma </i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"spip_document_17681 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<img class=\"no-display appear\" src=\"http://www.makuruki.rw/local/cache-vignettes/L702xH467/dsc_0111-4-03221.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"467\" width=\"702\"></span><br class=\"autobr\">\r\n<i><br class=\"autobr\">\r\nInyubako zombi zihuzwa nâ€™inzira itwikiriye (Hotel na Convention)</i></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"spip_document_17684 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">