(67, '2017-04-26 23:30:59', ' IREBERE AHANTU HADASAZWE HAFITE ubwiza nyaburanga 20 ukwiye gusura mu Rwanda', ' URwanda ni igihugu cyâ€™ubwiza nâ€™uburanga kamere. Gitatswe nâ€™imisozi miremire nâ€™ahantu nyaburanga henshi huje ibibaya, inzuzi, imigezi nâ€™ibiyaga. Uwageze muri iki gihugu hari ahantu agomba gusura kugira ngo arusheho kukimenyaho byinshi kuko ari igihugu kihariye.', '<p><i>U Rwanda ni igihugu cyâ€™ubwiza nâ€™uburanga kamere. Gitatswe \r\nnâ€™imisozi miremire nâ€™ahantu nyaburanga henshi huje ibibaya, inzuzi, \r\nimigezi nâ€™ibiyaga. Uwageze muri iki gihugu hari ahantu agomba gusura \r\nkugira ngo arusheho kukimenyaho byinshi kuko ari  igihugu kihariye.</i></p>\r\n<p>Byongeye kandi, u Rwanda rutatswe nâ€™urunyurane rwâ€™inyamanswa \r\nnâ€™urusobe rwâ€™ibindi binyabuzima bikurura ba mukerarugendo benshi ku \r\nburyo uwageze muri iki gihugu ntatemberere aha hantu twashyize ku \r\nrutonde, aba anyazwe bidasubirwaho.</p>\r\n<p>Ntiwarondora ahantu nyaburanga nâ€™ahandi henshi watemberera mu rwa \r\nGasabo ngo uhamareyo;irebere 20 twaguhitiyemo.<br></p><p><strong>1. Pariki yâ€™Igihugu yâ€™Ibirunga</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 640px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH388/slide-166dc.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"388\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:800;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L800xH500/1403715916_volcano-31ce9.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"500\" width=\"800\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Kimwe mu byiza bitatse Intara yâ€™Amajyaruguru yâ€™u Rwanda ni ibirunga \r\nbitanu; Karisimbi, Bisoke, Sabyinyo, Gahinga na Muhabura. Ibi birunga \r\nbiri mu munani bigize uruhererekane rwâ€™urusobe rwâ€™ibirunga byo ku isunzu\r\n rya Congo Nili.</p>\r\n<p>Aha hantu nyaburanga kandi hakunzwe kuba harangwa nâ€™imvura, \r\namashyamba, nâ€™imigano. Ikirunga gisumba ibindi ni Kalisimbi, gifite \r\nmetero 4,507 zâ€™ubutumburuke.</p>\r\n<p>Ibi birunga byirengeye mu misozi miremire itatse uturere twa Musanze \r\nna Rubavu, hamwe mu hantu hakunda gutemberwa na ba mukerarugendo \r\nbanyuranye.</p>\r\n<p>Ibi birunga byâ€™u Rwanda bihana imbibi nâ€™ibirunga birimo ibyazimye byo muri Congo nka Mikeno, Bisoke na Nyiragongo.</p>\r\n<p>Iyi pariki irimo kandi amashyamba yâ€™amoko menshi yâ€™ibihingwa nâ€™ibiti birebire bigize ubwiza nâ€™uburanga bukurura abantu.</p>\r\n<p>Ubu butumburuke nibwo butuma u Rwanda ruba hamwe mu hantu hake cyane \r\nku Isi haba ingagi kuko zikunda iyi misozi miremire. Izi ngagi ziri \r\nhake, dore ko ziri no mu bwoko bwâ€™inyamaswa buri gucika cyane ku Isi. \r\nUbu habarwa ingagi zo mu birunga zigera kuri 720 ku Isi yose, kandi zose\r\n ziherere mu majyaruguru yâ€™igihugu cyâ€™u Rwanda, mu Majyepfo ya Uganda \r\nndetse no mu burasirazuba bwa Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Congo.</p>\r\n<p>Muri iyi parike harimo kandi nâ€™ibiyaga birimo icya Burera nâ€™icya \r\nRuhondo hamwe nâ€™indi migezi iteye amabengeza kuyitegera uyireba.</p>\r\n<p>Iyi pariki yatangijwe mu mwaka wâ€™ 1925 ikaba iri mu za mbere zabayeho\r\n muri Afurika. Irimo ikigo cyâ€™Ubushakashatsi kizwi ku izina rya \r\n\"Karisoke Research Center\" cyashinzwe na Diana Fossey, impuguke mu \r\nbyâ€™ubumenyi bwâ€™inyamaswa wakomokaga muri Amerika.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Ikiyaga cya Kivu </strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:800;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L800xH531/004-gisenyi-lake-kivu-1024x680-8111d.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"531\" width=\"800\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/late-afternoon-serena-hotel-lake-kivu-rwanda-9dbc5.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Ntako bisa kuruhukira ku Kiyaga cya Kivu kiza ku mwanya wa gatandatu \r\nmu bunini muri Afurika. Uwatembereye aha aba yitegeye ibirunga, mu \r\nmahumbezi yâ€™imisozi miremire igize Akarere ka Afurika yâ€™u Burasirazuba. \r\nNiho hantu heza cyane hari amazi ha mbere mu Rwanda wasohokera. Hari \r\namahoteli meza kandi ari ku rwego mpuzamahanga harimo na Serena Hotel.</p>\r\n<p>Kuruhukira ku mucanga waho, koga amazi yaho cyangwa kuhafatira \r\nakarahure wota akazuba wumva amahumbezi aturuka mu kiyaga nâ€™ibindi byiza\r\n bya Kivu byagufasha kurangiza weekend yawe neza.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Kigaki convention centre</strong></p><p><span class=\"spip_document_17682 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<img class=\"no-display appear\" src=\"http://www.makuruki.rw/local/cache-vignettes/L702xH467/dsc_0114-4-2bbe4.jpg\" alt=\"\" height=\"467\" width=\"702\"></span></p><strong>Inyubako Kigali Convention Centre yatashywe \r\ntariki ya 08 Nyakanga 2016 aho yatashywe ku mugaragaro na Perezida wa \r\nRepuburika yâ€™u Rwanda Paul Kagame, ni imwe mu nyubako nini mu Rwanda \r\nyubatswe mu gihe kigera ku myaka itandatu ikaba mu Murenge wa Kimihurura\r\n mu Karere ka Gasabo</strong> Iyi nyubako yubatse ku buso bwa Hegitari 12,6 ikaba igizwe nâ€™igice \r\ncya Hotel Radisson Blue ikaba yaratwaye akayabo kâ€™amafranga arenga \r\nmiliyoni 320 zâ€™amadorari yâ€™amerika.ni inzu nziza cyane iri mu&nbsp; Rwagasabo ifite ubwiza&nbsp; bwihariye.<br><p><strong>4. Ingoro Ndangamurage yo kwa Richard Kandt</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/6811291-44762.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Richard Kandt, umukoloni washinze akanayobora Kigali, yanavumbuye \r\nisoko ya Nile mu 1898, mu ishyamba rya Nyungwe ribyara Nyabarongo, \r\nnkâ€™uko bigaragazwa nâ€™urubuga rwa wikipedia.</p>\r\n<p>Ntibigira uko bisa gusura inzu yo mu buryo bugezweho ya mbere \r\nyubatswe muri Kigali mu myaka 100 ishize. Iyi nzu yubatswe na Richard \r\nKandt, akaba ari nawe wayibagamo nkâ€™inzu ye yâ€™ubuturo nâ€™ibiro byo \r\ngukoreramo dore ko ari nawe wabaye Rezida (RÃ©sident) wa mbere wâ€™u \r\nRwanda.</p>\r\n<p>Usuye iyi nzu iri ku Muhima, wabona intebe Kandt yicaragaho yandika, \r\nameza yandikiragaho, igitabo yanditse cyâ€™ukuntu yabonye isoko ya Nile mu\r\n ishyamba rya Nyungwe, amapine yâ€™imodoka ye nâ€™ayimodoka zabayeho mu gihe\r\n cyâ€™intambara ya mbere yâ€™Isi yose nâ€™ibindi bya kera.</p>\r\n<p>Uwageze muri iyi Ngoro kandi asobanurirwa ibijyanye nâ€™amateka yâ€™Isi \r\nakanagira amahirwe yo kwerekwa inyamaswa ziganjemo izâ€™ibikururanda \r\nnkâ€™inzoka zo mu bwoko butandukanye burimo impiri, uruziramire, inshira, \r\nikiryambeba, Cobra, inziramire, insharwatsi, nâ€™iniri (inzoka zâ€™umukara) \r\nnka bimwe mu bigize amoko yâ€™inyamanswa ziri mu mateka yâ€™u Rwanda.</p>\r\n<p><strong>5. Akarwa kâ€™Amahoro ku Kibuye</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/img-20121124-01483-5c31c.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Aha ni ku karwa k\'Amahoro mu kiyaga cya Kivu</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/1403715588_kibuye_4-1b564.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Ku wifuza kurangiza weekend neza, Akarwa kâ€™Amahoro ni hamwe mu hantu \r\nheza wahitamo ukanyurwa nâ€™akayaga gahehera gaturuka mu kiyaga cya Kivu. \r\nNiwo mutima wâ€™uburanga nâ€™ubwiza bwâ€™iki kiyaga.</p>\r\n<p>Aka karwa kari mu Kivu hagati, mu rugendo rwâ€™iminota nka 20 mu bwato \r\nuvuye ku nkombe. Ni kamwe mu turwa 16 turi mu Karere ka Karongi kakaba \r\nmu byiza bitatse aka gace.</p>\r\n<p>Habera imikino inyuranye, aho uba unareba zimwe mu nyamanswa zirimo \r\ninkende ukanabasha kwitegera ikiyaga neza ureba nâ€™amashyamba meza agize \r\nKivu. Ku bahageze bahifotoreza amafoto yâ€™urwibutso rwâ€™ibihe bidasanzwe \r\nbagiriye kuri aka karwa.</p>\r\n<p><strong>6. Pariki yâ€™Igihugu yâ€™Akagera </strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:500;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L500xH330/giraffes-at-akagera-national-park-2-fc633.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"330\" width=\"500\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Inzovu Mutware, twiga, Impala, imisambi, intare, isatura, imbogo, \r\ningwe, musumbashyamba (giraffe) izi ni zimwe mu nyamanswa ziba mu Rwanda\r\n ariko utapfa kubona udatembereye mu Ntara yâ€™i Burasirazuba muri Parike \r\nyâ€™Akagera. Uretse izi nyamanswa, muri iyi Pariki, ifite ubuso bwa 1,200 \r\nkmÂ², unabasha kuhabona imigezi inyuranye irimo uwâ€™Akagera.</p>\r\n<p>Hari kandi amahumbezi aturuka mu kibaya cyâ€™imbibi zâ€™u Rwanda na \r\nTanzaniya, aho bakwakiriza amafi arobwa mu biyaga byinshi bigize aka \r\nkarere.</p>\r\n<p><strong>7. Ikiyaga cya Muhazi Kayonza</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH425/picture-3-09dc3.png?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"425\" width=\"640\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Uyu ni umusambi, bumwe mu bwoko bw\'inyamanswa zigaragara ku Kiyaga cya Muhazi</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Mu Karere ka Kayonza, ku muhanda uva Kayonza ujya Kagitumba, niho \r\nhari ikiyaga cya Muhazi. Ni mu birometero bike uturutse ku muhanda ugana\r\n mu Mujyi wa Kigali.<br class=\"autobr\">\r\nAha niho ubonera ubwiza nyaburanga bwâ€™umwimerere bwâ€™u Rwanda. Ushobora \r\nkuharuhukira witegeye imisozi myiza isobetse nâ€™ibibaya nâ€™imigezi bitemba\r\n amazi.</p>\r\n<p>Wakirwa nâ€™abakozi ba Jambo Beach, iyi akaba ari hoteli yubatse kuri \r\niki kiyaga. Wahisemo kuhatemberera, uzahabona ibintu byinshi bigufasha \r\nkuruhuka harimo nâ€™imisambi iba ikinagira hafi yâ€™amazi.</p>\r\n<p>Iki kiyaga kizenguruka kikagera no mu Ntara yâ€™Amajyaruguru, muri \r\nGicumbi, giteye amabengeza, kandi kiri ahantu heza wakwishimira kugera.</p>\r\n<p><strong>8. Pariki yâ€™Igihugu ya Nyungwe</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH427/8989336480_639be75147_k-75270.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"427\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH427/8989300046_aeab65d779_k-cea8c.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"427\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 427px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L427xH640/1403715916_tea_plant-f82aa.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"640\" width=\"427\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Ishyamba rya Nyungwe riri mu mashyamba amaze imyaka ibihumbi amagana \r\nribayeho ku buryo riri mu mashyamba amaze igihe kirekire muri Afurika.</p>\r\n<p>Nyungwe ifite imisozi miremire irimo uwa Bigugu ufite uburebure bwa \r\nmetero 2950. hari inyoni zâ€™amoko 310 harimo amoko 26 asanzwe amenyerewe.</p>\r\n<p>Muri iyi pariki hari urusobe rwâ€™ibindi binyabuzima rwâ€™ingeri zose, inyamanswa ndetse nâ€™ibimera.</p>\r\n<p>Muri iyi pariki kandi niho hubatswe ikiraro cyo mu bushorishori kizwi\r\n ku izina rya \"Canopy Walkway\" nacyo kiri mu bikurura ba mukerarugendo \r\nbenshi mu Rwanda.</p>\r\n<p>Iyo ugiye gusura iyi parike kandi, ubasha kubona igihingwa cyâ€™icyayi,\r\n kimwe mu bintu bihingwa byiza bigaragaza ubwiza bwâ€™u Rwanda.</p>\r\n<p><strong>9. Kibeho</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:480;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L480xH640/yezu-nyirimpuhwe-81e84.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"640\" width=\"480\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH427/9175957418_bdde3f9d33_k-781d7.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"427\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Gusura Kibeho iri ku musozi wa Nyarushishi mu Karere ka Nyaruguru ho \r\nNtara yâ€™Amajyepfo yâ€™u Rwanda byaba kimwe mu bitekerezo byiza byo \r\nkurushaho kumenya neza ibijyanye nâ€™amabonekerwa yahabereye mu 1981.</p>\r\n<p>Wamenya neza uko Bikiramariya yagiye aganira mu bihe binyuranye \r\nnâ€™abakobwa batatu; Alphonsine Mumureke, Natalie Mukamazimpaka na Marie \r\nClaire Mukangango bo mu ishuri ryisumbuye ryâ€™ i Kibeho riyoborwa \r\nnâ€™ababikira bo mu Muryango wa Benebikira.</p>\r\n<p>Kibeho ni umujyi muto ariko watoranyijwe ku mugabane wose wa Afurika,\r\n ukaba ari wo ushyirwaho ishusho ya Yezu Nyirâ€™Impuhwe ifite uburebure \r\nbwa metero esheshatu (6), igapima ibiro magana cyenda na mirongo itanu \r\n(950 kg), ubusanzwe igaragara kuri buri mugabane mu yigize isi, muri \r\nAfurika ikaba iri i Kibeho.</p>\r\n<p>Ni heza, hari amahoteli nâ€™ibindi bikorwa byorohereza ba mukerarugendo\r\n kandi hagufasha kugira byinshi wiyungura nâ€™ibyo uhindura mu kwemera \r\nkwawe urushaho kwegera Imana mu masengesho.</p>\r\n<p>Igihe cyose wahasura ariko bikaba byiza kuhajya kuwa 15 Kanama kuko \r\nari wo munsi mukuru hizihirizwa ijyanwa mu ijuru rya Bikira Mariya \r\nhakoraniye imbaga nini yâ€™abantu baba baturutse imihanda yose.</p>\r\n<p><strong>10. Ku Nzu i Gisenyi</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:550;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L550xH366/1908073_10204326068292351_6537046255182086276_n-f77c4.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"366\" width=\"550\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Mu nyubako gakondo, hafi yâ€™ikiyaga cya Kivu aha hantu hitwa Ku Nzu ni\r\n hamwe abashyingiwe bakunze kujya kurira ukwezi kwabo kwa buki.</p>\r\n<p>Niba wararambiwe kurara mu mahoteli, uri umuntu ukunda udushya aha \r\nhantu hakubera heza kuharuhukira. Izi nyubako zubatse ku mazi zijyanye \r\nnâ€™imisozi yirengeye ihakikije, ku buryo hahora amafu nâ€™ikirere cyiza ku \r\nwifuza kuruhuka koko.</p>\r\n<p><strong>11. Ingoro Ndangamurage yâ€™u Rwanda</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:754;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L754xH389/ethnographic_museum-364c6.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"389\" width=\"754\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Ugeze i Huye muri Butare ubwirwa na buri wese ko uyu mujyi ari \r\nigicumbi gihatse amateka yâ€™u Rwanda. Aha niho hari inzu usura ukamenya \r\nneza amateka yose yâ€™u Rwanda. Hari amafoto yerekana imigenzo yose \r\nyakorwaga, imyambarire yâ€™Abanyarwanda bo hambere, imibereho yabo nâ€™uko \r\nubuzima bwose bwagiye butera imbere kugeza ubu.</p>\r\n<p>Ku giciro kijyanye nâ€™uwo uri we nâ€™aho uturutse, utemberezwa ibice \r\nbinyuranye biranga iyi Ngoro aho usobanukirwa neza ibijyanye nâ€™amateka \r\nyâ€™u Rwanda byose.</p>\r\n<p><strong>12. Ingoro Ndangamurage ya Nyanza- mu Rukari</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:600;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L600xH403/151c634392-8c0df.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"403\" width=\"600\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:960;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L960xH661/nyanza-2-66d7b.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"661\" width=\"960\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Ni mu birometero 88 uvuye mu murwa mukuru wa Kigali. Ni mu Mujyi wa \r\nNyanza, aho bakunze kwita mu Rukari; niho hari amateka yâ€™abami, aho \r\nutambagizwa ingoro Mutara II Rudahigwa yatuyemo kandi yubatswe mu buryo \r\nbwo hambere.</p>\r\n<p>Ni ingoro ishamaje yubakishijwe ibikoresho bya Kinyarwanda nkâ€™uko yari imeze mu kinyejana cya 19.</p>\r\n<p>Uzashimishwa no kuhasanga inka zifite amahembe maremare zâ€™inyarwanda \r\nzizwi ku izina ryâ€™Inyambo, kimwe mu byâ€™ingenzi bigize umuco nyarwanda. \r\nNi ku gasozi gaturanye na Rukari kitwa Mwima, hari umusezero wâ€™Umwami \r\nMutara III nâ€™imva yâ€™umugore we, umwamikazi Rosalie Gicanda.</p>\r\n<p><strong>13. Umusozi wâ€™ubukerarugendo wa Rubavu </strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:448;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L448xH299/uyu_niwo_musozi_wa_rubavu_uri_gutunganwa_kugira_ngo_hazabe_ahantu_nyaburanga_foto_antoinette_-fd2eb-e25d0.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"299\" width=\"448\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Mu bwiza gakondo bubereye ijisho, Umusozi wa Rubavu ni ahantu \r\nwatemberera ugasobanukirwa neza inkomoko yâ€™izina u Rwanda rwâ€™Imisozi \r\nIgihumbi. Uyu musozi wubatseho utuyira muyoborwamo nâ€™ababishinzwe \r\nbabatemberezamo babasobanurira ibyâ€™amateka yawo.</p>\r\n<p>Ugeze hejuru ku gasongero uba witegeye Umujyi wa Rubavu ureba no muri\r\n Congo ukanyurwa nâ€™uburanga bwabyo. Nta bikorwa remezo byinshi byari \r\nbyakorwa kuri uyu musozi ariko hateganywaga gushyirwa amahoteli \r\nnâ€™amaresitora ku buryo kuhatemberera byaba igitekerezo cyiza.</p>\r\n<p><strong>14. Ikiyaga cya Mirayi mu Bugesera</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/1971104_orig-f4e3c.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Ni ku muhanda ugana i Burundi, mu Karere ka Bugesera ahitwa i \r\nGashora. Aha ni ahantu heza ho gutemberera muri itsinda ryâ€™inshuti \r\nzishyize hamwe. Kuri iki kiyaga munezezwa no kurangazwa no kureba uko \r\nbaroba namwe babibigisha.</p>\r\n<p>Hari ibyo kunywa nâ€™ibyo kurya byâ€™ubwoko bwose nâ€™ibyumba byiza mu gihe wifuza kuhamara umwanya ukaharuhukira.</p>\r\n<p><strong>15. Ibere rya Bigogwe</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/11787853-ac844.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Ababonye uyu musozi w\'urutare batangazwa n\'izina witwa rya \"Ibere rya Bigogwe\"</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Umuntu wese unyuze ku muhanda munini uva Musanze werekeza Rubavu iyo \r\nageze mu Murenge wa Kanzenze ahari uyu musozi muremure witwa \"Ibere rya \r\nBigogwe\" atangazwa nâ€™uko ari muremure cyane.</p>\r\n<p>Uhaciye wese ahavana amakuru avuga ko abasirikare bo hambere bajyaga \r\nbahakorera imyitozo yo ku rwego rwâ€™ubuparakomando bawuzamukaho ku \r\nmigozi.</p>\r\n<p>Gusa uhasuye wabiteguye nibwo warushaho kumenya amateka nyayo yâ€™uko \r\nuyu musozi uri mu Kagari ka Nyamirango, wiswe gutya mu rwego rwo \r\nkuzirikana umukobwa witwaga Nyirabigogwe wahabaye wari ufite amabere \r\nateze nkâ€™uyu musozi.</p>\r\n<p>Aha wahasanga bamwe mu bakambwe bari bawuturiye kuva mu 1926, \r\nbashobora kukwibwirira imbonankubone uko uyu Nyamirango yakundaga \r\nkuharagirira inyana nâ€™uko yaje kuwitirirwa.</p>\r\n<p>Uyu musozi wâ€™urutare rurerure ruteye koko nkâ€™ibere, ni kimwe mu byiza\r\n nyaburanga utembereye muri aka gace wasura ukazahorana urwo rugendo \r\nnkâ€™urwibutso ku mutima.</p>\r\n<p><strong>16. Nyabugogo</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH427/10399703006_bb1f660202_k-37583.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"427\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Abahanzi nyarwanda bahavumbuye mbere batangiye kuhagaragaza mu \r\nmashusho yâ€™indirimbo zabo, ariko uko iminsi itera imbere aha hantu \r\nhagenda harushaho kuba ahasurwa nâ€™abâ€™ingeri zose. Hubatse hoteli yakira \r\nabakiriya ikabafasha kugira ibihe byiza bagatemberezwa muri iki cyuzi \r\ncya Nyabugogo.</p>\r\n<p>Uba witegeye imisozi miremire ya Gisozi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>17. Muhazi ku Rwesero</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/14644787-0b73c.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L640xH480/copy2ofimg_2016-b58e3.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"480\" width=\"640\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Kuba ari hafi yâ€™Umujyi wa Kigali bituma benshi basohokera aha hantu \r\nhaherereye mu Ntara yâ€™Amajyaruguru, ahahoze hitwa Byumba. Ni ku mazi, ku\r\n Kiyaga cya Muhazi, aho ubishaka utemberezwa mu bwato ukazenguruka iki \r\nkiyaga unyurwa nâ€™amahumbezi ya Muhazi.</p>\r\n<p>Ni hafi yâ€™Iseminari Nto ya Rwesero, ku muhanda wâ€™ibitaka aho niba \r\nuvuye hanze yâ€™u Rwanda nibura wavuga ko wageze ahantu hâ€™igiturage. \r\nImyubakire ya kinyarwanda yâ€™inyubako ziri kuri iki kiyaga, ifi nâ€™inkoko \r\nbyaho ni bimwe mu bishobora gutuma uharara ukazahora wibuka ijoro ryo ku\r\n Rwesero. Haba kandi imisambi nâ€™utundi dukoko tubereye ijisho kutureba \r\nuruhuka.</p>\r\n<p>Bigerageze uzambwira!</p>\r\n<p><strong>18. Ikirwa cya Nkombo</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:420;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L420xH340/1377286873thecon-db99e.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"340\" width=\"420\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:640;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Wakoreye urugendo i Cyangungu, ntiwavuga ko wahombye ngo ni uko \r\nrwakubanye rurerure. Amavunane yose wumva ashize ugeze kuri iki kirwa \r\nukaganira nâ€™abaturage baho wumva ubuzima babayeho. Ni Abanyarwanda ariko\r\n bafite izina bihariye bitwa ryâ€™Abashi. Kuri iki kirwa babayeho ubuzima \r\nbwabo bihariye mu mibereho yâ€™abatuye  rwagati mu Kiyaga cya Kivu.</p>\r\n<p>Ururimi rwabo usanga mu duce twa Kamembe, Busekanka, Rusizi, Goma, \r\nNkombo ni Ikinyarwanda ariko kivanzemo Igiswayire kuko baturanye \r\nnâ€™igihugu cya Congo.</p>\r\n<p>Haratangaje kandi byagushimisha kugera muri aka gace. Kugera kuri iki\r\n kirwa bigutwara iminota icumi, ni mu birometero 11 uvuye mu murwa \r\nmukuru wa Kamembe.</p>\r\n<p>Ntibyoroshye kuhabona icyo kurya kuko hasa nko mu giturage gisanzwe, \r\nariko unyurwa no kubona ubuzima bwâ€™Abanyarwanda batunzwe ahanini \r\nnâ€™uburobyi.</p>\r\n<p>Iki kirwa cya Nkombo kiza mu birwa binini bigize ikiyaga cya Kivu, nyuma yâ€™ibindi birimo Ijwi, Iwawa nâ€™ibindi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>19. I Rugende ahaba Amafarasi</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:600;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L600xH400/p1450336-c1ba1-9d015.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"400\" width=\"600\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Aha ni aho bita Rugende, i Kabuga hazwi cyane ikigo gihuriramo urubyiruko cya Rugende Training Center.</p>\r\n<p>Ni hamwe muri hake haba amafarasi mu Rwanda. Aha ni hamwe mu hantu \r\nhatuje wasohokera hegereye Kigali, cyo kimwe nâ€™uko wajya ahitwa Juru \r\nPark ku i Rebero, cyangwa se Meraneza i Nyamirambo. Aha hose ndondoye ni\r\n ahantu hitaruye ho gato Kigali, heza hari ubusitani nâ€™ibindi bikorwa \r\nnkâ€™izi nyamanswa warangarira ukaruhuka.</p>\r\n<p>Aha ni mu nkengero zâ€™umujyi ku buryo bidasaba igihe kinini cyo gutegura kuhajya.</p>\r\n<p><strong>20. Urutare rwa Kamegeri mu Ruhango</strong></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:860;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L860xH286/urutare-rwa-kamegeri-b0eff.gif?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"286\" width=\"860\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:719;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L719xH285/sdfsd-d6a61.jpg?1490653335\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" border=\"0\" height=\"285\" width=\"719\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Bivugwa ko uru rutare kera rwatukuraga nyuma y\'aho rutwikiweho umutware Kamegeri</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Uru rutare ruri mu Karere ka Ruhango rufite amateka menshi; aha niho \r\numutware Kamegeri yatwikiwe ku ngoma yâ€™umwami Mibambwe Sekarongoro \r\nMutabazi nyuma yâ€™aho asabiye iki gihano abanyabyaha.</p>\r\n<p>Uru rutare kuva icyo gihe rwahise rumwitirirwa, kandi bivugwa ko kuva icyo gihe rwakomeje gutukura.</p>\r\n<p>Binavugwa kandi ko uru rutare rwabagaho nta zina rugira ariko kuva \r\naho rutwikiweho Kamegeri rwakomeje kujya rumwitirirwa mu kwibuka uko \r\nyari umutware wâ€™umugome cyane wafataga ibyemezo bikarishye kugeza ubwo \r\nurwo yaciriye uwari wagomeye umwami ari we ruhitanye atwikirwa ku \r\nrutare.</p>\r\n<p>Ese ni gute utasura aha hantu, ngo wiyumvire ubuhamya bwâ€™abahatuye?</p><p>&nbsp;aha hantu hose hamwe nahandi tutavuze, hafite umwihariko ko hafitanye isano cyane numuco wabanyarwanda.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></p>', '1493242259RWANDA NZIZA.png', 0, 'admin', 2, 6, 'head', 508),
(68, '2017-04-28 23:58:04', ' MENYA Inkomoko yâ€™amaharakubiri ku mugani â€œYanyoye nzobyaâ€', 'Uyu mugani baca ngo: â€œYanyoye nzobyaâ€ cyangwa bagututse ngo â€œkanywe nzobyaâ€ wakomotse ku muntu witwaga Nzobya wâ€™i Ngarurira mu Buyenzi; yari umutoni wa Mibambwe Sentabyo, ahasaga umwaka wa 800.', '<p>Bawuca iyo babonye umuntu wanyoye agasinda cyane, bimwe bavuga ngo: â€œYabaye Sabizezeâ€<br>\r\nUwo mugabo Nzobya rero, yabaye umutoni wâ€™akadasohoka kwa Mibambwe \r\nSentabyo; bukeye Mibambwe afatwa nâ€™ubushita buramwica, agwa i Remera rya\r\n Rukoma na Ngamba (Taba, Gitarama).</p>\r\n<p>Amaze gupfa umuhungu we Gahindiro umuzunguye, yangana na ba sewabo, \r\nabo bitaga ibigina bya Ndabarasa Semugaza wari umutware wâ€™umutwe \r\nwâ€™ingabo zitwaga Urukatsa, afatanya na Nzobya banesha ibigina.</p>\r\n<p>Hanyuma ariko Nyiratunga (nyina wa Gahindiro), yanga Semugaza, bituma\r\n acikana nâ€™Urukatsa bajya mu Ndorwa. Nzobya asigara mu Rwanda.</p>\r\n<p>Hanyuma aho Gahindiro amariye gutoneshereza Rugaju rwa Mutimbo, \r\namugabiye akatsi ko haruguru yâ€™inzira no hepfo yayo, Nzobya asubira \r\ninyuma ntibamurebe neza. Bigeze aho arasezera ajya iwe mu Buyenzi, ku \r\nmusozi witwa Ngarurira.</p>\r\n<p>Amazeyo iminsi, abantu bâ€™amacuti ye baza kumubwira ko ibintu bimumereye nabi I Bwami.<br>\r\nNzobya ariyumvira, ati: â€œUruzi Semugaza ngo acike ansige mu Rwanda!â€ \r\nAhera ko akoresha amakoro yo gutura Gahindiro i Rubona rwa Gihara muri \r\nKomini Runda (Gitarama).</p>\r\n<p>Ahaguruka iwe i Ngarurira ataha mu i Ceni ku Bisi bya Huye; mu \r\ngitondo arahava ataha i Mayunzwe mu Nduga (Tambwe, Gitarama); bukeye \r\nataha i Gihinga na Ruzege mu nsi ya Kamonyi (muri Komini Taba).</p>\r\n<p>Ahageze araza inkera, arasinda nâ€™abagaragu be, inzoga imaze kumusaga \r\nabwira abagaragu be, ati: â€œUbonye ngo databuja Mibambwe ansige mu gihugu\r\n none mbe nsigaye inyuma ya Rugaju; mbese mwene databuja Semugaza we \r\ngucika akansiga mu Rwanda nabitewe nâ€™iki?â€ Ati: â€œUbu ndagiye nsange \r\ndatabuja Mibambwe ku musezero i Rutare, ningera ku mva ye niyahure \r\nmpwane na we!â€ Ubwo ayo yose yayavugishwaga nâ€™inzoga!</p>\r\n<p>Nuko abagaragu be baramuhana arabananira, ateshwa inzira ijya i \r\nRubona kwa Gahindiro, aboneza iyâ€™epfo ku Kavuza nâ€™Uruyenzi, yambuka \r\nNyabarongo ataha i Kinyinya mu Bwanacyambwe (muri Komini \r\nRubungo(Kigali)).</p>\r\n<p>Amaze kuhagera, na none araza inkera. Isindwe riramudanangira akomeza\r\n ya migabo ye yo kwiyabura ntiyagaruka. I Bwami bamenya ko acitse nka \r\nSemugaza, bohereza ingabo zo kumutangira ngo zimufate.</p>\r\n<p>Nzobya amaze kubyumva arahaguruka ngo acikane nâ€™ingabo ze nka \r\nSemugaza. Ariko abantu babonye ko babungerezwa nâ€™umusinzi, bamwegukaho \r\nbasubira i Gihara kwa Gahindiro barayoboka.</p>\r\n<p>Nzobya na we abonye abantu bamushizeho, yambuka Nyabarongo aboneza \r\niyâ€™i Buliza; ageze ku mugezi wa Rusasa na Ntarabana, inyota iramurembya,\r\n ajya mu mugezi anywa amazi, amaze kuyahuga ariyahura arapfa. Icyo \r\ncyambu yanywereyemo cyitwa Akazi, ni ho havuye ijambo rivugwa nâ€™ubu, ryo\r\n kunywa Akazi ka Rusasa.</p>\r\n<p>Ayo mafuti yose rero Nzobya yakoze kuva ku Kamonyi kugera i Rusasa na\r\n Ntarabana, yayakoreshwaga nâ€™itende ryâ€™inturire(Ikigage cyirimo ubuki) \r\nyihoshyaga; ni yo bise nzobya, babonye urupfu rwe ruturutse ku itende \r\nryâ€™ubuki nâ€™inturire ; barabimwitirira byitwa Nzobya.</p>\r\n<p>Kuva ubwo inzoga yose yâ€™itende bayita nzobya. Ni byo bavugira ku \r\nmuntu isindwe ryakoresheje ibidakorwa, bati: â€œNoneho si inzoga yanyoye, \r\nyanyoye nzobyaâ€.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Uburyo bwa kabiri bwâ€™inkomoko yâ€™uyu mugani</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ariko kandi kunywa nzobya uretse abavuga ko bikomoka kuri uwo mugabo \r\nNzobya wo mu Buyenzi, hari nâ€™abandi bavuga ko byakomotse ku nka ya \r\nsekuru wa Nyirarucyaba rwa Gihanga.</p>\r\n<p>Mu bitekerezo, bavuga ko Nyirarucyaba akiri umukobwa wâ€™inkumi \r\nyicishije amata sekuru ubyara nyina agira ngo abise se Gihanga yime \r\ningoma. Sekuru wa Nyirarucyaba yari umwami wo mu basangwabutaka; bukeye \r\nGihanga agisha umukobwa we inama, ati: â€œEse mwana wanjye ko naje ino \r\nngira ngo ni jye uzaba umwami, none databukwe uriya ari we sogokuru \r\nwawe, tumugize dute ngo ambise mbe umwami?â€ Nyirarucyaba aramusubiza, \r\nati: â€œHora nzi uko nzabigira; nzabikurangiriza.â€</p>\r\n<p>Ubwo kwa sekuru hari inka yitwa Nzobya, bukeye Nyirarucyaba ajyayo, \r\namarayo iminsi. Umunsi umwe sekuru ajya guhiga, ahigutse afite inyota, \r\nasanga Nyirarucyaba ari we uri mu rugo wenyine; avuruga amata ya Nzobya \r\nashyira mu nkongoro, aramuhereza.</p>\r\n<p>Sekuru amaze kunywa atangira kugira isesemi, araruka. Nyirarucyaba \r\nabibonye yihina mu cyanzu, urugo aruha inkongi yâ€™umuriro, araboneza \r\nyigira iwabo kwa Gihanga.</p>\r\n<p>Nyina wabo witwaga Gihogwe (ni we kuvuza iya Gihogwe byavuyeho) \r\nasohotse asanga urugo rwahiye kare. Induru ayiha umunwa, ariko habura \r\nuwagira, ati: â€œKomera.â€ Nuko sekuru wa Nyirarucyaba apfa atyo, azize ko \r\nyanyoye amata ya Nzobya; ni yo bagereranya nâ€™inzoga umuntu anywa \r\nagasinda byo gupfa, bati: â€œsi inzoga yanyoye,yanyoye nzobya (= icyishi).</p>\r\n<p>Ni uko Nyirarucyaba amaze kwica sekuru atyo, Gihanga yima ingoma, \r\numukobwa we arongorwa na Kazigaba, ariko asaba se ingororano yâ€™uko \r\nyamuhesheje ingoma. Gihanga amusezeranya ko abana bamukomokaho \r\nbazitirirwa izina rye nâ€™ubwo ari umugore bwose; bakitwa Abacyaba.<br>\r\nKunywa nzobya = Gusinda bita ubwenge</p>', '1493416684umugani.png', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, '', 130);
