(69, '2017-04-29 00:14:42', 'MENYA Inkomoko yâ€™umugani Umusazi arasara akagwa ku ijambo', 'Uyu mugani bawuca iyo bumvise umuntu wâ€™inshyanutsi usanganywe amagambo yâ€™ibitandampaka akocoye ijambo rikirakiranya ibyari byabuze uruhero rwâ€™umuti. Nibwo bavuga banamushima; ngo â€œUmusazi arasara akagwa ku ijambo ', '<p>Wakomotse ku musazi Rwugamo rwamaze Yuhi Mazimpaka uburakari yari \r\nyagiriye umuhungu we Nyarwaya atabarutse I Burundi, ahagana mu mwaka wa \r\n1700.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya rwa Mazimpaka yakundaga gushotorana cyane, bukeye atera u \r\nBurundi bwâ€™umusoni rwihishwa ise Mazimpaka atabizi, maze arabuyogoza; \r\nahitira mu Birangira bya Ntaga, ahica umuganwa waho Rusengo rwa Kanago; \r\nanyaga umugore we Kibero cyâ€™ubukombe aramuzana, hamwe nâ€™inka nyinshi \r\nnâ€™indi minyago.</p>\r\n<p>Byose abyereka se Mazimpaka. Aho kubishima arabimwirukana aramuca, \r\nngo kuko yagiye i Burundi atamwohereje, araruwe gusa nâ€™ubushotoranyi bwe\r\n buvanze nâ€™ishyaka ryo kwanga kurushwa ubugabo.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya yari afite imitwe itatu yâ€™ingabo, irimo uwo mu zitwa \r\nAbabito, zari intwari cyane. Bukeye atera mu Burundi bwâ€™umusoni \r\nbubangikanye nâ€™u Bugesera, arabanesha; ahanyaga inka nyinshi \r\nbarazambukana zifata hakuno mu Bugesera.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya ategeka kurobanura amabara, buri bara rikajya ukwaryo. \r\nBarobanura imikara, ibihogo, amagaju, ibitare, ibibamba, ubugondo nâ€™andi\r\n mabara yose yâ€™inka yari azirimo.</p>\r\n<p>Birangiye haza umugabo wâ€™umusaza abaza abo asanze mu nka, ati â€œIzi \r\nnka zâ€™ibihogo ni izande?â€ Bati â€œ Ni iza Nyarwayaâ€ . Ziriya se zâ€™ibitare?\r\n Bati â€œNazo ni izeâ€ . Akomeza kubabazaamabara yose yâ€™inka. Zose \r\nbakamubwira ko ari iza Nyarwaya atabarukanye.</p>\r\n<p>Arongera arababaza, ati â€œKo numva zose ari iza Nyarwaya, izanyu ni \r\nizihe ko mwatabarukanye ?â€ Batiâ€œ I zo twazanye zose ni izeâ€. Umusaza, \r\nati â€œMbega abantu baruhijwe nâ€™ubusa! Mwanyaze inka mwese none muzirekeye\r\n umwe ?â€ Bati â€œNâ€™ubwo ari ize, ni ize natwe, kuko turi ingabo zeâ€œ.</p>\r\n<p>Abagaragu ba Nyarwaya baramusanga bamubwira ayo magambo yâ€™uwo musaza.\r\n Ahamagara nyirâ€™ukuyavuga; ati â€œKuki unteranya nâ€™ingabo zanjye \r\nukazishyiramo umwuka mubi?â€œ</p>\r\n<p>Aramusingira aramuhondagura. Umusaza, ati â€œUrugomo ndeba ufite harya \r\nngo ni uko utabarutse i Busoni! Waba utabarutse mu Birangirwa bya Ntaga \r\nkwa Rusengo rwa Kanago ho ntiwavuze ugahora da! â€</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya aramureka, ahindukirana abo bari kumwe, ati â€œAho hantu \r\nmurahazi?â€ Baramuhakanira. Biramubabaza kuko batahamenye ngo atereyo. I \r\ngihe bakiri aho yibaza uburyo yamenya aho hantu bamwogereje ngo ahatere,\r\n abona umugabo wâ€™umurundi uje aho bari, ari kumwe nâ€™abana be bâ€™abasore \r\nbagera kuri batanu.</p>\r\n<p>Amugeze iruhande akoma mu mashyi, ati â€œmwana wâ€™umwami, mvuye i \r\nBurundi nshitse nza mu Rwanda, nshikanye nâ€™inka 250, nâ€™abana banjye 15, \r\nnâ€™abagore batanu. Byose mbizanye mu Rwanda rwa so,none unyakire \r\nuzanyereke so Mazimpakaâ€.</p>\r\n<p>Amaze kuvuga atyo, Nyarwaya aramubaza, ati â€œUzi mu Birangirwa bya \r\nNtaga kwa Rusengo ?â€ Undi, ati â€œNdahazi ndetse niho nturutseâ€.Nyarwaya \r\nashyira agatima mu nda. Ati â€œEse ntiwahangeza,ukahanyereka ?â€Uwo \r\nmurundi, atiâ€œUjya kwendayo iki?â€Ati â€œNdashaka kuhatera .â€</p>\r\n<p>Umurundi aramwenyura, ati â€œWowe utera mu Birangirwa bya Ntaga \r\n?â€Nyarwaya arikiriza. Umurundi, ati â€œUfite ingabo zingana zite ushaka \r\nkuhateza ?â€ Nyarwaya, ati â€œNi izi turi kumwe gusaâ€.</p>\r\n<p>Umurundi, ati â€œUbiziranyeho na so?â€ Undi,ati â€œOyaâ€. Umurundi, ati \r\nâ€œHari imana wejeje zo kuhatera?â€ Nyarwaya, ati â€œNtabwo naharagurije kuko\r\n ntari nsanzwe mpaziâ€.</p>\r\n<p>Umurundi amugira inama, ati â€œBanza ujyane iminyago, dore ni \r\nmyinshi,ndetse nanjye unshyiremo nâ€™abana banjye 15 nâ€™inka 250 nâ€™abagore \r\nbatanu, maze ujye inama na so, muragurize gutera mu Birangirwa, kandi \r\numwongeze ingabo izi ntizihagijeâ€ . Ati â€œNi ahantu ubarirwa; ati â€œMbese \r\nwumvise ko hari umwami wigeze kuhatera?â€ Nyarwaya, ati â€œNtawe numviseâ€.</p>\r\n<p>Umurundi, ati â€œNi aho rero genda ubanze ujye inama na so, nakwemerera\r\n uzatereyo, nzahakwerekaâ€. Nyarwaya ararakara kuko iyo nama itamunogeye.\r\n Abwira uwo murundi, ati â€œNamaramaje ndaterayo ntakibimbuzaâ€.</p>\r\n<p>Umurundi, ati â€œUtagira ngo ndi umunyabwoba, hogi nkujyaneyo;ndetse \r\nnâ€™abana banjye ntibasigara keretse abatoya nâ€™abagore; bo nibasigarane \r\nnâ€™abantu bawe basigaye muri iyi minyagoâ€ . Ati â€œAriko mwana wâ€™umwami, \r\nubwo wanze ko tujya imigabo nitugerayo turajya imikokwe (imikoke)! â€.</p>\r\n<p>Arongera, ati â€œNi byiza ko twajya tugenda nijoro, ku manywa \r\ntugatebera mu bibira tukazatumburuka tugezeyoâ€. Ati â€œNaho turamutse \r\ndutabaye ku manywa, twatangira kurasana tukiri ku nkiko, tukazashirira \r\nmu nzira, niburatutanagezeyo ngo uharebeâ€.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya yemera iyo nama; bakajya bahaguruka nijoro, bwajya gucya \r\nbakarigita mu mashyamba, kuko uwo murundi yari azi inzira zose zijyayo. \r\nBakomeza batyo barinda kugera mu Birangirwa.</p>\r\n<p>Batunguka kwa Rusengo ku mugoroba basanga adahari. Yari yaragiye mu \r\nrundi rugo rwe,ari narwo ingabo ze zâ€™intwari zabagamo. Nyarwaya ajya mu \r\nrugo aramukanya nâ€™umugore wa Rusengo. Birangiye amubaza aho umugabo we \r\nari. Umugore arahamubwira.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya, ati â€œYamenye ko namuteye arahunga?â€ Umugore, ati â€œSi \r\nuguhunga, yagiye hambere ahubwo namenya ako gakuru uzamubona!â€. \r\nNyarwaya, ati Â«Ndamuteye Nyarwaya rwa Yuhi ndi Inkaka ya Burunga! nishe \r\nNtagihera mucuza imfura iyanjye irandamira ndatsinda! ! ! Ati Â«Ndaye \r\nhano, kandi turaryamana.</p>\r\n<p>Undi ati Â«Naba nâ€™ibyo! naho ibyo gutera byo nta byo wishoboreye; niba\r\n rero wazanywe no kwisambanira dore ndi hano, umugabo wanjye ntahari \r\nsimfite undwanaho; ariko nibijya kugeza ejo iki gihe utarabona \r\nuwanshatse uzabona uwambyaye!Â».</p>\r\n<p>Umugore wa Rusengo amutumaho intumwa zâ€™impayamaguru ariko bucece; ati\r\n Â«Nimwihute mujye kumubwira ko Nyarwaya yamuteye; kandi mumubwire ko \r\nyahinduye urugo rwe ari we wabaye nyirarwo mu buriri; muti Â«Ahasigaye ni\r\n wowe warumukuramo, byaba bikunaniye rukaba urweÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Intumwa zigenda ubutarora inyuma zisohoza ubutumwa. Rusengo amaze \r\nkwumva ko Nyarwaya amubereye mu rugo aratangara cyane; ati Â«Hahisha \r\nMazimpaka wenyine! Umuntu wahishirije inzoga ku Ijuru rya Kamonyi, none \r\numuhungu we akaba yaje kuzinsindira mu Birangirwa bya Ntaga!Â»</p>\r\n<p>Ubwo arara atumye intumwa zigenda ijoro ryose, zijya mu ngerero \r\nguhuruza; bujya gucya Ingabo ze zimusesekaraho. Rusengo ahurura ubwo, u \r\nBurundi burashika; Ingabo ziba nyinshi cyane!</p>\r\n<p>Bigiye kugeza nimugoroba, Rusengo nâ€™Ingabo basesekara iwe mu \r\nBirangirwa. Basanga Nyarwaya yashegeye mu rugo kwa Rusengo yamwiteguye. \r\nIngabo za Nyarwaya zisanganira iza Rusengo icumu rirasabira.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya ava ku buriri, arambara afata intwaro ze arasohoka. Ageze mu\r\n muryango, umugore wa Rusengo aramukurikira, ageze mu rugo, umugore aba \r\nageze mu muryango. Nyarwaya arasitara, umugore, ati Â«Mpore ndi Kibero \r\ncyâ€™ubukombe umugabo twararanye ntakomerekaÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya arabyumva aramusubiza, ati Â«Urakoze wo kabyara we ubwo \r\numpumurije!Â» Nyarwaya yiruka avuna Ingabo ze. Umugore yisubirira mu nzu \r\nye. Ubwo ariko intambara yarahosheje kuko bwari bwije; bamwe bajya iwabo\r\n abandi kwa Rusengo mu rugo, aba Nyarwaya bajya mu ngando zabo.</p>\r\n<p>Mu gitondo cya kare bashinga ingamba; bamwe mu myanya yabo, abandi mu\r\n yabo. Na none bwira ari ntabaranesha abandi. Ariko ubwo Nyarwaya yari \r\nafite umutwe wâ€™ intwari cyane witwaga Ababito. Akaba yabakumirije \r\nababuza kurasana ngo bazarasana Abarundi bamaze gucogora.</p>\r\n<p>Rusengo nawe yari afite Ingabo zâ€™intwari cyane zitwaga Abana bâ€™Ingwe;\r\n nawe yabakumirije ngo bazarasana Abanyarwanda bamaze kunanirwa. Ubwo \r\nbwenge umwe yabugize ukwe undi abugira ukwe. Hashize iminsi itatu \r\nbarasana; imyambi nâ€™amacumu byâ€™Abanyarwanda bibashiriraho.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya abaza wa murundi wamucikiye akamuyobora ahongaho; ati Â«Mbese\r\n nta hantu wamenya hiherereye cyane ngo tujyaneyo abacuzi nâ€™abatanazi \r\ntujye gushakira ingabo imyambi nâ€™amacumu?Â» Undi ati Â«NdahaziÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya abwira umwana we bari batabaranye witwaga Bideri, ati \r\nÂ«Sigara ku rugamba ngiye gushaka intwaro zâ€™aba bantu dore izindi zimaze \r\ngushira; ati Â«Kandi ejo uzarekure Ababito bajye ku rugambaÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya ajyana na wa murundi, bajyana ahantu hâ€™ishyamba ryarimo \r\numukoke uteye ubwoba,urimo isuri nâ€™andi mahwa yâ€™imifatangwe. Bawushoka \r\nbaciye mu mwambu wawo; uwo Murundi yibutsa Nyarwaya rya jambo \r\nyamubwiraga yari kwumva inama ye; Ati Â«Sinakubwiye ko ubwo wanze ko \r\ntujya imigabo nitugerayo tuzajya imikoke?</p>\r\n<p>Ati Â«Dore imikoke nakubwiye ni yo yâ€™iyiÂ». Nyarwaya, ati Â«Ni koko \r\nwambwiye ukuri, ariko sindava ku izima; ndacyakomeje imigabo yo \r\nkurwanaÂ».Ubwo rero bamaze kugera aho hantu, batangira umurimo wo \r\ngucukura no gutanaga, no gukwikira amacumu yavunikiye mu babisha; \r\nbabikorana umwete.</p>\r\n<p>Ubwo Bideri nâ€™ingabo zabo basigaye ku rugamba. Bukeye umwimirizi \r\nwâ€™Ababito arabazibukira bajya ku rugamba. Rusengo nawe akaba yararanye \r\numugambi wo kurekurira Abana bâ€™Ingwe ku rugamba. Uwo munsi. Ababito \r\nnâ€™Abana bâ€™Ingwe barasakirana. Rucura akabunda rwiyama impunzi barutera \r\namazi aragaruka.Nukuvuga ko bose barasanye badasubira inyuma.</p>\r\n<p>Hashize iminsi itatu bikimeze bityo Rusengo ahamagara Bideri ati Â«Ye \r\nBideri bya Nyarwaya we! Undi aramwitaba. ati Â«Hagarika abawe nanjye \r\nmpagarike abanjye maze tuvuganeÂ». Bahagarika intambara,ingabo zose \r\nziraruhuka.</p>\r\n<p>Rusengo; ati Yewe Bideri we, undi ati Â«Yee!Â» ati Â«Waje uzanye na so \r\nmuza munteye muza muri abatindi musanga ndi umwinazi, mwaje muri icyago \r\nmusanga ndi kabutindi, mwaje muri bunyice mu kanzungura birabananira, \r\nnanjye nibwiraga ko nzabica mu minsi ibiri nkaba mbamazeho none \r\nsinabishoboye; ati Â«Ndagira ngo nkubwire inama mfite nâ€™ubwo ntaheruka \r\nkubona so ariko uri mucyimbo cye: enda dutorane inka izanyu muzijyane \r\nizibaye izanjye nzisigarane, kandi izo muzabona zitageze hano \r\nmuzazitware nazo!Â» Bideri ati Â«NdabyemeyeÂ» Intamba irahosha.</p>\r\n<p>Bukeye inka zose ziratumizwa, ziteranira hagati yabo, barazitoranya. \r\nBirangiye hasigara inka imwe ariko nziza cyane! Rusengo abwira Bideri \r\nati Â«Nararagiye, narafukuye nduhira, naciye icyarire narakenuye, none \r\niyi nka yingororereÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Bideri, ati Nanjye nishwe nâ€™izuba, naranyagiwe naraye indaro mbi, \r\nnone iyi nka yinzimanireÂ». Rusengo aranga, Bideri aranga. Inka barayipfa\r\n bongera kurasana. Uwo munsi bakora ibyo Nyarwaya arangiza umurimo wa \r\nmujyanye.</p>\r\n<p>Yari yanacurishije icumu ryâ€™umuhida rinini na rirerire, nâ€™umuhunda \r\nwaryo munini kandi muremure. Barikwikira mu ruti runini rukomeye. \r\nNyarwaya ariterera ku rutugu, bava muri wa mukoke bajya mu ngando aho \r\nabandi bari bateraniye. Bahagera ni joro. Bideri amutekerereza uko \r\nyatoranye inka na Rusengo, nâ€™uko bananiranywe ku nka imwe, hakabura \r\nuwayiharira undi.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya ashima Bideri kuko yanze kuyimuharira. Ati Â«Kandi iri joro \r\nndamwica ntakabuzaÂ». Ubwo Nyarwaya asezera ku ngabo ze, ati Ndagiye, \r\nnamwe nimugeza mu gicuku, mutere kwa Rusengo muvuge ibyivugo musese \r\nimyugariro, bamwe muce imbere abandi inyuma mugote urugo. Aragenda \r\nagezeyo aca igico. Aragumya yumva uko bavuga imihigo yabo.</p>\r\n<p>Bigejeje mu gicuku barasinzira. Aromboka no mu muryango wâ€™ inzu \r\nRusengo aryamyemo acukurira rya cumu mu irebe ry â€˜umuryango; arishinga \r\nimpirike rireba mu nzu; ararishimangira cyane; yurira inzu yicara hejuru\r\n y â€˜uruhamo rwâ€™umuryango afata icumu mu ntoki.</p>\r\n<p>Bitinze ho gato I ngabo ze ziratera nk â€˜ukÃ¶ yÃ¤bibabwiye. Basesa \r\nimyugariro bavugira ibyivugo icyarimwe. Abari mu nzu Rusengo yarayemo \r\nbakangukira mu bitotsi. Ugize ngo arasohoka akibamba kuri rya cumu, ati:\r\n Â«Ndashize mwo kanyagwa mwe! Rimaze kwica batatu riravunika.</p>\r\n<p>Ubwo Rusengo nawe arabyuka arambara arasohoka; ageze imbere y \r\nâ€˜umuryango Nyarwaya amutera icumu mu gihumbi rimutunguka hejuru y \r\nâ€˜umukondo akubita ibipfukamiro hasi; ati Â«Nkwice Karuretwa Imanzi ya \r\nBurunga! Â» Abari muri urwo rugo iza Nyarwaya zirabarimarima: ingo \r\nzirashya, inka ziranyagwa.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya yinjira mu nzu abwira wa mugore Kibero cy â€˜Ubukombe, ati \r\nÂ«Wambwiye ko umugabo wakurayeho adakomereka none ntabwo ngusigaÂ». \r\nBaramuheka aramutabarukana. Nyarwaya atabaruka mu Burundi afite ishema \r\nashoreye iminyago myinshi avanye mu Birangirwa.</p>\r\n<p>Ageze mu Rwanda atumiza iyo yakuye mu Busoni; inka zirakubita \r\nziruzura, iminyago iba ishyano ryose. Ariko kandi, mu bantu ibihumbi \r\n3000 bisaga yari yatabaranye, yari asigaranye nk â€˜ igihumbi gusa; abandi\r\n baraguye ku rugamba. Atuma kuri se ko atabarutse; yohereza nâ€™abavuzi \r\nbâ€™amacumu. Mazimpaka aramwitegura, I ngabo ziriraba ( zisiga ingwa) .</p>\r\n<p>Zigeze hafi y â€˜ ibwami bararirimba, iminyago ibajya imbere. Hari \r\nimandwa yabaga ibwami yari yarahawe gusanganira iminyago ya Nyarwaya \r\nibigenza uko isanzwe. Ingabo ziravunywa ziza mu rugo I bwami. Mazimpaka \r\nazibonye asanga ari nkeya cyane; abaza Nyarwaya, ati Â«Abantu banjye \r\nwabaguranye inka aba ari zo unzanira?Â» Cyo!</p>\r\n<p>Untekerereza ko nkeneye inka kurusha abantu? Nyarwaya, ati Â«None se \r\nko twarasanaga nâ€™abantu bâ€™ intwari, twajyaga kubicamo bakatureka gusa?Â».\r\n Mazimpaka, ati Â«Mbese nâ€™ayo yose wagiye woherejwe na nde udafite imana \r\nnâ€™umugaba?Â» Undi, ati Â«Ubundi se ko nari nsanzwe ntabara ntakubwiye \r\nnarazaga ukangaya? Ahubwo ntiwanshimaga ndetse ukangororera?</p>\r\n<p>Mazimpaka aranga ararubira aramuca,kuko yateye I ngabo icyorezo. \r\nNyarwaya arakerakera, abura iyo ajya biramushobera. Abantu bagerageje \r\nkumuhakirirwa birananirana, Mazimpaka, ati Â«Najye gutegeka igihugu \r\nyatsinzeÂ» .</p>\r\n<p>Bimaze gushoberana haza umusazi witwa Rwugamo; yari asanzwe aza I \r\nbwami; abwira Mazimpaka, ati Â«Ngufitiye ijambo rikomeye ariko banza umpe\r\n akayoga kuko mfite inyotaÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Bamuha inzoga aranywa. Bimaze akanya, ati Â«Reka nkwicare ku bibero \r\nmaze nkubwire. Mazimpaka kuko yamukundaga byâ€™igikinisho aremera. Rwugamo\r\n amaze kumugera ku bibero, ati Â«Aho kuba intwari ibwami nahaba \r\numusazi,ati Â«Dore Nyarwaya umwana wâ€™umwami yatabaye i Burundi yica \r\nRusengo mu Birangirwa bya Ntaga atabarukana iminyago itabarika, none \r\nbamuciye arakerakera naho jye Rwugamo rwâ€™umusazi nicaye ku bibero \r\nbyâ€™umwami ndanywa inzoga yâ€™ubuki!Â».</p>\r\n<p>Abantu bateraniye aho bahoze basabira Nyarwaya imbabazi baraseka; \r\nbati: Â«Umusazi ariguyeho!Â» ( ijambo ryâ€™ukuri) ! Â«Umwami abwira wa musazi\r\n ati Â«Mvira ku biberoÂ». Ahamagaza Nyarwaya abyicaraho. Abari aho \r\nbamukurira ubwatsi barishima bashima nâ€™uwo musazi Rwugamo.</p>\r\n<p>Mazimpaka abaza Nyarwaya, ati Â«Ko mbona ugenda utera itako, abo wica \r\nubica ute? Nyarwaya, ati Â«Ndi Inkuba nkâ€™iyo hejuru kandi nâ€™uwajya \r\nkunsiga ntiyasiga icumu ryanjye. Nyarwaya rero amaze kwicara ku bibero \r\nbya se, inzoga ziratumirwa, Ingabo ziravunywa, inkera irararwa; \r\nMazimpaka atega amatwi intwari zimubwira imihigo zimutura iminyago \r\nnâ€™ibinyita.</p>\r\n<p>Nyarwaya aragororerwa, na wa murundi bajyanaga imikoke aragororerwa: \r\nndetse cyane kuko Mazimpaka yamugororeye na Nyarwaya akamugororera, \r\nHanyuma bagenda batanga ingororano no mu bandi batabarukanye bakurikije \r\nuko barushanwa ubugabo.</p>\r\n<p>Wa mugore wa Rusengo Kibero cyâ€™ubukombe, Nyarwaya aramutunga \r\nbanabyarana abana benshi. Ibyâ€™igororerwa bihetuye banzika ibiganiro \r\nbisanzwe; havamo umugabo muri abo bari I bwami abwira Nyarwaya, ati \r\nÂ«Dore ko ngo uri inkuba nkâ€™iyo hejuru jye twirutse nagusigaÂ». Abandi \r\nbati: Â«Nimwiruke turebeÂ».</p>\r\n<p>Bariruka wa mugabo agiye kumusiga Nyarwaya amukurikiza icumu \r\nrimwahuranya mu gihumbi amutsinda aho. Mazimpaka agiye kurakara, abari \r\naho bati Â«Urarakazwa nâ€™ubusa uriya mugabo ni we wisengeye urupfuÂ». Bati \r\nÂ«Nyarwaya yakubwiye ko ari inkuba nkâ€™iyo hejuru kandi nâ€™uwajya kumusiga \r\natasiga icumu ryeÂ». Birasekwa umugabo ahera atyo; na we wa musazi \r\nRwugamo; Nyarwaya aramuvuza arakira aranamukiza.Nuko rya jambo ngo \r\nÂ«Umusazi ariguyehoÂ», rubanda bakomeza kuryogeza kuko ryakijije Nyarwaya \r\nuburakari bwa se. Bukeye rihimbirwaho uyu mugani ngo Â«Umusazi arasara \r\nakagwa kwâ€™ijamboÂ», ari wo baca iyo hagize inshyanutsi isanzwe ivuga \r\nibitandampaka ikocora ijambo bakaryenderaho inkunga yo gukiranura ibyari\r\n byabuze uruhero rwâ€™umuti. Kugwa ku ijambo = Kwunguka inama \r\nyâ€™ingirakamaro.</p><p><br></p><p>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></p>', '1493417682umugani.png', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'sub', 151),
(70, '2017-05-02 19:53:26', 'sobanukirwa umugani:\" Impamba itazakugeza I Kigali uyirira ku Ruyenzi\"', 'Uyu mugani baca ngo impamba itazakugeza i Kigali uyirira ku Ruyenzi wakomotse ku ngabo zâ€™ i Nduga zari ziri mu rugerero ku Ibuye rihetse irindi,i Nyabugogo ahayinga umwaka wâ€™ 1700.', '<p>Igihe kimwe Abagesera bateye urugerero rwâ€™ u Rwanda rwari ruherereye i\r\n Kigali ku murenge wa Busasanzobe bwa Musimba, ahayinga umwaka wâ€™ 1700, \r\nhari ku ngoma ya Mibambwe Gisanura.</p>\r\n<p>Ubwo ngo ingabo zâ€™ abanyabugesera zambutsa Abanyarwanda Nyabugogo, \r\nbafata umusozi Nyamweru na Shyorongi hâ€™ i Kigali, ariko Abanyarwanda \r\nbarabahindurana babambutsa Nyabugogo bashinga urugerero ku Ibuye rihetse\r\n irindi.</p>\r\n<p>Icyo gihe,abagemuraga baturutse mu Nduga no mu yandi majyepfo yâ€™ u \r\nRwanda bagera ku Ruyenzi bagacika intege kuko babonaga ko ingabo zâ€™ \r\nAbagesera ziri bubambure ayo mazimano, ni ko kwiyicarira bagafungura.</p>\r\n<p>Ubwo urugerero rwarahagumye kugeza ubwo Gi9sanura atangiye, azungurwa\r\n nâ€™ umuhungu we Mazimpaka, na we azungurwa nâ€™ umugungu we Cyirima \r\nRujugira ariwe warwanye nâ€™ Abagesera arabatsimbura, ahera ko ashinga \r\nurugerero mu Mpanga za Magerere.</p>\r\n<p>Nyuma yâ€™ iyima rya Rujugira, inkiko zâ€™ u Rwanda zaterwaga nâ€™ \r\nAbarundi. Batera mu Buyenzi, Bushumba, Nyakare, na Mvejuru muri Butare. \r\nIbi byatumye Abanyarwanda barwana impande zose, bityo ingemu ziba nke mu\r\n ngerero. Ariko, inyuma yâ€™ urugerero rwa Mpanga hari ishyamba rinini \r\ncyane, bakahita mu Gitabage, maze abahagiye bahasanga imboga zitwa \r\nimiheka bazisoroma rwihishwa baraziteka, barafungura, nyamara nyuma yaho\r\n abandi baza kubimenya, nabo bagasoroma bakajya guteka bihishe ngo \r\nhatagira uhamenya zikazahashira.</p>\r\n<p>Byatumaga uwashakaga kuharangira undi akoresha amarenga bagira bati: \r\nâ€œNiko sha, i Kiboga muherukayo ryari?â€ abandi benshi baza kuvumbura iryo\r\n banga, bigaba muri iryo shyamba bararishitura ntihasigara nâ€™ agati \r\ngahagaze.</p>\r\n<p>Inkuru rero yaratinze iza kugera kwa Cyilima ko urugerero rwo mu \r\nMpanga rurya ibiti byitwa imiheka, biramubabaza cyane, ni ko gutumiza \r\nabatware bâ€™ urgerero aho bari hose ngo bamusange i Nduba ya Bwanacyambwe\r\n bwa Kigali. Bagezeyo, yababajije igituma ingabo ze zishonje, ati: \r\nâ€œCyane cyane izo mu rugerero rwa Mageragere ya Mpanga ni rwo rutwambitse\r\n urubwa kuko rurya ibiti byo mu ishyamba rya Rugarika.â€ Na bo bati: \r\nNyagasani turi abatware bâ€™ ingerero ariko ntituri abâ€™ ibihugu.â€</p>\r\n<p>Cyilima ni ko gushinga itegeko ati: â€œKuva ubu ingerero zizajye \r\nzigemurirwa, mu gihe ndiho cyangwa ntanze.â€ Yongeraho ati: \r\nâ€œUtazazigemurira nzamunyaga.â€ Arongera ati: â€œKandi uko muri aha muzi ko \r\nnta Munyarwanda utazi gutegeka.â€ Ni uko abategeka kubanza urugerero rwa \r\nMpanga za Mageragere.</p>\r\n<p>Arangije kubabwira atyo barikubura, ariko bataha bafite ubwoba, ni ko\r\n gusesekazayo ingemu nyinshi, ingabo ziranezerwa, zikira umuheka wo mu \r\nGitabage. Kuva ubwo, aho hantu hitwa i Kiboga kugeza magingo aya.</p>\r\n<p>Urwo rugerero rumaze kwijuta ingemu, ni ko gutuma kuri Cyilima ruti: \r\nâ€œNyagasani, turakwifuza mu rugerero rwacu.â€ Cyilima ahaguruka I Nduba \r\najya I Mpanga nâ€™ ingemu nyinshi zirimo ingumba zâ€™ ibimasa byo kubaga.</p>\r\n<p>Umwami ageze i Mpanga araza inkera, mu gitondo agabanya ingabo ingemu\r\n yabazaniye. Yongera kuraza inkera, ni uko ati: â€œNimumbwire icyo \r\nmwanshakiraga.â€ Abahungu bati: â€œTumaze iminsi tudaterwa kandi natwe \r\ntudatera, none Nyagasani turagira ngo tukwiture ineza watugiriye, kuko \r\naho udukuriye ku miheka yo ku Rugarika, imbaraga zacu zaragarutse.</p>\r\n<p>Ingororano tuguhaye ni uko tugiye gutera Ubugesera, nta yindi twabona\r\n irenze kubukugabira.â€ Umwami abyumvise aramwenyura. Abahungu bati: â€œEjo\r\n tuzatanga abatware i Bugesera.â€ Cyilima ati: â€œNoneho ubwo mwiyemeje \r\nkuzatera ejo, nimureke kunywa inzoga nyinshi.â€ Bati: â€œNyagasani, nta \r\nrundi rugerero dushaka ko rutwivangamo.â€</p>\r\n<p>Bati: â€œNimuririmbe dutere Ubugesera.â€ Naho ubwo, Abanyabugesera \r\nbamaze kumenya ko bazaterwa. Bakijya impaka, bumva Abanyabugesera \r\nbivugira ku Karubanda, na bo baraha intwaro batangira kurwana.</p>\r\n<p>Muri iyo mirwano Abanyarwanda babanesha uruhenu bicamo benshi, babaha\r\n umugongo barahunga. Ubwo urugerero rurimuka rushingwa i Gihinga cya \r\nBugesera, barwita ingororano ya Cyilima.</p>\r\n<p>Abavuzi bâ€™ amacumu baza kubwira Cyilima ko urugerero rwashinzwe i \r\nGihinga cya Bugesera, ni ko guhaguruka abasangayo. Urugerero rwâ€™ i \r\nMututu (mu Mayaga ya Butare) na rwo rwumvise ko urwa Mpanga rwafashe \r\nigice kinini cya Bugesera, rurambuka rutera Bugesera intambike.</p>\r\n<p>Banyagayo inka nyinshi, ariko ntibararayo ahubwo bazishyira Cyilima \r\nho intashyo i Mututu. Aho ni ho rubanda bafatiye, babona ikintu \r\nkibabereye iyanga bakagihuhura bagira bati: â€œImpamba itazakugeza i \r\nKigali, Uyirira ku Ruyenzi.â€</p><p><br></p><p>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></p>', '1493747606Ruyenzi.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 558),
(71, '2017-05-02 20:31:37', 'SObanukirwa  Aho kubandwa byaturutse namateka ya Ryangombe.', 'Benshi mubariho ubu aya mateka ntayo bazi:Ryangombe  wari umwana wâ€™ikinege, ari na we wazanye kubandwa.  Akaba yaraje gupfira mu muko ari wo bita umurinzi iyo babandwa cyangwa baterekera.  Umuko ni igiti gikomeye mu kubandwa kubera ko ari cyo cyakijije Ryangombe imbogo yamuteye ihembe.', '<p><strong>Ryangombe&nbsp; wari umwana wâ€™ikinege, ari na we wazanye \r\nkubandwa.&nbsp; Akaba yaraje gupfira mu muko ari wo bita umurinzi iyo \r\nbabandwa cyangwa baterekera.&nbsp; Umuko ni igiti gikomeye mu kubandwa kubera\r\n ko ari cyo cyakijije Ryangombe imbogo yamuteye ihembe.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Ryangombe amaze kuvuka se yasize amuraze&nbsp; ubwami, ariko asiga \r\natamwimitse, ari byo byatumye bene se wabo batangira kumwanga. Uwitwa \r\nMpumutumucuni yavugaga ko adakwiriye&nbsp; kwima ingoma. Yabwiye Ryangombe \r\nngo azaze babuguze.<br>\r\nUyu Ryangombe akaba yaragombaga kuraguza ku gakecuru gapfuye ijisho \r\ngataha mu rutare. Ajya gushaka indagu, yajyanye nâ€™imbwa ze agenda ahiga,\r\n aho yaje kukagwaho kakamuha indagu kamubwira ko umwana azabyarana nâ€™ \r\numukobwa bazahurira mu nzira aca ubwatsi ari kumwe nâ€™abandi, ari we \r\nuzamurengera akazatuma yima ingoma .<br>\r\nNyuma yo guhura nâ€™uwo mukobwa&nbsp; Nyirakajumba, Ryangombe yasize&nbsp; amuteye \r\ninda, babyarana umwana witwa Binego wari icyohe; aho yarerewe kwa \r\nnyirarume bamuhaga kuragira inka yazikubita akazigusha. Binego yaje \r\nkujya gushakisha se, ariko aho yanyuraga hose yarayobozaga umurangiye \r\nnabi akamukubita icumu akamwica. Kugeza ubwo yaje kugera aho se \r\nRyangombe yarimo abuguza na Mpumutumucuni, amwereka uko abuguza atwara \r\nnteba. Nyuma yo gutsinda&nbsp; ndetse Binego agakubita icumu Mpumutumucuni \r\nakagwaho, impundu zaravuze, Ryangombe arima, aba mu ngoma ze zâ€™u Burengo\r\n nâ€™abahungu be Binego na Ruhanga na mukuru we Nyabirungu na Mashira na \r\nKagoro.<br>\r\nRyangombe rero arara agambiriye umuhigo wo&nbsp; guhigira Nyabikenke, abwira \r\nabahungu be ko&nbsp; azabatanga&nbsp; inyamaswa ya Nyabikenke.&nbsp; Nyiraryangombe \r\nyaje kwicura abwira umuhungu we Ryangombe ati â€œ Siba umuhigo wa none \r\ncyana kimwe cya Mukanya cyamaze nyina ubugwe nâ€™ubugweshyamba. Siba \r\numuhigo wa none, bibero birinda ibibanda, shebuja wa Ruhanga umugabo, \r\nsiba umuhigo wa noneâ€. Undi ati â€œOya ntabwo nsiba ndahigiye Nyabikenkeâ€.\r\n Nyina ati â€œ Narose inzozi mbi, narose itukura rya Nyabikenke, narose \r\nurukwavu rutagira ishyira nâ€™umurizo, narose imbogo yâ€™ihembe rimwe, \r\nnarose inkware yâ€™ibara, narose umugezi utemba ujya ruguru wa \r\nNyabikenke.â€ Undi aratsimbarara.<br>\r\nMu rukerera Ryangombe abaza&nbsp; amayombo yimbwa ze ngo ajye guhiga, amayombo arabura. Naho Nyiraryangombe yari yayahishe.<br>\r\nNyirakajumba niwe wamwongoreye ko amayombo ari mwa Nyiraryangombe. Ni \r\nbwo Ryangombe aje aturutse hirya nâ€™uburakari, urugi arukubita umugeri \r\nruragwa, rugwira ibiseke, amayombo mu giseke aravuga.<br>\r\nNyiraryangombe&nbsp; akomeza kumubuza kujya guhiga, aba yatambamye mu bikingi\r\n byâ€™amarembo, yijishura umweko awurambika muri ibyo bikingi, amubwira \r\nngo asibe umuhigo.&nbsp;&nbsp; Ryangombe asimbuka umweko awugwa inyuma maze \r\naraboneza.<br>\r\nMu kujya guhiga Ryangombe yagiye ahura nâ€™inyamaswa zidasanzwe; urukwavu \r\nrutagira ishyira nâ€™umurizo, inkware yâ€™ibaba rimwe, nâ€™ imondo yâ€™ibara \r\nrimwe. Abo bari kumwe bakamubwira ko ari indagu ya Nyiraryangombe yenda \r\ngutaha.<br>\r\nRyangombe agiye&nbsp; kumanuka umugezi wa Nyabikenke asanga wahindutse ituku \r\nryâ€™amaraso,&nbsp; araboneza ngo agere hirya aca imitwe na Nyagishya \r\ncyâ€™impenebere gihetse umwana imbebe. Agiye gusimbuka wa mugezi bati \r\nâ€œSigaho wirenga itukura rya Nyamikenke garuka Ryangombe. Garuka cyana \r\nkimwe cya Mukanya cyanze kwumvira se na nyina umunsi wa nyuma ukazumvira\r\n ijeri ku mugani wa Nyiraryangombe uko yabivuzeâ€. Undi ati&nbsp; â€œOya, nta \r\nndagu yâ€™agakecuru ntibimbuza guhiga i Nyabikenkeâ€.<br>\r\nNyagishya amwaka impetso yâ€™umwana wanjye, ati â€œndashaka uruhu \r\nrwâ€™inyamaswa iri muri kiriya gihuru.â€&nbsp; Ryangombe yohereza imbwa ze \r\nkuvumbura ya nyamaswa yâ€™imbogo. Hagendaga imbwa imwe imwe igezeyo imbogo\r\n ikayirenza ihembe kugeza zishize.&nbsp; Ryangombe yigirayo, imbogo ayikoza \r\nagahende mwâ€™ipfupfu, iba imukojeje ihembe iramwirenza, ageze mu kirere \r\nasumira igiti cyâ€™umuko ajya muri cya giti aragikomeza.&nbsp; Abo bari kumwe \r\nbiruka&nbsp; bajya gutabaza.</p>', '1493749897Aho-kubandwa-byaturutse-300x220.png', 0, 'admin', 6, 10, 'sub', 279),
(72, '2017-05-06 10:36:26', 'REBA Amafoto Yaranze igitaramo cya Gakondo Group Teta Diana wari umaze umwaka i Burayi yatunguye abitabiriye igitaramo.', 'Abaririmbyi nâ€™abacuranzi bahuriye muri Gakondo Group bakoze igitaramo cyo kumara ipfa abakunda umuziki gakondo.', 'Igitaramo cya Gakondo Group cyiswe â€˜Gakondo Twataramyeâ€™ cyabereye kuri \r\nHÃ´tel des Mille Collines mu Mujyi wa Kigali rwagati mu ijoro ryo kuri \r\nuyu wa Gatanu tariki ya 5 Gicurasi 2017, cyitabiriwe mu buryo bukomeye \r\nku buryo hari abatashye batarebye igitaramo kubera ubwinshi bwâ€™abafana.<br><p>Sentore Jules wari urangaje imbere Gakondo Group mu gitaramo yatangiye kuririmba ahagana saa mbili, maze mu buryo \r\nbutunguranye Teta Diana wari umaze igihe kigera ku mwaka mu mahanga aba \r\nyiyiretse abafana. Yinjiye aririmba indirimbo za Kamaliza abafana \r\nibyishimo birabasaba bamukomera mu mashyi abandi bamwereka ko igihe yari\r\n amaze adahari bamukumbuye byâ€™ikirenga.</p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1000px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/ry6b7767-bd99a.jpg?1494058125\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Teta Diana yanyuze benshi ubwo yaririmbaga zimwe mu ndirimbo ze \r\nzakunzwe mbere yâ€™uko ajya kuba ku Mugabane wâ€™u Burayi gusa byabaye \r\nikirenga ubwo yafatanyaga na Jules Sentore mu ndirimbo â€˜Umpe Akanyaâ€™.</p>\r\n<p>Indirimbo yose Teta yaririmbaga yacishagamo akabaza abakunzi be uko \r\nbamerewe bose bagaterura bamusubiza ko â€˜banyuzweâ€™. Uyu mukobwa yagiye \r\nazenguruka mu bantu akabahereza ikiganza abandi biganjemo abo baziranye \r\nakabagwa mu nda.</p>\r\n<p>Nyuma yâ€™iminota mike Teta Diana amaze kuririmba imvura ikomeye \r\nyisutse hasi abafana baratatana abacuranzi na bo bazinga ibyuma \r\nigitaramo gisozwa ubwo.</p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:1000;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH666/ry6b7454-31f26.jpg?1494058125\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"666\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Uyu mukobwa ari mu basubiramo indirimbo za Kamaliza bikaryohera benshi</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:1000;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/ry6b7461-5b2a7.jpg?1494058125\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Gakondo Group irayasubukuye subukura ibitaramo byayo kuri Mille Collines</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position:relative;width:1000;padding:5px;margin-bottom:20px;margin-right:3px;background-color:#ffffff;align:center;text-align:center;-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/ry6b7464-9369e.jpg?1494058125\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Ni umuziki wa gakondo wari uherekejwe na bimwe mu bicurangish