\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-top:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-right:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:10.0pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin-left:0in;\r\n	line-height:115%;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><div align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nfont-weight:normal;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Umukirigitananga DEO MUNYAKAZI\r\numaze kuba ubukombe mu gusakaza umuco Nyarwanda ku isi, Nyuma yâ€™uko hashize\r\niminsi mike avuye gutarama mu gihugu cya Kenya ndetse nâ€™ubufaransa</span></strong><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">&nbsp;</b> akomotse muri DOADOA\r\nFestival&nbsp;, iserukira muco ryaberaga mu gihugu cya Uganda&nbsp; rikaba\r\nryaratangiye taliki ya 2/05/2017 rigasoza kuri 06/05/2017,&nbsp; rikaba\r\nryaritabiriwe nâ€™abahanzi bâ€™ibyamamare yaba abo<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>mu gihugu cya Uganda ndetse nâ€™abandi bari bahagariye ibihugu byabo.\r\n\r\n</div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\">Mu baryitabiriye harimo Cindy\r\nSanyu(Uganda),Giovanni Kiyingi(Uganda),Eddie Grey(Kenya), Mswanugogo Vibes(Tanzania), Nina Ogot(Kenya),Cocodo Band(Tanzania),Charmant\r\nMuchaga(Uganda),Bernard&amp;Alfred(Burundi) nâ€™abandi. umukirigitanaga <b>Deo\r\nMUNYAKAZI</b> ari kumwe na <b>ERIC soul</b> na <b>Ange UMUTONI</b> nibo\r\nbahesheje ishema u Rwanda baseruka gitore. &nbsp; <br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RtPzI6d.jpg\" height=\"460\" width=\"690\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; DEO akirigita inanga</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Nyuma yo gushyika mu Rwanda akubutse muri Uganda, DEO\r\nMUNYAKAZI yaduhaye ishusho nyakuri yâ€™iryo serukira muco agira ati &lt;&lt; Ni\r\nkunshuro<br>ya mbere nitabiriye DOADOA festival, <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>Natewe ishema no guhura na bahanzi bakomeye\r\nnka NINA OGOT na WINYO babanya Kenya ndetse na bandi bahanzi gakondo <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>tukungurana ibitekerezo.&gt;&gt;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span class=\"mycenter\"><span class=\"image-share-wrap\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43048 cool-image-share td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"http://izubarirashe.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/15592172_1608930199415199_930091033_n.jpg\" alt=\"15592172_1608930199415199_930091033_n\" height=\"500\" width=\"750\"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\">Nubwo yasanze inanga nyarwanda\r\nitazwi , yitwaye neza kurubyiniro ndetse anashimisha<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>cyane abari bitabiriye . Twamubajije imigambi\r\nafite yo gutuma I nanga nyarwanda irushaho kumenyeka mu bihugu byâ€™abaturanyi\r\nndetse no mu mahanga yose , adusiba agira<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;\r\n</span>ati &lt;&lt; Ndikwitabira ibitaramo bitandukanye kandi hari ni bikorwa\r\nbijyanye no gutunganya izindi nanga nshya muri studio, hakaba harimo niri\r\nkurangira mpamya cyane ko izabanyura <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>ikaba\r\niri bubagereho mu gihe cya vuba.&gt;&gt; <br></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://izubarirashe.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Umucuranzi-Munyakazi-D_o-ari-kumwe-n%C3%86icyamamare-Jef-Neve-ku-rubyiniro.jpg\" data-caption=\"Umucuranzi Munyakazi DÃ©o ari kumwe nâ€™icyamamare Jef Neve ku rubyiniro (Ifoto/Interineti)\" class=\"td-modal-image\"><img class=\"entry-thumb td-animation-stack-type0-1\" src=\"http://izubarirashe.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Umucuranzi-Munyakazi-D_o-ari-kumwe-n%C3%86icyamamare-Jef-Neve-ku-rubyiniro-696x464.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"umucuranzi-munyakazi-d_o-ari-kumwe-naeicyamamare-jef-neve-ku-rubyiniro\" height=\"464\" width=\"696\"></a><br><span class=\"mycenter\"><span class=\"image-share-wrap\"></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Munyakazi ubwo aheruka mubufaransa<br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; N.JERO\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n', '1494331053Deo.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 10, 'head', 541),
(79, '2017-05-12 22:53:29', 'Itorero bethesda holly church ryateguye ibihe bidasanzwe binyuze murubyiruko hamwe na  *Pastor Nsenga Emmanuel,Pastor Jimmy Muyango na Ev.Lambert BARIHO.', 'Mu murenge wa Kinyinya , mu karere ka Gasobo ,hafi yo mu Gakinjiro ka Gisozi ho mu Mujyi wa Kigali hateguwe igiterane cyo Kuramya no Guhimbaza kizava kuwa16 Gicurasi-19. Iki giterane kizitabirwa nâ€™abakozi bâ€™Imana  ndetse nâ€™amachoral afite umwihariko muguhimbaza Imana hano mu Rwanda.', '<br><div align=\"left\"><b>Urubyiruko rwa Bethesda Holy church, nkuko \r\nrusanzwe rutegura ibihe bitandukanye&nbsp; byo kuramya no Guhimbaza Imana \r\nkuri iyi nshuro rwateguye igihe gihagije cyo gusobanuro bimwe mubibazo \r\nabantu benshi&nbsp; bibaza kw\'ijambo ry\'Imana hamwe ninzobere zitandukanye </b><i><b>nama choral benshi bakunda cyane Light&nbsp; Gospel Choir,sauti \r\nHewani,Boanergers group,Bethesda Choir hamwe na Worship Team baramya \r\nbahimbaza Imana.</b></i></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XP6nIL8.jpg\" width=\"620\"><br><br>Nkuko umwe mubo twegereye utashatse ko dutangaza amazina ye yatubwiye mumagambo ye ati \"<b>Nkuko&nbsp;\r\n wabibonye&nbsp; nawe  kurupapuro rwubutumire, bariya bagabo nabahanga \r\nsubuhanga mubuzima busanzwe,&nbsp; bafite gusa , ahubwo bafite&nbsp; nimpano \r\ny\'IMANA&nbsp; mugusobanura ijambo ryayo , ntuzabure </b><b><i>Ndakwifuriza kutazabura</i>.\"<br></b><br>twashatse kumenya ubuhanga&nbsp; aba bagabo bagaragara kurupapuro rutumira abantu bafite:, <br><br><b>nuko mubuhanga ikinyamakuru&nbsp; umucowacu gisanzwe gikoresha&nbsp; twasanze <br><br></b><br>*<b>Pastor Nsenga Emmanuel</b>*&nbsp; <i>ni\r\n umwe mubagaragara bazaba bari Bethesda dusanga uretse kuba ari Pastor \r\numukozi w\'Imana ugabura ibyayo ahubwo afite numwihariko kuko ni \r\nimpunguke muri _Mass communation and journalism_ numuhanga cyane akaba \r\nimpuguke benshi bigiraho byinshi ,akaba&nbsp; numwe mubagabo bazi kuganira \r\ncyane.<br><br>uyu mugabo umwihariko afite nubwo ari umuhanga ukomeye&nbsp; \r\nyafashe iyambere nyuma yuko asanze umuhamagaro we ari uwo gukorera Imana\r\n yafashe iyambere yo guhugura urubyiruko,akunda cyane kubona urubyiruko \r\nby\'umwihariko ruhinduka.<br>Ni Pastor muri&nbsp; Eglise Vivante/Kimihurura.<br><br></i><br>twakomeje dushaka kumenya ubuhanga urubyiruko rwa<b> Bethesda Holly church</b> rutangaza dore ko biba&nbsp; byitenzwe nabatari bakeya bavuga ko ntawukwiye kubura.<br>&nbsp;<b><br><br>umucowacu uzagushaka kumenya byinshi kumugabo wundi uzagaragara i Bethesda kuwa16 kugera 19</b><br>&nbsp;<br><b><br>*Pastor Jimmy Muyango</b><i>\r\n ni&nbsp; umwe bugabo bakoresha impano zimurimo akorera Imana akaba akomeje \r\nkugarurira benshi kuri Yesu ni&nbsp; Senior Pastor wa _Rwanda for \r\nJesus,Umuyobozi wa The Potter\'s Hand Ministries_<br>sibyo gusa kuko ni impuguke mubijyanye no kubaka(Ingeneer)<br>&nbsp;uyu\r\n mugabo yakoze ibinanira benshi kuko afite nawe umwihariko , yahagaritse\r\n iyo mirimo yiyemeza gukorera Imana.Afite amagambo y\'ubwenge&nbsp; kuburyo \r\nbenshi bahora bumva bafite inyota. azaba nawe ari i Bethsda .<br></i><br><br><b>umucowacu uzagushaka kumenya byinshi kumugabo wundi uzagaragara i Bethesda kuwa16 kugera 19<br></b><br><b>*Ev.Lambert BARIHO</b> <i>nawe ni umwe mubabana na&nbsp; Antoine RUTAYISIRE <br>sibyo gusa afite umwihariko abamuzi neza bakunda amagambo aherekejwe ningero zumvikana atanga iyo yigisha.<br><br>Nyuma\r\n yo kurangiza amasomo ye i London mu bwongereza yagarutse mu Rwanda \r\nahatangiza umuryango w\'ivugabutumwa uzwi nka *Ellel Ministries* mbibutse\r\n ko uyu muryango wavutse muri za 80 mu bwongereza. Uyu muryango umaze \r\ngufasha benshi mu bashumba ndetse na abayobozi b\'amatorero mu Rwanda.<br>&nbsp; <br><b>Kwibutse\r\n ko ababagabo bazaba&nbsp; bari Bethesda Holly church kuva kuwa 16 Gicurasi \r\nkugera kuwa 19 hamwe nama choral benshi bakunda cyane Light&nbsp; Gospel \r\nChoir,sauti Hewani,Boanergers group,Bethesda Choir hamwe na Worship Team\r\n baramya bahimbaza Imana.</b><br><br></i><b><br><br><i><br>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs</i></b><i><br></i></div>', '1494622409123.png', 0, 'admin', 6, 2, '', 334),
(81, '2017-05-16 11:20:46', 'AMAFOTO_Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda yafashije abantu 40 barwaye ishaza kuvurwa ku buntu', '  Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda, Iradukunda Elsa yatangiye ubukangurambaga bwo gufatanya nâ€™inzobere zâ€™abaganga kuvura ku buntu abafite uburwayi bwâ€™ishaza,Uyu mukobwa wâ€™imyaka 19 yateguye iki gikorwa kizamara iminsi igera kuri irindwi.', '<p>Miss Iradukunda yagiye mu Karere ka Rubavu mu mpera zâ€™icyumweru \r\ngishize , azahamara iminsi igera kuri irindwi yita ku bafite ibibazo \r\nbyâ€™uburwayi bwo kutabona neza. Kuri uyu wa Mbere tariki ya 15 Gicurasi \r\n2017 yafashije abantu 40 bavurwa ku buntu ndetse ngo azavayo havuwe \r\nabagera kuri 200 barwaye ishaza.</p><p><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/whatsapp_image_2017-05-15_at_11.02.43_pm-4b80c.jpg?1494918959\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\"></p>\r\n<p>Uyu mukobwa wâ€™imyaka 19 yateguye iki gikorwa cyo kuvura aba bantu ku \r\nbuntu yifashishije inzobere zâ€™abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Kabgayi.</p>\r\n<p>Urwaye ishaza ntabona neza ndetse iyo areba ikintu aba abona kirimo \r\nibihu nâ€™urumuri rwinshi, ibi bikamubuza kureba neza. Iyi ndwara ikunze \r\nkwibasira 20% byâ€™abarengeje imyaka 65, ikaba ifata 60% byâ€™abarenze \r\nimyaka 85.</p><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1080px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/whatsapp_image_2017-05-15_at_11.02.29_pm-fa434.jpg?1494918959\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Umuyobozi wâ€™ibyo bitaro, Maj Dr Kanyankore William, yavuze ko \r\nubuyobozi bwâ€™ibitaro bwishimiye iki gikorwa cyateguwe na Nyampinga wâ€™u \r\nRwanda dore ko mu minsi ishize bari basigaye bohereza abarwayi kwivuriza\r\n mu bitaro bya Kabgayi nyuma yâ€™uko mugenga wâ€™inzobere wakoreraga i \r\nRubavu ubu yimuriwe i Kibuye.</p>\r\n<p>Ibitaro bya Gisenyi ngo byoherezaga abarwayi bâ€™ishaza nibura bagera \r\nku ijana buri kwezi, ariko ubu Nyampinga ngo aruhuye benshi kuko \r\nubukangurambaga bwe buzasiga abagera kuri magana abiri bavuwe kandi ku \r\nbuntu.</p>\r\n<p>Yagize ati â€œKuba Nyampinga yahisemo kuza ku Bitaro bya Gisenyi \r\naruhuye benshi mu barwayi bari baroherejwe ku bitaro byisumbuye ariko \r\nbakaba bari barabuze ubushobozi bwo kujyayo. Ubu bagiye kuvurirwa hafi \r\nkandi ku buntu, ubu umurwayi ari gusabwa amafaranga yo gusuzumwa yaba \r\nagomba kubagwa akabikorerwa ku buntu.â€</p>\r\n<p>Iradukunda Elsa yavuze ko yahisemo gukorera iki gikorwa mu Ntara \r\nyâ€™Uburengerazuba mu rwego rwo gushimira no kwitura abo muri aka gace \r\nyiyamamarijemo. Yashimiye byimazeyo abaganga bo mu Bitaro bya Kabgayi \r\nbemeye kuza kwifatanya na we kugira ngo batange ubu buvuzi.</p><p>Miss IRADUKUNDA&nbsp; akomeje kugaragaza umuco wogufasha yita cyane cyane kubabaye .<br></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1000px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/whatsapp_image_2017-05-15_at_11.02.03_pm-afbe1.jpg?1494918958\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Miss Iradukunda Elsa yafashije abantu 40 barwaye ishaza bavurwa ku buntu, azava i Rubavu avuje abasaga 200</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center>\r\n<p>Yagize ati â€œNyuma yo kuganira nâ€™ibitaro bya Kabgayi bakambwira ko 53%\r\n byâ€™abarwaye amaso bashobora kuvurwa bagakira nifuje gutangiza gahunda \r\nyo kuvura abarwayi bafite ikibazo cyâ€™ishaza bityo mpitamo guhera i \r\nRubavu kuko ariho natorewe bikaba bizagera mu gihugu hose nifashishije \r\nizina rya Miss nkagirira baturage akamaro.â€</p>\r\n<p>Iki gikorwa kizamara iminsi itanu gikorwa ndetse Nyampinga \r\nazagikurikirana kuva kigitangira kugeza gisojwe nyuma azasura \r\nabanyeshuri yemeye kwishyurira ishuri biga ku ishuri ribanza rya \r\nRusamaza mu Murenge wa Rugerero, azavayo anasuye urubyiruko ruri \r\nkugororerwa ku kirwa cya Iwawa.</p>\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1080px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/whatsapp_image_2017-05-15_at_11.02.09_pm-59cfd.jpg?1494918958\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1080px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/whatsapp_image_2017-05-15_at_11.02.26_pm-b8ec4.jpg?1494918959\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"667\" width=\"1000\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1080px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1080px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http