(82, '2017-05-20 11:22:34', 'Ese niki cyaba cyihishe inyuma yizimira  rya zimwe muri  kirazira n\'indangagaciro by\'umuco nyarwanda?!', 'Abasheshe akanguhe bemeza ko uko imyaka igenda  n\'Umuco Nyarwanda ariko ugenda ugana mu marembera kuko bavugako ibyo bafataga nka kirazira bisigaye ari ibisanzwe bitagihabwa agaciro cyane cyane Mumijyi byumwihariko uwa Kigali aho iterambere rizana nÂ¡Â¯imico mvamahanga. ', '<br>&nbsp;Bitewe nÂ¡Â¯agaciro Abanyarwanda bahaga imwe mu migenzo ariko ubu ikaba ibonwa nkÂ¡Â¯iyashaje, bamwe mu basheshe akanguhe bababazwa cyane nÂ¡Â¯uko abenshi bibagiwe umuco wakabaranze ukabatandukanya nÂ¡Â¯amahanga nkÂ¡Â¯uko bimwe mu bihugu nkÂ¡Â¯u Buhinde cyangwa u Bushinwa biwurambaho. <br>Ibi rero bikaba bikomeje gutera impungenge ababyeyi nabarezi ndetse abasheshakanguhe bo babifata nko kurimbura nkana umuco nyarwanda hazanwa umuco wamahanga abasheshe akanguhe bafata nkicyasha mumuco.<br>Izi ni zimwe muri kirazira zibagiranye zisigaye mumateka gusa,<br>I. Cyaraziraga ko umugore ubyaye impanga ahamagara sebukwe na nyirabukwe kuko byafatwaga nkÂ¡Â¯amahano, ariko ababikoze ubu bafatwa nkÂ¡Â¯abatazi aho isi igeze.<br><br>II. Cyaraziraga gusomeza (kunywesha) amata inyama cyangwa imegeri, ariko bimwe mu biribwa nka sambusa, gozete nÂ¡Â¯ibindi bikorwa mu nyama kandi bigakoreshwa ahenshi mu Mujyi wa Kigali nÂ¡Â¯ahandi Bisomezwa amata .<br>III. Cyaraziraga ko umukobwa yaryama yifashe hagati yÂ¡Â¯amaguru, babyitaga gukungura, ariko ubu ubivuze baguha inkwenene,<br><br>IV. Cyaraziraga ko umukobwa arya ihene kuko ngo byari gutuma amera ubwanwa, Ariko abubu ntibazirebera izuba.<br><br>V. Cyaraziraga ko umukobwa anyara mu rugo rwa musaza we rutahamo inka, ngo zipfira gushira, Ariko ibyo ubu Birakorwa cyane.<br>VI. Cyaraziraga ko umukobwa akenyera umweko wa nyina, nubwo ubu yasimuwe nÂ¡Â¯imikandara, aho usanga abana nab a nyina bambarana.<br><br>Abasaza baba mu Mujyi wa Kigali twaganiriye bo bavuga ko nÂ¡Â¯ikinyarwanda ubwacyo kitakibonerwa umwimerere wacyo mu bakiri bato kuko kivangwa cyane.<br><br>Haruna Gashumba wÂ¡Â¯imyaka 79 wavukiye ahitwa i Butamwa we yagize ati Â¡Â°None se umuntu yavuga ko umuco ugihari ate mu gihe nta nÂ¡Â¯uvuga Ikinyarwanda cyiza iminota gusa? uretse ibyo imyambaro yÂ¡Â¯urubyiruko rwÂ¡Â¯iki gihe ni agahomamunwa.Â¡Â±<br>Ibyo byose rero ngo Bikaba Bikomeje Gutera Benshi impungenge, Doreko Ko Benshi Bemeza ko byoroshye Kwandura imico yahandi kubera iterambere ryitumanaho, na Murandasi ikabifashamo urubyiruko kwigana abo mubihugu byateye imbere binyuze Mumbuga nkoranya mbaga.<br><br>NDIZEYE Lionel', '1495272154122.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 14, 'head', 665);
