(83, '2017-05-23 12:24:00', 'IBISiGO ndetse ni IBYIVUGO bimwe mu Biranga umuco nyarwanda bigenda bicika intege   \"Nsubirize umwami mu rushya\" Soma iki gisigo Kirarata intsinzi yâ€™u Rwanda ku Bumpaka ho muri Uganda, yo mu mwaka wa 186.', ' Kuva kera na kare Abanyarwanda bagize umwihariko wabo muri wo bakagira mo IBISINGIZO,IBISIGO,IBYIVUGO nibindi \"Nsubirize umwami mu rushya\" Iki gisigo kiri mu bwoko bwâ€™Ikobyo, cyahanzwe na Nyakayonga. Kirarata intsinzi yâ€™u Rwanda ku Bumpaka ho muri Uganda, yo mu mwaka wa 186.', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><b>Mu Rwagasabo kuva kera nakare,Bene Kanyarwanda bagira umwihariko utasanga ahandi,IBISIGO kimwe mubiranga abanyarwanda ubundi iyo bahimbarwaga cyangwa bari mu maringoshyo bagiraga umwanya uhagije wo gutarama, Abasizi bagakora mu nganzo maze bagakeza Igitamo. <br></b></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><b>Iki gisigo kiri mu bwoko bwâ€™Ikobyo, cyahanzwe na Nyakayonga. Kirarata \r\nintsinzi yâ€™u Rwanda ku Bumpaka ho muri Uganda, yo mu mwaka wa 186.</b></p><b>\r\n</b><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nsubirize umwami&nbsp; mu rushya</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">None atsinze ishyanga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Atabarukanye ishya,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Batwe-i-Nyange</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">005 Ba Mukenuka-Magambo na Mudakenesha,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Barwanye mu Gakoni.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Shyanga rinyura i Shyunga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ryatomora ubusembwa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nâ€™imirase yakura i Gisange.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">010 Ngozi, Rwamagana-macwa.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ye mwega abacu,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abo ku Rucunda</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abâ€™i Rwanga-gucubira,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mucanira Gaca-nkamba</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">015 Aciye abahizi inka.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Na njye ngihari nihangane nisuganye, nisaruze</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nsubire mu myambazo nkwibwire.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nsigire Umwami uko nsanzwe,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nibwire Gisanura</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">020 We wansamye akansazura,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Akansubiza i bugongo bwa njye.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mukobanya ko urwana ukomeje</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nakumva ngakirimbira,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ijabo rikamvuna.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">025 Ndi inkoro nabije inkara</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ugwije indashi ya twese,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Icyo utabariye uragitahanye.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndagira ngo nkenkemure</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nkereranye nihunde imyishywa,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">030 Twizihirwe mu ngoro umu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nsanganize umugabe impundu,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nâ€™ishimwe, nâ€™ibirato</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Muratire amahanga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bitare bitamuye inzobe,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">035 Baziga, Batazimbwa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bazima bo mwa Mbabay-imbavu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Batura, Batukura baraye mu Ntuku</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bagatera&nbsp; i Mututu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kiruta-minyago, Myano-mike</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">040 Rugarura-byaro, Nyiri i Nduga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Udutsindiye Ndagura.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nduhiye wari uvuye</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I Nyamikobe ya Ruteteza,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mutambira-ngoma</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">045 Mutima utanga utaziganya Mutazigwa,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mutabarukira kuronka.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Muronko urampe umubano</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mpigure Ndagano,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Indagu yanjye iratashye.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">050 Dore ko wagwije amatungo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ugumya kungukira mwo ayandi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Urundurira mu yawe</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">U Rwanda rwasazwe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abahe nâ€™abahange wabahagije</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">055 Na njye ngihari nje kukwitura,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nguture ineza yuzuye</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nâ€™inganzo yuzuye,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ubwuzu bwawe mbuhorana ku mutima.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndakwibuka sindyame ngo nsinzire</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">060 Ariko nakubona nkaberwa imihayo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngahimbarwa amagambo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Buhabiro, Buhungiro</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mpinga-nzima, Rugaba-bihumbi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Zina ryagutse inzeru nâ€™inzugu</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">065 Mukuguha ingoma,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ntarakaguharika bakeba</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ibitwerera wabitembagaje ku ngoma.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Na twe abakubita-mbari</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Intiti zitari intunda-matama,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">070 Nimuze twitegure dusanganire</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umwami yatabarutse,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abandi batadutanga ibirori.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yemwega abacu benge,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ubwenge mugira mubukoza iki?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">075 Nimuze duhimbye imihayo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dusukiranye imisango yâ€™ingoma,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Duhimbye igicumbi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Sinabera isibe mu busaza.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ubukuru ntibwankura ku mwuga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">080 Nameze amajerwe atari mwo ubujogo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nzarinda nihwitira.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rudahinyuka uko wampatse utaramparuruka</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umpakana umwishyo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nsakaze nsese urukundo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">085 Rwari mwo urundi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Urwo wankunze ntirwakuyeho.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umvunye nkuvumire abanzi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ubice mbace inkwanzi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Iyo mijyo nzayibuze amajyo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">090 Ndi umusobanura wâ€™amagambo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndi umuhanuzi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nâ€™uko nahannye intumva</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Baranga barandengera,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bashyingura indiga mu nda.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">095 Nti : nzabwira abanyumvira,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abayoboke bâ€™Umwami si bake.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nimucyo twibumbe</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Twimane nâ€™iyi Mana yâ€™i Rwanda,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nakubana iki?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">100 Ruhiga wangize umuhizi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngo nguhiganire nâ€™amahanga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndihandagaza duhuza inama</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nyiri i Nkoma namukaburiye ibikago,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Igikuba kiracika kwa Gica-ruzi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">105 Ngo Zuba araguye.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nabifatiye ku ruhanga,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nigize impamagazi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nkâ€™ingoma yâ€™impuruza,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nti : yamwica Rugomberera</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">110 Yamwica Rugondo rwâ€™Imfizi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Arambitse ingogo i Kabarore kâ€™Abahanza</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ako kaba akarorero,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yâ€™uko Yuhi abarusha ubugabo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nabansembya ngo ndasebanya,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">115 Simbisembereza sinzabasuhukira</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngira uwanyemeye.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nemewe nâ€™Imbonwa yabonywe nâ€™Imana</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nyimera hambavu,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndi uwa Mukanza</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">120 Ndi uwa Rukangira-batimbo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndi umwiru wâ€™iyi ngoma.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Negamiye urugangazi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ninjiye mu nzu ntazasohoka mwo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bitero, icyanteranije nâ€™Abami bâ€™i Swa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">125 Nâ€™uko twasaritse kera,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mbaroga urubashyitsa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mbatera igishyika.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kwa Cyumya icyago nabasigiye</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Cyabaye icyorezo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">130 I swa&nbsp; iyo ndi i Sake</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nitwa Gasema-ntambara.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">I Gisaka nâ€™u Bugesera ni jye bazira</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Narabasheshaguje ingoma,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bayiheruka ubwo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">135 Rushika ndamushinyagurira</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nti: yamwica Gacura-nkumbi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yamuvugira hejuru Rwambara-micuzo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ibya Bazimya byagiye ubwo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Migongo ayiteranya na Buganza,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">140 Ngo nibarembe bahakwe</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Uwashumbirijwe yisunga umugabo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mugaba-nyinshi, Mugaba-jana</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mugabanya-joro wa Jembe,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umva ko nkubwira impaka ziboneye</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">145 Ntaboba ku rurimi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nabibeshya abo ntibibare.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Burabakereye, henga avane ruhande</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ahindukire abahinge ubudehe,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abo bahinza nta we azasiga</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">150 Azabasangiza ibambo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ruvukura, Ruvunya-ntwari</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mvunya nkuvugire amacumu yâ€™abanzi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nzabarire Muca-nkamba, Mucuma-ngendo</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Cumu ryica icyigenge.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">155 Ni Nkubira, ni Nkomati</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Akoranya ubuto buri mwo ubutwari,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rwamahungu ntiyiganda, ntaganyiriza.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yahungiye abâ€™ijuru inyuma,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nâ€™abarambira arabarambika.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">160 None dore ibyo bihanga</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Asize i Bumpaka nâ€™i Ruhinda,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Byabaye agahabwa, ni agahorero.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abungeri baracyabihanuriza</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngo uyu Mwami wakize ntibazamuhimbira,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">165 Bazamuhungira kure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rwikubira-shema</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mwami wâ€™ishema,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ishema wimanye ugihabwa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Murekezi utarerekerana nâ€™ababisha,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">170 Ngo uzashira uburakari bashize.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umva ingoma yâ€™ingunge</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mbwirana akarusho,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ko tubarusha Umwami nyakuri</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Wegamiye ubukuru.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">175 Nagumirize abakurane umusanzu nâ€™umuganda</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rusumba-mitwe yarabisumbuye arabasumba,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bikwigereranya, bihimbira</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Izina ritari iryabo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rifite nyiraryo, Muganwa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">180 Umugabe ubakuye imigabo mu nda,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngabo-nzima, iminsi ni imibarwa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mvuye kugusuzumira ku Gisenyi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ndeba ko bishubiranyije</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">None nje kugutakira.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">185 Nigize intasi nsanga zibogoza,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Zica injishi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Zanga abakamyi nâ€™abakamisha,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngo ni wowe zishaka,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umuhunguzi wa Gahaya</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">190 None gira ukome ibihindizo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Useture ingundu ubutazisiga inyuma</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abazikuburanya bigire aha,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bagaragare bazigarame imbere.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Zitahe i Bwami bwâ€™itanganika</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">195 No mu bitega byâ€™ingabe,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">No mu mirwa iteze amaraba</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kwa Bitate na Matungiro,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ku Mugongo kwa Rugambw-amazima.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bigambirize Mugabe uganje</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">200 Utsinze imikiko uyigejeje kure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Urengeje inkweto</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Aho abandi batageza,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Weho urahigereye,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Wigaruriye ibyo byaro.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">205 Mbe Baganwa muri Migabo ki?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngarambe yarenze inganizi</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mwami wa Rwogogoza mukimuhungira he?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abo bari bashyamiranye</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Yabashyinguye mu byobo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">210 Rugaragara mu ngoma</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Byunguko, nungutse inkuru yawe,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nkunzi irakunkumbuza.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nzi ko urwana intambara itarekana,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Murenzi warimbuye imbaga</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">215 Ya bene Murinja.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ejo numva ko kwa Mwendo rwabaye</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rubaga yanshubije mwo urubango,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Kabego yamusutse ho imigina</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Impamvu ari we ivuyeho,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">220 Aramuzingira amazinga-burago.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Baroba nimumpe umwito</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mbabwire imyato yâ€™uyu Mwami,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ntako atabaruka ubusa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Narabaze ndasigwa,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">225 Ngiye gusobanura nsaga ku ijana.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mpakanyiki, urampake</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Uko unduzi uku,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Umpakiye mu zabukuru</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Sinkikora mu ngabo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">230 Ubugabo nagiraga bwaragabanutse</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ubugunde burangamburuje.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nsigaye mbaririza ibirari warengeye,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nti: uyu Mwami mwamundangira he?</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Bati: ari iyâ€™ibihugu biherera</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">235 Ngo arabicira kutabasigira indamyi,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngo arabanyaga inkubirane</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngo Ndarigize ararwana nka Ndoli.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Dore uko umugabo akamirwa nâ€™umuheto</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rukorera-mizo, abanzi arabakembera ku rugendo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">240 Yemwega abâ€™i Butanga-mpundu</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nimumuhe impundu zivuge umutuzo,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ziremereze zishyira i Mutakara</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Na bwo ubutaka bukwitabye kurorera,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ngo: kagarishye se Nyamurwana.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">245 Wihaye ubugabo nâ€™ingoma yawe</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Utsinze amagomerane na bya bihugu,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Urabyihariye ubirambirije mwo.</p><br><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><i><b>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs</b></i><br></p>', '1495535040122.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 14, 'head', 650),
(84, '2017-05-24 12:40:54', 'Ese Twitege Iki Umwaka utaha Muri Shampiyona Yubwongereza?! Chelsea na none? Cyangwa nindi! dore uburyo bwonyine bushoboka ngo ibe yakamburwa igikombe.', 'Buri wese ukurikirana umupira w\'abongereza yakibaza ibi bibazo bikurikira, Ese Niki cyo kwitega Umwaka Utaha Muri Shampiyona Ya Bongereza? Ese Igikundi Kirutse inyuma Ya Chelsea cyazayihigika Umwaka Utaha? Cyangwa nubundi izongera itware  igikombe?', 'Chelsea Yegukanye igikombe namanota 93 , amanota 7 niyo yarushije \r\niyayikurikiye, Mugihe yo yashyiragaho agahigo gashya muri shampiyona \r\nyabongereza Premier League ko gutwara igikombe ifite intsinzi \r\nnyishi,intinzi 30.<br> ese ni gute esheshatu zirangije inyuma ya Chelsea zazayihigika 2017-18?<br>Chelsea\r\n yatsinzwe imikino itanu, kurusha Tottenham yo yatakaje ine bisa Nkibya \r\nManchester united nayo yatsinzwe imikino itanu, gusa yo kubera \r\nubushobozi yagaragaje Bwo Kwitwara neza ntinganye imikino myinshi \r\nBiyigeza Kugikombe. <br>Iyi Premier League ya 2016/17 yari yuzuyemo \r\nguhangana gukomeye ko kurwego rwohejuru ikaba inasize ikipe ya Arsenal \r\nhanze yenye zambere (Big Four) zizerekeza muri Champions League, Gusa \r\nesheshatu zaje inyuma ya Chelsea nazo zabonye neza uko kwiruka utareba \r\nkuruhande byakugeza kure.<br>Hagati yikipe zirindwi zambere nizisigaye \r\nharimo ikinyuranyo cy\'amanota 15 , ikipe nka Southampton cyangwa na \r\nLeicester iyi yatwaye igikombe cyumwaka ushize, bikaba bigaragaza ko \r\nbitazazorohera kuba zakongera kugaruka muri zirindwi zambere mugihe \r\nbyagaragaye ko uyu mwaka utazigendekeye neza, cyangwa igitangaza kikaba \r\ncyakongera kikagaruka nk\'Ibirura bitwara shampiyona Muri 2016,Nubwo \r\nbigaragara ko bitapfa kongera kuba. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;\r\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br>ubu haribazwa niba izi kipe zaje inyuma ya chelsea zayambura iki igikombe . <br>Aha tugiye kurebera hamwe niki amakipe yazakosora &nbsp;akaba yabasha guhagarara imbere ya chelsea umwaka utaha,<br>Duhere kuri:<br>Tottenham Hotspur ( Yarushijwe 7)<br><br>Iyi\r\n niyo yariyoboye izirukaga kuri chelsea. Spurs yari hafi yo kugikozaho \r\nimitwe yintoki ngo itware Premier League yayo yambere. <br>Iyi yagaragaje Ubwugarizi Bwambere, ubusatirizi Bwiza ndetse nubufatanye bwabo hagati bwabyitwayemo neza. <br><br>Niba\r\n koko Totenham ishaka igikombe icyambere isabwa nukugumana abeza Bayo \r\nntibareke ngo bagende. Birashoboka ko Kyle Walker ashobora kugende gusa \r\nagiye wenyina ntacyo bitwaye; hanyuma abandi nka Danny Rose, Eric Dier, \r\nToby Alderweireld, Dele Alli na Harry Kane, Totenham ikihangana \r\nikabagumana. <br><br>Gusa na none Spurs ikeneye Kugura. Ikeneye kuba \r\nyagura nibura umwe cyangwa Babiri, Bo kurwego rwo Hejuru Bakongera \r\nimbaraga Hagati Bo gukinira Kukibuga kigari cya Wembley Bazakiriraho \r\nimikino 19 yo murugo Muri Shampiyona itaha nanone kandi igomba gushaka \r\nundi Mukinnyi ugomba Gufasha Kane. <br><br>Manchester City ( Yarushijwe 15)<br><br>Gabriel\r\n Jesus, Raheem Sterling, Leroy Sane na Kevin De Bruyne nibamwe \r\nMubishimiwe nabafana biyi kipe Gusa na none ntawamenya niba abandi nka \r\nDavid Silva na Sergio Aguero Bazahaguma<br> Gusa ikigaragara Mwiyi kipe \r\nnuko ikibazo cyayo atari ubusatirizi, ahubwo Abinyuma Ba City Bose uko \r\nari Batanu Bakeneye Kongerwamo imbaraga kuko ubwugarizi Butameze Neza \r\nNiba bifuza koko kuzahanganira na Chelsea igikombe umwaka utaha. \r\nIcyambere cyihutirwa nugushaka Umuzamu, ndetse na Myugariro wo Hagati wo\r\n Guhanganira Umwanya na John Stones, Nicolas Otamendi ndetse na Vincent \r\nKompany ndetse City ikanagura Umukinnyi winyuma kuruhande ukina agaruka.\r\n Gusa kugura Umukinnyi umwe cyangwa Babiri ntacyo byamara; nibura City \r\nikeneye abakinnyi bane, Mugihe ikeneye Numukinnyi wo hagati ndetse niyo \r\nYaya Toure yaba yasinye undi mwaka. <br><br>Liverpool &nbsp;(Yarushijwe 17)<br><br>Liverpool\r\n ikeneye gushaka umuti wuburyo yatsinda amakipe mato. Iyi Liverpool \r\nikaba itarigeze itsindwa na zirindwi zimbere kurutonde, gusa nayo \r\namanota menshi yayataye kumakipe yinyuma.<br>ikipe &nbsp;West Ham, Swansea City, Bournemouth na Crystal Palace zose zabashije kuyiteshereza Murugo i anfield. <br>Myugariro\r\n wo hagati wo guhabwa inshingano zo kuyobora ba myugariro, byumwihariko \r\nkumipira yimiterekano arakenewe, ari nako hakenewe myugariro winyuma \r\nkuruhande rw\'ibumoso wo kuza gufasha ba myugariro, kuko byaza gufasha \r\nakazi gakorwa na Alberto Moreno na James Milner. <br><br>Na none kandi \r\nhakaba hakenewe umukinnyi wo kuruhande rwimbere unyaruka. Hakarebwa \r\nnikibazo cyubusatirizi Liverpool igaragaza igihe Sadio Mane adahari, \r\ngusa habonetse rutahizamu uza ari butsinde nibura hejuru y\'ibitego 20 \r\nbyafasha ikipe. <br><br>Arsenal (18 Yarushijwe)<br>Aba barashi Nibo \r\nbonyine &nbsp;Murizikipe zirindwi zimbere bagiye kwinjira mugihe cyigura \r\nnigurisha batazi akazoza Kumutoza wabo ndetse buzakomezakubakomerera \r\nkugeza hemejwe uzagumana iyi kipe mu mwaka utaha wa shampiyona. Ikindi \r\nkandi nukumenya, niba aguma ari Arsene Wenger cyangwa undi wo \r\nkumusimbura , gusa ibigaragarira amaso byo nuko iyi kipe ikeneye \r\nimpinduka.<br>Petr Cech nawe yungamo ati &nbsp;hakenewe umukinnyi wo hagati \r\nmukibuga wo kuza kuziba icyuho cyasizwe na Santi Cazorla nyuma yuko \r\nuyumwaka ubaye mubi. <br><br>Arsenal igomba kuzana Umwataka ukomeye wo \r\nkuza guhanganira umwanya na Danny Welbeck, mugihe kwizera kugumana \r\nAlexis Sanchez byo bikiri ihurizo. Abandi nka Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain, \r\nbagomba guhabwa amasezerano mashya. <br>Muriyi shampiyona na none \r\nArsenal yongeye kwibasirwa ninvune, bityo rero ikipe ya Arsenal ikeneye \r\ngushakira umuti ikibazo cyubuvuzi. <br><br>Manchester United ( Yarushijwe 24) <br><br>Jose\r\n Mourinho ntakindi atunga urutoki uretse invune ikipe ye yahuye nazo, \r\nzikaze imbere mubyamubujije amanota, gusa iyikipe icyambere ikeneye \r\nnukubanza abakinnyi bayo bakavurwa , hakabaho kuganirizwa &nbsp;ndetse no \r\nguhuza umukino. Gusa bikaba byiza igihe Mourinho yagerageza korohera \r\nabakinnyi no kuba inshuti nabo buri gihe , urugero warukura kuri Conte \r\nna Pochettino. <br>Umukinnyi winyuma kuruhande rwibumoso nawe arakenewe,\r\n dore ko bigaragara ko Mourinho atizeye neza Luke Shaw, hakanashakwa \r\numukinnyi wo Mukibuga hagati wo kuza gufasha Paul Pogba na Ander Herrera\r\n dore ko Michael Carrick ari kugenda akuramo ake karenge. <br><br>Nyuma \r\nnanyuma, hategerejwe umwataka utazuyaza imbere yizamu ikipe ya Man.U \r\nigomba kuzana, dore ko hakenewe uwo kuza gusimbura Zlatan Ibrahimovic \r\nwahetse iyi kipe uyu mwaka ariko invune ntizimworohere. <br><br>Everton ( Yarushijwe 32) <br><br>Iyi yo ntigomba kugurisha Ross Barkley na Romelu Lukaku. <br><br><br>(nubwo bigaragar ko, bitayikundira kuza muzimbere.&nbsp; Abafana ba, Everton mukomeze kwihangana...)<br><br><br>KUVA Kera imikino,imyidagaduro mu muco Nyarwanda byahozeho aho abanyarwanda bakiranaga,bakamasha bagakora ndetse imyitozo ngorora mubiri.<br><br>Byanditswe na NDIZEYE Lionel', '1495622454EPL.jpg', 0, 'admin', 6, 9, 'sub', 172),
(85, '2017-05-27 12:24:30', 'Amateka ya Nyagakecuru wo mu bisi bya Huye DUTEMBERE: Mu bisi bya Huye no kwa Nyagakecuru wari uhatuye yarigometse ku mwami  Amateka na- AMAFOTO', 'Amateka nâ€™umuco ni bimwe mu bintu biha umwimerere igihugu, umuryango cyangwa igice cyâ€™abaturage runaka. Hari uburyo bwinshi amateka agenda ahererekanwamo, ntazimangatane yewe nâ€™ubwo haba hashize imyaka myinshi.', '<p align=\"left\"><strong>Nyagakecuru&nbsp; wari utuye mu bisi bya Huye ubu biri mu karere \r\nka Huye. Nyagakecuru uyu&nbsp; ubusanzwe izina rye ryari Benginzage akaba \r\nyari umugore wâ€™umugabo witwa Samukende.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Amateka akunda kumuvuga nkâ€™umugore wari ukomeye&nbsp; kandi uzwi cyane \r\nkuruta umugabo we Samukende. Samukende amateka ntagaragaza ibigwi bye \r\nyewe ntanagaragaza niba yarabaye umwami&nbsp; wâ€™iyo mpugu yariku mukika \r\nwâ€™umusozi wa Huye kumanuka ugana Nyakibanda yâ€™abaseminali kugeza ku \r\nBurundi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Ingoma yâ€™Ubungwe (Abenengwe)</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Iki gihugu cyari gikikijwe&nbsp; mu majyepfo nâ€™uruzi rwâ€™Akanyaru&nbsp; intara \r\nya Ngozi na Kayanza, mu Rwanda cyri gikikijwe&nbsp; na Buganza yâ€™epfo, \r\nBashumba na Nyakare.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Gusa Nyagakecuru uvugwa mu ngoma yâ€™abenengwe&nbsp; yari umwamikazi \r\n(umugore wâ€™umwami) wâ€™igihugu cyitwaga Bungwe. Ingoma ngabe yabo yitwaga&nbsp;\r\n Nyamibande. Ubwoko bwabo bwari abenengwe ikirangabwoko cyabo ari ingwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Cyari igihugu gikomeye ku buryo ku ngoma yâ€™abanyiginya mu rwanda byari byarananiranye kwigarurira u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Iyo hataba amayeri yo gutanga igitambo&nbsp; igihugu cya Nyagakecuru nticyari kwigarurirwa</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Urugamba rwo kwigarurira u Bungwe rwatangiye ahagana ku ngoma ya \r\nRuganzu. Bimwe&nbsp; mu bitekerezo byo kwagura ingoma nyiginya bigaragaza ko u\r\n Bungwe (igihugu cya Nyagakecuru ) cyaba cyarigaruriwe na Ruganzu Ndoli.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ikirari cyo kwigarurira&nbsp; iyo ngoma kivugwa ku ngoma ya Yuhi II \r\nGahima. Yuhi II gahima yari&nbsp; umuhungu wa Mibambwe I Sekarongoro I \r\nMutabazi. Uyu ni we watangiye uburyo bwo gushaka&nbsp; uko yazigarurira \r\nigihugu cyâ€™u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>&nbsp;Uko byagenze</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu gushaka uko igihugu cyâ€™Abenengwe cyatsindwa nâ€™ u Rwanda yashatse \r\ngukoresha inzira yâ€™ubucengeri(ubutabazi). Abapfumu bagaragaje ko \r\nkugirango u Bungwe butsindwe murumuna wa Nyagakecuru witwaga Nyankaka \r\nagomba kujya kwa&nbsp; Samukende akaba mukeba wa mukuruwe hanyuma umwana wa \r\nmbere akazamubyarira mu rwanda ku buryo ari we uzatsinda u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu kugenza gutyo&nbsp; hateganywaga ko nibura umwuzukuru wa Gahima ari we wagombaga kugira uruhare mu kwigarurira u Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyankaka yagiye kwa Samukende aramurongora ariko atazi icyari \r\nkigambiriwe. Amaze gutwara inda yagarutse i Rwanda &nbsp;ahabyaririra \r\numuhungu wiswe Binama.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu Binama aho amariye gukurira ni we wagiye gutabarira u rwanda \r\nBucengeri. Nyuma&nbsp; ni ho u Bungwe bwafashwe ndetse buratsindwa. Ingoma \r\nngabe Nyamibande ifatwa ubwo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Amateka yâ€™ imitsindirwe&nbsp; ya Bungwe ihurizwa ku bami babiri aribo \r\nRuganzu wa II Ndoli nâ€™umuhungu we Mutara I Semugeshi bitaga Muyenzi.</p><p align=\"left\"><br></p><p align=\"left\"><strong><em>Twibukiranye amateka y\'ibi bisi bya Huye</em></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ibisi ubundi mu Kinyarwanda bisobanura uruhererekane rwâ€™imisozi. \r\nIbisi bya Huye, kuri ubu biherereye mu karere ka Huye mu ntara \r\nyâ€™Amajyepfo, ni umusozi muremure ufite ubutumburuke bugera kuri metero \r\n2400. Ni ahantu hateye amabengeza dore ko ugeze mu bushorishori bwâ€™uyu \r\nmusozi asanganirwa nâ€™akayaga gahuhera ndetse nâ€™isura nziza yâ€™indi misozi\r\n migufi kuri uyu. Kuwuzamuka bisaba iminota iri hagati ya 50 na 60 \r\nnâ€™amaguru. Uyu musozi wambaye ishyamba ririmo ibiti bitandukanye \r\nibyinshi bya kimeza, ibiti byambika uyu musozi ubwiza ndetse \r\nnâ€™amahumbezi &nbsp;adasanzwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><em>Uwo Nyagakecuru wahatuye we ni muntu ki?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu Nyagakecuru yamenyekanye cyane ku ngoma yâ€™umwami Ruganzu wa II \r\nNdoli. Yari umugore ubundi witwaga Beginzage afite umugabo witwaga \r\nSamukende. Amateka ntagaruka cyane kuri uyu mugabo wa Beginzage, nyamara\r\n ahubwo agaruka kuri Beginzage wari warahimbwe Nyagakecuru nyine, nyuma \r\nyo kwigomeka ndetse no kuzengereza uyu mwami Ruganzu.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uku kwigomeka kwatangiye ubwo umwami Ruganzu yashakaga kwigarurira \r\nigihugu cyâ€™Ubungwe, ari na cyo Nyagakecuru uwo yari abereye umwamikazi, \r\nubwoko bwâ€™abo mu bungwe bwari Abenengwe. Bungwe.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu Nyagakecuru rero ngo yari yaranze gutanga amaturo ajya i bwami \r\nnkâ€™uko abandi baturage babigenzaga, nuko birakaza umwami, dore ko nâ€™ubwo\r\n umwami yajyaga yohereza ingabo gutera uyu mugore, zose zatsindwaga.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Itongo ryâ€™uyu Nyagakecuru riri mu bushorishori bwâ€™uyu musozi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><em>Reka dutemberane ibisi bya Huye mu mafoto noneho:</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>Amafu atangwa nâ€™ibiti biri kuri uyu musozi bituma uwuzamuka atumva umunaniro cyane</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335569_b30a9159_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335569_b30a9159_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Uyu musozi wambaye ishyamba ryâ€™ibiti bitandukanye</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Reka twihute tugere ku bushorishori, kuko ibanga ryâ€™aha ni ho rizingiye...</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><br></p><p align=\"left\">Twegere hirya gato dusure itongo rya Nyagakecuru wavuzwe haruguru. \r\nBirumvikana ko tutari buhasange inzu ye cyangwa se ibindi bimenyetso \r\nbinini byerekana ko hari hatuwe, nyamara haragaragara.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335570_b30a9185_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335570_b30a9185_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Ng\'ibi ibiti byo mu bwoko bwâ€™ibitovu byaba mu marembo yâ€™urugo rwe, bivugwa ko byari birebire</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyagakecuru, uvugwaho kuba yari afite izindi mbaraga zidasanzwe \r\n(ibirozi), ngo yaba yari afite inzoka nini zamurindaga zari zituriye mu \r\nrugo iwe. Ntagoo turi bubashe kuzibona, ariko imyobo yazo yo turayibona.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9192_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9192_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9193_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9193_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;<em>Ng\'iyi imyobo izo nzoka za Nyagakecuru zari zituyemo ubwo yari ariho</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyagakecuru kandi yari afite aho yajyaga kwisukurira, aho yajyanaga nâ€™abaja be nuko akajya \r\nkwiyuhagira. Twigiye hirya gato, turahasanga iryo riba.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9199_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335828_b30a9199_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Iriba Nyagakecuru yajyaga kwiyuhagiriraho nâ€™ubu riracyahari mu ishusho yâ€™ikizenga cyâ€™amazi.</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em></em><em>&nbsp;</em>Nyuma yo gusobanukirwa nâ€™amateka ya Nyagakecuru, reka noneho dutembere ubushorishori bwâ€™uyu musozi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9216_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9216_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335982_b30a9302_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335982_b30a9302_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Mu bushorishori wakirwa nâ€™utwatsi duherereye turushaho kongera ubwiza bwâ€™aha hantu</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9218_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335829_b30a9218_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Hakurya ibiti byiza biteye amabengeza biterausuye hano hantu gusubiranayo akanyamuneza</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335981_b30a9224_copy.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201612/attachments/1482335981_b30a9224_copy.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><em>Hakurya, indi misozi yongera isura nziza yâ€™aha hantu</em></p><p align=\"left\"><em><br></em></p><p><em><br></em></p><p><em>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></em></p>', '1495880670ibisi bya Huye - Copy.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 813),
(86, '2017-05-28 14:14:22', 'Amateka nâ€™inkomoko yâ€™urutare rwa Kamegeri nâ€™isomo rikomeye ukwiye kubikuramo AMATEKA-AMAFOTO', 'Uru rutare ruri mu Karere ka Ruhango rufite amateka menshi  Bitangaza benshi rukaba isomo rikomeye kubamenya amateka yarwo -ninkuru mpamo peee', '<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en-GB\" align=\"left\"><span dir=\"auto\">Urutare rwa Kamegeri</span></h1><p align=\"left\">Uru rutare rwitiriwe umugabo witwaga Kamegeri, akaba yararuboneyeho \r\nakaga yashakaga kugushamo abandi, bihita biba aka ya mvugo yâ€™umugani \r\nnyarwanda bagira bati: \"<i>Urucira mukaso rugatwara nyoko\".</i> Hari ibitabo bimwe bigaruka kuri aya mateka, aho usanga bamwita \"Kagemeri\" ariko izina nyaryo ni Kamegeri.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Kamegeri&nbsp;uyu yari umutware ku ngoma yâ€™umwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro \r\nII Gisanura, ahagana mu mwaka wâ€™1672. Kamegeri yitiriwe uru rutare, \r\nnyuma yâ€™uko barumutwikiyeho, ibyo bikaba byarabayeho ku itegeko \r\nryâ€™umwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, ibi akaba yarabyifuje \r\nnyuma yâ€™aho Kamegeri yari yabwiye umwami ko abazajya bagira nabi bazajya\r\n barujugunywaho rumaze gucanirwa.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/IMG/jpg/urutare_rwa_kamegeri.jpg\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"570\" width=\"480\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><dl class=\"spip_document_2972 spip_documents spip_documents_center\"><dt><br></dt></dl></div>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uyu mwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, yari azwiho ubwitonzi,\r\n kugira ubuntu, guha amata abakene begereye ibwami no kwanga akarengane.\r\n Ibyo byatumye bamuhimba igisingizo bamwita <strong>â€œRugabishabirengeâ€</strong> kuko yatangaga atitangiye itama. Yari azwiho kandi kuba umucamanza utabera kandi wangaga ko hatangwa ibihano bidakwiye umuntu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Umunsi umwe, Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II Gisanura, yabajije abatware \r\nbe igihano gisumba ibindi bumva umuntu mubi cyane mu gihugu yajya ahabwa\r\n , buri wese muri abo batware agenda avuga icye. Umwami yumvise hari \r\nabatware bifuriza rubanda ibihano birimo ubugome, maze asanze bikabije \r\nburi wese amuhanisha icyo yagiye avuga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Umutware witwaga Kamegeri, we yari yavuze ko igihano cyiza ari \r\nugusambura inzu ziri hafi aho, bagacaniriza urutare iyo sakamburiro \r\nkugeza aho urutare rutukura, noneho umuntu wâ€™umugome bakarumushyiraho \r\nagashirira. Umwami nyuma yo gutekereza kuri icyo gihano, yasanze nta \r\nmuntu mubi (wâ€™umugome) kurusha Kamegeri. Nuko aca iteka ko uwo Kamegeri \r\nbamuhanisha icyo gihano kibi yahimbiye abandi, noneho baramuboha \r\nbamujugunya ari muzima ku rutare bacaniriye rwatukuye nkâ€™uko \r\nyabyifurizaga abandi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Burya koko ngo umwami ntiyica, hica abamuhuza na rubanda kandi nabo \r\nari rubanda! Mu buzima busanzwe, hari ubwo abantu usanga bifuriza abandi\r\n ibibi nkâ€™uko Kamegeri yabikoze, ibyo bikaba byabatera kugambanira \r\nabandi, kubateranya ku bayobozi cyangwa abandi babakuriye, bakifuza ko \r\nikibi cyaba ku bandi. Ibi ariko abateye batyo bakwiye kubyitondera, \r\nbakamenya ko hari ubwo ikibi wifuriza abandi nawe gishobora kukugeraho.</p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ku bemera Imana, kwifuriza abandi ibibi bikuzanira umuvumo ariko \r\nkwifuza ko na mugenzi wawe yagira umugisha akagira amahoro nâ€™iterambere,\r\n ibyo ubwabyo ni byiza kuri wowe kuko bikuzanira imigisha. Ntabwo \r\nkugirira ishyari umuntu ku bwâ€™umugisha afite bizatuma umugisha we uba \r\nuwawe, ahubwo bishobora kuzakwambura nâ€™umugisha wowe wari wisanganiwe.</p><p align=\"left\">Umunsi umwe, Gisanura yabajije abatware be igihano gisumba \r\nibindi, buri wese agenda avuga icye. Umwami asanze bikabije, buri wese \r\namuhanisha icyo yagiye avuga. Nguko uko umwe wari watahuye ko igihano \r\ncyiza ari ugusambura inzu ziri hafi, bagacaniriza urutare iyo \r\nsakamburiro kugeza aho urutare rutukura, noneho umugome bakarumushyiraho\r\n agashirira. Ibyo byahimbwe nâ€™umutware witwaga Kamegeri. Umwami yasanze \r\nnta muntu mubi (wâ€™umugome) kurusha Kamegeri. \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"thumb tright\" align=\"left\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><br>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\">Urutare rwa Kamegeri bamaze kurucanira</div></div></div><div align=\"left\">Nuko\r\n aca iteka ko uwo Kamegeri bamuhanisha icyo gihano kibi yahimbiye \r\nabandi. Noneho baramuboha bamujugunya ari muzima ku rutare bacaniriye \r\nrwatukuye.\r\n\r\n<center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 860px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L860xH286/urutare-rwa-kamegeri-b0eff.gif?1493381638\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"286\" width=\"860\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</center><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 719px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L719xH285/sdfsd-d6a61.jpg?1493381638\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" height=\"285\" width=\"719\" border=\"0\">\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"center\">Bivugwa ko uru rutare kera rwatukuraga nyuma y\'aho rutwikiweho umutware Kamegeri</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</center></div>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uru rutare ruri mu Karere ka Ruhango rufite amateka menshi; aha niho \r\numutware Kamegeri yatwikiwe ku ngoma yâ€™umwami Mibambwe Sekarongoro \r\nMutabazi nyuma yâ€™aho asabiye iki gihano abanyabyaha.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uru rutare kuva icyo gihe rwahise rumwitirirwa, kandi bivugwa ko kuva icyo gihe rwakomeje gutukura.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Binavugwa kandi ko uru rutare rwabagaho nta zina rugira ariko kuva \r\naho rutwikiweho Kamegeri rwakomeje kujya rumwitirirwa mu kwibuka uko \r\nyari umutware wâ€™umugome cyane wafataga ibyemezo bikarishye kugeza ubwo \r\nurwo yaciriye uwari wagomeye umwami ari we ruhitanye atwikirwa ku \r\nrutare.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ese ni gute utasura aha hantu, ngo wiyumvire ubuhamya bwâ€™abahatuye?</p><p align=\"left\">IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></p>', '1495973662kamege.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 228);
