(87, '2017-05-29 16:04:47', 'Ese Gihanga Ngoma Ijana Niwe Wahanze u Rwanda Koko? Sobanukirwa?', 'Gihanga Ngoma Ijana uvugwa ko  ariwe wahanze u Rwanda yabayeho ahayinga mu mwaka wa 1091 -1124. Uyu mwami uvugwaho byinshi mu mateka yâ€™u Rwanda , abantu bibaza niba mbere yâ€™uko abaho nta Rwanda  rwabagaho.', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><br></p><p><b><i>U Rwanda rwagiye rutegekwa nâ€™abami batandukanye kuva rwabaho \r\nkugeza ubwo abanyamateka babagabanyamo ibyiciro bitatu bakurikije ibihe \r\naribyo: Abami bâ€™ibimanuka, abami bâ€™umushumi nâ€™abami bâ€™ibitekerezo.</i></b></p><b>\r\n</b><p><b>Abami bâ€™Ibimanuka ni abakomoka kuri Shyerezo, Abami bâ€™umushumi ni \r\nabatazwi igihe bategekeye nâ€™ibyabaye ku Ngoma zabo, naho Abami \r\nbâ€™Ibitekerezo ni Abami bazwi neza igihe bategekeye nâ€™ibyabaye ku ngoma \r\nzabo.</b></p><b>\r\n</b><p><b>Abami bâ€™Ibimanuka bahera kuri Shyerezo bakagera kuri Kazi. Naho Abami\r\n bâ€™umushumi bahera kuri Gihanga cyahanze Inka nâ€™Ingoma bakagera kuri \r\nCyilima I Rugwe. Abami bâ€™Ibitekerezo ari nabo ba nyuma bahera kuri \r\nKigeli I Mukobanya bakageza ku Mwami wa nyuma wâ€™u Rwanda ariwe Kigeli V \r\nNdahindurwa.Tukaba tugiye kubagezaho amateka yâ€™Umwami wa mbere \r\nwâ€™Umushumi, Gihanga I Ngomijana</b></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><strong>Mr Kagame</strong>\r\n avuga ko umuntu ahereye ku mateka yâ€™abami bâ€™ibimanuka bivugwa ko \r\nbakomoka mu ijuru, usanga bavugwa ko baba baramanukiye bwa mbere mu \r\nMubari (</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px;color:#ff0000\">mu burasirazuba bwâ€™u Rwanda ahitwa ku rutare rwa Kinani</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">) aho baje basanga hatuwe kandi hategekwa muri icyo gihe nâ€™uwitwa Kabeja wo mu bwoko bwâ€™Abazigaba.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Uyu\r\n Mwami witwa Gihanga ngo ntibikwiye kuvugwa ko yahanze u Rwanda nkâ€™uko \r\nbivugwa ahubwo icyakwemerwa ni uko ngo ari we ntangiriro yâ€™ubutegetsi \r\nbwâ€™ingoma nyiginya (</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px;color:#ff0000\">fondateur de la dynastie</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">.)</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Byongeye kandi <strong>Alegisi Kagame</strong>\r\n ntiyemera ko Gihanga ariwe wahanze inka nâ€™ingoma kuko ngo Gihanga atari\r\n we wazanye ubutegetsi bushingiye ku kimenyetso cyâ€™ingoma (tambour \r\nemblÃ¨me) kuko ngo mu ntangiriro zâ€™ubutegetsi bwe, Gihanga nta ngoma \r\nyimanye ahubwo yategekeshaga ibindi birango bibiri aribyo<b> inyundo</b> nâ€™ikindi gikoresho cyâ€™umuziki bita&nbsp;<b>urusengo</b>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ibyo gushyiraho ingoma nkâ€™ikimenyetso cyâ€™ubwami ngo yaba yarabizaniwe nâ€™uwitwa <strong>Rubunga</strong>\r\n nawe abikopeye mu bucurabwenge bwakoreshwaga nâ€™abitwa Abarenge. \r\nAbarenge ngo akaba ari bo bari mu gihugu mbere yâ€™uko iriya ngoma \r\nnyiginya iza kurutegeka(U rwanda).</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Uyu munyamateka nyarwanda avuga ko ingoma ya mbere yakoreshejwe nâ€™ubutegetsi bwa Gihanga yahawe izina rya <strong>Rwoga</strong> bituruka ku ijambo Â«<strong>kwogera </strong>Â» cyangwa se Â« <strong>kwamamara</strong> Â»</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Rubunga\r\n wayizaniye Gihanga ni we bakunze kwita Mwungura ari naho banakomerezaho\r\n bagira bati ni Â« Mwungura wunguye ingoma ubwiruÂ», akaba akomokwaho \r\nnâ€™umuryango wâ€™Abatege bituruka ku izina ryâ€™umwe mu bakurambere babo \r\nwitwaga Nyabutege.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ikoreshwa\r\n ryâ€™ingoma nkâ€™ikimenyetso cyâ€™ubwami bwa Gihanga ngo ntiryakuyeho burundu\r\n ikoreshwa rya biriya bimenyetso bindi byakoreshwaga mbere ari byo <strong>urusengo nâ€™inyundo</strong> nkâ€™uko <strong>Mr Kagame</strong> akomeza abivuga.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Uyu\r\n mwanditsi atanga urugero rwâ€™uko iyo i bwami bamenyeshaga icibwa \r\nryâ€™umuntu runaka cyangwa se umuryango runaka ariko mu buryo butari \r\nburundu bakoreshaga <strong>umurishyo</strong> wâ€™ingoma, mu gihe iyo iryo cibwa ryemezwaga mu buryo bwa burundu baritangazaga bakoresheje urusengo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Nâ€™ubwo\r\n hashidikanywa niba Gihanga ari we wahanze u Rwanda cyangwa atari we ngo\r\n ntibikuraho ko yaba yarabayeho kuko kubaho kwe kugaragarira ku kuntu \r\nuruhererekane rwâ€™abamukurikiye mu butegetsi bamwubahiriza kandi ugasanga\r\n mu ntekerezo zose agarukamo nkâ€™uko uyu mwanditsi abigaragaza.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><strong>Mr Alegisi Kagame</strong>\r\n avuga ko iyo umwami runaka yageraga ku butegetsi yubakishaga ingoro ye,\r\n ariko ku ruhande agashyiraho nâ€™ahagenewe kubahiriza umukurambere \r\nGihanga ariho bitaga&nbsp;<b>urukamishirizo.</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Uretse nâ€™ibyo kandi ngo aho umusezero (imva yâ€™umwami) wa Gihanga wari ku gasozi ka&nbsp;<b>Muganza ya\r\nKayenzi</b> ngo naho hakorerwaga imihango yo kumuterekera niba ari ko nabyita.\r\nAha ngaha i bwami ngo bakaba barahoherezaga abiru bo kuhakorera imihango\r\nyabugenewe.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Mr\r\n Kagame avuga kandi ko hari indi mihango yamukorerwaga yari ishingiye ku\r\n nka ikaba yarakorwaga nâ€™abo mu muryango bita Abaheka ; umutware wabo \r\nagatura i Runda ndetse akaba yarafatwaga nkâ€™umwiru mukuru wâ€™inka.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ntawakwirengagiza\r\n ubwoko bwâ€™Abatsobe nabwo ngo bukomoka kuri Gihanga, kuko ngo uwo \r\nbakomokaho witwa Rutsobe ari umuhungu yabyaye hanze. Uyu muryango nawo \r\nukaba waraje kubahwa ibwami kubera imihango yâ€™ubwiru wakoraga, dore ko \r\nngo banagiraga ingoma yabo yitwa Rwamo naho umurwa baturagaho ukaba wari\r\n i Kinyambi muri Runda.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Kagame\r\n avuga ko umuryango wâ€™ Abatsobe wari ufite agaciro mu butegetsi bwite \r\nbwâ€™igihugu kuko bari bashinzwe imihango yâ€™ubwiru ijyanye nâ€™umuganura \r\nbagatura mu karere kâ€™u Bumbogo bakagira nâ€™umutwe wâ€™ingabo bayoboraga \r\nwitwa Gakondo ukomoka kuri Gihanga.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ikindi\r\n kivugwa kuri Gihanga ni uko igihugu yategekaga cyarengaga imbibi zâ€™u \r\nRwanda tuzi ubu. Ibi bigashingirwa ku ntekerezo zigaragaza ko ubutegetsi\r\n bwe bwageraga hakurya mu burengerazuba bwa RDC aho bitaga mu Bunyabungo\r\n ndetse nâ€™ahitwa Buhindangoma hakurya muri Rucuru.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ahandi\r\n hagaragara ibirari byâ€™amateka bishobora kwemeza ko Gihanga yabayeho ni \r\nmu majyaruguru yâ€™u Rwanda ahitwa Buhanga hagati ya Nyamutera na \r\nNyakinama ku bazi amazina yâ€™uturere twa cyera.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Aha\r\n Mgr Kagame avuga ko hagaragaraga ibigabiro byâ€™aho uyu mwami yari atuye \r\nariko umuntu akaba atakwemeza ko ibyo bigabiro bigihari magingo aya \r\nkubera ibikorwa byâ€™ubuhinzi nâ€™imiturire.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Imwe mu mihango yakorerwaga muri aka gace ni iyakorwaga\r\nku mfizi yitwa <b>Rugira</b> ngo yabanaga nâ€™inka zitwa&nbsp;<b>Ingizi</b> \r\nnkuko uyu munyamateka abivuga.Iyi mihango ngo yaba ratangiye ku ngoma \r\nyâ€™umwami Yuhi II Gahima ari nabwo umutwe wâ€™ingabo zitwa Gakondo \r\nzatandukanaga nâ€™izitwa Abangakugoma nyuma aba Bangakugoma bakoherezwa \r\nkuba hariya mu Buhanga.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Undi\r\n murwa wa Gihanga uvugwa na Mgr Kagame ni uwari ahitwa Nyamirembe \r\ncyangwa se Humure yo mu Mutara,aho uyu mwami ngo yaba yarageneye \r\numuhungu we Kanyarwanda ngo azabe ari we umusimbura ku ngoma amaze \r\ngutanga.Gihanga yarongoye abagore benshi</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Muri\r\n izi nyandiko Mgr Alegisi Kagame avuga ko Gihanga yagiye abyara abana \r\nbatandukanye badahuje ba nyina kuko nawe yari afite abagore benshi \r\nnkâ€™uko byari bisanzwe bimenyerewe mu Rwanda rwo hambere.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Uyu mwanditsi avuga ko umugore wa mbere wa Gihanga ari\r\nuwitwa Nyamususa akaba umukobwa wa <b>Jeni</b> uturuka mu bwoko bwâ€™Abarenge akaba yarabyaranye nâ€™uyu mugore&nbsp;<b>Kanyarwanda Gahima</b>,\r\n Kanyandorwa Sabugabo se wa Mushambo ukomokwaho nâ€™ubwoko bwâ€™ Abashambo \r\nndetse nâ€™uwitwa Kanyabugesera Mugondo se wa Muhondogo sekuruza wâ€™ubwoko \r\nAbahondogo, ndetse na nyirarucyaba umukuramberekazi wâ€™ubwoko \r\nbwâ€™Abacyaba.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Gihanga\r\n yarongoye kandi Nyangobero ukomoka mu Bunyabungo barabyarana Kanyabungo\r\n Ngabo waje gutegeka mu Bunyabungo ndetse arongora na Nyirampirangwe \r\nbabyarana Gashubi se wa Gashingo ukomokwaho nâ€™abitwa Abashingo ndetse \r\nngo babyarana nâ€™undi mwana witwa Gafomo.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Mgr\r\n Kagame avuga kandi ko Gihanga yari afite undi mugore wâ€™inshoreke \r\nwitwaga Nyirarutsobe babyarana Rutsobe umukurambere wâ€™abo mu bwoko \r\nbwâ€™Abatsobe.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">&nbsp;Amateka n\'umuco biragendana iyo ujyenzuye amateka y\'uRwanda&nbsp; usanga afitanye isano rikomeye numuco w\'uRwanda.<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 13.6pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></span></p>', '1496066687iaa.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 6, 'head', 304),
(88, '2017-06-01 22:04:15', 'Ese umuhango wo kurya ubunnyano no kwita izina wakorwaga ute? Umuco wo kwita izina no kurya ubunnyano warakendereye mu Rwanda', '        Umuco wo kwita izina no kurya ubunnyano warakendereye mu Rwanda  Umuhango wo kurya ubunnyano, wakorwaga umwana amaze iminsi 8 avutse. Bafataga amasuka yâ€™udufuni, bagaha abana bakiri bato, bakajya guhinga hafi aho yâ€™urugo, iyo bamaraga guhingura bajyaga mu rugo, bagasanga babateguriye intara bashyizeho ibyo kurya. Ku ntara basasagaho amakoma, bagashyiraho ibishyimbo bacucumiyemo imboga, kandi bagizemo utubumbe twinshi, buri mwana akagira akabumbe ke.', '<div align=\"left\"><em><strong></strong></em></div>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_14401\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://www.dove.rw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/12118598_1072533802799013_8777294118469230650_n.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-14401\" src=\"https://www.dove.rw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/12118598_1072533802799013_8777294118469230650_n.jpg\" alt=\" Bamwe biyambazaga n\'imyumbati igeretse ku bishyimbo\" height=\"458\" width=\"815\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><em> Bamwe biyambazaga nâ€™imyumbati igeretse ku bishyimbo</em></strong></p></div>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nkuko tubikesha impuguke mu muco nyarwanda ndetse nâ€™abasaza bamazeho \r\niminsi, batubwirako akabumbe kose kabaga kageretseho agasate kâ€™umutsima.\r\n Bakazana amata yâ€™inshyushyu nâ€™ayâ€™ikivuguto bagatereka aho, abana bakaza\r\n bakabaha amazi bagakaraba bakarya, bakabaha nâ€™amata bakanywa bose uko \r\nbangana. Ngâ€™uko kurya ubunnyano. Kubyita ubunnyano nâ€™uko babaga babigize\r\n utubumbe twinshi tumeze nkâ€™utwo umwana annya impande zose.<span class=\"gh_articlecontent\"><br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Iyo bamaraga kurya, ntibabahaga amazi yo gukaraba, barazaga \r\nbagahanaguriza intoki zabo ku mabere ya wa mubyeyi, bavuga bati:Urabyare\r\n abana benshi, abahungu nâ€™abakobwa â€Nâ€™uko abana bakita uruhinja \r\namazinaâ€.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Abana ntibatahaga iwabo imuhira na nyina wâ€™Umwana ntiyahagurukaga aho\r\n yicaye, kereka umwana abanje kunnya cyangwa se kunyara.Nyina yabaga \r\nyamuhaye amata, yamuhaye ibere, agira ngo annye cyangwa anyare vuba.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Iyo umwana yabaga yatinze kunnya cyangwa se kunyara, bamutamikaga \r\nitabi akaruka, bakabona kugenda. Kugenderaho ni ugusurira umwana nabi, \r\nagapfa. Ubwo buryo akaba aribwo buryo bwo kurya ubunnyano bwakoreshwaga \r\nmu Rwanda rugari rwa Gasabo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu Ngoma yâ€™i Gisaka cyâ€™Epfo na hamwe mu Buganza, abana bafite \r\nakabyino babyinaga, bajya gusuka ku nsina ibyo bakuye ku kiriri. Insina \r\nakenshi yabaga ari iyâ€™inyamunyo. Haza abana umunani, bane bâ€™abahungu na \r\nbane bâ€™abakobwa, bose bâ€™amasugi(bafite ba se naba nyina ).Barazaga \r\nbagakikiza urutaro (intara) bayoreyeho ibyo ku kiriri, bakayiterurira \r\nrimwe bagenda urunana bakabyina ngo : Bwerere yavutse, Bwerere yakura, \r\nBwerere yavoma, Bwerere yasenya (yatashya), Bwerere yahingaâ€¦..Bagasuka \r\nku nsina bavuga ngo:Dore aho nyoko yakubyariyeâ€Bakajya no ku yindi nsina\r\n babyina kwa kundi.Batanga insina ebyiri cyangwa se eshatu, bagasukaho \r\nibyo ku kiriri. Insina basukagaho ibyo ku kiriri(ibyo basigaje barya \r\nubunnyano) yerekanwa nâ€™umugore washashe ikiriri.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Insina iba iyâ€™umwana ababyeyi bazira kuyimunyaga. Iyo ari umukobwa agashyingirwa kure, igitoki cyayo barakimugemurira.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Uwo munsi babaga bashakiye umwana ingobyi ebyiri iyâ€™uruhu rwâ€™inka \r\nnâ€™iyâ€™uruhu rwâ€™intama, bakazimukozaho, kugirango imwe nibura bamuheke mu \r\nyindi. Iyo babigenjeje batyo bukeye bakamuheka muyo batamukojejeho icyo \r\ngihe, imusurira nabi,agapfa. Umwana wâ€™uruhinja iyo afite mukuru we, ku \r\nmunsi wo gusohoka baramumuhekesha,kugirango bazahore barutana, umukuru \r\nntarutwe na murumuna we, bitewe nâ€™uko yazingamye.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Icumu nâ€™ingabo nâ€™umuheto, cyangwa ishinge umugore yasohokanye, babimanika mu ruhamo rwâ€™umuryango, kirazira kubijugunya gusa.</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_14440\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://www.dove.rw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/UMUCO.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-14440\" src=\"https://www.dove.rw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/UMUCO.jpg\" alt=\" Wasangaga ibiryo bya kinyarwanda aribyo byiganjemo\" height=\"540\" width=\"815\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"> <strong><em> Wasangaga ibiryo bya kinyarwanda aribyo byiganjemo</em></strong></p></div>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>1.Kwita izina cyangwa guterura umwana</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"gh_articlecontent\">Iyo bamaraga kurya ubunnyano, umwana \r\nyanyaye akanannya, bwamaraga kwira abana bagasubira iwabo. Umugore \r\nagasasa, noneho agataha ku buriri akararana nâ€™umugabo we, ariko umwe \r\nakirinda undi. Igihe cyo mu museke, umugabo akabwira umugore ngo naze \r\nbaterure umwana (gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina). Barangiza umugabo \r\nagasohoka akajya hanze, yava hanze, akaza agasanga umugore yamushyiriye \r\nintebe mu irebe ryâ€™umuryango. Iyo umugabo yaterurega umwana atavuye \r\nhanze, byabaga ari ukumuvutsa ibyiza akazaba imbwa, akazapfa atagize \r\nicyo yimarira. Nuko umugabo akaza akicara ku ntebe ati : â€œMpa uwo mwana \r\nyewe wa mugore weâ€, umugore akamuhereza umwana. Se wâ€™umwana akamusimbiza\r\n agira ati : â€œKura ujye ejuru, nkwise kanakaâ€. Umugore nawe iyo ashatse \r\nyita umwana izina, akagira ati : â€œNnya aha, nyara aha, nkwise kanakaâ€, \r\nubwo akita umwana izina, akabisubiramo ariko izina rihama ni iryo umwana\r\n yiswe na se.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>2. Impamvu nyamukuru yo kwita umwana izina</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Abakurambere bacu , bari bafite ubugenge nâ€™ubucurabwenge bwo kwita \r\numwana izina, kwita izina byagendanaga ahanini nâ€™impamvu zâ€™ingenzi \r\nzikurikira :</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>*Bitaga izina bakurikije ibihe barimo bamubyara</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Iyi mpamvu yagendanaga nuko imibereho yâ€™umuryango uwo mwana avukamo \r\nyifashe mu gihe uwo mwana yavukaga, bikagendana kandi nuko igihugu \r\ncyifashe muri rusange.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Niyo mpamvu bafatiraga ku bintu byinshi birimo :</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><ul><li>&nbsp;Uko babanye nâ€™abaturanyi,niba babanye neza, ugasanga barita ba \r\nMugenzi, Nkundabagenzi, Ngirabakunzi nâ€™ayandi. Baba batameranya neza \r\nniho wasangaga bita ba Ntamuturano, Sibomana, Mpitabazenga, Mpitabanyika\r\n nâ€™ayandi.</li><li>&nbsp;Uko mu gihugu byifashe, aha bafatiraga ku mutekano bakita ba \r\nNtambara, Rugamba aho amashyaka aziye bita ba Murwanashyaka, Mukashyaka \r\nnâ€™ayandi. Izo akaba ari ingero zâ€™ibanze, naho muri iki gika habamo \r\namazina menshi. Imvugo bakoreshaga niyo bakunze kwita â€œKugenuraâ€ari naho\r\n hava amazina yâ€™amagenurano. Usibye ko amazina yose yaba meza cyangwa \r\nmabi, yose aba afite icyo bahereyeho bayita.</li></ul></div>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>*Bitaga umwana izina bitewe nicyo bamwifuriza ko azaba</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Abanyarwanda kandi bitaga umwana izina bitewe nicyo bamwifuriza ko \r\nazaba. Aha niho wasangaga babita ba Ntwari, Mutunzi, Mukire, Cyogere \r\nnâ€™andi nkâ€™ayo. Aha niho wanasangaga bita umwana izina ryâ€™intwari runaka \r\nyabayeho kugira ngo nawe azabe yo, niho wasangaga amazina nka Ndoli, \r\nRwabugili, Mpilimbanyi, Kamananga nâ€™ayandi. Muri make amazina bitaga \r\numwana yabaga ari ayo kumwifuriza imigisha yâ€™uburyo bwose.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Icyo tutakwirengagiza aha ni uko bashoboraga kwita umwana izina \r\nrikazamukururira imivumo mu minsi yo kubaho kwe yose, aha niho havuye ya\r\n mvugo ikoreshwa kenshi igira iti : â€œIzina niryo muntuâ€. Iyo umwana \r\numwise Rubebe aba rubebe nta kabuza, wamwita izina ryâ€™umuntu mubi \r\nwabayeho cyangwa wâ€™indwanyi, igihugu akakiyogoza. Iyo wamwitaga izina \r\nrijyanye nâ€™uburyo utabanye neza nâ€™abaturanyi nabyo byamugiraga ho \r\ningaruka mbi mu mibereho ye bakaba banamugirira nabi kuko nta kamaro \r\nbabaga bamutezeho.</p>\r\n<div id=\"attachment_14442\" style=\"width: 825px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://www.dove.rw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ibiryo_bya_kunyarwanda.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-14442\" src=\"https://www.dove.rw/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ibiryo_bya_kunyarwanda.jpg\" alt=\" Byabaga ari ibirori kuri uwo munsi\" height=\"611\" width=\"815\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong><em> Byabaga ari ibirori kuri uwo munsi</em></strong></p></div>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>*Umwihariko wâ€™amazina amwe nâ€™amwe</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Hari amazina yakundaga kugira umwihariko wayo. Ayo mazina ni nkâ€™ayo \r\nbitaga abana bavutse ari impanga, aho bakungaga kubita ba Gakuru cyangwa\r\n se Gatoya. Hakaza nâ€™ayo bitaga umwana wavutse ari uwa Karindwi aho \r\nbamwitaga nka Nyandwi, Rwasa, Nyamwasa nâ€™ayandi.Umwana wa \r\nMunani,bakamwita Minani, Nyaminani nâ€™andi. Uwacyenda bakamwita \r\nNyabyenda, Mwenda nâ€™ayandi. Uwa cumi bakamwita Macumi nâ€™ayandi naho uwa \r\ncumi nâ€™umwe ari we wakunze kuba ihame ryo gucura kwâ€™abagore bo ha mbere \r\nbakundaga kumwita Misago. Hakaba nâ€™amazina yabaga afite umwihariko \r\nwâ€™amazina atarakundaga kubaho kenshi wâ€™abana babaga barapfushije ba se \r\nbakabasiga bataravugak niho wasangaga babita ba Misigaro, Bisigara \r\nnâ€™ayandi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ngiyo rero imvano yo kurya ubunnyano mu Rwanda rwo ha mbere, ngiyo impamvu nyamukuru yatumaga bita abana bavutse amazina.</p><p align=\"left\"><br></p><p align=\"left\">IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></p>', '1496347455ibiryo_bya_kunyarwanda.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 6, 'head', 441),
(89, '2017-06-03 16:16:09', 'Inka n\'amata ni ibintu by\'agaciro mumuco nyarwanda .zimwe muri kirazira abantu bagenda birengagiza- IKESHAMVUGO.', 'Reka duhere ku magambo yakoreshwaga ku nka nâ€™amata kugirango tuyibukiranye  tujye tunayakoresha kuko agaciro byahabwaga nâ€™abakera ntaho kagiye umuco ntugacike .', '<p align=\"left\"><i><b>Ikinyarwanda ni <a href=\"https://rw.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Ururimi_%28kuvuga%29&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ururimi (kuvuga) (page does not exist)\">ururimi</a> rwâ€™<a href=\"https://rw.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Abanyarwanda&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Abanyarwanda (page does not exist)\">Abanyarwanda</a>\r\n n\'abavuga ikinyarwanda badatuye u Rwanda. Ikinyarwanda kivugwa mu \r\nRwanda no mu burasirazuba bwa Congo iharanira demokarasi. Ibindi bihugu \r\nbikikije u Rwanda bifite indimi zijya gusa n\'ikinyarwanda: ikinyarwanda \r\ngisa nâ€™<a href=\"https://rw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kirundi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kirundi\">Ikirundi</a>, ururimi rwâ€™i <a href=\"https://rw.wikipedia.org/wiki/Burundi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Burundi\">Burundi</a>.</b></i></p><div align=\"left\"><i><b>\r\n</b></i></div><p align=\"left\"><i><b>Ikinyarwanda gifite umwanya ukomeye mu mibereho yâ€™Abanyarwanda. Ni \r\nrwo rurimi ruha Abanyarwanda ubushobozi bwo kuranga isi, kugaragaza \r\nimbamutima, gushyikirana baganira, bungurana ibitekerezo, bagezanyaho \r\nubutumwa.</b></i></p><div align=\"left\"><i><b>\r\n</b></i></div><p align=\"left\"><i><b>Ururimi rwâ€™Ikinyarwanda rufite uruhare rukomeye mu guhamya \r\nUmunyarwanda udafite isoni nâ€™ubwoba byâ€™umuco we kandi utisuzugura. Umuco\r\n wâ€™u Rwanda ukeneye abawurinda nâ€™abawubungabunga ngo hato imico \r\nyâ€™amahanga itawumira. Iyo nshingano rero ni iyâ€™Abanyarwanda ubwabo. \r\nInzira ya mbere iriho ni ukwigisha Ikinyarwanda.</b></i></p><div align=\"left\"><i><b>\r\n</b></i></div><p align=\"left\"><i><b><a href=\"https://rw.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Ikinyanduga&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ikinyanduga (page does not exist)\">Ikinyanduga</a>\r\n si cyo Kinyarwanda cyonyine, uretse ko abapadiri bashatse kwandika \r\nIkinyarwanda bahera ku Kinyanduga, kuko abacyanditse bari i Kabgayi.</b></i></p><div align=\"left\"><i><b>\r\n</b></i></div><p align=\"left\"><i><b>Kwigisha Ikinyarwanda bihamye rero ni ugushimangira ubunyarwanda. Ni \r\nugushyikiriza umwana wâ€™u Rwanda ibyo abakurambere bahanze bakabisigira \r\nUmunyarwanda wese ho umurage. Bityo kwiga Ikinyarwanda bikaba guhura \r\nnâ€™ibyo kibumbatiye: uko giteye, ubugeni gihetse, umuco nâ€™imyumvire \r\nyâ€™Abanyarwanda. Ibi bisobanura ko kwigisha Ikinyarwanda ari ugufasha \r\numwana wâ€™u Rwanda kugicengera ari mu miterere yacyo no bwiza bwacyo: uko\r\n cyemerera ukivuga gutaka imvugo ye.</b></i></p><div align=\"left\"><i><b>\r\n</b></i></div><p align=\"left\"><i><b>Kwigisha Ikinyarwanda rero bikwiye kuba umwanya wo guha Umunyarwanda \r\nubushobozi bwo kwirinda kumirwa nâ€™amahanga, ibyiza agisangamo \r\nakabyamamaza, ibyo anenga akabikosora, akagikungahaza ngo gihangane \r\nnâ€™iterambere isi ihorana.</b></i></p><div align=\"left\"><i><b>\r\n</b></i></div><p align=\"left\"><i><b>Ikinyarwanda kandi gifitemo amagambo menshi asa nayo mu rurimi rwitwa\r\n Ikizulu rw\'abirabura bo muri Afurika y\'Epfo: urugero, umuntu, abantu, \r\ningwe, amanzi, umutwaro, ingata, inyama, inyoni, iminwe, marume, umukwe,\r\n abatwa.</b></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><i><b><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Reka\r\n duhere ku magambo yakoreshwaga ku Nka nâ€™Amata kugirango tuyibukiranye \r\nbinashobotse tujye tunayakoresha kuko agaciro byahabwaga nâ€™abakera ntaho\r\n kagiye kuko nubu amwe baracyayakoresha.</span></b></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><i><strong><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><span style=\"line-height:150%; color:#666666;font-famil