wakera bwanyuragamo kugeza bubaye</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Kera iyo ababyeyi babonaga ko umuhungu cyangwa umukobwa wabo yakuze, bajyaga inama yo <strong>kubashyingira</strong>,\r\n bagahagurukira kubashakira uwo bazashyingiranwa. Kugira ngo bamubone \r\nbabazaga mu nshuti no mu bavandimwe baba aba kure no hafi kugira ngo \r\nbagerageze kubabonera umugeni cyangwa umuhungu utunganye. Mu Rwanda \r\nhose, mu moko yose ibice byarangaga umuhango wâ€™ubukwe byabaga ari bimwe \r\nbikurikirana kuri ubu buryo:</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">A.Kuranga\r\nCyangwa Kurangira.</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Abanyarwanda\r\n bo hambere baricaraga bagashaka umuhungu cyangwa umukobwa ukwiranye \r\nnâ€™umwana wabo. Habagaho kungurana ibitekerezo ku bisekuruza \r\nnâ€™ubunyangamugayo bwâ€™abagize umuryango runaka bifuza gushakamo maze \r\nbagahitamo neza.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">B.Gusaba\r\nUmugeni</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Hose bajyaga gusaba umugeni hakagenda Se wâ€™umwana cyangwa undi muntu wo mu muryango wabo wizewe bajyanaga inzoga<b>.</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">C.Batangaga\r\ninkwano</span></b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">: </span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Bamwe batangaga inka, abandi amasuka, abandi batangaga amatungo (ihene), hari nâ€™aho batangaga amasaka nâ€™uburo.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">D.Gutebutsa</span></b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Gutebutsa nâ€™ukujya kubaza igihe bazashyingirwa hakagenda abaje gusaba umugeni kandi bakajyana inzoga.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">E.Gushyingira.</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Bose baherekezaga umugeni mu\r\nijoro. Yagendaga mu kirago kereka hamwe nko mu Ndorwa. Ahenshi mu Rwanda\r\nbarongozaga umwishywa. Abandi bambikaga igikangaga, ariko hakeya.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">F. Kwakira Umwishywa byâ€™ababyeyi byari hose mu Rwanda.</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Izo\r\n ngingo twasanze zihuriweho nâ€™abakurambere bacu mu turere twose mu moko \r\nyose ari mu Rwanda. Hose mu Rwanda, ababyeyi nibo bashakiraga abana \r\nbabo, bakabubakira. Umwanya wâ€™abana mwâ€™ishakana ntiwari uriho,ababyeyi \r\nbatoranyaga neza bifuzaga ko umwana aremya urugo.&nbsp;Gushyingira umwana \r\nbyari bishyigikiwe nâ€™umuryango wose. Izo ngingo zose zihuriweho mu \r\nRwanda nizo twagerageje kubaza neza turazandika.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">G.\r\nGutwikurura</span></b></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Umugeni yaratinyaga,\r\nakihisha ntagaragare, kugera igihe bamubwira ko hari umurimo wo gukora. Kera\r\niyo umugeni yabaga ataratwikururwa ntiyagaragaraga byeruye. Nta mirimo yo mu\r\nrugo yakoraga. Umuhango wo gutwikurura wakorwaga kugira ngo umugeni ajye\r\nahabona atangire gukora imirimo yo mu rugo byeruye. Ni byiza rero ko umuco u\r\nRwanda rwubatseho, umenyekana mu bato ukazanahora mu mateka, kandi tukanamenya\r\nko gushyingirwa ari rimwe mu mabango akomeye u Rwanda rushingiyeho kugira ngo\r\nrube rwiza kandi</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">rugire amahoro nâ€™ubumwe bikomotse mu kugira ingo nziza, imiryango myiza nâ€™igihugu cyiza.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <br></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><i><b><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Ubu dutegereje Imyanzuro izakuva&nbsp; muri iyi nama.</span></b></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><i><b><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">&nbsp;Tuributsa kandi ko&nbsp; </span></b><b>Ijambo â€˜Chargeurâ€™ ryabonewe Ikinyarwanda ryitwa â€œ Indahuzoâ€</b></i></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><b><i>Umuco ntugacike</i></b><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></span></p>', '1496766775ubukwe.jpg', 0, 'admin', 7, 13, 'head', 307),
(91, '2017-06-13 11:47:33', 'Hari ubwo wumva abantu bavuga ngo abantu bateye rwaserera.Ese uhita umenya aho iyo mvugo yaturutse? Inkomoko yâ€™umugani â€™Bateye Rwasereraâ€™', 'Uyu mugani bawuca iyo babonye abantu basahinda bateye imvururu, niho bavuga ngo â€˜Bateye rwaserera!â€™ Wakomotse kuri Rwaserera wâ€™i Rusororo mu Rukaryi (Kigali); ahagana mu mwaka wa 1700. ', '<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><br></span></i></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Iyimvugo\r\n yadutse ivuye ku mugabo witwa Rwaserera ahagana mu mwaka 1700 ku ngoma \r\nyâ€™umwami&nbsp;cyirima rujugiro ,uyu mugabo Rwaserera yari atuye iRusororo \r\n(rukaryi)&nbsp;ubu\r\nni mu murenge wa Rusororo akarere ka Gasabo umujyi wa Kigali.Abenshi tuhazi\r\nnkazwi ko hari irimbi rishyi ngurwamo abitabye imana bari bakomeye. </span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Aha\r\n hari hatuye umugabo&nbsp;akaba umukungu ,haje gutera inzara muduce \r\ntwâ€™ubwanacyambwe,urukaryi nâ€™ubuganza.Rwaserera yari afite ibigega \r\nnâ€™utugega byâ€™amasaka abantu bo muri utwo turere batangira kuza kumucaho \r\nincuro,abafite ibimasa na masoka&nbsp;(inka zâ€™inyana)\r\nbakazimuha akabahahira. </span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Inzarantiyahise\r\n ishira vuba bukeye umugabo witwa Rubanguka rwa mpama wari utuye mu \r\nbuganza bwa kiramuruzi (ubu aho ni mu karere ka Gatsibo) yarikoze ajya \r\nkwa Rwaserera ajya kumukeza agezeyo ati&lt;nje kugukeza ngo unsindire \r\niki cyago cyâ€™ inzara&gt;. Maze Rwaserera aramwemerera aramuhaka maze \r\namushyira mubahinzi agezeyo atangira kubadehesha ntibakore. Rwaserera \r\najya kugenzura abakozi asanga badeshye maze atuka Rubanguka rwa mpama \r\nati&lt;urabona ino nyana yâ€™imbwa yâ€™umuganza ngo irandeheshereza \r\nabahinzi,ati&lt;nkabona iwanyu hari inzara niubunebwe bwanyu&gt;</span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Rubanguka\r\n yahise yikubita isuka ayijugunya hasi ahita ataha yuzuye akabaro ku \r\nkuntu Rwaserera yari amusuzuguye,ageze iwabo ajya inama nâ€™abandi \r\nbaturage zo gutera Rwaserera bakamunyaga ubutunzi akangisha.Bamwe \r\nbarabyanze bati umutware abimenye byadukoraho. Ariko ubwo rwaserera nawe\r\n yararahiye ati sinzongera gukoresha abaganza ukundi.</span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Ariko\r\n bamwe baremera bugorobye barikor baraboneza nâ€™I Rusororo ijoro ryose. \r\nUmuseke wambere utambitse bavuza induru bati â€œumwami yatanze Rwaserera!â€\r\n Ubwo abaturage babyumvise barahurura abanyenzara bose baturutse igihugu\r\n cyose barashika nisahinda batera Rwaserera baramusakiza basahura ibyo \r\nyari afite byose urugo basararutwika iwe haratikira hazize umucancuro \r\nRubanguka rwa Mpama wâ€™I Kiramuruzi</span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">Kuva\r\n ubwo rero ababonye abantu bari ku musozi basahinda bavugaa ko bateye \r\nRwaserera bagereranya nâ€™abateye Rwaserera I Rusororo azize agasuzuguro \r\nke.</span></i></b></p><p align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"></span>Nuko ngo bugorobe,barikora baboneza iyâ€™I Rusororo ijoro ryose, \r\numuseke wa mbere utambitse bavuza induru ndende, bati: â€Umwami yatanze \r\nRwaserera!â€ Rubanda bakangukira hejuru, abanyanzara bose babyumvise \r\nbatanguranwa kwa Rwaserera, mbese igihugu cyose kirashika nâ€™isahinda, \r\ngitera Rwaserera, baramusakiza basahura ibyo yari afite byose. Urugo rwe\r\n baruha inkongi, ahari iwe haratikira hazize uwo mucanshuro Rubanguka \r\nrwa Mpama wâ€™I Kiramuruzi. Kuva ubwo rero, babona abantu bari ku musozi \r\nbasahinda, bakavunga ngo: â€Bateye Rwaserera!â€. Ubwo baba bagereranya \r\nnâ€™abateye Rwaserera wâ€™I Rusororo azize agasuzuguro kâ€™umurengwe. \r\n</i></b></p><p align=\"left\"><b><i>Gutera Rwaserera=Gutera imvururu zâ€™urudasca.\r\n</i></b></p>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\"><i><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hifashishijwe\">Hifashishijwe</span></i></h2>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><ul><li><b><i>Irari ry\'insigamigani, igitabo cya mbere, icapisho ry\'Ingoro y\'Umurage w\'u Rwanda, 2005.\r\n</i></b></li></ul></div><p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><br></span></i></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><br></span></i></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\"><br></span></i></b></p><p style=\"margin-top:3pt;text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><b><i><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-size:18px;font-family:Verdana\">IRADUKUNDA MOSEs</span></i></b></p>', '149734725334444.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'sub', 223),
(92, '2017-06-19 13:20:50', 'Menya umubare w\'ibisigo byagiye biturwa buri mwami w\'u Rwanda ndetse n\'uwabihimbye..\"', 'Ubundi IGISIGO cyagwa IBISIGO ni amagambo arata cyangwa ashima(asingiza) umuntu uyu nâ€™uyu haba ubutwari, umurava,cyagwa indi mirimo ye yâ€™ubutwari.', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"umubare_ibisigo\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></a></h3><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Abanyarwanda\r\n bo hambere mu gihe cy\'abami, bagiraga bimwe mu byo baturaga umwami . \r\naha ntawakirengagizaga ko igisigo cyari muri bimwe mu byafatwaga \r\nnk\'ishimwe cyagwa ituro rikomeye ryaturwaga umwami.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Abenshi\r\n muri iki gihe ntibazi cyagwa ngo basobanukirwe n\'igisigo icyo aricyo. \r\nUbundi IGISIGO cyagwa IBISIGO ni amagambo arata cyangwa ashima(asingiza)\r\n umuntu uyu nâ€™uyu haba ubutwari, umurava,cyagwa indi mirimo ye \r\nyâ€™ubutwari.&nbsp;&nbsp; Habaho ubwoko bubiri bwâ€™ibisigo:&nbsp;</span></p><blockquote><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Â»ibisigo NYABAMI </span></strong></p></blockquote><blockquote><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Â»ibisigo bya RUBANDA.</span></strong></p></blockquote><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height:107%;font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ku\r\n bisigo nyabami niyamagambo yabaga asingiza ingoma cyagwa umwami muri \r\nrusange&nbsp;cyagwa arata ibikorwa bye byakataraboneka. Naho ibyarubanda byo \r\nbyabaga bisingiza cyagwa birata umuntu runaka usanzwe.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"umubare_ibisigo\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">UMUBARE Wâ€™IBISIGO</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">J.Vansina\r\n avuga ko ngo ibisigo nyabami byose hamwe byaba bigera kuri 400, Kagame \r\nwe yashoboye kubarura ibigera kuri 176 nâ€™ibindi 42 biziwe interuro gusa \r\nbyose hamwe bikaba 218. G. Mbonimana we ahamya ko birenga 300. \r\nDukurikije uko imbonerahamwe ibyerekana, kuva ku ngoma ya Ruganzu Ndori \r\nkugeza kuri Yuhi Gahindiro dusanga hari ingoma zasizweho cyane nâ€™izindi \r\numuntu yavuga ko ubusizi bwacumbagurikaga. Impamvu yaba iyihe? \r\nTutibagiwe ko hari nâ€™abami batavugwa kandi barategetse igihe kinini: ku \r\nngoma ya Ruganzu Ndoli, Kigeri Nyamuheshera ndetse na Gisanura, abasizi \r\nbari bake cyane. Urebye ni nkâ€™aho ari Muguta wenyine wabasigiye ibisigo \r\numunani.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"mazimpaka\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"mazimpaka\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KU NGOMA YA YUHI MAZIMPAKA:</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ku ngoma ye ibisigo byariyongereye kubera ko na we yari umusizi bitaga \r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€œumusizi wâ€™umusinzi nâ€™umusaziâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">.\r\n Mazimpaka yarwanijwe na mwene nyina Nyagasheja ahungira i Gatsibo mu \r\nNdorwa. Aho afatiye ubutegetsi, bene Nyagasheja arabarimbura. Yishe bene\r\n se babiri abyohejwe nâ€™Abakono bo kwa nyina. Mu kwihorera, amaze kumenya\r\n ukuri, arimbura Abakono bose nâ€™ubwo nyina yari yamwinginze ngo abareke,\r\n yica abagore be babiri bâ€™Abacyaba ngo bamuroze, icyo gihe umwami abona \r\nko inshuti zimushizeho, bihumira ku mirari abonye umuhungwe Musigwa \r\nabakurikiye kandi ari we umwishe, biramubabaza cyane, ni ko gusiga \r\nigisigo cyâ€™intashyo yâ€™abasigaye ati:</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" width=\"60%\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"2\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n<tbody><tr><td> \r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"justifyr\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><b>â€Singikunda ukundiâ€</b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"justifyr\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Singikunda ukundi<br>\r\nIbyo nkunda ntibinkundira<br>\r\nAho kunkunda birampunga bikigira gukungika kure<br> Gukunda ikitagukunda ni nkâ€™imvura igwa mu ishyambaâ€.</i></span></p>\r\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Bamwe\r\n bavuga ko ku ngoma ye habonetse ibisigo bigera kuri 12. Uretse ibisigo \r\nbye bwite, abasizi bagombaga kuba barayobotse Karenera Rwaka wamusimbuye\r\n akamara imyaka 15 ariko ibya Karemera babiburijemo, ari ugushaka \r\nkwerekana ko ntawe uzungura uwo bava inda imwe. Impamvu Karemera Rwaka \r\nyavanywe ku rutonde rwâ€™abami ni uko:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"left\"><ul><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> Yari yarabyawe nâ€™umunyiginyakazi kandi nta munyiginyakazi wabaga umugabekazi</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Izina rya Karemera ntiryari iryâ€™abami bâ€™i Rwanda</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> Ntiyari yaratowe nâ€™abiru</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ikindi kandi ngo yari yarabandishijwe.</span></li></ul></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rujugira\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rujugira\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KU NGOMA YA CYILIMA RUJUGIRA</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ku ngoma ye ibisigo byashoboye kuboneka ni 29 cyakora nka G. Mbonimana \r\nwe avugako byaba bigera kuri 30. Kuba ibisigo byariyongereye bituruka ku bintu byinshi\r\n byabaye ku ngoma ye:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div align=\"left\"><ul><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">\r\n Hari ukuba yarimye nyuma yâ€™igisa nâ€™amagomerane kubera Karemera Rwaka, \r\nkuba yarahungiye mu Gisaka no kuba ari we washyizeho bwa mbere ingerero \r\nKuba yarimikanywe na nyina wâ€™ikitiriro witwaga Turira wari nyina wabo \r\nakaba umukonokazi. Nyina wâ€™ukuri witwa Kirongora yaje kuza nyuma. Mu \r\nguhunguka mu Gisaka yabifashijwemo na Busyete wari umugesera, bigatuma \r\nubwoko bwâ€™Abagesera bwinjizwa mu bibanda (Ega, Gesera, Ha na Kono)</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Yabaye igihangange kuko yabaye uwa gatatu mu batekereza bâ€™ibwami nyuma ya Gihanga na Kibaga</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ni we wa mbere wimitse umutware wâ€™imandwa ibwami</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Yarambye\r\n ku ngoma aboneraho no kororoka benshi. Abahungu be babaye ibisekuruza \r\nbyâ€™imiryango ikomeye: Abasharangabo, Ibidende, Ibikore, Abakobanyi,...</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">\r\n Yabaye umurwanashyaka anesha abamurwanyaga, arema imitwe yâ€™ingabo igera\r\n kuri 14. Ingabo ze zarwanye nâ€™izaâ€™Abarundi, Abanyagisaka, Abanyandorwa,\r\n ntawakwibagirwa ko ari na zo zishe Mutaga III Sebitungwa wâ€™i Burundi.&nbsp;</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">\r\n Ku ngoma ye kandi hari abasizi bâ€™abahanga twavugamo Bagorozi na \r\nMuhabura tutibagiwe na Kalimunda. Abo bombi bigaragaje muri bya bisigo 7\r\n bise&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€ibisigo byâ€™ibyumaâ€!</i></span></li></ul></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"ibisigo_ibyuma\"></a></p><h4 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"ibisigo_ibyuma\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KUKI BYISWE IBISIGO BYâ€™IBYUMA?</span></a></h4><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Byaturutse\r\n ku makimbirane yabaye hagati ya Kalimunda na Muhabura, ubwo Kalimunda \r\nyajyaga gucurisha amacumu (ibyuma) byâ€™abarwanyi maze Muhabura \r\nakamurangarana, avuga ko yabanje gushaka ibikoresho byâ€™abacengeri \r\n(abatabazi). Bityo amakimbirane aravuka, haba kwibaza niba hatsinda&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>ingabo</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> cyangwa </span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>abatabazi.</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> Ibyo bituma Kalimunda \r\najya kurega Muhabura kwa Rujugira. Yamureze mu gisigo yise: </span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Ibyuma bitsindira abamiâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">. Mu kwiregura Muhabura yerekana ko yabanje gucura ibyangombwa byâ€™abatabazi, abivuga mu gisigo yise:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Ibyuma bimerira abami urubanza?â€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">. Umwami asaba abandi basizi kumufasha guca urubanza maze uwitwa Nyamugenda asa nâ€™ushyigikira Kalimunda mu gisigo yise&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Iyo urubanza rwagombye abakuruâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">. Abandi bari aho na bo bagize icyo babivugaho , ni bwo Bagorozi agize \r\nati </span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Zemeye inganzo ingongoâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">. Maze Muhabura, mu kwiregura asubiza Bagorozi ati </span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Mbwire Bagorozi umunsi ugumyeâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">. Umuhungu wa Muhabura witwaga Ndamira, aramwunganira mu gisigo \r\nyise:</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Abatabazi bagira ubatemeraâ€.</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> Mwene Bagorozina we yunganira se mu gushyigikira\r\n Kalimunda ati</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Urubanza ruhari ntiruhumburwaâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> asa nâ€™ushaka kuvuga ko urubanza rwaciwe nâ€™umwami rudasubirwamo.</span></p>\r\n	\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Muri ibyo bisigo kandi banajyaga impaka kugira ngo bagaragaze umusizi wâ€™umuhanga kurusha undi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"ndabarasa\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"ndabarasa\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> KU NGOMA YA NDABARASA.</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Nâ€™ubwo\r\n Ndabarasa na we yabaye intwari cyane, agatsinda i Ndorwa yâ€™Abashambo, \r\nakongera inka mu gihugu azikuye mu Nkole no mu Bumpaka, akigarurira \r\nUmubali amaze kwica Biyoro na Nyirabiyoro, yasigiwe ibisigo bine gusa.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ndabarasa yateye i Butembo ashaka kugumayo ngo ahimenyereze ni\r\n bwo abiru batumye Kibarake kujya kumuhamagara, babimutuma mu gisigo cyahimbwe na \r\nMusare cyitwa</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Mbwire umwami uko abandi bami bantume Byangabwanaâ€</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">. Kibarake \r\naragenda arakimubwira. Nuko Ndabarasa ngo yaba yaramukubise ni bwo Kibarake agarutse\r\n abasubiza mu gisigo cye yise</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Batewe nâ€™iki uburakeâ€.</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">\r\n Ngo na bo baramukubise asubirayo yongera kubwira Ndabarasa mu kindi \r\ngisigo cyahimbwe na Musare kitwaâ€None wamaze ubuhingeâ€. Ndabarasa \r\narabihorera. Nyuma yaje kuharwarira ibikoba (indwara yâ€™imitsi bamwe bita\r\n imitezi). Atari yagaruka se yahise yimika umwuzukuru we Sentabyo. \r\nNdabarasa yaje gupfira mu Ndorwa. Ku ngoma ye kandib abanyandorwa bari \r\nbaramutuye igisigo</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i> â€Agati bamanitse abamiâ€.&nbsp;</i></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Birashoboka ko impamvu yatuwe ibisigo ari uko yiberaga \r\nhanze arwana, ikindi kandi mu rwimo rwe nta magomerane yabaye kuko se yari \r\nyaramwimitse atarapfa.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"sentabyo\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"sentabyo\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KU NGOMA YA SENTABYO</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Nâ€™ubwo\r\n yamaze igihe gito ku ngoma (imyaka 5) ku ngoma ye habonetse ibisigo \r\nbigera kuri 21. Ibyo bikaba biterwa nâ€™uko se amaze gupfa habaye ibyo \r\nkurwanira ingoma nâ€™ubwo yari yarimitswe na sekuru se atarapfa. Bene se \r\nna bo bashakaga gutegeka. Barimo Ruzamba na Katarabuhura na nyina, \r\nbashyigikiwe na Rukari. Hari abandi bari bashyigikiwe na Gasenyi. Ibyo \r\nbyose byavuzwe mu bisigo nka</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Umwami si umuntu&nbsp;</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">na </span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Ko bavuga iridakuka abamiâ€.&nbsp;</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">\r\n Aho amariye gutsinda, ashyigikiwe na Kimanuka na Vuningoma waNyarwaya, \r\nndetse na nyina Nyiratamba (umwegakazi) na Nkebya hamwe nâ€™abiru \r\nbâ€™abatsobe ari na bo bari bakomeye kuruta abandi, abasizi bahise \r\nbapfunuka ari benshi baje kumushimira ko yatsinze. Urugero ni&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>â€Ntawe urenga icyo aziraâ€&nbsp;</i></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">cyari ikinyeto cya Gatarabuhura. \r\nUmusizi Muganza agira ati:</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" width=\"60%\" cellspacing=\"3\" cellpadding=\"2\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n<tbody><tr><td> \r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><i>Ko abatindi bakibeshya kwinshi<br>\r\nKo bagize ngo bageze barore<br>\r\nBakure ibyo Imana yavuze<br>\r\nIbyo Murema yaremye<br> Umwami aba ari Imana akabonwa nâ€™iyindi<br>\r\nIkamuha izina akima agahaka abantu<br>\r\nUwo Imana yameneye amata<br>\r\nNtiyunamuzwa amaboko</i></span></p>\r\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Sentabyo\r\n yishwe nâ€™iseru akiri umusore nta kana.Ubwo hahise haba â€Coup dâ€™Etatâ€: \r\nNkebya na Baryinyonza bashyigikira Nyiratunga, wari umupfakazi wa Gihana\r\n cya Rujugira wari warapfuye ari umucengeri i Burundi. Ubwo Nyiratunga \r\nakaba yari amaze kubyara Gahindiro, abanza gutegekerwa na nyina kuko \r\nyari akiri muto.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"gahindiro\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"gahindiro\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KU NGOMA YA GAHINDIRO</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Se\r\n yatanze ari bwo akivuka ku buryo yabanje gutegekerwa na nyina witwaga \r\nNyiratunga. Abaturage ntibari bamuzi igihe yagirwaga umwami. Amaze \r\ngukura yigaragaje nkâ€™umwami ucisha make kandi witonda. Ku ngoma ye \r\nibisigo byashoboye kuboneka bigera kuri 12.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rwogera\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rwogera\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> KU NGOMA YA RWOGERA</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Uyu\r\n na we yimye akiri muto abanza gutegekerwa na nyina witwaga Nyiramavugo \r\nNyiramongi mushiki wa Rwakagara rwa Gaga, bakundaga kwita umwogabyano \r\nkubera uburanga yari afite. Kwima kwa Mutara Rwogera kwahise \r\ngukurikirana nâ€™intsinzi yâ€™Abanyarwanda kuri Ntare IV Rugamba wâ€™u Burundi\r\n ndetse no kwigarurira i Gisaka. Ibyo byatumye abasizi barabukira umwami\r\n bwangu maze bamutura ibisigo bigera kuri 30. Rugaju rwa Mutimbo wari \r\ninkundwakazi yâ€™akadasohoka ya se ni bwo yanyazwe aricwa nâ€™umuryango we \r\nwose, ahagana mu wâ€™ 1848. Rwogera yari afite ingabo zâ€™intwari \r\nzamurwaniriye, kandi yahanze nâ€™indi mitwe irimo itorero Abakwiye \r\nyabyirukiyemo, umutwe witwa Inzirabwoba za Nkoronko, Uruyange zaRugaju \r\nzaje guhabwa Rwakagara se wa Kanjogera. Hakaba Intaganzwa za Marara, \r\nAbashakamba za Nkusi ya Gahindiro, Imvejuru za Nyarwaya, Urutesi \r\nnâ€™abakemba za Rwihimba nâ€™abandi. Izo ngabo ni zo zamuhaye gutsinda \r\nAbarundi mu gitero cya Rwagatana. Ku ngoma ye ni bwo habaye igitero \r\nkizwi cyane cyâ€™Imbungiramihigo kwa Makombe ho mu Bushi.</span></p>\r\n\r\n 	\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rwabugiri\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rwabugiri\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> KU NGOMA YA RWABUGIRI</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ku\r\n ngoma ye habonetse ibisigo byinshi ugereranije nâ€™abandi bami. Habonetse\r\n ibisaga 40. Ibyo bituruka ku mpamvu nyinshi zitandukanye:</span></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><ul><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> Yarambye ku ngoma</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"> Yari igisare gitegekesha igitugu, akica umubangamiye wese (Havugwa ko yakundaga \r\nkunywa inzoga maze ushatse kugira uwo yicisha akabimubwira (kuregesha umugono) akamutanga\r\n atabizi).</span></li><li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Yaharaniye ikuzo abigaragariza mu bitero yagabye akigarurira ibihugu, mu kuvugurura\r\n ubutegetsi no kwiyegereza abamusingiza (abasizi).</span></li></ul></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Mu\r\n kiciro cya kabiri abatavugwamo ni Mibambwe Rutarindwa wategetse amezi \r\n16 mbere yo gupfira ku Rucunshu ahagana mu 1986. Yabanje gutegekana na \r\nRwabugiri ku buryo no mu bisigo babavugwamo bombi Sezisoni wiswe \r\nRwabugiri amaze kwima, akaba avuka kuri Murorunkwere na Nkoronko, yaje \r\ngushyingirwa abakobwa batatu ba nyirarume Nzirumbanje, babiri muri bo \r\nbataha iwe bafite abana, abo bana bâ€™abazanano barimo Muhigirwa na \r\nRutarindwa, Rwabugiri abagira abe arabiyitirira asa nâ€™ukurikiza urugero \r\nrwa Rwogera wamwimitse kandi atari uwe. Nguko uko yimitse Mibambwe \r\nRutarindwa waje kwigizwayo nâ€™Abega ku ntambara yo ku Rucunshu kubera \r\nmuka se Kanjogera washakaga ko muhungu we Musinga ari we wima.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"musinga\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"musinga\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KU NGOMA YA MUSINGA</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ku\r\n ngoma ye habonetse ibisigo bigera kuri 9 gusa kubera ko agaciro \r\nkâ€™ubwami kasaga nâ€™agatangiye kugabanuka; ni bwo abazungu baje mu Rwanda,\r\n bakaba ari bo basaga nâ€™abari hejuru ye. Aaaaaaicyamuranze cyane ni uko \r\nyagerageje kurwanya abakoro ni kugeza nâ€™ubwo abizize bakamukura ku ngoma\r\n ndetse bakamwirukana mu gihugu, bakimika ku buryo bunyuranije n,ubwiru \r\nmuhungu we Rudahigwa.</span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rudahigwa\"></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><a name=\"rudahigwa\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">KU NGOMA YA RUDAHIGWA</span></a></h3><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">Ku\r\n ngoma ye naho habonetse ibisigo bike, birindwi gusa. Yaranzwe no kuba \r\nari umwami wakoranye nâ€™abakoroni bamwimitse, avanaho ubuhake nâ€™ibindi \r\nbyagiye biranga ingoma zamubanjirije, abazungu bamaze kubona ko ari \r\numwami washakaga ubumwe bwâ€™Abanyarwanda bahisemo kumwivugana mu buryo \r\nbutasobanukiye Abanyarwanda. Nta yindi mpamvu yabiteye ni uko babonaga \r\nbizabagora gushyira mu bikorwa politiki yabo yaâ€Diviser pour reignerâ€.</span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\"><br></span></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:18px\">IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></span></p>', '1497871250ibisigo.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 0, 'head', 114),
(93, '2017-07-05 18:55:31', 'Nyuma yuko mugihugu cyabaturanyi \"UGANDA\" hari imyambaro imwe yahagaritswe kwambarwa mukazi  kubera umuco wabo, hari icyo bamwe munanaribonye kumuco nyarwanda bagize icyo batangaza.', 'twegereye Umusaza MAKANYAGA,umubyeyi MARIYA ndetse  twaganiriye na Dr Nzabonimpa Jacques umuyobozi wâ€™Umuco mu Nteko Nyarwanda yâ€™Ururimi nâ€™Umuco (RALC) bagize icyo badutangariza............', '<div align=\"left\">Mwitangira ry\' icyicyumweru kumunsi wacyo wa mbere umuyobozi&nbsp; ushinzwe umurimo mu gihugu cya Uganda&nbsp;&nbsp; <b>Catherine Bitarakwate</b> yashyize hanze itangazo rihagarika imyambaro imwe nimwe muri icyi gihugu avuga ko itemewe mukazi. Yagize ati\'<br><br>&nbsp;kubagore <br></div><div align=\"left\">Imyambaro migufi irenze amavi, niyegereye umuntu igashushanya bimwe mubice byumubiri&nbsp; ntabwo yemewe mu kazi\"<br><br>yongeye ho kandi ko imyenda ibonerarana nayo itemewe mukazi .<br><br><img class=\"size-full wp-image-45286 tie-appear\" src=\"https://www.independent.co.ug/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/KCCA-dress-code-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"324\"><br><br><br>Ibi bibaye nyuma yuko muri Uganda hagenda hagaragara kwambara ubusa bikabije, bigenda byambuka umupaka bikaza no mu Rwanda. Muri Uganda bamwe mubagore ntibatinya kwamabara uko bashatse aho bari hose ndetse batitaye kucyo barigukora.Ibi bitera bamwe kuvuga ko bataye umuco. Bikomeza&nbsp; kandi kugaragara cyane kubahanzi bo muri icyigihugu aho amashusho y;indirimbo zabo aba arimo amafoto yabagore nabakobwa bambaye hafi ubusa.Burya bwabusa.bamwe mubona muri za video no kumafoto agaragara kumbuga nkoranya mbaga ngo abagandekazi&nbsp; bo babyambara no mukazi.!<br><br>ESE ABANYARWANDAKAZI BO BIGEZE HE? <br><br>Umunyarwanda yaravuze ati nyamara ujya gutera uburezi arabwibanza, kandi ati ijya kurisha ihera kurugo. <br><br>Nyuma yo kubona ko icyi cyorezo cyimyambarire mibi kigenda gifata indi ntera no&nbsp; mu Rwagasabo twagerageje kubaza bamwe bafite inara ribonye uko babibona.<br><br>Mu kiganiro twagiranye na MAKANYAGA umwe mubahanzi bakuze benshi bigiraho byinshi \'.<br><br>umunyamakuru wa umucowacu.com: yamubajije uko abona imyambarire yabanyarwanda bariho ubu <br><b>yagize ati Ntakintu itwaye&nbsp; nuko twavangiye umuco wacu</b><br>amubajije niba kuva nakera byarahozeho kwambara&nbsp; nkibiriho ubu<br><b>&nbsp;yagize ati kuva nakera byahozeho nuko twari dukomeye ku muco,kera Min jupe zabagaho&nbsp; barazikuye mumico yahandi gusa abazambaraga ntibavugagwa neza </b><br>umunyamakuru wa umucowacu.com:&nbsp; yakomeje amubaza niba&nbsp; abona nta&nbsp; ruhare rwabahanzi&nbsp; mumyambarire iriho mu Rwanda.<br>&nbsp;<b>MAKANYAGA&nbsp; ati\" kuva kera umuhanzi mbere yuko asohora indirimbo yayijyana ga kuri Radio Rwanda bakareba niba ntajambo ribi ryanditsemo ikiri munyandiko, ubu rero aba basore nabo mbafata nkabavuga butumwa bwiza , ntawutanga ubutumwa bubi. kwambara ubusa si ubutumwa bwiza,<br>ikindi abahanzi nabo harebwa ukuntu basohora indirimbo zagenzuwe kandi namashusho yazo yagenzuwe .<br>ese ugirango nabanyamakuru ntibafitemo uruhare ? Bakabona abantu bambaye ubusa bagakomeza kwerekana&nbsp; izo ndirimbo !.Nimureke dufatanye\".<br>&nbsp;</b><br><div align=\"left\"><br><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.igihe.com/IMG/jpg/arton990.jpg\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" width=\"853\" height=\"480\" border=\"0\"><br>Makanyaga<br></div></center><br><br>Mu kiganiro twagiranye na MARIYA YOHANA <br><br>umunyamakuru wa umucowacu.com: ese mwamenye ko muri Uganda bahagaritse imyenda imwe nimwe kubagandekazi mu gihe cyakazi?<br>MARIYA YOHANA: erega bariya nabagande buriya&nbsp; byari bibarembeje ariko abanyarwandakazi bo ntitwari twatangira gutesha dukomeje .<br>umunyamakuru wa umucowacu.com:&nbsp; ese mubona nta&nbsp; ruhare rwabahanzi&nbsp; mumyambarire iriho mu Rwanda?<br>MARIYA YOHANA: erega dutinya kwinjira mubuzima bwite bwabantu, abahanzi bafite uruhare kuko bakurikiranwa cyane gusa inama nabaha nuko kwambara neza atari ukwambara ubusa, kwambara uki kwiza niwo muco. Umukobwa wu Rwanda niyambare kuburyo umuntu umubonye avuga ko ari umunyarwandakazi ,erega umuhanzi akwiye kwikwiza cg yanakwambara bigufi ntarenze mumavi ndetse naza pasura zubu ntizibe zambitse umuntu ubusa , erega kwambara neza sukwambara ubusa. Natwe abakuze&nbsp; byadushimisha tubona abana bambaye neza.<br>&nbsp;<br><br><center>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<img src=\"http://igihe.com/IMG/jpg/19920303173_12026c6609_h.jpg\" style=\"-moz-border-radius:10px; -webkit-border-radius:10px; border-radius:10px;\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" border=\"0\"><br></div></center></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"gh_articlep_dphotos\" align=\"left\">Mariya Yohana ni umwe mu bahanzi bakoze indirimbo zivuga ku kwibohora zakunzwe cyane<br>&nbsp; <br><br><br>Nyuma yo kuganira nabahanzi twashatse kumenya icyo<br><br></div><div align=\"left\">\r\n\r\n<b>Dr.Nzabonimpa Jacques</b> umuyobozi wâ€™Umuco mu Nteko Nyarwanda yâ€™Ururimi nâ€™Umuco (RALC) abivugaho <br><br><br><br><img class=\"size-full wp-image-212053\" src=\"http://www.umuseke.rw/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Dr-Nzabonimpa-Jacques-umuyobozi-w%E2%80%99Umuco-mu-Nteko-Nyarwanda-y%E2%80%99Ururimi-n%E2%80%99Umuco-RALC.jpg\" alt=\"Dr Nzabonimpa Jacques umuyobozi wâ€™Umuco mu Nteko Nyarwanda yâ€™Ururimi nâ€™Umuco (RALC)\" width=\"743\" height=\"496\"><br>Mukiganiro twagiranye twamubajije imyambarire ihuye numuco Nyarwanda&nbsp; iyariyo.<br>Dr Jacques yavuze ko kwambara bijyanye numuco wabanyarwanda ari ukwambara uki kwiza kuburyo nawe ubwawe uba utabangamiwe kandi ntanundi wabangamiye.<br>tumubajije uko abona Abakozi bo Mu rwanda nimyambarire abona yatubwiye ko umukozi agomba kwambara yibuka nakazi baribukore kandi kuburyo bitamubuza gukora akazi neza,&nbsp; harigihe ubona umukozi yambaye ariko atakunama kandi icyo gihe aba abangamiwe .<br>tumubajije uko abona abahanzi nindirimbo zitavugwaho rumwe nabenshi <br>Dr Jacques yakomeje avuga ko nâ€™itangazamakuru rikwiye kujya ribanza rigashishoza kumashusho ndetse ko nabahanzi bakomeza kuba intore dore ko benshi banaciye mwitorero ndetse ko abahanzi bakwiye gukora ibihangano bitabangamira umuco&nbsp; ko kandi abo bizananarira bagakomeza kubangamira umuco nkibisanzwe ibihangano byabo bizahagarikwa. <br><br>Abwirwa benshi hakumva bene yo?<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">umuco ntugacike.<br></p></div><div align=\"left\"><br><br>&nbsp;IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></div> ', '14992737311433236291_abagore.jpg', 0, 'admin', 3, 11, 'head', 254);
