(94, '2017-07-07 12:19:45', 'ïƒ˜	Tuyisenge Olivier kuri iyi nshuro atiâ€ ndi igisigo\"', 'ïƒ˜	Umusizi tuyisenge Olivier akuzaniye igitaramo cy\'ubusizi  yise â€œNDI IGISIGO\"', ' <div align=\"justify\"><b>Tuyisenge olivier</b> ni rimwe mu mazina azwi cyane mu isi y\'abakunda ubusizi, abategura amarushanwa y\'imivugo ndetse no mu ma filime. kurubu aragira ati \"ibyo nari ntetse biri gushya bishyira kuribwa\".Nyuma yo kuvuga imivugo mwakunze n\'ibisigo bisiganye ubuhanga bihangara umutima bigatuma ibyishimo byuzura abataramiwe, yongeye kugutegurira igitaramo yise \"<b> NDI IGISIGO</b>\" kizaba tarikiya <b>06/ 08/2017 </b>kikabera muri<b> FEEL AT HOME BAR&amp;RESTO( REMERA).</b> Ntazaba ari wenyine muri iki gitaramo azaba ari kumwe na&nbsp; bakabuhariwe mu nganzo y\'ubusizi ndetse ni zindi nganzo gakondo, bazi gutarama cyane nka : <br><b><br>MUNYAKAZI DEO</b>, umukirigitananga&nbsp; uzwi cyane kubw\'inanga za nyuze benshi nka;&nbsp;&nbsp; \"<b>Isoko dusangiye</b>\", \"<b>Urakwirye mwami</b>\" , nizindi nyinshi.<br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201603/attachments/1459254483_img20160329wa0020.jpg\" title=\"undefined\" alt=\"deo\"><br>MUNYAKAZI DEO<br><br><br><br><b>ERIC ONEKEY</b>,umusizi wamenyekanye kubwo  gukora imivugo irimo ubuhanga buhanitse ndetse isiguye mu ndimi \r\nzitandukanye, Ikinyarwanda, Igifaransa ndetse nâ€™Icyongereza<br><br><br><br><img class=\" wp-image-1349\" src=\"http://iwacumag.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/onekey-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"Ibyerekeye byose Expericment 3.0\" height=\"344\" width=\"344\"><br>ERIC ONEKEY<br><br>Saba gusa bazitabira ikigitarmo, tuzaba turikumwe na bandi benshi muzi cyane mu nganzo gakondo nka: <b>BAHATI INNOCENT, PASCAL SOLO,&nbsp; MUNEZERO FERDNAND, MANIRAGUHA CARINE, NIYOMUKIZA GILDAS, NINA RUTH HARRIS na&nbsp; ANGE POETRY RWANDA</b>. udushya two nitwinshi nka :<b> LIVE PAINTING</b>, aho abafana babishaka bazajya bakorerwa amafoto yabo ashushanyijwe muri ako kanya.!<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://fb-s-d-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-fbx/v/t1.0-9/19701984_868951109918648_1106366349371062411_n.jpg?oh=1227ad29425af1ad4148ff7e109b109d&amp;oe=59C516C1&amp;__gda__=1510928396_4311c37ea3d3d8589de2d48e4b80b151\" alt=\"Image may contain: 7 people, text\" class=\"spotlight\"><br><i><b>URUPAPURO RWAMAMAZA IKI GITARAMO</b></i><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>N. JERO<br></div>', '1499422785umusizi Tuyi.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 14, 'break', 250),
(95, '2017-07-13 10:13:39', 'Kaneza Sheja washyize ahagaragara indirimbo ivuga ibigwi Perezida Paul Kagame yemeza ko nyuma yo guhimba indirimbo Yise \" Kagame karambe\" inzozi ze zabaye impamo .', 'Umuhanzi Kaneza Sheja wamaze gushyira ahagaragara indirimbo â€œKagame Karambeâ€ ivuga ibigwi byâ€™umukuru wâ€™igihugu Perezida Paul Kagame.', '<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><b>Umuhanzi Kaneza Sheja</b> uri mu cyiciro cyanyuma umwaka wa gatanu mu ishuri ryâ€™umuziki ku Nyundo ndetse wamaze gushyira ahagaragara indirimbo â€œ<b>Kagame Karambeâ€</b> ivuga ibigwi byâ€™umukuru wâ€™igihugu <b>Perezida Paul Kagame</b>, yemeza&nbsp; byakabaye ngombwa abahanzi bose bagaca mu ishuri ryâ€™umuziki kuko bibafasha kuyobora neza impano bafite no guhanga ibyubaka igihugu bifite umumaro.</p><p align=\"left\"><b>Kaneza &nbsp;Sheja</b> witegura guhabwa impamyabumenyi muri muzika,yemeza ko yagiye kwiga muzika nyuma yo kubwirwa na benshi \r\nndetse akabona ko afite impano yâ€™ubuhanzi yabonye adashobora kuyiyobora \r\nneza atanyuze mu ishuri ngo amenye indagagaciro na kirazira \r\nzizamuyobora. Nyuma yo kwiga muri iri shuri &nbsp;ryo ku Nyundo ,Kaneza \r\nyemeza ko yasobanukiwe ibyo akora ndetse amenya kubitandukanya nâ€™ibyo \r\nyarazi &nbsp;no guha abanyarwanda ibintu bisobanutse kandi bishyitse.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/13315394_634245976727445_7265419093409892166_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-30733\" src=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/13315394_634245976727445_7265419093409892166_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"619\" height=\"412\"></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Kuri ubu uyu muhanzi Kaneza isheja yemeza ko nyuma yaho \r\nahimbiye iyi ndirimbo byatumye akabya inzozi dore ko yemeza ko, yabonye \r\niterambere ryihuse kandi rifatika ry\'uburyo bwose haba mukubona abakunzi\r\n benshi ndetse n\'iterambere&nbsp; ry\'ibifatika.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Kaneza numwe mu bahanzi bakomeye baririmba indirimbo zibanda ku muco,kandi akagira umwihariko ndetse&nbsp; ibihangano bye abihanga <br>\r\nagendeye ku ndangagaciro na kirazira ari nayo mpamvu&nbsp; yemeza ko ibyo<br>\r\naririmba bigomba kugira ireme haba mu<br>\r\nmiririmbire,imyandikire,<wbr>imicurangire nâ€™ijwi.<br></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Ikindi twavuga kuri uyu muhanzi intore idasobanya Kaneza \r\nubu yabaye uwa mbere mu Turere dutanfukanye aho agomba kwamamariza Umu \r\ncandidat wa <b>RPF</b>  mu turere dukurikira:<br>\r\nRusizi <br>\r\nKarongi<br>\r\nRubavu <br>\r\nKayonza.</p><p align=\"left\"><a href=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Captureaaa.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-30735\" src=\"http://kigalihit.rw/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Captureaaa.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"541\" height=\"555\"></a></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\">Mukiganiro Kaneza yagiranye na <a href=\"http://umucowacu.com\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://umucowacu.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1500017902875000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFqC1sE41WINQZDdt_tg3Umx8TxBQ\">umucowacu.com</a>\r\n akomeza yibutsa abafana be ndetse n\'abandi bose gukomeza kumushyigikira \r\nndetse no gukomeza gutunga indirimbo ye <b>\'\' KAGAME KARAMBE\'</b>\'&nbsp; asoza abwira\r\n abakunzi be ko kubaka u Rwanda ari inshingano ya buri wese ati kandi \r\nguhitamo neza niyo nkingi yabyose.\r\nKaneza asoza asezeranya abakunzi be ko indirimbo zirimo ubutumwa bwo kwiyubakira igihugu zizaba zigeze hanze vuba aha ziherekejwe na amashusho ya \"KAGAME KARAMBE\".\r\n  <br><br><br>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></div>', '1499933619kaneza.jpg', 0, 'admin', 4, 3, 'break', 241),
(96, '2017-07-20 20:30:56', '\"Nta mukobwa n\'umwe uratumwa guhagararira u Rwanda muri Miss Supranational\"-RALC yahakanye abakobwa babeshya ko yabatumye mu marushanwa mpuza mahanga', 'Ibi byatangajwe na Dr Jacques Nzabonimpa umuyobozi wâ€™umuco muri RALC', 'Muri iyi minsi hadutse inkuru ivuga ko umukobwa witwa Ingabire Habibah \r\nariwe munyarwandakazi uzaba ari mu marushanwa ya Miss Supranational, \r\ngusa amakuru ahari ni uko Habibah hari ibyo asabwa gukora kugira ngo \r\nagende nkâ€™umukobwa uhagarariye igihugu.<br>Ibi byatangajwe na Dr Jacques Nzabonimpa umuyobozi wâ€™umuco muri RALC \r\nubwo yari abajijwe nâ€™umunyamakuru wa inyarwanda.com uko bigenda ngo \r\numukobwa runaka ahagararire igihugu mu marushanwa anyuranye, cyane ko \r\nabakobwa benshi mu bajya muri Miss Supranational bataha bavuzweho \r\namakuru atari meza.\r\n<p><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500550204_colombe.jpg\" alt=\"MISS COLOMBE\" class=\" b-loaded\" width=\"800\" height=\"540\"><em><br></em></p><p><em>Akiwacu Colombe ni we munyarwandakazi wari muri aya marushanwa umwaka ushize</em></p>\r\n<p><strong>Nta mukobwa n\'umwe urahagararira u Rwanda muri Miss Supranationalâ€¦</strong></p>\r\n<p>Dr Nzabonimpa Jacques yatangaje ko abakobwa bose bagiye bitabira Miss\r\n Supranational babaga bahamagawe ku giti cyabo bakagenda&nbsp; ku giti cyabo \r\nbatanamenyesheje igihugu ngo nacyo kibatume kugihagararira ari nayo \r\nmpamvu ibyo bakorayo akenshi bitakabaye bibazwa igihugu ahubwo byakabaye\r\n bibazwa bo ubwabo.</p>\r\n<p>Akomeza avuga ko aba bakobwa bajya muri Miss Supranationa ku giti \r\ncyabo, baramutse&nbsp;bitwara neza, ngo bashimirwa nkâ€™undi munyarwanda \r\nwakwitwara neza ariko ngo singombwa ko abitwaye neza bose baba batumwe \r\nnâ€™igihugu.</p>\r\n<p>Dr Jacques Nzabonimpa yakomeje abwira Inyarwanda ko umuntu ujya mu \r\nirushanwa ahagarariye igihugu hari inzira acamo ndetse agahabwa \r\nnâ€™ibendera ryâ€™igihugu nkuko bigenda ku bajya guhagararira igihugu muri \r\nMiss World cyangwa Miss Hertage Global bityo rero ngo uwagiye \r\natamenyesheje ubuyobozi ko agiye ntabwo aba ahagarariye igihugu kuko \r\numuntu ahagararira uwamutumye.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500550204_dr.jpg\" alt=\"dr jacques\" class=\" b-loaded\"><em><br></em></p><p><em>Dr Nzabonimpa Jacques ushinzwe umuco muri RALC</em></p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Barifuza kubonana n\'uwohereza abanyarwandakazi muri Miss Supranationalâ€¦</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>Twabajije Dr Nzabonimpa Jacques niba koko baba bazi umuntu utoranya \r\numunyarwandakazi witabira amarushanwa mpuzamahanga ya Miss Supranational\r\n atubwira ko batamuzi ariko yungamo ko ari nuburenganzira \r\nbwâ€™umunyarwandakazi kwishakira inzira yacamo ngo agerageze amahirwe ye \r\nahubwo ikibazo akaba ari uko iyo bagiye kugenda bategera inzego \r\nzibishinzwe kugira ngo zibaganirize zibahe impamba nkâ€™abagiye \r\nguhagararira igihugu ndetse banagire ibyo bibutswa nka Kirazira zâ€™umuco \r\nnyarwanda. Bityo ngo bari gushaka uko bahura n\'utoranya aba bakobwa \r\nkugira ngo berebere hamwe uko byashyirwa ku murongo.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Habibah Ingabire uzitabira iri rushanwa uyu mwaka &nbsp;wa 2017 hari ibyo asabwa gukora ngo agende ahagarariye igihuguâ€¦</strong></p>\r\n<p>Dr Nzabonimpa Jacques yabajijwe na Inyarwanda icyo umukobwa wenda \r\nguhagararira u Rwanda yakora ngo azitabire iri rushanwa atumwe nâ€™igihugu\r\n abwira Inyarwanda.com ko Habibah Ingabire yashaka uburyo abimenyesha \r\ninzego zibishinzwe bakagirana ibiganiro bakagira impanuro bamuha ndetse \r\nbakamutuma nkuko batuma abandi bose bahagararira igihugu.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500550204_habibah.jpg\" alt=\"HABIBAH\" class=\" b-loaded\" width=\"800\" height=\"535\"><strong><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br></em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Habibah utarahiriwe muri Miss Rwanda, kuri ubu ni we munyarwandakazi ugiye kwitabira Miss Supranational</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>Ibi bije nyuma yaho mu myaka yashize abakobwa benshi bitabiraga iri \r\nrushanwa hari ingingo yagiye ibagonga rimwe bakagwa mu mutego wo \r\nkwambara imyambaro itavugwaho rumwe dore ko baba basabwa kwambara \r\numwambaro wo kogana uzwi nka â€˜Bikiniâ€™.</p><p>SRC inyarwanda.com<br></p><p><i><b>@umucowacu Ntugacike</b></i><br></p>', '1500575456umuco.jpg', 0, 'admin', 5, 12, 'head', 162),
(97, '2017-07-21 14:37:00', ' IKIGANIRO na Miss Iradukunda Elsa  Nyuma yo kugaragara ari kumwe  na Perezida Kagame  yatanze ubutumwa â€“ REBA AMAFOTO', 'Kuwa 19 Nyakanga 2017 ubwo Perezida Kagame yajyaga kwiyamamariza mu karere ka Bugesera yari yaherekejwe n\'abanyarwanda batari bake barimo na Miss Iradukunda Elsa,', '<div align=\"left\"><span class=\"surtitre\"><p>&nbsp;AMATEKA YA Iradukunda\r\n Elsa ni umukobwa muremure wâ€™inzobe ushinguye, ukunda guseka akagira \r\namenyo yererana mu ishinya nziza yâ€™umukara,niwe Nyampinga wâ€™u Rwanda umwaka wa 2017.</p></span></div>\r\n														 	\r\n												<div class=\"col col-lg-12\" align=\"left\">  \r\n														<div class=\"fulltext margintop10\">\r\n															<p>Yabyawe na Samuel Mana ufite ibiro byâ€™ivunjisha mu \r\nMujyi wa Kigali rwagati naho nyina akitwa Mukandekezi Christine akora \r\nakazi kâ€™ubucuruzi, batuye mu Kagari ka Kanserege, mu Murenge wa Gikondo,\r\n mu Karere ka Kicukiro.</p>\r\n<p>Iradukunda Elsa areshya na metero imwe na sentimetero 76 (1,76cm) \r\nakaba apima ibiro 50. Afite imyaka 19 yâ€™amavuko kuko yavutse kuwa 25\r\n Werurwe 1998, avuka mu muryango wâ€™abana umunani[abakobwa batandatu \r\nnâ€™abahungu babiri] akaba ari uwa kane.</p>\r\n<p>Mu ijoro rya taliki 25 Gashyantare 2017 Iradukunda Elsa yatorewe kuba\r\n Nyampinga uhiga abandi mu buranga nâ€™ubuhanga. Yahawe ibihembo bikomeye \r\nbirimo imodoka nziza ya Suzuki SX4 ifite agaciro ka miliyoni 15 \r\nzâ€™amafaranga yâ€™u Rwanda.</p>\r\n<p>Mu gihe cyâ€™umwaka azamarana ikamba azajya ahembwa umushahara \r\nwâ€™amafaranga ibihumbi magana inani (800,000frw) bivuze ko ku mwaka \r\nazajya aba yahawe miliyoni icyenda nâ€™ibihumbi Magana atandatu \r\n(9,600,000Rwf) hakiyongeraho nâ€™ibindi bihembo bitandukanye.</p>\r\n<p>Azahabwa ibindi bihembo birimo imyambaro igezweho, gukorerwa imisatsi\r\n buri kwezi, kogerezwa imodoka, gutemberezwa mu mahanga ya kure ndetse \r\nmu mpera zâ€™umwaka wa 2017 azaserukira u Rwanda mu irushanwa ryâ€™ubwiza \r\nrya Miss World.</p>\r\n<p>Iradukunda Elsa avuga adategwa indimi eshatu, Igifaransa, Icyongereza\r\n nâ€™Ikinyarwanda. Yari ahagarariye Intara yâ€™u Burengerazuba, .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Umushinga yifuza gukora mu gihe azamarana ikamba rya Nyampinga wâ€™u \r\nRwanda ngo â€˜ni ugufasha leta guha ingufu gahunda ya Made in Rwandaâ€™ no \r\nguteza imbere ba rwiyemezamarimo bafite ibikorwa byihariye bishyigikira \r\numurongo arimo.</p><p>Kuwa 19 Nyakanga 2017 ubwo Perezida Kagame \r\nyajyaga kwiyamamariza mu karere ka Bugesera yari yaherekejwe \r\nn\'abanyarwanda batari bake barimo na Miss Iradukunda Elsa, uyu ukunze \r\nkugaragara aherekeza Perezida Kagame ahantu hanyuranye aba yagiye \r\nkwiyamamaza, icyakora mu mafoto yafotowe uyu mukobwa biragaragara ko \r\nyagize amahirwe yo guhura imbonankubone na Perezida Kagame ndetse \r\nnâ€™umufasha we.</p>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1000px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\">\r\n<b>REBA MU MAFOTO UKO BYARI BIMEZE:</b><br><div class=\"artlogo\">\r\n					<a href=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/logos/1500537794_logo.jpg\" rel=\"prettyPhoto[gallery2]\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/logos/1500537794_logo.jpg\" alt=\"Miss Iradukunda Elsa yagize amahirwe yo guhura imbonankubone na Perezida Kagame â€“AMAFOTO\" class=\" b-error\"></a>					\r\n				</div>\r\n			\r\n			\r\n				\r\n					<p><br></p><br>\r\n<p><strong><em><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542497_4.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" class=\" b-loaded\">Iradukunda Elsa aganira na Perezida Kagame </em></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><em><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542497_3.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" class=\" b-loaded\">Miss Elsa Iradukunda yaganiriye kandi na Madame Jeannette Kagame</em></strong></p><p><strong><em><br></em></strong></p><p><br></p><p>Tukimara kubona aya mafoto twifuje kumenya uko uyu mukobwa yakiriye \r\nguhura nâ€™umuryango wa Perezida Kagame, adutangariza ko yabyishimiye \r\ncyane. Miss Elsa Iradukunda yabwiye umucowacu.com&nbsp; ko i cyari cyiraje inshinga ari ugushyigikira&nbsp; uwasubije agaciro umunyarwandakazi ndetse akamuha&nbsp; ijambo kandi njyewe ndi urugero rwiza&nbsp; rwuko twahawe ijambo.<br></p>\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n<p><strong><em><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542497_2.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" class=\" b-loaded\"><img src=\"http://inyarwanda.com/img/201707/attachments/1500542498_1.jpg\" alt=\"miss rwanda\" class=\" b-loaded\" width=\"1080\" height=\"708\">Miss Rwanda Iradukunda Elsa ari mu rubyiruko rwanahuye na muzehe <span>Ngarambe</span><span>&nbsp;FranÃ§ois&nbsp;</span>umunyamabanga mukuru wa FPR-Inkotanyi</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Tumubajije&nbsp; ubutumwa yatanga muri icyigihe cy\'amatora ati:Inama nagira&nbsp; abanyarwanda nugutora umucandida&nbsp; babona ubereye U Rwanda uwo babona uzabageza ku Rwanda&nbsp; </em></strong><em><b>bifuza.</b><br></em></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<p><strong>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></strong></p></div></div>', '1500640620MISS RWANDA @017.jpg', 0, 'admin', 5, 12, 'head', 429),
(98, '2017-08-09 13:06:32', '  Umusizi Tuyisenge olivier umenyerewe cyane mu busizi kuri ubu yamaze gukora igitaramo cy\'akataraboneka yise Ndi igisigo REBA-AMAFOTO', 'Igitaramo cy\'Umusizi Tuyisenge yakoze yise NDI IGISIGO cyagaragayemo udushya twinshi', '\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Iki gitaramo cyabaye kuri iki cyumweru tariki 6<br>\r\nKanama 2017 guhera I saa<br>\r\nkumi nâ€™ebyiri nâ€™igice i Remera ahitwa muri Feel at home hafi ya controle<br>\r\nTechnique imbere neza yâ€™igicumbi cyâ€™intwari. Igitaramo Ndi igisigo \r\ncyabaye akataraboneka aho uyu musore, <b>Tuyisenge </b>ukiri muto nyuma yo \r\ngukora iki gitaramo kikagenda neza maze aho cyari cyabereye hagakubita \r\nhakuzura dore ko kwinjira byari 2000rwf na 5000rwf muri VIP.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Abasizi n\'abakunda ibisigo ntibahatanzwe dore ko hari hakubise huzuye bose bishimye cyane.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Iki gitaramo ni kimwe mu bitaramo byagaragayemo bamwe mu bahanzi gakondo kandi bamaze kugaragaza itandukaniro.<br>\r\naribo nka <b>Munyakazi Deo</b> umwe mubakirigitananga bakomeye muri uru Rwanda,<br>\r\n<b>Munezero Ferdinand</b> umutaramyi akaba nâ€™umusangiza wâ€™amagambo byâ€™umwuga<br>\r\nndetse akaba nâ€™umukirigitananga, Uyu munezero niwe wari wabaye umusangiza w\'amagambo muri Ndi Igisigo, Bahati Innocent<br>\r\nIki gitaramo cyâ€™ubusizi cyarimo agashya kuko hagaragayemo <b>Pascal solo</b> umwe mu<br>\r\nbaririmbyi bafite umwihariko wo gucurika indirimbo(igifefeko) wamenyekanye cyane mugucurika <br>\r\nindirimbo ya King james Nturare utabivuze,hagaragayemo kandi Mr rimer umusizi ukora ubusizi<br>\r\nbwiganjemo urwenya mu rurimi rwâ€™icyongereza.<br>\r\nNdi igisigo kandi yagaragayemo itsinda <b>Ikome group</b> rikora ubusizi<br>\r\nbuvanze nâ€™imbyino ndetse nâ€™umuziki.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a3NGKbY.jpg\" width=\"515\" height=\"342\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Muri iki gitaramo hagaragayemo ubuhanga bwo<br>\r\ngushushanya umuntu ako kanya (live painting) byakonzwe na <b>celestin Munezero </b>umwe mu banyabugeni batanga icyizere k\'ejo hazaza.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><b>Ndi igisigo</b> kimwe mu bitaramo&nbsp; bitazibagirana mu mitima ya benshibemeza ko byari ibihe<br>\r\nbyiza,Nkuko n\'amafoto abyerekana.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Mu kiganiro twagiranye n\' <b>Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier</b> wateguye<br>\r\niki gitaramo yatangiye<br>\r\nashimira abasizi,ndetse n\'abandi bose baje<br>\r\nkwifatanya nawe,akomeza avuga ko<br>\r\nibyiza biri imbere kandi ko agikomeje gukora cyane.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RxOmI01.jpg\" width=\"569\" height=\"379\"></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">Agashya kagaragaye mu gitaramo ndi igisigo nuko \r\numuririmbyikazi ukomoka muri Amerika Rachel yaririmbye mu kinyarwanda \r\nbigaherekezwa n\'umurya w\'inanga wa Deo Munyakazi ndetse n\'ibisigo \r\nby\'Umusizi Tuyisenge aribyo amaso ararengana ndetse na mukumbure mukure \r\nhe?</p><p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\"><br></p><p dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">REBA AMAFOTO:<br></p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/riScgaM.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><strong>Umusizi Tuyisenge afatanije na Deo Munyakazi</strong><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TY0as9b.jpg\" width=\"360\"><br>Carine <br><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7DwGGaN.jpg\" width=\"360\"><br>Mr rimer<br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ws0XMCA.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><span class=\"spip_document_4285 spip_documents spip_documents_center\"></span><strong>Uwera na Pascal Solo</strong><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gnpNPVQ.jpg\" width=\"360\"><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a1ly73t.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Fdzr3Ba.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br>NIYITEGEKA uzwi nka SEBU<br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/N4Ftxg3.jpg\" width=\"360\"><br><p><span class=\"spip_document_4287 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<br></span></p><p><strong>Munezero celestin yahakoreye ibihangano ashushanya imbonankubone</strong></p><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0MQG1iK.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RxOmI01.jpg\" width=\"569\" height=\"379\"><br>UMUSIZI TUYISENGE<br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/quztLNL.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><strong>Itsinda Ikome ryasusurukije abitabiriye igitaramo Ndi Igisigo</strong><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WCD29R7.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br>umuririmbyikazi ukomoka muri Amerika Rachel<br><br>AMAFOTO:Mon Light Picture<br><br><b><br>IRADUKUNDA MOSEs<br></b><br><br><br><br></div>', '1502276792PhotoGrid_1502205579451.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 14, 'head', 353),
(99, '2017-08-17 08:05:57', ' Itariki y\'ubukwe bw\'Umusizi Munezero Ferdinand yamenyekanye', ' Munezero Ferdinand umuhanzi wâ€™imbyino gakondo nyarwanda akaba nâ€™umusizi ukomeye yamaze kugaragaza uwo bakundana ashyira hanze nigihe bazakorera ubukwe.', '<br><div align=\"left\">Inkuru yagiye ahagaragara kwifoto yashyize kurukuta rwe \r\nrwa facebook Munezero Ferdinand yagaragaje ko yiteguye nawe gukora ubukwe mu mpera zâ€™uyu mwaka wa 2017<br>agira ati <b>\"Muraho neza Inkubito yabadahunga mbatumiye munkera nkiyi. Muzaze dusangire ingamba twizihirwe n\'inganzo\'\'</b><br><br>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://ci4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/r4Vphg6kfd1W3xpPtnrPtprs5YHYyMDDZ1aUNXggtaANTFU5rKyvFkoZabtMYQThA14jqQ=s0-d-e1-ft#http://i.imgur.com/mcVDxwo.jpg\" class=\"CToWUd a6T\" tabindex=\"0\" width=\"360\"><br><br>Twakwibutsa\r\n ko Munezero Ferdinand&nbsp; ari&nbsp; umuhanzi wâ€™imbyino gakondo nyarwanda akaba \r\nnâ€™umusizi ukomeye ndetse amenyerewe kuvuga inka,Akaba umusangiza \r\nw\'amagambo ukomeye mugihugu dore ko ikinyarwanda akivuga atacyototera.<br>Munezero akubutse muri  Koreya yâ€™Amajyepfo mu Mujyi wa Seoul.<br>Aho\r\n yari mu mahugurwa ya â€œCulture Paternership Initiative  aya mahugurwa \r\nahuza abahanzi bakora muzika gakondo baturutse mu mpande zitandukanye \r\nzâ€™isi. akaba ariwe Munyafurika wari witabiriye&nbsp; ayo&nbsp; mahugurwa<br><span><span class=\"m_6335105650120230747gmail-fsm m_6335105650120230747gmail-fwn m_6335105650120230747gmail-fcg\"><a class=\"m_6335105650120230747gmail-_5pcq\" href=\"https://web.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=325434641122273&amp;set=a.183595511972854.1073741827.100009672195729&amp;type=3\" rel=\"theater\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=https://web.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid%3D325434641122273%26set%3Da.183595511972854.1073741827.100009672195729%26type%3D3&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1503036143768000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHvdEtgQZOGFR9_4ed_KJwkpOisZQ\"><abbr title=\"Thursday, August 11, 2016 at