(100, '2017-08-17 09:45:33', ' Amateka y\'umusizikazi Carine Maniraguha umukobwa usa na TETA Diana  akaba na Divine ukina muri Seburikoko', ' Carine Maniraguha umusizikazi ufite umwihariko ukomeye mubuzisi bwe akomeje gukundwa nabenshi ndetse uyu azwi nka Divine ugaragara muri filime ya Seburikoko.', '<div align=\"left\"><b>Carine Maniraguha</b> nimwene&nbsp; <b><i>Karikumutima Pierre Celestin</i></b> na \r\n<b>Mukakabera Jacqueline</b> yavutse 1993 avukira i Kigali kacyiru gasabo .\r\n Ni umwana wa kabiri mu muryango \r\nwâ€™iwabo ugizwe nâ€™abana batanu abakobwa babiri nâ€™abahungu batatu. \r\n<br> â€‹Carine&nbsp; yize amashuri abanza&nbsp; kuri EPAK don BOSCO .&nbsp; amashuri \r\nyisumbuye yayize kuri Ecole des Science de Nyamagabe&nbsp; yaje gukomereza \r\nkuri Groupe Notre dame de la Paix Cyanika i Nyamagabe.Nyuma yaje kujya \r\nmuri Kaminuza aho avuga ko yarangirije amashuri muri University of Kigali\r\n UoK.mwishami rya Business and&nbsp; Information&nbsp; Technology.<br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GIJIFXA.jpg\" width=\"330\" height=\"330\"><br>Umusizi Carine<br><br><br><br>Carine\r\n akubwira ko akunda ururimi rwerw\' Ikinyarwanda akaba ariyo mpamvu arirwo \r\nakoramo ubusizi gusa ngo ni cyongereza agikoramo burya. Ngo akaba \r\nyarigeze no kuba uwahize abandi muri kigali itatswe n\'ubusizi.Carine&nbsp; akunda Nyina cyane ngo nubwo nta se afite ariko ngo mubabaho \r\nbose&nbsp; akunda kurusha abandi akubwira ko ari Nyina uza kwisonga.<br><br>carine\r\n umusizikazi ngo iyo atari mubusizi ngo aba ari Kacyiru aho afite \r\nSalon afatanyije na Nyina ndetse ngo nayo imufasha mubusizi,Iyo\r\n umubajije nimba imivugo avuga nibisigo hari icyo bimaze kumugeza ho \r\nakubwira ko iyo agiye mubukwe bamuha amafaranga, Iyo aguhimbiye Igisigo \r\numuha amafaranga ndetse ngo nomubitaramo bamuha amafaranga.<br><br>Carine\r\n ubusanzwe ngo acisha makeya ntakunda kwenderezanya ndetse yanga amatiku\r\n namahane.iyo umubajije niba nta mukunzi agira agusubiza yihuze ati \r\nntawe rwose wumwihariko ndagira.<br><br>Carine twamubajije ku mpano \r\nidasanzwe afite yo gukina filime doreko ariwe Divine muri Seburikoko \r\nFilime yuruhererekane igaragara kuri RTV yatubvwiye ko ari umwuga akora \r\nakunda utamubangamiye ko kandi akunda gukina imikino irimo inyigisho.<br><i><b><br>Carine afite imivugo myinshi aha twavuga nka</b></i> <br><b>Birabe ibyuya<br>ISI ya none&nbsp; <br>Ijwi Ryawe mubyeyi<br>Mbiguhunzwe Urwunge <br>Uwo Nigeze ntamenya <br>Ndagarutse nindi myinshi</b><br><br><br><img src=\"https://ci6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/2o3WwTZ5G-_h92pt9YD_eIH1WwQZXWflx0beviOSCC9pUkQ46mLdYjxnwksinTKd5PQqoA=s0-d-e1-ft#http://i.imgur.com/TY0as9b.jpg\" class=\"CToWUd a6T\" tabindex=\"0\" width=\"302\" height=\"453\"><br>Carine&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br><img class=\"m_-4379244092425858392gmail-irc_mi CToWUd a6T\" src=\"https://ci4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/rWRIkuUfG50tKhdAkwPP2PP_ej67BeofdduvMiGdGB0wuqBKrFbuhZTVlLy2NnfNga_EkO6f2wOOBDKSErMA6tDO3RPav5KePg29-nvrqw-ifAX-zIfRSHMbOAk=s0-d-e1-ft#http://eachamps.rw/images/artists/7f1de29e6da19d22b51c68001e7e0e54.jpg\" alt=\"Image result for teta diana\" style=\"margin-top:0px\" tabindex=\"0\" width=\"368\" height=\"368\"><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; TETA <br><br><br><br>Iyo\r\n witegereje aba bombi Carine Maniraguha na Teta Diana ubona basa kandi \r\nbose bakagira umwihariko mujyana Gakondo ndetse Carine ngo byumwiriko \r\nakunda Teta,Twamubajije nimba we abona Adasa na Teta atubwira ko ngo \r\nabamuzibamubwira ko baba bafitanye ishusho.<br><br>Carine iyo \r\numubajije intumbero afite akubwira ko aharanira kuzaba umuntu ukomeye \r\nndetse ko yifuza ko afatanyije nabandi Basizi yifuza guhindura uko \r\nabantu bafata ubusizi nyarwanda ko bakwiye kubufata nkubuhanzi mubundi \r\nndetse abantu bagashora mo amafaranga afatika.<br><br><br><b><i>DORE IGICE cy\'amagambo meza Carine yandika</i></b><br><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/