(102, '2017-08-24 11:34:42', 'umukirigitananga Deo Munyakazi ari ku isonga mubafite ubudasa mu iserukiramuco ryitwa Pop Kurtur riri kubera mu Mujyi wa Berlin mu gihugu cy\' Budage.', ' Deo Munyakazi, umukirigitananga umaze kugira izina rikomeye yatoranyijwe mu bahanzi icumi bafite umwihariko ku isi batumiwe mu iserukiramuco rikomeye rya Pop kurtur ririkubera mu mujyi wa Berlin', '<div align=\"left\">Munyakazi yatumiwe nkâ€™umuhanzi ufite<br>\r\numwihariko mu Rwanda, akaba<br>\r\nyarahuriye mu Budage nâ€™abandi bahanzi bakomeye<br>\r\nbo mu bihugu icyenda<br>\r\nbitabiriye iserukiramuco rya muzika ryitwa â€˜Pop-<br>\r\nKultur Festivalâ€™rimaze gutangira mu masaha make ashize rikazarangira<br>\r\nkuwa 25 Kanama 2017.<br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AucqQgS.jpg\" width=\"542\" height=\"304\"><br><br>\r\nMUNYAKAZI YARAYE ASHIMISHIJE BENSHI<br><br>\r\nMu kiganiro twagiranye ari i Berlin Munyakazi Deo<br>\r\nyadutangarije ko yishimye<br>\r\ncyane ati \"Narishimye kongera kwamamaza ibyiza<br>\r\nby\'u Rwanda,inanga buriya<br>\r\niba yahagarariye igihugu. Ati kandi ubona abantu<br>\r\nbishimira umwihariko w\'u<br>\r\nRwanda ubudasa bwacu buraturanga,aho twabanje<br>\r\nkuba twahereye kubiganiro<br>\r\ngusa ibyanjye barabikunze,kandi nanjye nahigiye<br>\r\nbyinshi gusa igitangaje<br>\r\nn\'ukuntu abantu bakunda Inanga batazi niyo biva<br>\r\nariko abanyarwanda bo<br>\r\nugasanga batara byumva neza\'\'.<br><br>\r\nMunyakazi yashoje atubwira ko yishimiye uyu<br>\r\nmujyi by\'umwihariko kandi ko<br>\r\nyiteguye kuzamura Ibendera ry\'igihugu.<br><br>\r\nNkuko Bigaragara Munyakazi Deo uhagarariye<br>\r\nigihugu cy\' u Rwanda yaraye <br>\r\nAgaragaye akirigita inanga&nbsp; <br>\r\naho bita Kulturbrauerrei ashimisha benshi&nbsp; agaragaza ubudasa .<br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fTD2DE6.jpg\" width=\"510\" height=\"743\"><br>\r\nMUNYAKAZI ARI I BERLIN<br><br>\r\nNdakwibutsa ko Munyakazi mu ntangiriro zâ€™uyu<br>\r\nmwaka yatumiwe mu<br>\r\niserukiramuco rya Doa Doa muri Uganda ndetse ari<br>\r\nmu batumiwe muri Kenya mu<br>\r\nihuriro â€˜ONGEA, East African Music Summit ryahuje<br>\r\nabahanzi bafite<br>\r\numwihariko muri Afurika yâ€™Uburasirazuba.<br><br>\r\nIkindi Munyakazi mu ntangiriro z\'uyu mwaka yari mu batumiye mu gihugu<br>\r\ncy\'ubufaransa aho yitabiriye ikitwa \"Les printemps de poetes\"<br>\r\nafatanyije na Kifran itsinda rikora ubusizi rigizwe na Eric Onekey<br>\r\nndetse n\'Umusizi Tuyisenge bafatanyije n\'umucaranzi w\'umufaransa<br>\r\nPierre Jean Fasan.<br></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1503567282munya.jpg', 0, 'admin', 2, 3, 'break', 218),
(103, '2017-08-25 11:58:16', 'Ese Umuco urakura? MENYA BYINSHI Umuco wâ€™u Rwanda wakiriye imico ituruka hanze ugira ibyo wunguka nâ€™ibindi utakaza.', ' Dore bimwe mubyiyongereye mu muco w\'u Rwanda bitahozeho, kubera impamvu zitandukanye zishingiye ku mateka yâ€™Igihugu, imibereho, imibanire nâ€™imyitwarire byâ€™abanyarwanda byarahindutse.', '<div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nUmuco wâ€™u Rwanda wakiriye imico ituruka hanze<br>\r\nugira ibyo wunguka nâ€™ibindi<br>\r\nutakaza muri ibyo byose harimo imiturire, imibanire yâ€™abagize umuryango<br>\r\nnâ€™iyâ€™abaturanyi,<br>\r\nimyambarire nâ€™ibindi.<br><br>\r\nDore zimwe mu<br>\r\nndangagaciro nshya:<br><br>\r\na) Imyemerere ishingiye ku madini yavuye hanze.<br><br>\r\nAmadini yavuye hanze yarushije ingufu iryo<br>\r\nabanyarwanda bari basanganywe maze bayoboka<br>\r\namadini atandukanye. Ayo<br>\r\nmadini yazanye indangagaciro zihindura zimwe<br>\r\nmu zo abanyarwanda<br>\r\nbemeraga. Haza uburyo bushya nko mu kubatizwa,<br>\r\ngushyingirwa, guherekeza<br>\r\nuwitabye Imana nâ€™ibindi.<br><br>\r\n&nbsp;b) Amatwara ya<br>\r\ndemokarasi.<br><br>\r\nAmatwara ya<br>\r\ndemokarasi Demokarasi nâ€™andi mahame<br>\r\nayishingiyeho byahinduye amatwara<br>\r\nyâ€™imiyoborere yâ€™u Rwanda.<br><br>\r\nc ) Uburinganire nâ€™ubwuzuzanye.<br><br>\r\nMuri ibi bihe<br>\r\nguteza imbere umuryango nâ€™igihugu bisaba<br>\r\nuruhare rwâ€™abagore nâ€™abagabo,<br>\r\nabakobwa nâ€™abahungu.<br>\r\nKu bwâ€™ibyo, guha agaciro kangana abagore<br>\r\nnâ€™abagabo, abakobwa nâ€™abahungu<br>\r\nbijyana no kubahiriza ihame ryâ€™uburinganire<br>\r\nnâ€™ubwuzuzanye bigashimangirwa no<br>\r\nkutarobanura abana mu turere no mu burezi,kutarobanura abagore<br>\r\nnâ€™abagabo, abakobwa nâ€™abahungu mu mirimo,mu kutabasumbanya mu<br>\r\nizungura no mu micungire yâ€™umutungo<br>\r\nw\'umuryango,mu kubaha uruhare<br>\r\nrungana mu miyoborere yâ€™Igihugu, mu kubarinda<br>\r\nihohoterwa iryo ari ryo<br>\r\nryose ndetse no mu bundi buryo bwinshi bushimangira uburinganire<br>\r\nn\'ubwuzuzanye mu Rwanda.<br><br>\r\nd) Ubumenyi bushya.<br><br>\r\nIshuri ryasimbuye itorero, rizana<br>\r\nubumenyi bushya nâ€™indangagaciro zabwo nuko uruhare rwâ€™ababyeyi mu<br>\r\nburere bwâ€™abana babo ruragabanuka maze mwarimu agira<br>\r\nuruhare runini mu burere<br>\r\nbwâ€™umwana. Bityo ubumenyi bushya buhabwa<br>\r\numwanya kuruta uburere<br>\r\nbwâ€™ababyeyi. Ishuri rero ni aho umuntu ajya<br>\r\nkwiyungurira ubumenyi bigatuma<br>\r\nanoza imikorere nâ€™imibereho ye. Kwiga kandi<br>\r\nntibijya birangira, ntibirangirira ku ntebe yâ€™ishuri gusa, umwana nawe<br>\r\nubwe ashobora kwiyigisha no<br>\r\nkwigira ku bandi ahura nabo.<br>E)Ikoranabuhanga<br><br>\r\nIkoranabuhanga ryahinduye isi umudugudu umwe, ryigisha itumanaho<br>\r\nryihuta kandi rigera kuri<br>\r\nbenshi. Ibyiza byaryo<br>\r\nbigera no mu Rwanda ariko bidasize nâ€™ibibi byaryo<br>\r\nbigomba kwirindwa.<br><br>\r\nf) Indimi zâ€™amahanga<br><br>\r\nAbanyarwanda bakiranye umwete<br>\r\nindimi zâ€™amahanga bituma Igihugu cyacu cyagura<br>\r\namarembo kiragendwa.<br>\r\nAbanyarwanda nabo bagenda amahanga. Ni byiza,<br>\r\nariko tukirinda ko indimi<br>\r\nzâ€™amahanga zimira ururimi kavukire.<br><br>\r\ng) Gukoresha ifaranga.<br><br><br>\r\nGukoresha ifaranga byazanye<br>\r\nuburyo bushya bwo guhahirana, kugura ibintu no<br>\r\nkugirana amasezerano.<br>\r\nIfaranga rero ryinjiye mu buzima<br>\r\nbwâ€™Abanyarwanda. Ni byiza kumenya<br>\r\nkuyakorera ariko ntube imbata yayo.<br><br>\r\nIzi zikaba zimwe mu ndangagaciro ziyongereye<br>\r\nmu muco w\'u Rwanda, bityo rero<br>\r\nibyiza tubyakire ariko Ibibi twoye kubyimika ino hato bidazasenya uyu<br>\r\nmuco karande w\'abanyarwanda.<br><br>\r\nYanditswe na @ NDIZEYE Lionel<br></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1503655096RWANDA NZIZA.png', 0, 'admin', 7, 13, 'head', 85),
(108, '2017-08-25 13:42:55', 'Umuganura 2017 ntusanzwe. Udushya,imitegurire byarahindutse. Reba hano amafoto y\'umutambagiro,imurikabikorwa.', 'Tariki 20 Kanama nibwo icyumweru cy\'umuganura cyatangiye ndetse byagaragaye ko harimo udushya twinshi, abateguye iki gikorwa aribo inteko nyarwanda y\'ururimi n\'umuco(RALC) ifatanyije na minisiteri y\'umuco na siporo(MINISPOC) bagaragaje imbaraga n\'ubudasa mu mitegurire.', '<div align=\"left\">Tugarutse mu mateka yâ€™u Rwanda, umunsi wâ€™umuganura wari<br>\r\numunsi mukuru ukomeye haba<br>\r\ni bwami ndetse no muri rubanda, kuri uwo munsi umwami<br>\r\nyamurikirwaga umusaruro<br>\r\nwâ€™Abanyarwanda bavuye impande zose zâ€™iguhugu<br>\r\n,agasangira nâ€™abaturage ndetse<br>\r\nakishimana nabo.<br><br>\r\nUyu muhango wari ufite akamaro ko gusangira no<br>\r\nkwishimira umusaruro<br>\r\nwabonetse, byakorwaga mu gitaramo cyiswe<br>\r\nicyâ€™umuganura.&nbsp; Uyu muganura ariko<br>\r\nwagiraga nâ€™undi mumaro wo kuzirikana umwami<br>\r\nnka nyirâ€™uburumbuke bakamutura<br>\r\nurutete rwâ€™imyaka yeze.<br><br>\r\nUyu muhango wakomeje gukorwa no mu yindi<br>\r\nmyaka yakurikiye ubutegetsi<br>\r\nbwâ€™umwaduko wâ€™abazungu, gusa ukaba waragiye<br>\r\nuhindurirwa inyito nâ€™uburyo bwo<br>\r\nkuwizihiza. Umuganura wa none usigaye ukorwa mu rwego rwo<br>\r\nkwishimira umusaruro,abanyarwanda<br>\r\nbagahura bagasangira ibyo kurya, bakanywa, bagahigura imihigo.<br><br>\r\nUmuganura w\'uyu mwaka wabanjirijwe<br>\r\nn\'umutambagiro ndetse n\'igikorwa k\'murikabikorwa kiri kubera igikondo<br>\r\naho cyatangiye kuwa<br>\r\n23 Kanama kikazarangira kuwa 6 Nzeri. Muri iryo murika bikorwa iyo<br>\r\nurebye aho bakorera ubona ubudasa isuku ndetse<br>\r\nna gahunda ifatika yo<br>\r\nkugirango abanyarwanda barushe ho gukunda no<br>\r\ngusobanukirwa umuco.<br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WBqeCXd.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VygJyj2.jpg\" width=\"504\" height=\"336\"><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TlDCv0d.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cOEmhc2.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mY7zPOj.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uoqmRLC.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UaQSBl2.jpg\" width=\"540\" height=\"315\"><br><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" align=\"left\">Nyuma hakurikiyeho imurikabikorwa ryaranzwe n\'abahanzi b\'u Rwanda<br>\r\nbiteguye kubagezaho<br>\r\nibyiza byose bikubiye mu muco w\'u<br>\r\nRwanda binyuze muri firime, muzika, imideri,<br>\r\nikinamico, ubugeni n\'ibindi<br>\r\nbyinshi.<br>\r\nREBA AMAFOTO Y\'IMURIKA BIKORWA RIRAKOMEJE.</p><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HvVj1J4.jpg\" width=\"691\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nIGIKONDO AHO IMURIKA BIKORWA RIRI KUBERA<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MO3PXJU.jpg\" width=\"691\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nUHAGEZE UBONA HATATSE NEZA<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mGjlRMt.jpg\" width=\"691\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0VYkFJS.jpg\" width=\"691\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mukpW5F.jpg\" width=\"692\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/E2sHXzn.jpg\" width=\"691\"><br></span></p><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" align=\"left\">AMASAHA YOSE BABA BARI MUKAZI</p><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" align=\"left\">Turakwibutsa ko igikorwa nyirizina cy\'umuganuro<br>\r\nkizaba tariki ya 27 kanama<br>\r\nguhera saa mbiri za mugitondo kuri stade<br>\r\ny\'akarere ka Nyanza bikaza<br>\r\nbikurikiye igitaramo ndangamuco kiswe Nyanza twataramye giteganyijwe kuwa 26<br>\r\nKanama ku gicamunsi.<br>\r\nBurya umuco dusangiye uraturanga nawe sura<br>\r\nRALC muri EXPO umenye byinshi<br>\r\nk\'umuco ishingiro ry\'abanyarwanda.<br>\r\n</p><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nYanditswe na IRADUKUNDA MOSEs</div></div>', '1503661375Dr.jpg', 0, 'admin', 7, 13, 'head', 185);
