(109, '2017-08-28 09:57:06', 'REBA amafoto Adasanzwe yaranze umunsi w\'Umuganura 2017', '  Abaturage babarirwa mu bihumbi bahuriye mu birori byo kwizihiza umunsi wâ€™Umuganura byaranzwe nâ€™ibyishimo bisangiwe hagati yabo nâ€™ababayobora', '<div align=\"left\"><div><br>Ibi birori byâ€™Umuganura byizihizwaga mu Rwanda rwo hambere bigahuza \r\nabishimira umusaruro nâ€™ibyejejwe, kuri iyi nshuro byabereye mu Karere ka\r\n Nyanza.<br><p>Mu ijambo rye, Minisitiri wâ€™Umuco na Siporo, Uwacu Julienne, yavuze \r\nko kwizihiza Umuganura ku rwego rwâ€™umuryango, ari umwanya wo \r\ngushimangira ubumwe bwâ€™abawugize no gusabana ariko byâ€™akarusho uwâ€™uyu \r\nmwaka ukaba ubaye mu gihe Abanyarwanda bakishimira intsinzi ya Perezida \r\nwa Repubulika, Paul Kagame.</p>\r\n<p>Yagize ati \"Umuganura ni umunsi ukomeye ku Banyarwanda kubera agaciro\r\n kawo, ni umwanya wo kwishimira ibyo tumaze kugeraho mu iterambere \r\nryâ€™igihugu cyacu. Ni umwanya wo kwisuzuma tukareba ibitaragenze neza no \r\nguhigira imyaka ije, ni nâ€™umwanya wo gusabana kwâ€™abayobozi nâ€™abayoborwa.\r\n Muri iki gihe, tuganura twishimira umusaruro tugezeho mu nzego zose \r\nzâ€™ubuzima bwâ€™igihugu.\"</p><br><br><br><br><div><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/umuganura_11-aee7c.jpg?1503865178\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"282\" height=\"188\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n</div><br><br><br><br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nYongeyeho ati â€œUmuganura ugomba kongera kutwibutsa ko umuryango ari \r\nwo shingiro ryâ€™imbaraga zâ€™Abanyarwanda, uje mu gihe tukishimira ibyo</div><div align=\"left\">u \r\nRwanda rumaze kugeraho nyuma yâ€™imyaka 23. Ni uwa mbere twizihije muri \r\nmanda nshya yâ€™imyaka irindwi ya Perezida wa Repubulika, Paul Kagame. \r\nUbaye mu gihe tukizihiza intsinzi Abanyarwanda twagaragarije mu matora \r\naherutse.â€\r\n</div><p align=\"left\">Yasoje avuga ko ashimangira agaciro Umuco Nyarwanda ufitiye \r\nabanyagihugu nkâ€™uko ku munsi wari wabanje bongeye kwiyibutsa \r\nubukungahare bwawo mu gitaramo â€˜I Nyanza Twataramyeâ€™ cyaranzwe \r\nnâ€™ibyishimo byâ€™ikirenga ku bacyitabiriye bakabikomereza mu kwizihiza \r\nUmuganura.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Nyuma yâ€™Ijambo rya Minisitiri Uwacu hakurikiyeho umuhango wo kumurika\r\n Inyambo no kwinikiza ndetse nâ€™uwo guha abana amata. Abitabiriye iki \r\ngikorwa bakoze ubusabane basangira ibigori nâ€™indi myaka yejejwe mu \r\nKarere ka Nyanza kakiriye uyu muhango.</p><p align=\"left\"><br></p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36008438684_8b245d0ce8_k-955d7.jpg?1503856316\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"317\" height=\"212\" border=\"0\"><br>Minisitiri wâ€™Uburinganire nâ€™Iterambere ryâ€™Umuryango, EspÃ©rance Nyirasafari aha abana amata mu muhango w\'Umuganura<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1000px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\" align=\"left\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br></div><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH768/36033676953_f98d217e94_k-3e172.jpg?1503856316\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"281\" height=\"215\" border=\"0\"><br>Minisitiri wa Siporo nâ€™Umuco, Uwacu Julienne aha abana amata<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1000px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\" align=\"left\">\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Umuhango wo kwizihiza Umuganura wanabereyemo igikorwa cyo kuremera \r\nabatishoboye aho abaturage bagera kuri 400 bahawe ubwisungane mu kwivuza\r\n ndetse hakanatangwa inka 12. Bamwe mu baturage biteje imbere batanze \r\nubuhamya bwâ€™uko babigezeho mu gufatanya ndetse bagateza imbere na \r\nbagenzi babo mu gutanga imirimo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Ibi birori byasusurukijwe nâ€™Itorero Urukerereza ryasusurukije imbaga \r\nmu mbyino zishimangira ubumwe, ubusabane ndetse zishimangira \r\nindangagaciro zâ€™Umuco Nyarwanda. Byanaririmbwemo nâ€™Indatabigwi, \r\nabanyeshuri bize umuziki ku Nyundo nâ€™abahanzi batandukanye bakomeye \r\nbarimo Riderman, Charly &amp; Nina, Rafiki, Ama G The Black nâ€™abandi.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Umunsi wâ€™Umuganura kandi wanizihirijwe mu bice bitandukanye byâ€™igihugu ku rwego rwâ€™umudugudu.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>Ibyo wamenya ku birori byâ€™Umuganura byizihizwa buri mwaka</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu mateka yâ€™u Rwanda, Umuganura wari umunsi mukuru ngarukamwaka \r\nwubahwaga kandi ugahabwa agaciro mu muryango wâ€™Abanyarwanda. Watangiye \r\nkwizihizwa ahagana mu kinyejana cya cyenda, uza kongera guhabwa imbaraga\r\n nâ€™Umwami Ruganzu II Ndoli (1510-1543) ubwo yabohoraga u Rwanda nyuma \r\nyâ€™imyaka irenga 10 ruri mu maboko yâ€™abanyamahanga (Abanyabungo).</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Umuganura wizihizwaga mu buryo bubiri, ku rwego rwâ€™Igihugu \r\nwayoborwaga nâ€™Umwami afashijwe nâ€™abanyamihango bawo. Imihango yâ€™ibwami \r\nyari iyo guhuza Imana nâ€™Igihugu, bagahuza ibikorwa byâ€™idini nâ€™imigenzo \r\ngakondo hamwe nâ€™imirimo yâ€™ubuhinzi nâ€™ubworozi. Ku rwego rwâ€™umuryango, \r\nwayoborwaga nâ€™umukuru wawo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Mu miryango abana basabanaga nâ€™ababyeyi, hakabaho kwishimira \r\nibyagezweho cyane cyane mu musaruro. Mu wa 1925, kwizihiza Umuganura \r\nbyaciwe nâ€™abakoloni, umwiru mukuru mu bawuyoboraga, Gashamura ka \r\nRukangirashyamba aciribwa mu Burundi. Nyuma yâ€™uko u Rwanda rubonye \r\nubwigenge, abantu bakomeje kwizihiza Umuganura mu miryango yabo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Kwizihiza Umuganura muri iki gihe byarenze imbibi zo kwita ku \r\nmusaruro wâ€™ubuhinzi nâ€™ubworozi gusa, bigera no mu zindi nzego zireba \r\nubuzima nâ€™iterambere byâ€™Abanyarwanda hagamijwe kugaragaza urugendo \r\nAbanyarwanda barimo baharanira kwigira no kwibohora nyako bifashisha \r\numuco wabo.</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Umuganura wâ€™ubu wizihizwa hishimirwa umusaruro wagezweho mu nzego \r\nzitandukanye zirimo ubuzima, uburezi, ikoranabuhanga, imikino \r\nnâ€™imyidagaduro, ubucuruzi, ubucukuzi bwâ€™amabuye yâ€™agaciro, \r\nibikorwaremezo, inganda ndangamuco, ubukerarugendo nâ€™ibindi. Usibye \r\nkwishimira ibyagezweho hanafatwa ingamba zo kugera ku mihigo itandukanye\r\n iba yaratekerejwe muri buri rwego.</p>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36033695293_fb598592be_k-1f42a.jpg?1503856316\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"308\" height=\"228\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br></div><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/abejeje_urutoki_n_indi_myaka_bagaragarije_abayobozi_ibyo_bagezeho-eaf9d.jpg?1503856316\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"325\" height=\"217\" border=\"0\"><br>Abejeje urutoki bagaragarije ubuyobozi ibyo bagezeho<div style=\"position: relative; width: 1000px; padding: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-right: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; border-radius: 10px;\" align=\"left\">\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br></div><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/36033657493_a00e9f062d_k-d531c.jpg?1503856316\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"374\" height=\"249\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br></div><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/umuganura_10-9f595.jpg?1503865178\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"384\" height=\"256\" border=\"0\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<div align=\"left\"><br></div><img src=\"http://igihe.com/local/cache-vignettes/L1000xH667/umuganura_23-63a5e.jpg?1503865178\" class=\"artimgv5 img-responsive\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" width=\"339\" height=\"226\" border=