(114, '2017-08-30 14:30:59', 'BYINSHI Kuri Kigali International Fashion Week Europe', 'Iki gitaramo kikazaba ku matariki ya 24 na 25 Ugushyingo uyu mwaka kikabera mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'ububiligi  brussels', '<div align=\"left\">Kigali International Fashion Week Europe ni igitaramo gihuza abahanzi<br>\r\nb\'abanyarwanda bahimba imyambaro ndetse n\'abamurika imyambaro. Iki<br>\r\ngitaramo kikaba gitegurwa mu rwego rwo guha urubuga abanyempano<br>\r\nbose kugirango bakomeze kumenyekanisha<br>\r\nigihugu binyuze mu buhanzi n\'ubugeni nkuko tubikesha Dady de Maximo<br>\r\nMwicira-Mitali umuhuzabikorwa ushinzwe ubuhanzi ubugeni<br>\r\nn\'imyidagaduro muri Kigali International Fashion Week Europe.<br><br>\r\n&nbsp;Iki gitaramo kikazaba ku matariki ya 24 na 25 Ugushyingo uyu mwaka<br>\r\nkikabera mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'ububiligi&nbsp; brussels. Kigali<br>\r\nInternational Fashion Week Europe uyu mwaka izitabirwa n\'abahanzi<br>\r\nbahimba imyambaro ndetse n\'abayimurika bose hamwe cumi n\'umwe kongera<br>\r\nn\'abanyamuziki bazasusurutsa abazitabira icyo gitaramo.<br><br>\r\nAbahanzi bahimba imyambaro ndetse n\'abayerekana bazitabira Kigali<br>\r\nInternational Fashion Week Europe ni<br>\r\n1. Murorunkwere Sandrine<br><img class=\"spotlight\" alt=\"Image may contain: 1 person, smiling, shoes\" src=\"https://fb-s-c-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-fbx/v/t1.0-9/21192105_10155043007177956_8358568347739154644_n.jpg?oh=0b150530d337b6e54823b2bdb2b1592e&amp;oe=5A280F6F&amp;__gda__=1511155121_538ffdd45195c351de5991c89d0030b5\" width=\"371\" height=\"371\"><br>\r\n2.Uwamahoro Delphine<br><img class=\"spotlight\" alt=\"Image may contain: 1 person, smiling, standing\" src=\"https://fb-s-d-a.akamaihd.net/h-ak-fbx/v/t1.0-9/21106580_10155043007412956_8007311422572265734_n.jpg?oh=52f273946ee324161afb712566f94efe&amp;oe=5A22A64D&amp;__gda__=1512061075_f8135809a554d9a585b9d1fb578ca502\" width=\"346\" height=\"346\"><br><br>\r\n3. Muhire Patrick<br><img class=\"spotlight\" alt=\"Image ma