\nNdabibutsa ko iki gitaramo ari kimwe muri bike muri diaspora byereka<br>\r\nisi muri rusange urwego ubuhanzi bw\'imyambaro no kuyerekana bigezeho<br>\r\nku ruhande rw\'abanyarwanda babikora<br><b><br>YANDITSWE </b>NA Umusizi TUYISENGE Olivier<br></div>', '1504096259dady.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'sub', 108),
(116, '2017-09-05 13:48:32', 'Amatorero ndangamuco yaza Kaminuza zitandukanye hano mu Rwanda agiye guhurira mu marushanwa yiswe \"Inkera y\'Inyamibwa\".', 'Igitaramo inkera y\'inyamibwa ni amarushanwa azahuriza hamwe amatorero ndangamuco ya za kaminuza 4 hano mu Rwanda,iki gitaramo kikazaba ku wa gatanu tariki ya 8 Nzeri 2017 muri Kigali Serena Hotel.', '<div align=\"left\">Inkera y\'inyamibwa ni amarushanwa ari gutegurwa na Rwanda Culture<br>\r\nPromoters Initiative umuryango w\'abanyeshuri b\'abanyarwanda bari muri<br>\r\nza Kaminuza&nbsp; zitandukanye hano mu Rwanda ndetse no mu bindi bihugu 14<br>\r\nbitandukanye byo ku isi bagamije guteza imbere umuco nyarwanda.<br><br>\r\n&nbsp;Mu kiganiro kirambuye ikinyamakuru Umucowacu.com cyagiranye na Bwana<br>\r\nMutarasisi Uwayo christian uhagarariye Rwanda Culture Promoters<br>\r\nInitiative yatangiye atubwira byinshi kuri iyi nkera y\'inyamibwa no ku<br>\r\nmuryango yashinze muri rusange agira ati &lt;&lt;<br>\r\nRwanda Culture Promoters Initiate twiyemeje guteza imbere umuco<br>\r\nnyarwanda cyane cyane mu rubyiruko kuko ugenda ucika, hanyuma aya<br>\r\nmarushanwa turi gutegura y\'inkera y\'inyamibwa afite udushya<br>\r\ntwinshi,ikindi kandi icyiza nuko ku munyeshuri ufite ikarita y\'ishuri<br>\r\nkwinjira ari ubuntu.&gt;&gt;<br><br>\r\nMudarasisi yakomeje atangariza ikinyamakuru umuco wacu ko inkera<br>\r\ny\'inyamibwa izitabirwa n\'amatorero ndangamuco ane ahagarariye za<br>\r\nkaminuza enye, ayo matorero ni Itorero rya kaminuza y\'u Rwanda(UR),<br>\r\nItorero rya kaminuza ya Mount Kenya,Itorero rya kaminuza ya UTB(yahoze<br>\r\nari RTUC) ndetse n\'itorero rya kaminuza ya IPRC Kigali.<br><br>\r\nMu gitaramo inkera y\'inyamibwa uretse kandi aya matorero azarushanwa<br>\r\n,hazanagaragaramo ibikorwa bindi byerekana umuco, nk\'imyiyereko<br>\r\ny\'abahanzi berekana bakanahimba imyambaro ishingiye ku muco nyarwanda.<br>\r\nIki gitaramo kandi kizasusurutswa na Wimas Band mu rwego rwo<br>\r\nkwibutsa abazakitabira uburyohe mw\'umuziki nyarwanda wo hambere.<br><br>\r\nMu gitaramo inkera y\'inyamibwa hazanamurikwa urubuga<br>\r\nnkoranyambaga(websites) ruzajya ruhuza abanyarwanda bose bakunda umuco<br>\r\nwabo baba abimbere mu gihugu cyangwa hanze yacyo(Diaspora) mu rwego<br>\r\nrwo kungurana ibitekerezo ku iterambere ry\'umuco nyarwanda.</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K98cXDA.jpg\" width=\"615\" height=\"436\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nNdabibutsa ko inkera y\'inyamibwa izaba kuri uyu wa gatanu tariki ya 8<br>\r\nNzeri 2017 guhera i saa kumi n\'imwe z\'umugoroba muri Kigali Serena<br>\r\nHotel kwinjira ni 2000Rwf ahasanzwe ndetse na 5000Rwf mu cyubahiro ku munyeshuri ufite ikarita y\'ishuri<br>\r\nkwinjira ni ubuntu.<br>\r\nGucikwa ni ukunyagwa zigahera.<br><br><br>\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier<br></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1504612112INYAMIMBWA.jpg', 0, 'admin', 4, 3, 'break', 287),
(118, '2017-09-09 12:37:43', 'Inkera y\'inyamibwa Itorero Indahigwa rya IPRC ya Kigali ryahize andi matorero ya za kaminuza >AMAFOTO', 'Inkera y\'inyamibwa ni igitaramo cyabaye mu ijoro ryo kuri uyu wa gatanu tariki ya 8 NZERI muri Kigali Serena Hotel kikaba cyahuje amatorero ndangamuco ya za kaminuza.', '<div align=\"left\">\r\nInkera y\'inyamibwa ni igitaramo kiba gikubiyemo amarushanwa ahuza<br>\r\namatorero yaza kaminuza, iki gitaramo kikaba gitegurwa n\'umuryango<br>\r\nwitwa Rwanda Culture Promoters Initiative umuryango w\'abanyeshuri<br>\r\nb\'abanyarwanda bari muri za Kaminuza zitandukanye baharanira guteza imbere umuco.</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bqr9KnB.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nIki gitaramo cyatangiye ahagana mu ma saa moya z\'umugoroba maze<br>\r\nkwikubitiro Winners Band aba ariyo isusurutsa abitabiriye iyi nkera<br>\r\ny\'inyamibwa, hanyuma ikurikirwa na Bageni Hyacinthe umuhanzi gakondo<br>\r\nucuranga iningiri,bidatinze abashyushyarugamba b\'iyi nkera aribo<br>\r\nUmusizi Munezero Ferdinand na UWIMANA Honorine batangije amarushanwa ku<br>\r\nmugaragaro maze itorero indahigwa rya IPRC ya Kigali ribanza ku<br>\r\nrubyiniro rirabyina karahava,abahungu bagwa mu nka,bashiki babo<br>\r\nbarashayaya bishyira kera.&nbsp;</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jGWtlZo.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br>\r\nIndahigwa zaje gukurikirwa n\'itorero rya kaminuza ya <br></div><div align=\"left\">African leadership University. maze nabo <br></div><div align=\"left\">barabyina karahava ibirori biba ibirori koko.</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qWbzjd5.jpg\" width=\"362\" height=\"241\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br><br>\r\nHanyuma&nbsp; abagize itorero rya Kaminuza y\'u Rwanda ishami rya Rukara<br>\r\nbaje ku rubyiniro nabo bunga mu rya bagenzi babo, barabyina bajya mu<br>\r\nkinimba,mu mishyayayo... maze inama nkemurampaka yari ikuriwe na<br>\r\nMariya Yohana akazi kayibana akazi</div><br><br><br><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a0fQVBL.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/x1quAnr.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\">ABAGIZE INAMA NKEMURAMPAKA<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br><br><br>\r\nNyuma yuko amatorero uko ari atatu amaze kurushanwa inkera yakomeje<br>\r\nmaze bahamagara ku rubyiniro kabuhariwe Munyakazi Deo inanga<br>\r\narayikirigita karahava. <br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1N9bOPw.jpg\" width=\"543\"></div><div align=\"left\">MUNYAKAZI DEO<br><br>\r\nNyuma inama nkemurampaka yaje gutangaza ko indahigwa za IPRC ya Kigali<br>\r\narizo zihize andi matorero maze umudiho n\'ikobe by\'indahigwa biba<br>\r\nbyose bishimira intsinzi.<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dD951Zp.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\">BATANGAZA UWATSINZE<br><br>\r\nNyuma inkera y\'inyamibwa yaje gusozwa n\'Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier mu<br>\r\nbisigo n\'imivugo biherejejwe n\'umurya w\'inanga wa Munyakazi Deo ndetse<br>\r\nn\'iningiri ya Bageni Hyacinte</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2GmAVg7.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\">UMUSIZI TUYISENGE<br>\r\nNdabibutsa ko mu nkera y\'inyamibwa ari naho hamurikiwe urubuga rwa<br>\r\ninternet <a href=\"http://wwww.rcpi.rw\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://wwww.rcpi.rw&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1505031444201000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFEa7uoyT4UjIraqQaRy-wnRDROdA\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">wwww.rcpi.rw</a> ruzajya rufasha guhuza abanyeshuri ndetse<br>\r\nnabandi bantu bashaka guteza imbere umuco nyarwanda nk\'intego yarwo<br>\r\nnkuko twabitangarijwe na Mutarasisi Uwayo Christian umuyobozi wa<br>\r\nRwanda Culture Promoters Initiative.</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ynuwC8.jpg\" width=\"360\"></div><div align=\"left\">CHRISTIAN MUTARASISI UWAYO UMUYOBOZI WA RCPI<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\">ANDI MAFOTO:</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RbVEnDt.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tEAscTV.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\">aba M.C MUNEZERO na UWIMANA <br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WpD5KZe.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FWatzKi.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><br><br><br><br><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GtdSDze.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><div align=\"left\"><br></div>AMAFOTO: IRADUKUNDA MOSEs</div>', '1504953463PhotoGrid_1504945604233.jpg', 0, 'admin', 3, 11, 'head', 366);
