(119, '2017-09-16 08:43:46', 'Amateka ya Ryangombe rya Babinga ba Nyundo.', 'Ryangombe ni mwene Nyiraryangombe umusumbakazi Na Babinga ba Nyundo, ni yo mpamvu bamwise Ryangombe rya Babinga ba Nyundo.\r\n', '<div align=\"left\">Yavutse ari ikinege. Abahungu bamukomokaho<br>\r\nni Binego, Ruhanga, Nyabirungu, Mashira na<br>\r\nKagoro. Bene se wabo bazwi ni Nyabirungu wari<br>\r\numuhigi na Mpumutumucuni, ari na we<br>\r\nbakundaga kubuguza. Igisingizo cye ni:<br>\r\nRyangombe, bibero birinda ibiramba,<br>\r\nNyamunyaga iziburiwe, izitaburiwe akazazinyaga<br>\r\ninkingi nâ€™imyugariro yitwa Nkingiyinka, mu<br>\r\nnkingi yâ€™abagabo yitwa Nkungiyabagabo.<br><br>\r\nYari umuntu wâ€™intwari cyane, akaba nâ€™umuhigi<br>\r\nwâ€™umukogoto yifashishije imbwa ze na zo zitari<br>\r\nnke, zirimo Bakoshabadahannye, Nyakayonga,<br>\r\nBabikana umuranzi uruguma,<br>\r\nBabikamurwinanuriro, Ikinyabutongo gitoto<br>\r\nkimara isimbo, Nyinaramuzi ntazamumpora,<br>\r\nBakosha cyane bazakarushya irimura,<br>\r\nUruyongoyongo rwa Miramba, Buhuru bunuka<br>\r\nuruhumbu, na Maguru ya Sarwaya yasize imvura<br>\r\nnâ€™umuyaga, Bisimbo birabomborana,<br>\r\nMwangamwabo na Bikwirashyamba.<br>\r\nRyangombe azwi nkâ€™imana yâ€™i Rwanda, ndetse<br>\r\nni we wabaye inkomoko yo guterekera kuko<br>\r\nmbere yo gupfa kwe bitabagaho.<br><br>\r\n&nbsp;Ryangombe ni<br>\r\nimandwa imwe mu zizwi neza mu Rwanda rwo<br>\r\nhambere, ari zo Ryangombe, Binego, Mugasa,<br>\r\nKagoro, Ruhanga, Nkonjo, Mashira, Umuzana, na<br>\r\nNyabirungu. Izindi zongerwaho ni Umurengetwe,<br>\r\nUmunyoro, Ruhende, nâ€™Intare.<br>\r\nSe wa Ryangombe ajya gupfa, yasize amuraze<br>\r\nubwami, ariko asiga atamwimitse. Bene se wabo<br>\r\nrero baje kubimwangirira, uwitwa<br>\r\nMpumutumucuni ati: â€œNtakwiriye kwima! Se<br>\r\nyamubeshye ingoma.â€ Muri urwo rwangano<br>\r\nrwabo, Mpumutumucuni abwira Ryangombe ati:<br>\r\nâ€œUzaze tubuguze.â€<br><br>\r\nNaho Ryangombe bakaba<br>\r\nbaramuraguriye kuzajya kuraguza kwa<br>\r\nNyamuzinda i Butumbi. Ryangombe ajyayo,<br>\r\nNyamuzinda aramubwira ati: â€œNta ndagu yawe<br>\r\nmfite, ifite agakecuru gapfuye ijisho gataha mu<br>\r\nrutare.â€<br>\r\nRyangombe agenda ahiga nâ€™imbwa ze, ni bwo<br>\r\nasanze agakecuru kariho kota izuba imbere<br>\r\nyâ€™urutare. Kamwikanze, Ryangombe ati:<br>\r\nâ€œHumura!â€ Agakecuru kati: â€œUragahumurizwa<br>\r\nnawe, uragahumurizwa nâ€™Imana yâ€™i Rwanda.â€<br><br>\r\nAgakecuru ni ko kumubwira kati: â€œHogi genda,<br>\r\nuzane imbwa yawe yitwa Bakoshabadahannye,<br>\r\nuhamagaze Nyakayonga, uhamagaze<br>\r\nBabikamurwinanuriro, uhamagaze<br>\r\nNtakitambarinkanda, uhamagaze Nyinaramuzi<br>\r\nntazamumpora, uhamagaze Bakosha cyane<br>\r\nbakazarushya irimura, uhamagaze<br>\r\nBatekibikokoye, maze uzizane.â€ Numara<br>\r\nkuzizana, ugende uhiga. Uzabona inyamaswa<br>\r\nyâ€™ibara, numara kuyica, uzayibambe ku mugina<br>\r\nuyibamburure ku mugendo.<br><br>\r\nIyo nyamaswa izaba<br>\r\nari imondo.<br>\r\nKa gakecuru kari karabwiye Ryangombe kati:<br>\r\nâ€œUzasanga abakobwa umunani bazaba baca<br>\r\nubwatsi kwâ€™iriba, uwa cyenda azaba ashoye inka<br>\r\nyâ€™igitare yonsa rutare. Azabwira abandi bakobwa<br>\r\nati: â€œMbega uruhu rwiza! Nimurore kariya gahu<br>\r\nbakobwa, uwakampa! Wa mugabo we,<br>\r\nwanyihereye ako gahu.â€<br>\r\nAgakecuru kati: â€œUmunsi yaje kukuzimanira<br>\r\nuzamurongore.â€ Umwana uzabyara kuri uwo<br>\r\nmukobwa ni we uzakurengera akazatuma wima<br>\r\ningoma zawe zâ€™u Murengo.<br>\r\nRyangombe amaze kwumva indagu, aragenda,<br>\r\nagenda ahiga, yica ya nyamaswa, uruhu<br>\r\nararujyana. Ahura na Nyirakajumba amanutse<br>\r\nashoye inka, naho abandi bakobwa baca<br>\r\nubwatsi.<br><br>\r\nNyirakajumba ati: â€œBakobwa dore uruhu<br>\r\nrwiza.Ngiye kurwisabira uriya mugabo.â€ Bati:<br>\r\nâ€œNyirakajumba washira isoni. Uriya mugabo uko<br>\r\nangana, ukamusaba ruriya ruhu!â€ Ati: â€œNyihera<br>\r\nako gahu wa mugabo we.â€ Undi ati: â€œNagaha<br>\r\nugiye kunkamira iriya nka yabo yâ€™igitare yonsa<br>\r\nrutare, kandi akancumbikira.â€ Umukobwa ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNgwino njye kuyigukamira kandi<br>\r\nngucumbikire.â€ Aramuzamukana nâ€™iwabo, agira<br>\r\nse ati: â€œNimucumbikire uyu mugabo, dore aka<br>\r\ngahu yampaye.â€ Bati: â€œKoko agira ubuntu,<br>\r\numuntu uguhaye uruhu rusa rutyo!â€<br>\r\nBaramucumbikira, burira.<br>\r\nBazanye amazimano yo kumuzimanira,<br>\r\nRyangombe arayanga. Bati: â€œWa mugabo yanze<br>\r\namazimano! Ayangiye iki?â€ Bamutumaho bati:<br>\r\nâ€œKo twakuzimanye ukanga wabitewe nâ€™iki?â€ Undi<br>\r\nati: â€œNdazimanirwa nâ€™uwancumbikiye.â€ Bati: â€œIii.â€<br>\r\nBohereza Nyirakajumba. Se ati: â€œGenda<br>\r\nucumbikire uwo mugabo wawe Nyirakajumba<br>\r\nushira isoni! Kandi uzampamagarira!â€ Araza, aza<br>\r\naje gucumbikira Ryangombe, azanye amata<br>\r\nyâ€™inshyushyu yakamye ya nka. Arayamuhereza,<br>\r\nRyangombe arayasomye arayamucira.<br>\r\nAmushyizemo umwishywa. Nyirakajumba<br>\r\nagenda arira. Ati: â€œWa mugabo dore ibyo<br>\r\nankoreye.â€<br>\r\nRyangombe amugenda mu nyuma. Basaza be<br>\r\nbaraza baramukubita baramunoza,<br>\r\nbaramumenesha arasohoka. Ageze inyuma<br>\r\nyâ€™inzu, Nyirakajumba arasasa. Ngo ajye<br>\r\nkwendwa nâ€™agatotsi asanga aryamanye na<br>\r\nRyangombe. Ati: â€œDore re, wa mugabo yanteye<br>\r\nhano!â€ Basaza be barabyuka, baramwirukana,<br>\r\nbabwira Nyirakajumba bati: â€œSasa mu kirambi.â€<br>\r\nAshashe mu kirambi, ngo ajye kongera kwendwa<br>\r\nnâ€™agatotsi asanga undi bari kumwe.<br>\r\nNyirakajumba ati: â€œWa mugabo kandi yankurikiye<br>\r\nhano.â€ Bati: â€œNi ubushizi bwâ€™isoni bwawe,<br>\r\nNyirakajumba.â€<br><br>\r\nUbwo Ryangombe baramugeretse, ariko yatse<br>\r\nNyirakajumba urwuya, amaze kwimarira<br>\r\nurubanza rwe ararikiye. Bagenda bamwirukana<br>\r\nbamukubita. Yitera inyuma yâ€™urugo, ageze<br>\r\ninyuma yâ€™igikari, ati: â€œMurabeho ndagiye,<br>\r\nmuramenyere umugore, kandi uwo mugore<br>\r\nndamurongoye, ndarongoye birashize! Nsize<br>\r\nmutwitse inda, azayibyaramo umwana<br>\r\nwâ€™umuhungu. Uwo mwana wâ€™umuhungu najya<br>\r\nkumubyara azajye kuri uriya mugina uri inyuma<br>\r\nyâ€™urugo. Maze uwo mwana muzamwite Binego<br>\r\nna Bigina. Abandi bati nagende icyo cyohe.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe arigendeye, asanga Mpumutumucuni<br>\r\nbajya kubuguza: Bakabuguza Mpumutumucuni<br>\r\nakamuganza, bakabuguza akamuganza. Binego<br>\r\naruhira iyo avuka.<br>\r\nIgihe cyo kuvuka, Binego aba ari we ubwira<br>\r\nnyina ati: â€œMawe, pfukama umbyare!â€<br>\r\nNyirakajumba ati: â€œReka mbanze ntegure,<br>\r\nnkubure, nteke mpishe, nimbirangiza<br>\r\nndakubyara.â€ Arabikora, abirangije, Binego<br>\r\narongera aramubwira ati: â€œPfukama umbyare!â€<br>\r\nNyina aramubyara. Binego avukana icumu<br>\r\nnâ€™ubuhiri byâ€™icyuma.</div><div align=\"left\"><span class=\"spip_document_45914 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.imirasire.com/IMG/png/amateka-y_umwami-w_u-rwanda-kanyarwanda-gahima-580x360.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"384\" height=\"238\"></span><br>\r\nAmaze kuvuka arererwa<br>\r\niwabo kwa nyina, aba kwa ba nyirarume. Ari<br>\r\numwana, yazijyamo aragiye, yayikubita<br>\r\nakayigusha. Bati: â€œUyu mwana ni icyohe.â€<br>\r\nBakamukura mu nyana, bamushyira mu nka<br>\r\nnkuru. Bukeye, yibuka kuba umwana utwara<br>\r\nagacumu. Ba nyirarume baza bashoye inka, no<br>\r\nmu ibuga. Binego ahagarara imbere yâ€™ikibumbiro<br>\r\nyikandagira ku ivi. Imfizi iza gutambutsa<br>\r\nukuboko gukandagira mu kibumbiro, ayikomera<br>\r\nagacumu mu rwano ayigarika mu ibuga. Ba<br>\r\nnyirarume baza kuzamuka baramukubita. Agira<br>\r\nnyirarume amukubita icumu, agira undi na we<br>\r\namugenza uko, asiga abagize uburiri abasiga mu<br>\r\nibuga. Arazamuka nâ€™imuhira, ashikuza nyina<br>\r\nNyirakajumba amukubita urushyi aramushorera,<br>\r\nati: â€œHogi tugende.â€ Agira sekuru aramwica.<br><br>\r\nBinego aboneza ubwo. Asiga kwa nyirarume<br>\r\nahageregese.<br>\r\nBinego araza, aza ashoreye nyina. Ageze mu<br>\r\nnzira ahura nâ€™umugabo, ati: â€œWa mugabo!â€ Undi<br>\r\nati: â€œIii.â€ Ati: â€œNtiwanyobora?â€ Ati: â€œMu minsi<br>\r\nibihumbi, mu minsi ibihumbi, mbese nta<br>\r\nmayombo wumvaga? Nta kamiro kâ€™abahigi?â€<br>\r\nUmugenzi ati: â€œKino kigabo cyabaza ibyo ntazi!â€<br>\r\nBinego amukubita icumu amugarika aho,<br>\r\narakomeza ashoreye nyina.<br>\r\nAgeze imbere, asanga umugabo arahingira<br>\r\nurutoki, aca mu rutoki aje kumuyoboza. Undi ati:<br>\r\nâ€œUbonye kiriya kigabo kinciriye mu rutoki! Kiriya<br>\r\nkigenda gite?â€ Amukubita icumu amugarika mu<br>\r\nrutoki rwe. Ni byo mujya mwumva ngo Binego<br>\r\nyishe nyiri agatoke. Aragenda asanga umugabo<br>\r\naracoca, agenda agiye kumuyoboza, ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNyobora!â€<br>\r\nMu minsi ibihumbi, mu minsi uduhumbi, nta<br>\r\nmayombo wumvaga, nta kamiro kâ€™abahigi<br>\r\nwumvaga? Undi, ati: â€œUbonye uriya mugabo<br>\r\numbyogera mu masinde!â€ Binego aba<br>\r\namukubise icumu amugarika mu masinde.<br><br>\r\nBinego arakomeza ahura nâ€™igitambambuga,<br>\r\narakiyoboza. Umwana ajijinganije, Binego<br>\r\namukubita ubuhiri amutsinda aho. Ni cyo gituma<br>\r\nubandwa wese Binego, abandwa avuga ngo<br>\r\nntabyara kubera ko Binego yishe igitambambuga<br>\r\nntacyo yishisha.<br>\r\nNgo agere hirya ahura nâ€™umusaza, ati: â€œEwe wa<br>\r\nmugabo we! Mu minsi ibihumbi, mu minsi<br>\r\nuduhumbi, nta mayombo wumvaga, nta kamiro<br>\r\nkâ€™abahigi wumvaga?â€ Undi ati: â€œMu minsi<br>\r\nibihumbi mu minsi uduhumbi najyaga numva<br>\r\namayombo avuga nkumva ahahigi bamira.â€ Undi<br>\r\nati: â€œIgendere.â€ Binego ageze hirya, ahura na<br>\r\nRuhanga na we ashoreye nyina nkâ€™uko.<br>\r\nBaribwirana, hanyuma batangira kuyoboza<br>\r\nbombi. Bashyira buyira barashoreye ba nyina<br>\r\nbaraza. Bamaze kuboneza, bahura na<br>\r\nNyabirungu.<br>\r\nHagati aho, Ryangombe yari yabwiye mukuru we<br>\r\nNyabirungu ati: â€œAho uhigira hose, nyabuna<br>\r\ninyamaswa izagutungukaho, urayinyoborere.â€ Ni<br>\r\nbwo Binego ahuye na se wabo Nyabirungu<br>\r\nyahize. Ati: â€œWa mugabo we!â€ Undi ati: â€œIii.â€ Ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNtiwandangira umugabo wâ€™umuhigi witwaga<br>\r\nLyangombe?â€ Undi ati: â€œRyangombe se ni iki?â€<br>\r\nUndi ati: â€œNyobora wa kigabo we naba<br>\r\nutanyoboye urorere.â€<br>\r\nNyabirungu yumvise ko amukaramiye, ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNgwino njye kukuyobora.â€ Amujya imbere araza<br>\r\nno kwa Ryangombe, asanga Ryangombe yagiye<br>\r\nkubuguza kwa Mpumutumucuni. Asanga<br>\r\nNyiraryangombe, ati: â€œEwe wa gikecuru we!â€ Undi<br>\r\nati: â€œIii.â€ Ati: â€œMfungurira.â€ Azana inzoga<br>\r\nyâ€™amarwa, undi ati: â€œOya.â€ Ati: â€œIyo yihe ibyo<br>\r\nbikecuru! Njye sinshaka amarwa. Reba igicuma<br>\r\ncyâ€™umuhungu wawe wajyaga ubikamo urwagwa,<br>\r\nunyunyugurize mo amazi umpe.â€ Undi ati:<br>\r\nâ€œSindinda kuguha amazi hinga nkwereke.â€ Azana<br>\r\nku rwagwa rwa Ryangombe mu gacuma arabaha<br>\r\nbaranywa. Binego ati: â€œNdangira aho Ryangombe<br>\r\nyagiye.â€ Undi ati: â€œRyangombe yagiye kubuguza<br>\r\nna Mpumutumucuni, kandi umunsi wo gupfa ni<br>\r\nuyu.â€ Yaramusezeranije ngo nasubira<br>\r\nkumuganza, aramwaka isunzu ryâ€™ubugabo. Undi<br>\r\nati: â€œIii.â€<br>\r\nUbwo Binego ajyana na mwene se Ruhanga,<br>\r\nasanga Ryangombe arabuguza na<br>\r\nMpumutumucuni. Ahagarara hejuru yabo, ati:<br>\r\nâ€œYabuguza nabi uno mugabo, ese urabuguza<br>\r\nute? Kora mu mutwe maze ubuguze urase iriya<br>\r\nnteba, uganze inka zâ€™uwo mugabo.â€ Ryangombe<br>\r\nakora mu mutwe, arasa nteba, aramuganza.<br>\r\nMpumutumucuni aramukebuka hejuru, ati:<br>\r\nâ€œUbonye kiriya kigabo cyâ€™icyohe! Ko gisanze<br>\r\ntwibuguriza, kitugendera mu nka gite?â€ Binego<br>\r\naba azamuye icumu rye, arimukomera mu ntutu<br>\r\nyâ€™ibere amugarika aho.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe impundu<br>\r\narazivuza. Bahaguruka ubwo, azamuka ashoreye<br>\r\nabahungu be, bavuza impundu ko amaze kwica<br>\r\nMpumutumucuni.<br>\r\nRyangombe arakunda yima ingoma ze zâ€™u<br>\r\nBurengo kuko Mpumutumucuni yari apfuye,<br>\r\nazibamo nâ€™abahungu be, Binego, Ruhanga,<br>\r\nNyabirungu, Mashira na Kagoro. Bukeye,<br>\r\nicyagiye kumuca urutsi ni ya mihurire ye na<br>\r\nRuganzu.<br><br><br>\r\nRuganzu ni we wamutereye Nyagishya<br>\r\ncyâ€™impenebere, gihetse umwana imbebe, ni cyo<br>\r\nRyangombe yakuyeho impamvu zo gupfa.<br>\r\nRyangombe rero arara agambiriye umuhigo, ati:<br>\r\nâ€œEjo tuzahigire Nyabikenke.â€ Agira abahungu be,<br>\r\nati: â€œNzabatanga inyamaswa ya Nyabikenke!â€<br>\r\nBati: â€œNtuzayidutanga!â€ Barara bagambiriye<br>\r\numuhigo, bawuhigiye. Ryangombe, bibero<br>\r\nbirinda ibiramba, Nyamunyaga iziburiwe,<br>\r\nizitaburiwe akazazinyaga inkingi nâ€™imyugariro<br>\r\nyitwa Nkingiyinka, mu nkingi yâ€™abagabo yitwa<br>\r\nNkungiyabagabo, arahaguruka nâ€™umuhungu we<br>\r\nBinego bya Kajumba, nyamunigamapfizi<br>\r\namasumbi akazatamata imirinzi, rukarabankaka,<br>\r\nrutukuzambuga, rwugumbira mutarinkuba ya<br>\r\nNyirakajumba, ni urwamba rwâ€™impiri, ni ubwaayi<br>\r\nbwâ€™urubingo, ni amaganga yâ€™inkuba<br>\r\narashigishwa ntanyobwa.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe arahaguruka nâ€™umuhungu we<br>\r\nRuhanga rwa Milimo, rukayamaziri,<br>\r\nruhangarabimashi rwa Muhabwa mu macumu<br>\r\natwara amacinya, mu myambi atwara imisakura,<br>\r\ni Ndorwa ya Ndori ahanyaga imitamu, i Burundi<br>\r\nbwa Kiburungwa ahanyaga Bugondo bwâ€™imbimba<br>\r\nmuri zo. Arahaguruka nâ€™umuhungu we Kagoro<br>\r\nka Ryangombe, shegenya, sharinyanga,<br>\r\nmunanuzi, twababa utwa mpimbi na Muzana,<br>\r\nmikoni itwakwa abarenzi, rubango rwa<br>\r\nNyabirungu, rubangura abiri rwa Janja,<br>\r\nnyamunyagisha uko iburyo ukwa moso<br>\r\nyaguhagije imicuzo yâ€™Abenerubenge. Nkora<br>\r\nyâ€™imiyombo avuguta ibitero ibitenzi bigata<br>\r\nimiheto mwâ€™igerero kwa Mivuba ni we wanze<br>\r\nkwigira Ruhamagara mu ntara itari iyabo.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe araranye umuhigo, Nyiraryangombe<br>\r\naricura, arakanguka maze araragura, ati: â€œSiba<br>\r\numuhigo wa none cyana kimwe cya Mukanya<br>\r\ncyamaze nyina ubugwe nâ€™ubugwe-shyamba!<br>\r\nSiba umuhigo wa none bibero birinda ibibanda,<br>\r\nshebuja wa Ruhanga umugabo, siba umuhigo wa<br>\r\nnone. Undi ati: â€œOya ntabwo nsiba ndahigira<br>\r\nNyabikenke.â€ Nyina ati: â€œNarose inzozi mbi,<br>\r\nnarose itukura rya Nyabikenke, narose urukwavu<br>\r\nrutagira ishyira nâ€™umurizo, narose imbogo<br>\r\nyâ€™ihembe rimwe, narose inkware yâ€™ibara, narose<br>\r\numugezi utemba ujya ruguru ya Nyakenke,<br>\r\nwihigira Nyabikenke.â€ Undi ati: â€œNtabwo nasibira<br>\r\nntahigiye Nyabikenke!â€ Ryangombe arara<br>\r\n(araryama), ngo bigeze mu museke arabaduka<br>\r\nahamagara imbwa ze.<br><br>\r\nImbwa ze ziraza ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNimumpe amayombo yâ€™imbwa zanjye!â€<br>\r\nAmayombo arabura, naho Nyiraryangombe<br>\r\nyayahishe.<br>\r\nAjya mwa Nyirakagoro ati: â€œAmayombo yâ€™imbwa<br>\r\nzanjye!â€ Bati: â€œAmayombo ari mwa<br>\r\nNyiramugarura.â€ Ajya mwa Nyiramugarura, ati:<br>\r\nâ€œAmayombo yâ€™imbwa zanjye!â€ Bati: â€œAmayombo<br>\r\nari mwa Nyiraruhanga!â€ Ajya mwa Nyiraruhanga,<br>\r\nati: â€œAmayombo yâ€™imbwa zanjye!â€ Bati:<br>\r\nâ€œAmayombo ari mwa Nyirakajumba!â€ Ajya mwa<br>\r\nNyirakajumba, ati: â€œAmayombo yâ€™imbwa zanjye!â€<br>\r\nBati: â€œAmayombo ari mwa Nyiraryangombe!â€<br>\r\nNkonjo aramwongorera ati koko ari kwa<br>\r\nNyiraryangombe.<br><br>\r\nNi bwo Ryangombe aje aturutse hirya<br>\r\nnâ€™uburakari nâ€™iki, urugi rwâ€™umusego arukubita<br>\r\numugeri rugwira ibiseke, amayombo mu giseke<br>\r\naravuga.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe akuramo amayombo,<br>\r\nAhamagaza imbwa ze: yambika Nyakayonga,<br>\r\nyambika Bashokabadahannye, yambika<br>\r\nBabikamurwinanuriro, yambika Nyanaramuzi<br>\r\nntazamumpora, yambika Ikinyabutongo gitoto<br>\r\nkimara isimbo, yambika Ntakitambarinkanda,<br>\r\nyambika Uruyongoyongo rwa Miramba.<br><br>\r\nImbwa<br>\r\namaze kuzambika, ati: â€œNdaboneje!â€<br>\r\nNyiraryangombe aba yatambamye mu bikingi<br>\r\nbyâ€™amarembo, yijishura umweko awurambika<br>\r\nmuri ibyo bikingi byâ€™amarembo. Ati: â€œSiba cyana<br>\r\nkimwe cya Mukanya cyamaze nyina ubugwe<br>\r\nnâ€™ubugweshyamba, siba umuhigo wa none!â€<br>\r\nUndi ati: â€œSinsiba ntahigiye Nyabikenke!â€<br>\r\nUmweko arawutambuka, arawusimbuka awugwa<br>\r\ninyuma araboneza.<br>\r\nRyangombe arashogoshera nâ€™umuhigi we<br>\r\nNyarwambari rwa Ngweja ya Murema, na we ari<br>\r\nkumwe nâ€™umuhigi we Rwamukwisi. Ngo bagere<br>\r\nmu irembo, babona agakwavu karatitiba.<br>\r\nBongeye gutarabuka, baca imitwe nâ€™inkware<br>\r\nyâ€™ibaba rimwe, iraguruka. Ati: â€œKiriya ni igiki ko<br>\r\nkitaraboneka aho mwabereye?â€ Abandi bati: â€œNi<br>\r\nya ndagu ya Nyiraryangombe yenda gutaha.â€<br>\r\nUndi ati: â€œNta ndagu yâ€™agakecuru, si ko<br>\r\nkambuza guhigira Nyabikenke!â€ Ngo agere<br>\r\nimbere, babona imondo yâ€™ibara rimwe iratitiba.<br>\r\nBarayivuma bati: â€œPu, Nigende!â€ Ati: â€œBiriya ni<br>\r\nibiki?â€ Bati: Ni ya ndagu ya Nyiraryangombe<br>\r\nyenda gutaha. Ashyira buyira, ataboneza<br>\r\naragenda. Ngo ajye kumanuka umugezi wa<br>\r\nNyabikenke, asanga wahindutse ituku<br>\r\nryâ€™amaraso.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe araboneza ngo agere hirya aca<br>\r\nimitwe na Nyagishya cyâ€™impenebere gihetse<br>\r\numwana imbebe. Agiye gusimbuka wa mugezi<br>\r\nbati: â€œSigaho wirenga itukura rya Nyamikenke<br>\r\ngaruka Ryangombe! Garuka cyana kimwe cya<br>\r\nMukanya cyanze kwumvira se na nyina umunsi<br>\r\nwa nyuma ukazumvira ijeri ku mugani wa<br>\r\nNyiraryangombe uko yabivuze!â€ Undi ati: â€œOya,<br>\r\nnta ndagu yâ€™agakecuru ntibimbuza guhiga i<br>\r\nNyabikenke!â€ Ni bwo aciye imitwe na Nyagishya<br>\r\ncyâ€™impenebere gihetse umwana imbebe (iri ni<br>\r\nizina ryâ€™uyu mugore), ati: â€œYewe wa mugore we!â€<br>\r\nUndi ati: â€œIii.â€ Ati: â€œMpa urwuya!â€ Umugore ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNaguha urwuya umaze kumpa impetso<br>\r\nyâ€™umwana wanjye!â€ Ryangombe ati:<br>\r\nâ€œNdayiguha!â€ Ryangombe amuha uruhu<br>\r\nrwâ€™inyemera ararwanga, amuha uruhu rwâ€™impara<br>\r\nararwanga, amuha uruhu rwâ€™impongo ararwanga,<br>\r\namuha uruhu rwâ€™inzobe ararwanga, amuha<br>\r\nuruhu rwâ€™isasu ararwanga. Ati: â€œEse ushaka iki?â€<br>\r\nUndi ati: â€œNshaka uruhu rwâ€™inyamaswa iri muri<br>\r\nkiriya gihugu!â€ Undi ati: â€œIii! Nibayihige<br>\r\nndaruguha!â€ Ati: â€œNimungondagondere mbanze<br>\r\nnsogore uyu mugore.â€ Bamugondagondera<br>\r\ningando, amwinjizamo. Abwira Nyarwambari ati:<br>\r\nâ€œHiga urenza, nuvumbura inyamaswa<br>\r\nyâ€™insindanya murampamagare.â€<br>\r\nNyamwambari arahize, imbwa zikoze hasi no<br>\r\nhejuru, zivumbura imbogo yâ€™ihembe rimwe.<br>\r\nYohereza imbwa mu gihuru: bashyirayo<br>\r\nBakoshabadahannye, imbogo iyikoze ihembe<br>\r\nirakunkumura irirenza. Bashyirayo<br>\r\nBabikamurwinanuriro, irayikunkumura iyijugunya<br>\r\ninyuma yayo.<br>\r\nBashyirayo Kinyabutongo gitoto irayikunkumura<br>\r\nijugunya inyuma yayo. Bashyirayo<br>\r\nRuyongoyongo rwa Mirambi irakunkumura<br>\r\nijugunya inyuma yayo. Maze Nyamwambari ajya<br>\r\nruguru atakira Ryangombe ati: â€œImbwa zawe<br>\r\nzashize!â€ Undi ati: â€œHiga urenza nuvumbura<br>\r\ninyamaswa yâ€™insindanya murampamagare!â€ Undi<br>\r\nati: â€œOya imbwa zawe zashize, ibintu byacitse<br>\r\nbirayoba tabara!â€<br>\r\nRyangombe ubwo aba amaze kuva kuri<br>\r\nNyiragishya cyâ€™impenebere, aboneza ubwo. Ati:<br>\r\nâ€œIyo nyamaswa ni bwoko ki?â€ Undi ati: â€œUkuboko<br>\r\nnâ€™ukuguru ni inka ariko iyo nyamaswa<br>\r\nyatuyobeye.â€ Undi ati: â€œMwashyizeho<br>\r\nNyakayonga?â€ Undi ati: â€œOya.â€ Maze ahamagara<br>\r\nimbwa ye Nyakayonga, ati: â€œNimuyishyireyo!â€<br>\r\nAshyirayo Nyakayonga, imbogo iyikoza ihembe<br>\r\nirakunkumura ijugunya inyuma yayo.<br><br>\r\nRyangombe abibonye ati: â€œNyakayonga imbwa<br>\r\nyanjye, Nyakayonga twajyanye Injurijuri,<br>\r\nNyakayonga twajyanye ijuru inyuma, Nyakayonga<br>\r\ntwajyanye i Burundi kwa Kiburungu, Nyakayonga<br>\r\nnta gihugu tutageranyemo. Imbwa yanjye<br>\r\nntinsize!â€ Maze Ryangombe imbogo<br>\r\narayendereza, haba haje yo. Ayikoza icumu mu<br>\r\nipfupfu, iba yubitse itya imukoza ihembe mu<br>\r\nnsyanyango irakunkumura irirenza.<br><br><br>\r\nRyangombe ageze mu kirere asumira igiti<br>\r\ncyâ€™umuko aragikomeza. Biruka ubwo bati ibintu<br>\r\nbiracitse. Bajya gutabaza bene Ryangombe aho<br>\r\nbahigiye. Bene Ryangombe bahageze, bati: â€œIyo<br>\r\nnyamaswa iri he?â€ Binego, ati: â€œIyo nyamaswa<br>\r\nirihe?â€ Bati: â€œNgiriya iri muri kiriya gihugu!â€ Ati:<br>\r\nâ€œEse mwabonye isa ite?â€ Bati: â€œUkuboko ni inka,<br>\r\nukuguru ni inka, ariko iyo nyamaswa<br>\r\nyatuyobeye!â€ Binego bya Kajumba<br>\r\nrukarabankaba, rutukuzambuga,<br>\r\nrwugumbiramutara inkuba ya Nyirakajumba<br>\r\nyishe nyirarume asangira na nyina, yishe nyiri<br>\r\nudusinde tubura gicoca, yica nyiri urutoki rubura<br>\r\ngihingira, yica Buranumye kâ€™Urukamira, yica<br>\r\nnâ€™abatukanye barwana, arayangangiza<br>\r\ninyamaswa iba yabyutse. Yenda icumu ariyikoza<br>\r\nmu rwano arihingura mu nyuma, inyamaswa<br>\r\nirirenga. Asanga Ryangombe.<br><br><br>\r\nRyangombe ahamagaza Mashira ati: â€œMashira<br>\r\nngwino ngutume kuri Nyiraryangombe!â€ Mashira<br>\r\nati: â€œSinabona iryo mbwira Nyiraryangombe!â€ Ati:<br>\r\nâ€œKagoro ngutume?â€ Kagoro ati: Sinatunguka mu<br>\r\nmaso ya Nyiraryangombe ngo mbone icyo<br>\r\nmubwira, nje kukubika mvuge ngo wapfuye!â€<br>\r\nAbakuza bose uko bangana, bamaze kubyanga<br>\r\nni bwo ahamagaje Nkonjo. Nkonjo ati: â€œNtuma!â€<br>\r\nAti: â€œUgende umbwirire Nyiraryangombe, uti<br>\r\nUmwana umwe si umuryango, igiti kimwe<br>\r\nntikibamo ishyamba! Uti umugore ambandwe,<br>\r\numugabo ambandwe. Uti reba amata ya gitare<br>\r\nmu gitereko wende nâ€™icyahi cya Murenziwera<br>\r\nmuhurire ku rutare rwa Butaza ujye gutegera<br>\r\nababyeyi i Raba!â€</div><div align=\"left\"><span class=\"spip_document_45915 spip_documents spip_documents_center\">\r\n<img src=\"http://www.imirasire.com/IMG/png/abaturage_baje_mu_iyimikwa_rya_ryangombe-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"345\" height=\"252\"></span></div><div align=\"left\"><span class=\"spip_document_45915 spip_documents spip_documents_center\"></span>Umuko Ryangombe yapfiriyemo, ni wo</div><div align=\"left\"> bita umurinzi iyo babandwa cyangwa baterekera.<br>\r\nBaragiye babikojeje Nyiraryangombe.<br>\r\nNyiraryangombe amaze kubona ubutumwa yenda<br>\r\nicyahi cya Murenziwera yenda amata ya Gitare<br>\r\nmu gitereko. Nyiraryangombe ahaguruka ubwo<br>\r\nahurirana nâ€™abunguje bahetse Ryangombe<br>\r\nbaboneza bamujyana mu birunga. Ryangombe<br>\r\napfa atyo. Ngo bitere kabiri umuzimu wa<br>\r\nRyangombe utera ibwami kwa Ruganzu. Afata<br>\r\nabantu bose bo mu rugo, ibintu biracika.<br><br>\r\nInka imiriro iraka ku mahembe, ingo zirashya<br>\r\nrubura gica. Ibwami bashaka imitsindo bereza<br>\r\nimitsindo yo kumwigana. Kubandwa ni aho<br>\r\nbyaturutse. Ku zindi ngoma ntibyabagaho.<br>\r\nKubandwa ni imitsindo ngo amakuba yateye u<br>\r\nRwanda nyuma yâ€™urupfu rwa Ryangombe rya<br>\r\nBabinga ba Nyundo ye kongera kugaruka. Uretse<br>\r\nrero umwami gusa, kubandwa biba umuhango<br>\r\nmu gihugu cyose. Naho abantu bose, ari<br>\r\nabakuru nâ€™abato bajye babandwa Ryangombe.<br><br><br>\r\nUmuko Ryangombe yapfiriyemo, ni wo bita<br>\r\numurinzi iyo babandwa cyangwa baterekera.<br>\r\nUmuko rero ni igiti gikomeye mu kubandwa<br>\r\nkubera ko ari cyo cyakijije Ryangombe<br>\r\ngushwanyaguzwa nâ€™imbogo ubwo yamuteraga<br>\r\nihembe.<br><br>\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier.<br><br>\r\nIvomo: Imirasire.com</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1505544226ryangombe_3-2.jpg', 0, 'admin', 7, 13, 'sub', 104),
(120, '2017-09-17 13:36:06', 'Transpoesis yamaze gukora ikindi gitaramo cy\'ubusizi yise \'\'Poetic Fever\'\'.AMAFOTO', 'Poetic fever ni igitaramo cy\'ubusizi cyabaye ku mugoroba wo kuri uyu gatandatu tariki ya 16 Nzeri i Kigali muri Blue Note.', '<div align=\"left\">Transpoesis yari isanzwe imenyerewe mu gutegura amarushanwa nayo<br>\r\ny\'ubusizi yiswe Kigali Vibrates with Poetry amarushanwa ngaruka<br>\r\ngihembwe. Kuri ubu Transpoesis igiye kujya ifatanya ibyo bikorwa<br>\r\nbyombi ari amarushanwa ndetse ni iki gitaramo poetic fever kizajya<br>\r\nkiba ngarukakwezi nkuko twabitangarijwe na Dr Andrea Grieder umuyobozi<br>\r\nwa Transpoesis.</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZYIKTEY.jpg\" width=\"515\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nPoetic Fever ni igitaramo cyatangiye ahagana ku i saa mbili<br>\r\nz\'umugoroba mu mujyi wa Kigali rwagati mu Kabari kitwa Blue Note,maze<br>\r\nku ikubitiro Kivumbi cyangwa Lion King abimburira abandi basizi<br>\r\nbinyura imbaga mu gisigo cye kiri mu rurimi rw\'icyongereza yise\" King<br>\r\nmeet</div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;\r\nking\",igitaramo cyaje gukomeza maze abasizi bagiye batandukanye<br>\r\nbarimo Bahati Innocent, Ella Bikwemu,Delice Mukazi,Carine<br>\r\nManiraguha,Andrea Grieder,Amina Umuhoza, Esther Uwibambe basusurutsa<br>\r\nabitabiriye poetic fever karahava.<br>\r\nNyuma y\' igitaramo ikinyamakuru umuco wacu cyaganiriye numwe mu basizi<br>\r\nbitabiriye iki gitaramo ari we Kivumbi(Lion King) atangaza uko<br>\r\nyiyumva. Yatangiye agira ati&lt;&lt; Ku nshuro ya mbere nishimiye ubwitabire<br>\r\nbw\'abantu muri iki gitaramo ikindi ndashimira cyane Dr Andrea Grieder<br>\r\nkubw\'uru rubuga yashyiriyeho abasizi Imana imuhe umugisha,ndagira ngo<br>\r\nkandi mbwire abakunda ubusizi ko bashonje bahishiwe kuko ibikorwa byo<br>\r\nni byinshi&gt;&gt;.</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ATqqPOp.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4aDDypI.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div></div><div align=\"left\"><br>Dr Andrea Grieder</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f9GaDCQ.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nIki gitaramo kikaba cyari gifite umwihariko wuko buri musizi wese<br>\r\nyacurangirwaga ibisigo bye abifashijwemo na Band yitwa Kinga Blues<br>\r\nihagarariwe n\'umunyamuziki ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Uburundi Arnauld<br>\r\nNganji.</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><b>&nbsp;REBA AMAFOTO</b>:</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kw5hC8s.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MHXZpwE.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/91gjU4z.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlbFPXo.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9zWMpSn.jpg\" width=\"424\"><br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VPLujVX.jpg\" width=\"499\"><br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SFalW9I.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br><br><br><br><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6SD3pUa.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><br><br><br><br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Q1jwn1d.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0OxzOdA.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eZgM219.jpg\" width=\"540\"></div><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P96IGZu.jpg\" width=\"395\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cUvJKxZ.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OlawOhC.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/77LsBYj.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yVRf0GB.jpg\" width=\"540\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nNdabibutsa ko ntagihindutse igitaramo \"<b>Poetic Fever</b>\" kizongera kuba ku<br>\r\nwa 14 Ukwakira uyu mwaka nubundi muri Blue Note.<br><br>\r\nYanditswe na <b><i>Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier</i></b><br><br>\r\nAmafoto: <b>Tuyisenge Olivier</b></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1505648166PhotoGrid_1505647586130.jpg', 0, 'admin', 1, 14, 'head', 293),
(122, '2017-09-19 23:29:42', ' Abagize itorero Inkindi Itatse bishimiye bikomeye gukorana na Mani Martin ndetse na Eddy Kenzo muri Afro Remix/AMAFOTO', ' Itorero Inkindi Itatse rikorera mu kigo cyo kwa Gisimba mu Nyakabanda bishimiye bikomeye gukorana na Mani Martin ndetse na Eddy Kenzo nk\'abahanzi b\'abahanga kandi bamaze kumenyekana muri Afurika y\'uburasirazuba ndetse nahandi henshi hatandukanye.', '<div align=\"left\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco Wacu cyagiranye na Hitimana Constantin<br>\r\numuyobozi w\'itorero inkindi itatse yatangiye agira ati &lt;&lt; Twishimiye<br>\r\ncyane gukorana na Mani Martin kandi iyi ni intambwe nziza, ubundi<br>\r\ntwamenyanye na Mani Martin mu mushinga nanone w\'indirimbo yitwa<br>\r\nNdaraye turi gupanga nayo gukora gusa twabaye duhereye kuri Afro<br>\r\nisubiyemo(Afro Remix),yakunze cyane imibyinire yacu ikindi kandi Mani<br>\r\nMartin si Umuhanzi upfa gukorana na abantu babonetse bose kuba<br>\r\nyaraduhisemo tugakorana ni intambwe ikomeye...&gt;&gt;</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jGnVCSm.jpg\" width=\"390\" height=\"188\"><br><br>\r\nItorero Inkindi Itatse ni itorero gakondo ryatangiye mu mwaka&nbsp; 2013,<br>\r\nni ukuvuga ko rimaze imyaka ine yonyine. Kubw\'ibyo rero abagize iri<br>\r\ntorero bahamya ko gukorana n\'abahanzi nka Mani Martin ndetse na Eddy<br>\r\nKenzo umuhanzi rurangiranwa ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'ubugande&nbsp; ari ntambwe<br>\r\nnziza bateye ibaganisha ku ntsinzi.<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gBF4SiP.jpg\" width=\"394\" height=\"394\"><br>\r\nNdagira ngo mbibutse ko indirimbo Afro itorero inkindi itatse<br>\r\nrizagaragaramo ari Afro isubiwemo(Afro Remix) umuhanzi nyarwanda Mani<br>\r\nMartin yasubiranyemo na Eddy Kenzo umuhanzi ukomoka mu gihugu<br>\r\ncy\'ubugande, bikaba binateganyijwe ko amashusho yiyi ndirimbo azajya<br>\r\nhanze bidatinze.<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><i><b>REBA AMAFOTO:</b></i></div><div align=\"left\"><br><i><b><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IVzSslc.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"249\"></b></i></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2VOrx7F.jpg\" width=\"335\" height=\"223\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NGGzdNB.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"232\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S4ANEqF.jpg\" width=\"431\" height=\"288\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NLr0XOh.jpg\" width=\"341\" height=\"227\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P2ZTm4F.jpg\" width=\"337\" height=\"224\"><br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5wVcw8J.jpg\" width=\"366\" height=\"221\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FpxwgQy.jpg\" width=\"395\" height=\"267\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FM8yYmu.jpg\" width=\"388\" height=\"481\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jQS9Ffr.jpg\" width=\"370\" height=\"256\"><br><br><br><i><b>Yanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier</b></i></div>\r\n', '1505856582IMG-20170919-WA0027.jpg', 0, 'admin', 4, 3, 'head', 510),
(123, '2017-09-23 08:13:27', 'Abagize itsinda ComponentsRw ryaserukiye u Rwanda muri Bayimba Festival bati \"Duhagaze bwuma', ' Abagize itsinda ComponentsRw rigizwe n\' umuvangavangamiziki(Dj) Karengera Kirenga Eric Soul, umukirigitananga Munyakazi Deo, abaraperi babiri aribo Mazimpaka Prime na Angel Mutoni, guhera kuri uyu wa 22 Nzeri 2017 barabarizwa mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'Ubugande Kampala aho bitabiriye iserukiramuco ryitwa Bayimba Festival.', '<div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nAbagize itsinda rya ComponentsRw bahagurutse i Kigali mu gitondo cyo<br>\r\nkuri uyu wa Gatanu berekeza mu gihugu cya Uganda ahagiye kubera iri<br>\r\nserukiramuco rya Bayimba Festival rigiye kuba ku ncuro ya cumi, rikaba<br>\r\nryitabiriwe n\'abahanzi baturutse mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi. Iri<br>\r\ntsinda rihagarariye u Rwanda biteganyijwe ko riri bususurutse<br>\r\nabitabiriye iri serukiramuco uyu munsi tariki ya 23/ Nzeri 2017 guhera<br>\r\ni saa tatu z\'ijoro ku isaha yo mu bugande n\'ukuvuga saa mbili z\'ijoro<br>\r\nku isaha yo mu Rwanda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAba bahanzi baratangaza ko nyuma yo kugera Uganda amahoro bameze neza<br>\r\nko biteguye kuza gutarama bagacyura inganji nkuko Munyakazi Deo umwe<br>\r\nmu bahanzi bagize itsinda ComponentsRw yabitangarije ikinyamakuru<br>\r\numucowacu.com Yatangiye agira ati \"Mukuri turiteguye cyane,twagerageje<br>\r\ngukora imyitozo ihagije pee!! Ndagira ngo niba hari abanyarwanda bari<br>\r\ninaha bakunda umuziki w\'umwimerere bazi kuza badushyigikire twe nka<br>\r\nComponentsRw duhagaze bwuma\".<br>\r\n</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iynUhcb.jpg\" width=\"388\" height=\"388\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MUNYAKAZI DEO<div align=\"left\"><br></div><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lg6gvIB.jpg\" width=\"364\" height=\"260\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (DJ) KARENGERA KIRENGA&nbsp; ERIC SOUL<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cwYrpHy.jpg\" width=\"385\" height=\"256\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; MUTONI ANGEL</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tiUsbCH.jpg\" width=\"326\" height=\"217\"></div><div align=\"left\">MAZIMPAKA&nbsp; PRIME<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\">\r\nIri serukiramuco uretse itsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaryitabiriye,<br>\r\nryitabiriwe kandi nabandi bahanzi<br>\r\nbakomeye barimo itsinda rya Umoja Boys ryo mu<br>\r\nBuholandi,Slyvester &amp; Abramz, bo muri Uganda,<br>\r\nMaurice Kirya ,Makadem wo muri Kenya, Coopy<br>\r\nBly, Cindy Sanyu, Berita wo muri Afurika yâ€™Epfo,<br>\r\nFeridah Rose, Jose Chameleone ,Bobi Wine,ndetse nabandi benshi batandukanye.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nIri tsinda rya ComponentsRw ryaherukaga mu gihugu cya Uganda muri<br>\r\nGicurasi mu iserukiramuco ryiswe Doadoa Festival, iri tsinda kandi<br>\r\nryanitabiriye umuhuro w\'abahanzi bo muri Afurika witwa Ongea wabereye<br>\r\nmuri Kenya mu kwezi kwa Werurwe uyu mwaka.<br>\r\n</div>', '1506147207PhotoGrid_1506145682420.jpg', 0, '\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier', 4, 3, 'head', 223),
(124, '2017-09-29 23:26:49', 'Amwe mu mateka y\'umuhanzi Rugamba Dorcy, umuhungu wa nyakwigendera Rugamba Sipiriyani.', 'Rugamba Dorcy yavutse kuwa 29 Nzeri 1969,ni umuhanzi, umusizi akaba nâ€™umukinnyi ndetse n\'uwanditsi wâ€™amateyatere.', '<div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy yavutse kuwa 29 Nzeri 1969,ni<br>\r\numuhanzi, umusizi akaba nâ€™umukinnyi ndetse n\'uwanditsi<br>\r\nwâ€™amateyatere. Se umubyara<br>\r\nni umuhanzi Rugamba Cyprien naho<br>\r\nnyina akaba Daphrose Rugamba. Ni<br>\r\numwana wa kabiri (ubuheta) mu<br>\r\nmuryango wâ€™abana icumi. Rugamba akaba avuga indimi enye adategwa arizo<br>\r\nikinyarwanda,Igifaransa,<wbr>Icyongereza,Igiswahili.<br>\r\nNâ€™ubwo atari umuririmbyi nka se, Dorcy<br>\r\nRUGAMBA ni umwe mu banyarwanda<br>\r\nbake bagize ibikorwa byâ€™umuco<br>\r\nnkâ€™umwuga. Impano yo kubikunda akaba<br>\r\nyarabikuye kuri se wari umusizi<br>\r\nnâ€™umushakashatsi wâ€™intyoza, Rugamba<br>\r\nCyprien</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SMfo7hB.jpg\" width=\"347\" height=\"347\"></div><div align=\"left\">Rugamba Cyprien na Daphrose Rugamba</div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nAha tugiye kubanyuriramo amwe mu mateka ya Rugamba Dorcy mu bice<br>\r\nbibiri bitandukanye aribyo :ubuzima bwe bwo hambere ndetse n\'ubuzima<br>\r\nbwe bwo hanze y\'u Rwanda.<br><br>\r\nUbuzima bwe bwo hambere<br><br>\r\nMuri 1976, Rugamba Dorcy yinjiye mu itorero Amasimbi<br>\r\nnâ€™Amakombe , afite imyaka 7 gusa.<br>\r\nHagati aho yize amashuri abanza muri<br>\r\nEcole Belge de Butare, akomereza muri<br>\r\nSeminari nto ya Karubanda (PS Virgo<br>\r\nFidelis); ngo icyo yakundaga cyane mu<br>\r\nMasimbi nâ€™Amakombe ni ukwiyereka<br>\r\nkwâ€™intore.<br>\r\nYagiye muri tournÃ©e bwa mbere mu<br>\r\nmwaka wa 1991, hari muri Suisse na<br>\r\nBelgique. Nyuma yaje gukunda cyane ibi<br>\r\nbikorwa ndangamuco, cyane cyane<br>\r\nubuvanganzo nyemvugo nkâ€™ubusizi.<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uSiHAD2.jpg\" width=\"200\"></div><div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy</div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nIbi bihe byiza rero byaje kurangizwa na<br>\r\nJenoside yakorewe Abatutsi yo muri Mata 1994. Iki gihe akaba yarigaga muri<br>\r\nKaminuza Nkuru yâ€™u Rwanda mu ishami<br>\r\nrya Pharmacie. Iri sanganya ryamutwaye<br>\r\nababyeyi na batandatu mu bavandimwe<br>\r\nbe, hari tariki 7/Mata/1994.<br>\r\nUbuzima bwe hanze yâ€™u Rwanda</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLx5CRc.jpg\" width=\"360\" height=\"241\"></div><div align=\"left\">Rugamba Dorcy</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\">\r\nRugamba Dorcy arikumwe nâ€™abavandimwe be babiri, bahise<br>\r\nbajya i Burundi, bahava bajya i Paris.<br>\r\nNyuma yageze mu Bubiligi aho yatangiye gukorana na groupe yo muri diaspora<br>\r\nyitwa Amarebe nâ€™Imena. Yatangiye no<br>\r\ngukoresha inyandiko nâ€™ibihangano bya<br>\r\nse wari utangiye gufatwa nkâ€™icyatwa<br>\r\n(monument national) mu Rwanda aho<br>\r\nabantu kugeza nâ€™ubu bagikunda<br>\r\nindirimbo ze. Rugamba Dorcy yakoranye nâ€™umuryango<br>\r\nwitwa Groupov umukino (piÃ¨ce) wiswe<br>\r\nRwanda 94 ukaba umara amasaha 6<br>\r\nyose kuwukina</div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZwdbS4Q.jpg\" width=\"355\" height=\"238\"></div><br><div align=\"left\">\r\nMu rwego rwo kwihugura, yize muri<br>\r\nConservatoire de LiÃ¨ge ariko anitabira<br>\r\nibirori bitandukanye nka Fest Africa<br>\r\n2000, aho bamutumiye kuza gukina mu<br>\r\nRwanda muri 2004. Ahageze yahahuriye<br>\r\nnâ€™urubyiruko rukunda gukina ikinamico<br>\r\nbiyemeza gufatanya kugirango babashe<br>\r\nkuba abakinnyi bâ€™umwuga (comediens<br>\r\nprofessionnels). Ni muri urwo rwego<br>\r\nyashinze itorero â€˜Urwintoreâ€™. Muri 2007<br>\r\nyatangiye gukina umukino(piece) wiswe<br>\r\nLâ€™instruction akora tournÃ©e mu bihugu<br>\r\nbyinshi byo ku isi. Iyi tournÃ©e<br>\r\nyarakunzwe ku buryo ahantu nko mu murwa mukuru w\'igihugu cy\'Ubwongereza London<br>\r\nama salles yarakubitaga akuzura.<br>\r\nDorcy Rugamba yatangarije<br>\r\nikinyamakuru IKAZE mu mwaka wa 2008<br>\r\nko ikintu kimushimisha mu buzima ari<br>\r\nukuba atunzwe nâ€™ubuhanzi bwe ; kuri we<br>\r\nngo ni nkâ€™inzozi yakabije. Bamubajije<br>\r\ninzozi afite ubu arasubiza atiâ€ni Leta<br>\r\nZunze ubumwe za Afurika.â€ Abajijwe<br>\r\numuntu wamugiriye akamaro mu buzima<br>\r\nbwe, yavuze ko ari se Cyprien Rugamba.<br>\r\nIkindi ngo we ukwemera kwe gushingiye<br>\r\nku buzima bwo ku isi bwonyine kuko<br>\r\natemera ijuru; ati â€œnta dini ndimo.â€</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rBb2Pvc.jpg\" width=\"375\" height=\"267\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;Daphrose Rugamba na Rugamba Cyprien <br></div><div align=\"left\"><br>\r\nKuri ubu Rugamba Dorcy afite imishinga myinshi itandukanye igamije<br>\r\nguteza imbere ubuhanzi,ikindi kandi ubu ni umuyobozi<br>\r\nw\'ubuhanzi(Directeur Artistique) mu kigo Rwanda Arts Initiative(RAI).<br><br>\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier<br>\r\nIsoko: Wikirwanda.org ndetse na Theatreonline.com</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1506720409IMG-20170929-WA0028.jpg', 0, 'Yanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge', 3, 11, 'sub', 289),
(125, '2017-10-01 22:20:01', 'Umubyinnyikazi ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Ububiligi Hilde Cannoodt ashishikajwe bikomeye no kwiga kubyina kinyarwanda.', 'Hilde Cannoodt ni umubyinnyikazi ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Ububiligi gusa kuri ubu atuye mu gihugu cy\'Ubwongereza. Hilde Cannoodt yagaragaje ubuhanga n\'umuhate mu kubyina imbyino za kinyarwanda aho mu minsi ishize yabyinanye n\'itorero Intayoberana', '<div align=\"left\">Mu busanzwe Hilde Cannoodt ni umubyinnyi w\'imbyino zitandukanye<br>\r\nzikunzwe cyane ku isi arizo contemporary dance,Bally Dance,Hip Hop...<br>\r\nNyuma yizo mbyino zose uyu mubiligikazi abyina arashaka kongeraho ni<br>\r\nimbyino nyarwanda ngo kuko yabonye imbyino gakondo z\'abanyarwanda<br>\r\nzifite umwihariko&nbsp; wazo ku isi. Abajijwe icyo abona nk\'umwihariko mu<br>\r\nmibyinire y\'abanyarwanda,Hilde yasubije agira ati \" Mukuri<br>\r\nabanyarwanda babyina neza,babyinisha umubiri wose kandi bakabyina<br><div>\r\nbaseka\".</div><div><br></div><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nMedq0w.jpg\" height=\"258\" width=\"461\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hilde Canoodt <br></div><div align=\"left\">Hilde Canoodt uretse kuba ari umubyinnyi anategura amaserukiramuco aho<br>\r\nkuri ubu afite iserukiramuco ry\'imbyino yise Tribal Remix yakomoye ku<br>\r\nbwoko bw\' imbyino yitwa Tribal fusion nkuko yabitangarije ikinyamakuru<br>\r\nUmuco wacu.</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EuVqJ8U.jpg\" width=\"480\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hilde Canoodt</div><div align=\"left\">\r\nHilde Cannodt abajijwe aho igitekerezo cyo kubyinana n\'itorero<br>\r\nIntayoberana cyavuye, yatangiye agira ati \" Umwaka ushize ubwo<br>\r\nnitabiraga iserukiramuco Ubumuntu nabonye itorero ribyina gusa<br>\r\nsinibuka uko ryitwa,nyuma yaho nahise mbona uko babyina,bagenda<br>\r\ngake,bihuta,mbese mbona imibyinire ya kinyarwanda ihuye neza n\'ubwoko<br>\r\nbw\'imibyinire yanjye. Nyuma naje kugaruka mu Rwanda mpitamo gukorana<br>\r\nn\'itorero Intayoberana.<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qxACT4Z.jpg\" width=\"472\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hilde Canoodt</div><div align=\"left\">\r\nUyu mubyinnyi yakomeje abwira ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu ko afite<br>\r\nimishinga myinshi ateganya gukora harimo nko gukomeza gufatanya mu<br>\r\nmishinga ye n\'umukirigitananga Munyakazi Deo kuko ngo yakunze urwego<br>\r\nakoreraho n\'uburyo akunda ibyo akora, ndetse n\'abandi benshi<br>\r\nbatandukanye mu rwego rwo gufatanya nk\'abahanzi.</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SiCWvkt.jpg\" width=\"480\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hilde Canoodt na Munyakazi Deo <br></div><div align=\"left\">\r\nUyu muhanzi kandi yashimiye abanyarwanda uburyo bamwakiriye,urugwiro<br>\r\nbamweretse ndetse asoza avuga ko afata u Rwanda nk\'iwabo.<br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v01K6Hp.jpg\" width=\"480\"></div><div align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp; Ikirango cya Tribal Remix Iserukiramuco Ritegurwa na Hilde<br>\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '1506889201IMG-20171001-WA0008.jpg', 0, 'admin', 4, 3, 'sub', 225);
