ble Normal\";\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-priority:99;\r\n	mso-style-qformat:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:11.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\r\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\n	mso-bidi-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Umusizi Ashimwe Ange nubwo kuri ubu abana n\'ubumuga bw\'ingingo\r\nngo siko byahoze! Abajijwe uko byaje yasubije muri aya magambo </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\" Icyambere navutse nk\'abandi bana bose,gusa mfite\r\nimyaka itandatu kugenda byatagiye kwanga, ikibazo narimfite n\'imbaraga nke mu\r\nmaguru, naho ibya Scoliosis(inyonjo) byatewe no kwicara igihe kinini kuko\r\nntabashaga<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span>guhagarara. Bamwe bavuga ko\r\nbandoze gusa bamwe barabyemeza abandi bakabihakana, njye ntana kimwe mbiziho,mu\r\nrugo bamvuje ahashoboka hose haba mu Rwanda ndetse no hanze, gusa nabonye\r\nbyanze ndiyakira ubundi ndiyigira. Ubumuga bwanjye bwatangiye kuva ubwo, ubu\r\nmfite imyaka 18 bivuzeko uyu mwaka ari uwa 12 ntagenda.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5V1iVn4.jpg\" width=\"450\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Umusizi Ashimwe Ange </p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Hanyuma Ashimwe Ange abajijwe uko ibyo kuba umusizi byaje\r\nyasubije agira ati</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"></span>\"Nyine nize amashuri\r\nabanza ntabana n\'ababyeyi... noneho umukozi twabanaga yarankubitaga bikaze nuko\r\nyankubita nkanga kurira nkajya kwicara inyuma ya Doro nkarira ,nasoza kurira\r\nnkasoma ibitabo kuko mu mwaka wanjye wa mbere mu mashuri abanza narinzi gusoma\r\nikinyarwanda neza cyane.... Iyo nasomaga igitabo nkakirangiza nandikaga\r\nahantu... Mu wa mbere naharangije maze gusoma ibitabo bya Edition Bakame 17. Narangije\r\namashuri abanza maze gusoma nk\'ibitabo bigera kuri 70 kuko uko umuntu\r\nyambwiraga nabi nasomaga igitabo aho kumusubiza. \r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Uko nakuze nkunda gusoma niko naje gukunda kwandika nkumva\r\nnanjye nakwandika....Iyo nashakaga igitabo cyo gusoma nkakibura Numvaga nakwandika\r\nicyanjye...Ngeze mu mashuri y\'icyiciro rusange(Tronc Commun) nandikaga inkuru\r\nz\'uruhererekane mu ikayi, gusoma igice kimwe(chapter)abanyeshuri bakampa 300frw...\r\nNdi mu mwaka wa 4 mu mashuri yisumbuye ubwo twari mu bizamini nasoje gukora kare\r\nntangira kwibaza niba nzibukwa... Ndabyandika ku rupapuro rw\'ibibazo ,nuko\r\nnsohotse umuntu arusomye arambaza ngo\" uzi umusizi witwa Angel Uwamahoro?\r\nNdamubwira ngo oya, ahita ambwira ngo mwandika kimwe, ufite impano y\'ubusizi nuko\r\nutabizi..... nguko uko natangjye kubikunda no kubikora.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/etkr0zJ.jpg\" width=\"480\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Umusizi Ashimwe Ange </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Ashimwe Ange Theonastine kuri ubu ni umunyeshuri mu mwaka wa\r\ngatanu w\'amashuri yisumbuye mu ishami ry\'amateka,ubukungu n\'ubumenyi bw\'isi.(HEG)\r\nmu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Cyabingo mu ntara y\'amajyaruguru mu karere ka Musanze.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Ashimwe Ange Theonastine n\'umwe mu begukanye irushanwa ry\'ubusizi\r\nrikomeye hano mu Rwanda ariryo Kigali Itatswe n\'Ubusizi,aho yahembwe ibihembo\r\nbyinshi bitandukanye harimo n\'ishusho ya Nyiraruganzu Nyirarumaga, nyirakuruza\r\nw\'ubusizi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8mGKsrc.jpg\" width=\"480\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Ikindi kandi Ashimwe Ange Theonastine yizeye kuzakira nkuko\r\nabivuga muri aya magambo ati \"Nizeye kuzakira,naho bitabaho nkiri muri ubu\r\nbuzima na nyuma yabwo nzakira.\"</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Ange kandi yavuze icyo ubusizi aricyo kuri we muri aya\r\nmagambo ati \"Ubusizi ni ubuzima bwanjye, ndabucyeneye kugira mbeho bityo\r\nmbamyako kuri njye Ubusizi ni igisobanuro cy\'ubuzima.\"</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YCqIteT.jpg\" width=\"531\" height=\"531\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Umusizi Ashimwe Ange </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><br></p>\r\n\r\n', '1507056368IMG-20171003-WA0009.jpg', 0, '\r\nYanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier', 1, 14, 'head', 544);
