ni igitaramo cyari kitabiriwe\r\nn\'abasizi batandukanye bakomeye hano mu Rwanda ndetse no mu karere k\'Afurika\r\ny\'uburasirazuba(East Africa).</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Iki gitaramo cyatangiye ahagana ku i saa mbili z\'umugoroba\r\nmaze Kivumbi King abimburira abandi basizi kuri uwo mugoroba nuko atarama mu gisigo\r\ncye yise \"Questions\" tushyize mu kinyarwanda bisobanuye \"Ibibazo\",Kivumbi\r\nyaje gukurikirwa na isamiejr(Ruhindi Sam) nawe atarama mu gisigo yise \"Hear\r\nmy cry mama nation tugenekereje mu kinyarwanda bivuze ngo \"Ndumva amarira\r\ny\'igihugu cyambyaye\", nyuma ya Sam ku rubyiniro haje kabuhariwe Maniraguha\r\ncarine maze injyana arayipima mu tubangutso n\'utubeshuro aterura umuvugo yise\r\n\"Isi ya none\" ,abaraho ibyishimo bibasaba ku masura, Maniraguha\r\nyakurikiwe na kabuhariwe Eric Onyango Otienno (Rix poet) umusizi ukomoka mu\r\ngihugu cya Kenya akaba ari nawe wari umutumirwa mukuru w\'icyo gitaramo maze\r\natarama mu muvugo yise woman cg umugore mu rurimi rw\'ikinyarwanda, uyu\r\nyakurikiwe na Fefe Kalume atarama mu muvugo we yise \"La mort d\'une mere\"\r\nbisobanuye \"Urupfu rw\' umubyeyi w\'umugore\", bigeze aho ,igitaramo\r\ncyasaga nkikimaze kuryoha maze kiryoha kurushaho aho Akeem Marvin na <br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"> umusizi\r\nufite ubumuga bwo kutabona bageraga ku rubyiniro bagafatanya mu muvugo bise\r\n\"Only you\" cg \"Wowe gusa\". Uyu muvugo waba bombi wari wiganjemo\r\nimitoma, Anesie yagumye ku rubyiniro maze mu ijwi ryiza rizira amakaraza yigana\r\nnyakwigendera Kamariza mu ndirimbo \"Maragahinda\" maze abari aho ibyishimo\r\nbirabasaba, amarangamutima ababana menshi batangarira uburyo uwo musizi ufite ubumuga\r\nbwo kutabona yigana Kamariza bya nyabyo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Iki gitaramo cyagaragayemo imivugo n\'ibisigo bihimbitse mu\r\nburyo bwa gihanga, iki gitaramo cyasusurukijwe kandi na Bahati Innocent yifashishije\r\numuvugo we yise \"Mwana wa Mabukwe\" nindi myinshi myiza. Abasizi bagiye\r\nbasimburanywa mu buryo butandukanye gusa icyanga gikomeza kuba cyakindi\r\nbashimangira ko mu busizi harimo icyanga.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu cyagiranye na madamu Dr\r\nAndrea Grieder umuyobozi wa Transpoesis itsinda ritegura icyo gitaramo\r\nyatangiye agira ati \" Nukuri ndishimye bitavugwa, nabonye abasizi\r\nbakataraboneka ku rubyiniro ikindi kandi iyi gahunda yo kuvangavanga imivugo n\'ibicurangisho\r\nby\'umuziki ni byiza cyane nabonye bikora ku mitima na roho by\'abafana, ikindi\r\nnavuga Transpoesis ifite imishinga myinshi ku busizi nka Kigali itatswe\r\nn\'ubusizi ndetse niyi Poetic Fever bityo rero mboneyeho gutumira abantu muri\r\nrusange ngo baze twiyumvire icyanga cy\'ubusizi\"</p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pDGAbMN.jpg\" width=\"448\"></div><div align=\"left\">Dr\r\nAndrea Grieder<br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/isgaw7T.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lWKJrEt.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/e2gwdyb.jpg\" width=\"448\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VPmRlBP.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oGsTHsE.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0bPJp6N.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><br></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fkbmbWV.jpg\" width=\"448\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">isamiejr(Ruhindi Sam) </p><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cBmQdF2.jpg\" width=\"448\"></div><div align=\"left\"> Maniraguha<br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lR47YhW.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3QeA3Jm.jpg\" width=\"448\"></div><div align=\"left\">Eric Onyango Otienno (Rix poet) <br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xrXIRDX.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JPys6N5.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CNEYIxc.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1zCfiPo.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZwODEKp.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vvd66tf.jpg\" width=\"448\"><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jxhuC2P.jpg\" width=\"448\"></div><div align=\"left\">Anesie<br><br><br></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Aba basizi bose uko bagendaga batarama baherekezwaga\r\nn\'umuziki ucuranze neza mu bicurangisho byinshi bya muzika wacurangwaga ako\r\nkanya(live) ni itsinda ry\'abanyacuranzi(Band) bitwa Kinga Blues iyoborwa\r\nn\'umunyamuziki Nganji Arnauld ukomoka mu gihugu cy\'Uburundi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Mu bindi bikorwa iri tsinda riteganya vuba aha navuga Kigali\r\nitatswe n\'ubusizi ,amarushanwa y\'ubusizi azaba kuwa gatandatu tariki 28 Ukwakira/2017\r\ni Kigali mu kiyovu ahitwa Neo Cafe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Iki gitaramo ngarukakwezi kizongera kuba mu kwezi gutaha\r\ntariki ya 18/Ugushyingo/2017 n\'ubundi i Kigali muri Blue note imbere ya Ecole\r\nBelge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">Amafoto: Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier &amp; Ezekiel</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n', '1508170336PhotoGrid_1508169171060(1).jpg', 0, 'Yanditswe na Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier', 1, 14, 'head', 301),
(131, '2017-10-24 18:47:54', 'Intore Jabastar afatanyije na  N PAZZ0 bamaze gushyira hanze  indirimbo \'\'U RWANDA RURAGENDWA\'\'.', 'umuhanzi akaba intore Jabastar yamamaye cyane mundirimbo zivuga ibingwi by\'uRwanda akomeje gukora umuziki gakondo ufite umwihariko,Jabastar akaba yarahoze ari kapiteni w\'itorero ry\'igihugu Urukerereza.', '<div align=\"left\">Umuhanzi Semanza Jean Baptiste uyu yamenyekanye cyane nka Jabastar ubusanzwe&nbsp; n\'umwe mu bahanzi b\'abahanga mu njyana gakondo y\'abanyarwanda.<br>uyu Jabastar yamamaye cyane mu mbyino gakondo aho ari umwe mu nkingi za mwamba mu itorero ry\'igihugu Urukerereza by\'umwihariko akaba anakora umuziki gakondo ku giti cye. Semanza Jean Baptiste[ Jabastar]akomeje gukora indirimbo zikoranye ubuhanga zitaka u Rwanda. Semanza yakoze indirimbo zagiye zimenyekana aha twavuga nka \'\'Abashyitsi\" nizindi nyinshi.<br><br><br><br>Mu kiganiro&nbsp; Intore Jabastar yagiranye na ikinyamakuru cy\'umuco umucowacu.com yatubwiye ko we aho akura inganzo ntahandi aruko agendera ku mateka n\'umwihariko w\'abanyarwanda. Uyu muhanzi akaba yamaze gushyira hanze indirimbo nshya, tumubajije uko yagize inganzo yiyi ndirimbo nshya yise \'\'U RWANDA RURAGENDWA\'\'.<br>yadutangarije ko we nka Jabastar yishimiye urwego agezeho ati\" Nahimbye iyi ndirimbo nshaka kubwira abantu bari mu&nbsp;&nbsp; Rwanda ,abari hanze ko u Rwanda ari igihugu kigendwa ,ngaruka k\'umahoro, umutekano biri iwacu i Rwanda,ikindi buri muntu wese ku isi akwiye kumenya ko u Rwanda rugendwa .<br><br><br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/irrf7QW.jpg\" width=\"391\" height=\"490\"></div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\">indirimbo&nbsp; \'\'U RWANDA RURAGENDWA\'\'. yamaze kugera kuri youtube aho wayireba ukaryoherwa na muziki y\'umwimerere.<br><br><br>&lt;iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZFFCD79-PtI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</div><div align=\"left\"><br></div><div align=\"left\">https://youtu.be/ZFFCD79-PtI <br></div>', '1508863674IMG-20171024-WA0021.jpg', 0, 'Yanditswe na IRADUKUNDA MOSEs', 3, 3, 'sub', 70),
(132, '2017-10-25 14:34:43', 'Umusizi Tuyisenge yamaze gushyira hanze umuvugo yise \"Niba ari ibyo nta Rwanda\" aho agaragaza uburakari bwinshi ku myambarire y\'ikoma yateye.', 'Umusizi Tuyisenge Olivier ni umusizi by\'umwuga,kuri uyu wa gatatu tariki ya 25/Ukwakira/2017 nibwo yashyize ahagaragara umuvugo yise \"Niba ari ibyo nta Rwanda.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">Muri uyu muvugo ucuranze ukaba unahimbitse mu buryo bwa\r\ngihanga,Umusizi Tuyisenge aba yibaza byinshi ku myambarire n\'imitekerereze yo\r\nmuri iyi minsi! Imwe mu mirongo igize uyu muvugo twavuga ni nkaho agera akibaza\r\nati \"Ese Gihanga umuhanga ko yasize igihango,aho yagaruka agasanga ibyo\r\nyasize dusenga byarimukiye mu gusirimba,gusakuza biheruka burya? Ese yabikirwa ni\r\niki? Na odeur ya ocean?cyangwa nawe batwikira ikoma bagashyira ku karubanda ubwambure\r\nbw\'umwami? Babikora nta dini batunga!\". <o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><o:p><font face=\"arial\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">Uyu n\'umwe mu mivugo uyu muhungu asa naho yakoze atishimiye\r\nuko imyambarire y\'ubu imeze. Muri uyu muvugo Umusizi Tuyisenge yumvikana anenga\r\nbyeruye umuhanzikazi Odda Paccy usa nkaho ariwe wazanye iriya nkubiri yo\r\nkwambara ikoma.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><o:p><font face=\"arial\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">Mu kiganiro ikinyamakuru Umuco wacu cyagiranye na Tuyisenge\r\nOlivier yatangiye agira ati \" Kwambara ubushwange aho ni umuco? cyangwa ni\r\nubushwi bukuzwa bugakwirakwizwa? Ayo nayo n\'amwe mu magambo ari mu muvugo wanjye\r\ngusa icyo nifuza kuvuga n\'ukubwira abanyarwanda n\'abanyarwandakazi ko u Rwanda\r\nrugira umuco,kwambara amakoma ubundi ni igitutsi kibi,biriya si ibintu bikwiye\r\numwali cyangwa umusore w\'i Rwanda, biba ngombwa ko umuntu akosora mugenzi nubwo\r\nababikoze bose yenda ari bakuru kuri njye, ibuye ryahanuye inyoni bitangana.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><o:p><font face=\"arial\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NKUrySk.jpg\" width=\"360\"></font></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><o:p><font face=\"arial\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">Umusizi akomeza atangariza Umuco wacu ko atakoze uyu muvugo\r\nmu rwego rwo kwibasira ababikoze kuko we ahamya ko ntan\'umwe baziranye\r\nbyimbitse. Ikindi kandi akomeza asaba urubyiruko kutiruka inyuma y\'ibiguruka\r\nbyose.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><o:p><font face=\"arial\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">Uyu muvugo ukaba warakozwe n\'umuryango Iwacu in Africa\r\nbiciye muri situdiyo Rwanda image Films. Iwacu in Africa ni umuryango wamaze\r\ngusinyisha abasizi icyenda b\'abanyarwanda mu rwego rwo kubafasha mu iterambere\r\nry\'ibihangano byabo. Umusizi Tuyisenge aratangaza ko bidatinze n\'amashusho\r\ny\'uyu muvugo azaba kuba ugeze hanze.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\"><br></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"arial\">Yanditswe na Iradukunda Moses</font></p>', '1508934883niba aribyo.jpg', 0, 'IRADUKUNDA MOSEs', 1, 14, 'head', 312);
